NK075(bu)003:1: // ra t+na lo ke n+aa ma tsi t+ta ti la
NK075(bu)003:2: ka t+ai ka ba h+aa bi ha ra ti sma
NK075(bu)003:5: / // thugs kyi thigs pa'i 'grel bshad rin chen sgron ma zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK075(bu)003:8: bla ma dang lhag pa'i lha la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK075(bu)003:9: kun mkhyen mtha' bral chos dbyings kun rig cing //
NK075(bu)003:10: kun gzhi'i theg rgyal don ston kun bzang dang //
NK075(bu)003:11: rgyal tshab rgyal ba rigs lnga gsang bdag sogs //
NK075(bu)003:12: dgongs pa dbyer med dgongs rgyud rnams la 'dud //
NK075(bu)003:13: theg mchog bla med theg don thugs chud nas //
NK075(bu)003:14: rig pa rang grol rig 'dzin rgyal ba'i sras //
NK075(bu)003:15: mi la brgyud dang mi min gnyis la sogs //
NK075(bu)003:16: rig 'dzin rig par brgyud pa rnams la 'dud //
NK075(bu)003:17: gsang sngags bla med gsang don ma lus kun //
NK075(bu)003:18: snyan nas rim par snyan du rab brgyud pa /
NK075(bu)003:19: don dam kun rdzob don rnams rtogs gyur pa'i //
NK075(bu)003:20: brgyud pa'i gang zag rgyun mi chad la 'dud //
NK075(bu)003:21: 'phags mchog kun gyi gsang ba'i mdzod 'dzin cing //
NK075(bu)003:22: zab don dbyer med rang snang mngon byas pa //
NK075(bu)003:23: mkhyen brtse nus ldan 'gro ba'i mgon dang gnyen //
NK075(bu)003:24: mtshungs med drin chen bla ma rnams la 'dud //
NK075(bu)003:25: sgyu 'phrul man ngag snang ba bzhi yi don //
NK075(bu)003:26: 'grel bshad bdag gis brtsam par mi 'os kyang //
NK075(bu)003:27: don gnas bshes gnyen rnams kyis bskul phyir du //
NK075(bu)003:28: bla ma'i gsung bzhin rin chen sgron ma bri //
NK075(bu)003:29: rgyal rigs su sku 'khrungs pa'i slob dpon chen po
NK075(bu)003:30: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i man ngag thugs kyi thigs pa
NK075(bu)003:31: 'di nyid bshad pa'i dbang du bgyi na gsum ste
NK075(bu)003:32: / 'chad nyan ci ltar bya ba'i tshul dang /
NK075(bu)003:33: gang 'chad par bya ba dam chos kyi rnam bzhag dang /
NK075(bu)003:34: 'chad nyan mthar phyin pa'i don no //
NK075(bu)003:36: gang las nyan pa'i bshes gnyen gyi rang bzhin dang /
NK075(bu)003:37: gang gis nyan pa gang zag gi rang bzhin no //
NK075(bu)003:41: de ltar bshad pa'i phan yon no //
NK075(bu)003:43: mtshan nyid dang mi ldan pa ni /
NK075(bu)003:44: thos pa chung la nga rgyal che ba'i slob dpon dang /
NK075(bu)003:45: thugs rje chung la gdug rtsub che ba'i slob dpon dang /
NK075(bu)003:46: gdams pa chung la 'dod pa che ba'i slob dpon de gsum spangs te /
NK075(bu)003:48: log par spyod pa'i rnal 'byor ni //
NK075(bu)003:49: log lta'i spyi brtol khro gtum che //
NK075(bu)003:50: sdig spyod don dang mi ldan yang //
NK075(bu)003:51: bdag nyid nges pa kho na zhes //
NK075(bu)003:52: bab chol bka' brgyud slu byed bslad //
NK075(bu)003:54: gnyis pa bzang ba'i mtshan nyid ni /
NK075(bu)003:55: thos pa dang gdams ngag ldan pa'i bla ma dang /
NK075(bu)003:56: rtogs pa dang nyams myong ldan pa'i bla ma dang /
NK075(bu)003:57: thugs rje dang byin rlabs ldan pa'i bla ma de gsum bsten no //
NK075(bu)003:58: khyad par gsang sngags kyi slob dpon ni /
NK075(bu)003:59: chos kun mnyam pa nyid kyi gnas lugs rtogs shing goms pas spyod pa dang 'brel ba /
NK075(bu)003:60: bla ma brgyud pa'i zam ma chad pa /
NK075(bu)003:61: dbang bzhi'i chu bo ma nub pa /
NK075(bu)003:62: byin rlabs nyams rtogs kyi mdangs ma yal ba /
NK075(bu)003:63: snyan brgyud gdams ngag gi gnad ma 'chugs pa /
NK075(bu)003:64: snying rje phan sems kyis slob ma 'dzin pa'i gnyer dang ldan pa /
NK075(bu)003:65: gsang sngags kyi rgyud gzhung phrin las chog 'grig tha dag la mkhas pa pa dang ldan pa ste /
NK075(bu)003:66: lam rim gyi le'u bdun pa las /
NK075(bu)003:67: ston pa mdzod ldan chu bo rdzogs //
NK075(bu)003:68: gnyer ldan rgyud dang las la mkhas //
NK075(bu)003:72: bla med snying po smin pa'i rkyen //
NK075(bu)003:73: blo gros chen po dri ba'i yul //
NK075(bu)003:74: lam ston sa mkhan bshes gnyen mgon //
NK075(bu)003:75: mun sel sgron ma rin po che //
NK075(bu)003:76: mthong mig dbang po yid rnam shes //
NK075(bu)003:77: chu bo rab med sgrol ba'i gru //
NK075(bu)003:78: 'jigs pa'i rdzongs chen rten pa'i mkhar //
NK075(bu)003:80: mtsho gling rin chen len byed pa'i //
NK075(bu)003:81: ded dpon dam pa'i bla ma la //
NK075(bu)003:82: sngan du nges par shes par bya //
NK075(bu)003:84: gnyis pa 'chad tshul la gnyis las /
NK075(bu)003:86: shes lo dang mkhas lo'i sgo nas mi 'chad /
NK075(bu)003:87: khe grags dang bsnyen bkur gyi sgo nas mi bshad /
NK075(bu)003:88: rgyas 'debs dang zil gnon gyi sgo nas mi bshad do //
NK075(bu)003:89: gnyis pa don gnyer la gsum ste /
NK075(bu)003:90: mkhas pa'i shes rab dang ldan pas gdul bya'i the tshom gcod cing yid ches pa /
NK075(bu)003:91: brtse ba'i thugs rje dang ldan pas gdul bya rjes su bzung ba /
NK075(bu)003:92: sbyor ba'i bzod pa dang ldan pas chos 'chad pa la ngal dub med pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:94: bshad bya la mkhas pa ni /
NK075(bu)003:95: spyir shes bya rab 'byed rig pa kun la mkhas na legs mod kyis /
NK075(bu)003:96: 'on kyang rang gi gzhung lugs khas blang ba la mkhas shing /
NK075(bu)003:97: don khong du chud la the tshom chod pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:98: gnyis pa 'chad byed la mkhas pa ni /
NK075(bu)003:101: ci ltar bshad kyang 'thad pa gsum gyis ngag 'brel zhing /
NK075(bu)003:102: rang gis brjod bde gzhan gyis go sla /
NK075(bu)003:103: gnyis ka'i rna bar snyan cing yid cags pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:104: gsum pa rang gi kun spyod la mkhas pa ni /
NK075(bu)003:105: tshul chos ma yin par rang gi sgo gsum chos
NK075(bu)003:106: dang mthun par gnas pa'i sgo nas gdul bya dang
NK075(bu)003:107: ba 'dren cing dad pa'i gnas su gyur pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:108: gzhan gyi kun spyod la mkhas pa ni /
NK075(bu)003:109: gdul bya dbang po rno rtul dang rjes su mthun pa'i chos bstan pa la mkhas shing bshad pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:110: gzhan yang sems can gyi don bya ba'i phyir bshad kyis /
NK075(bu)003:111: rang gi che ba 'don pa'i phyir ma yin /
NK075(bu)003:112: snying rje chen pos bstan gyis /
NK075(bu)003:113: nga rgyal gyi phyir ma yin /
NK075(bu)003:114: 'khor ba rgyun gcod pa'i phyir bstan gyis /
NK075(bu)003:115: nyon mongs pa spel ba'i phyir ma yin no //
NK075(bu)003:116: gsum pa gsang sngags kyi don rtogs nas gzhan la bshad pa'i phan yon ni /
NK075(bu)003:118: rtogs nas smra bar gang byed pa //
NK075(bu)003:119: goms pas brjod dang smon pa yis //
NK075(bu)003:120: chos kyi rgyal por de 'gyur zhing //
NK075(bu)003:121: yon tan spyi gtsug nyid du 'gyur //
NK075(bu)003:122: de yang ci lta bu zhe na //
NK075(bu)003:123: 'das pa'i dus na sngon byung ba //
NK075(bu)003:124: drang srong rnal 'byor kal yas nas //
NK075(bu)003:125: drang srong rnam pa mang sde la //
NK075(bu)003:126: theg chen gsang ba'i basngagasa pa brjod //
NK075(bu)003:127: don rnams nges par bkod pa las //
NK075(bu)003:128: mang pos rigs chen 'dzin pa thob //
NK075(bu)003:129: gang der basngagasa pa brjod byed pa //
NK075(bu)003:130: gsang bdag chos kyi rgyal por 'gyur //
NK075(bu)003:131: des na theg chen gsang ba 'di //
NK075(bu)003:132: kun la basngagasa pa brjod par gyis //
NK075(bu)003:133: des ni nga yi dgongs pa thob //
NK075(bu)003:135: gnyis pa gang gis nyan pa'i gang zag gi rang bzhin la gsum ste /
NK075(bu)003:141: shes rab chung la nyon mongs pa che ba'i slob ma dang /
NK075(bu)003:142: dad pa chung la ser sna che ba'i slob ma dang /
NK075(bu)003:143: brtson 'grus chung la 'dod pa che ba'i slob ma de gsum spangs te /
NK075(bu)003:145: yang dag don gyi lta ba gsang ba 'di //
NK075(bu)003:146: gang zag phyin ci log dang lta ba dman //
NK075(bu)003:147: thos pa chung la blo rtul shes rab med //
NK075(bu)003:148: nor phangs kha ral la sogs snod med la //
NK075(bu)003:149: 'di bstan gnyis ka bsreg phyir rab tu gsang //
NK075(bu)003:151: gnyis pa bzang ba'i mtshan nyid ni /
NK075(bu)003:152: dad pa dang shes rab ldan pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:153: mos gus dang gtong phod ldan pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:154: ngang rgyud dang brtson 'grus ldan pa'i slob mar bstan pa yin te /
NK075(bu)003:155: klong gsal nyi ma'i rgyud las /
NK075(bu)003:156: dad ldan snying rje gtong phod che //
NK075(bu)003:157: rgyud dul sdig 'dzem dbang po rno //
NK075(bu)003:158: gsang thub nyams len brtul zhugs spyod //
NK075(bu)003:159: skyo shas sdug sran snying rus che //
NK075(bu)003:160: de ni gsang sngags gsang ba'i snod //
NK075(bu)003:162: gnyis pa ji ltar nyan pa'i tshul la gnyis las /
NK075(bu)003:165: nga rgyal dang ni ma dad dang //
NK075(bu)003:166: don du gnyer ba med nyid dang //
NK075(bu)003:167: phyi rol rnam g.yeng nang du sdud //
NK075(bu)003:168: skyo bas nyan pa dri ma yin //
NK075(bu)003:170: gzhan yang khe dang grags blo'i sgo nas mi nyan /
NK075(bu)003:171: ngo bsrung dang tshul chos kyi sgo nas mi nyan /
NK075(bu)003:172: rang dang gzhan khyad lta'i sgo nas mi nyan no //
NK075(bu)003:174: gzhi dang pa brtan pos btud /
NK075(bu)003:180: don gyi sbrang rtsi myong dgos par gsungs te /
NK075(bu)003:181: sdong po bkod pa'i mdo las /
NK075(bu)003:182: rigs kyi bu bdag nyid la nad pa'i 'du shes dang /
NK075(bu)003:183: dge ba'i bshes gnyen la sman pa'i 'du shes dang /
NK075(bu)003:184: chos la sman gyi 'du shes dang /
NK075(bu)003:185: nan tan rjes su bsgrub pa la nad 'tsho ba'i 'du shes bskyed par bya'o //
NK075(bu)003:187: gzhan yang 'khor ba sdug bsngal gyi rgya mtsho las
NK075(bu)003:188: sgrol bar byed 'dod pa la dam pa'i chos min
NK075(bu)003:189: pa cis kyang mi phan pa de'i phyir nyan /
NK075(bu)003:190: chos de bstan pa'i bla ma de yang dag par
NK075(bu)003:191: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas dngos dang 'dra ba yin pas
NK075(bu)003:192: de'i phyir mnyan / de'i zhal nas gsungs pa'i chos
NK075(bu)003:193: de shi sos kyi sman pas kyang gces pas de'i
NK075(bu)003:194: de'i phyir mnyan / phyir mnyan no // gsum pa de ltar mnyan pa'i phan yon ni /
NK075(bu)003:196: dam chos bshad pa'i dus ston phyir //
NK075(bu)003:198: thos pas byang chub thob gyur na //
NK075(bu)003:199: nyan phyir lhags pa smos ci dgos //
NK075(bu)003:201: khyad par gsang basngagasa thos pa'i yon tan ni /
NK075(bu)003:203: dper na gyi ling sgrog bkrol ltar //
NK075(bu)003:204: rnam grol thos bsam sgo mo yis //
NK075(bu)003:205: shes rgyud kun grol thogs med 'gro //
NK075(bu)003:207: gnyis pa gang 'chad par bya ba dam chos kyi rnam bzhag la gsum ste /
NK075(bu)003:208: gang zag 'jug ngo shes par bya ba'i phyir dam pa'i chos ngos bzung ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:209: de nyid kyi don ma nor bar shes par bya ba'i phyir bshad thabs bstan pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:210: bshad bya gzhung don dngos kyi skabs dang gsum mo //
NK075(bu)003:211: dang po chos ngos bzung ba ni /
NK075(bu)003:213: de la theg pa che chung gnyis las theg chen /
NK075(bu)003:214: theg chen la mdo sngags gnyis las gsang sngags /
NK075(bu)003:215: sngags la phyi nang gnyis las nang pa /
NK075(bu)003:218: a ti gsum las ma h+aa /
NK075(bu)003:221: gnyis med kyi rgyud dang gsum las /
NK075(bu)003:223: de la rgyud dang man ngag gnyis las 'dir man ngag /
NK075(bu)003:224: man ngag la'ang rgyud kyi don mngon par rtogs pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:225: bslab cing nyams su blang ba'i man ngag gnyis las /
NK075(bu)003:226: 'dir gnyis ka bshad kyang snga ma gtso che bar ston /
NK075(bu)003:231: gnyis pa bshad pa'i thabs ni /
NK075(bu)003:232: 'di nyid rgyud la brten pa'i man ngag yin pas /
NK075(bu)003:235: thos chung gsar bu yid ches bskyed pa'i phyir //
NK075(bu)003:236: man ngag spyi don rtsis 'gos klad nas gzhom //
NK075(bu)003:240: dgongs pa khrol ba'i slob don dang //
NK075(bu)003:241: mtshan lnga ldan pa'i dam chos dang //
NK075(bu)003:242: theg pa sde snod 'byung ba'i khungs //
NK075(bu)003:243: nye bar tshig gis bsdus gnas dang //
NK075(bu)003:244: don du 'gyur ba'i dgos pa rnams //
NK075(bu)003:245: bstan chos kun gyi rtsis mgo yin //
NK075(bu)003:247: dang po khungs btsun zhing yid ches par bya ba'i phyir slob dpon gang gis mdzad pa ni /
NK075(bu)003:248: brtsam tshad rab 'bring tha ma gsum dang ldan pa'i
NK075(bu)003:249: slob dpon chen po sangs rgyas gsang bas mdzad pa
NK075(bu)003:250: yin te / rdzogs chen rgyan las /
NK075(bu)003:251: chos nyid mngon sum rtogs pa rab //
NK075(bu)003:252: bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro yis //
NK075(bu)003:253: lung bstan thob pa 'bring po yin //
NK075(bu)003:254: la shan bka' lung tshig la mkhas //
NK075(bu)003:255: bye brag phyed pa tha ma yin //
NK075(bu)003:257: gnyis pa bka' dang mi 'gal bar bya ba'i phyir rgyud gang nas btus pa ni /
NK075(bu)003:259: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba rdo rje sems //
NK075(bu)003:260: gsang ba'i snying po'i rgyud dag las //
NK075(bu)003:263: stong phrag brgya pa'i rgyud dag las //
NK075(bu)003:265: thugs sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba le'u stong phrag brgya pa'i rgyud nas btus so //
NK075(bu)003:266: gsum pa theg pa'i rang gzhung tshugs par bya ba'i
NK075(bu)003:267: phyir phyogs gar gtogs pa ni ma h+aa yo ga'i
NK075(bu)003:270: mtshan nges shing don gyi mdo tsam zhig rtogs par bya ba'i phyir mtshan ni /
NK075(bu)003:276: don la btags pa dang lnga las /
NK075(bu)003:277: 'di ni thugs kyi thigs pa zhes pas /
NK075(bu)003:278: don rang gi ngo bo las mtshan du btags pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:279: lnga pa brtsam pa la don yod par bya ba'i
NK075(bu)003:280: phyir gang za ga gang gi don du mdzad pa
NK075(bu)003:283: slob dpon nyid kyi dngos 'khor dang ma 'ongs pa'i
NK075(bu)003:284: gang zag las 'phro dang skal bar ldan pa rnams
NK075(bu)003:286: gsum pa bshad bya gzhung don dngos kyii skabs la gsum ste /
NK075(bu)003:292: dang po mtshan bstan pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:300: tsit+ta bin+du u pa de sha na ma /
NK075(bu)003:302: thugs kyi thigs pa'i man ngag ces bya ba'o //
NK075(bu)003:303: gnyis pa mtshan bsgyur ba la /
NK075(bu)003:306: dkrugs te bsgyur ba dang gsum las /
NK075(bu)003:307: 'dir ni gcus pa dang bsnol ba mi mnga' bas dang po yin te /
NK075(bu)003:310: u pa de sha man ngag /
NK075(bu)003:311: na ma zhes bya ba ste /
NK075(bu)003:312: de yang sgyur mkhan gyi lo ts+aa ba la /
NK075(bu)003:313: tshig don gnyis ka la mkhas shing khong du chud pa ni zhus chen gyi lo ts+aa dang /
NK075(bu)003:314: sgra rkyang pa tsam shes pa sgra sgyur lo ts+aa dang /
NK075(bu)003:315: rgya skad la bod skad kyi mchan tsam btab shes pa ni mchan bu lo ts+aa dang /
NK075(bu)003:316: rgya gar gyi pan+di ta la bod du chos zhus
NK075(bu)003:317: shis bsgyur ba ni go lo ts+aa dang bzhi las
NK075(bu)003:318: / gzhung 'di nyid sgyur mkhan gyi rma rin chen mchog ni /
NK075(bu)003:319: zhus chen gyi lo ts+aa dang /
NK075(bu)003:320: go lo ts+aa gnyis ka yin no //
NK075(bu)003:321: gsum pa mtshan bshad pa ni /
NK075(bu)003:322: slob dpon a ro ye shes kyi zhal nas /
NK075(bu)003:325: skad ni thos par byed pa /
NK075(bu)003:328: gzhan mkhas pa rnams mthun pa'i dgongs pa ni /
NK075(bu)003:329: rgya gar ni 'dod rgyal gyi sgra yin la /
NK075(bu)003:330: 'o na thog mar smos pa'i dgos ched ni /
NK075(bu)003:331: 'phags pa rnams kyis bzhugs gnas yin pas khungs btsun cing yid ches pa'i phyir dang /
NK075(bu)003:332: lo pan rnams kyis phyi rabs pa la drin bzhag pa'i phyir ro //
NK075(bu)003:333: yul pa de rnams kyi skad du'am skad la zhes bya ste /
NK075(bu)003:335: du la sogs pa la dang mthun //
NK075(bu)003:337: tsit+ta bin+du u pa de sha na ma zhes bya la /
NK075(bu)003:338: boda ni kha ba can te bod dang bod chen po gnyis so //
NK075(bu)003:339: yul de nyid kyi skad du'am skad la /
NK075(bu)003:340: thugs kyi thigs pa'i man ngag cesa bya ba zhes 'dogs so //
NK075(bu)003:345: thugsa zhes pa sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes
NK075(bu)003:346: spros pa thams cad dang bral ba de nyid kyi
NK075(bu)003:347: ngo bo ni / nyung la 'dus pa /
NK075(bu)003:348: ma 'phros pa gsum gyi phyir thigs pa'i /
NK075(bu)003:349: de nyid tsheg chung la don che bas man ngag ces bya ba'o //
NK075(bu)003:351: thugs kyi rgyud rgya mtsho dang 'dra ba'i nang nas /
NK075(bu)003:352: thigsa pa lta bu'i tshig don nyung la 'dus pa 'phros pa gsum gyis bsgrub ste /
NK075(bu)003:353: de yang rgyud la le'u stong phrag brgyad pa'i rgyud kyi tshig tshogs rnams /
NK075(bu)003:354: 'dir tshig le'u bzhir byas pas nyung la /
NK075(bu)003:355: stong phrag brgya'i don rgyas pa snang ba bzhi po rnams /
NK075(bu)003:357: gdul bya gzu lums ras chod can dgag pa'i phyir rgyud don la brda tshig dang /
NK075(bu)003:358: ldem dgongs dang rgyud 'khrugs pa la sogs mar 'phros pa yin la /
NK075(bu)003:361: gab pa phyung bas yar 'phrosa pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:362: le'u stong phrag brgya'i rgyud don rnams gtan la phab
NK075(bu)003:363: cing nyams su len pa ni shin tu dka' la
NK075(bu)003:364: / 'di snang ba bzhi'i don le'u bzhir byas pa
NK075(bu)003:365: gtan la phab cing nyams su len pa ni tshegs
NK075(bu)003:366: / chung la / 'di nyid kyi nang du ston pa'i snang ba bzhi'i don rtogs na /
NK075(bu)003:367: stong phrag brgya'i rgyud don rnams khong du chud pas na man ngag ces bya ba ste /
NK075(bu)003:369: thabs chen tshegs chung don dpag med //
NK075(bu)003:370: bya sla dpag dka' man ngag go //
NK075(bu)003:374: phyag 'tshal lo zhes pa bshad pa'i gzhir bzhag /
NK075(bu)003:375: de'i khyad par gyi chos la lnga ste /
NK075(bu)003:382: sngon byung du slob dpon chen po sangs rgyas gsang bas /
NK075(bu)003:383: rjes 'jug 'chad nyan pa rnams kyis so //
NK075(bu)003:384: gnyis pa gang la na bcom zhes pa phrin las kyis bdud 'joms pa ste /
NK075(bu)003:386: nyon mongs pa lnga ye shes lngar ye nas gnas
NK075(bu)003:387: kyang de ngo ma shes pas nyon mongs pa'i bdud
NK075(bu)003:388: byung la / nyon mongs pa ye shes su gsal tsam na /
NK075(bu)003:389: nyon mongs pa'i bdud rang bzhin gyis bcom pa ni /
NK075(bu)003:391: phung po lnga rigs lngar ngo ma shes pas phung po'i bdud byung la /
NK075(bu)003:392: de nyid rigs lngar gsal bar rtogs pas phung po'i bdud bcom pa ni rgyas pa'i 'phrin las so //
NK075(bu)003:393: sems nyid skye shi gnyis med la gnyis su bzung bas /
NK075(bu)003:395: skye shi gnyis med du gsal tsam na 'chi bdag
NK075(bu)003:396: gi bdud bcom pa ni dbang gi phrin las so
NK075(bu)003:397: // don lha rtog gnyis med la gnyis su bzung bas lha'i bu'i bdud byung la /
NK075(bu)003:398: lha rtog gnyis med mngon du byas tsam na lha'i
NK075(bu)003:399: bu'i bdud bcom pa ni drag po'i 'phrin las yin
NK075(bu)003:401: bdud sde tshar gcod ces bya ba'i dam tshig ni /
NK075(bu)003:402: nyon mongs pa nyid rnam par dag /
NK075(bu)003:403: phung po lnga nyid mngon sangs rgyas //
NK075(bu)003:404: skye shi med pa'i g.yung drung gnas //
NK075(bu)003:405: bdag nyid lha yi dkyil 'khor ni //
NK075(bu)003:408: bdud bzhi la sogs rig pa'i gdeng gis bcom //
NK075(bu)003:410: ldan zhes yon tan gyi mtshan te /
NK075(bu)003:411: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga'am nyer lnga
NK075(bu)003:412: la sogs pa rnams thugs rang rig pa'i ye shes
NK075(bu)003:413: la lhun gyis grub pa yin ste /
NK075(bu)003:415: sku lnga la sogs che yon kun dang ldan //
NK075(bu)003:417: lung grwa chad ma nyams pa zur la bslang ba 'chad pa po'i gnyer bya ba yin pas /
NK075(bu)003:418: 'das zhes pa mtshan nyid kyi mtshan te /
NK075(bu)003:419: de nyid kyi ngo bo la yod med snang stong
NK075(bu)003:420: rtag chad la sogs phyogs re'i mtha' dang bral ba
NK075(bu)003:422: rang gi ngo bo 'di zhes bstan du med //
NK075(bu)003:424: dpal zhes pa che ba'i mtshan te /
NK075(bu)003:426: dang po gzhi rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dpal ni /
NK075(bu)003:427: gzhi don byang chub kyi sems rang byung gi ye
NK075(bu)003:428: shes la 'bras bu'i che yon nyer lnga lhun gyis
NK075(bu)003:429: grub pa ste / til la mar nag lhun gyis grub pa bzhin no //
NK075(bu)003:430: gnyis pa rtogs pa bdag gi dpal ni /
NK075(bu)003:431: don de nyid rtogs shing goms pas 'bras bu sku
NK075(bu)003:432: dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor mngon sum du gyur
NK075(bu)003:433: pa ste / nyi ma nam mkha'i mthongs su shar ba lta bu'o //
NK075(bu)003:434: gsum pa thugs rje chen po zhar la byung ba'i dpal ni /
NK075(bu)003:435: de ltar bdag don 'bras bu thob tsam na /
NK075(bu)003:436: gzhan gdul bya thams cad la mdzad pa phrin las ngang ngam shugs kyis 'byung ba ste /
NK075(bu)003:437: nyi ma'i 'od zer dro 'jam rtsol med kyis gzhan
NK075(bu)003:438: gyi mun pa dang 'khyag pa shugs kyis zhu ba
NK075(bu)003:439: bzhin no // de ltar dpal gsum lhun gyis grub pa'i ngo bo rdo rje'i don ni /
NK075(bu)003:440: rang bzhin dbyer med cing ngo bo 'dus ma byas pas mtshan nyid skye 'jig dang bral ba'o //
NK075(bu)003:441: de nyid las mi 'da' pas sems /
NK075(bu)003:442: des phyogs 'dzin thams cad phar la 'joms shing tshur
NK075(bu)003:443: la gang gis kyang mi tshugs pas dpa' bo de
NK075(bu)003:444: nyid dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo ste /
NK075(bu)003:446: rigs kyi rigs te rigs kyi gtso //
NK075(bu)003:448: des shes bya kun ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs par mkhyen pa ni /
NK075(bu)003:450: thugs kyi thugs te thugs kyi mchog /
NK075(bu)003:452: de'ang mtha' gnyis dang bdud bzhi las rgyal ba'i de
NK075(bu)003:453: bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi thugs kyi dgongs pa chos
NK075(bu)003:455: 'khor lo bsgyur rgyal gyis rgyal srid kyi thog mar gser 'khor sogs bskor ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:458: kun mkhyen sangs rgyas rnams kyis gdul bya la chos gsungs pa ni /
NK075(bu)003:460: gdul bya'i rgyud la go myong rtogs gsum du 'char ba ni 'khor ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:461: dpe gdul bya'i ma rtogs log rtog the tshom gyi
NK075(bu)003:462: d+r+wa ba dang sgrib pa sel ba ni gcod pa
NK075(bu)003:463: ste / de ltar chos kyi sgo mo brgyad khri
NK075(bu)003:464: bzhi stong bskor ba'i nang nas 'bras bu'i theg mchog
NK075(bu)003:465: gsang sngags bla med kyi rgyud gsang ba'i snying po'i
NK075(bu)003:466: don gab sbas rnams mngon sum du ston par mdzad
NK075(bu)003:468: gsum pa tshul ci ltar du 'tshal na gsum ste /
NK075(bu)003:469: ston pa dang rtsom pa po'i dgongs pa gnyis su
NK075(bu)003:470: med pa ni lta ba rtogs pa'am mi phyed 'dres
NK075(bu)003:473: ji ltar chu la chu blug gam //
NK075(bu)003:474: de bzhin mar la mar bzhag bzhin //
NK075(bu)003:475: rang gi ngang gi ye shes gang //
NK075(bu)003:478: yid kyis zhes sgom pa gom pa'i phyag ste /
NK075(bu)003:480: gang zhig rtogs nas 'jug pa yi //
NK075(bu)003:483: phyag 'tshal lo zhes pa spyod pa ya rab kyi phyag ste /
NK075(bu)003:485: lus dang ngag yid dwangs bas phyag bagyi'o //
NK075(bu)003:488: lus kyis phyag 'tshal yan lag sa la gtug /
NK075(bu)003:489: ngag gis phyag 'tshal bstod de ngag sang sang //
NK075(bu)003:490: yid kyis phyag 'tshal dga' dad yid bring bring //
NK075(bu)003:491: sgo gsum dang ba'i sgo nas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK075(bu)003:493: bzhi pa dgos ched ci'i phyir na gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:494: sngon byung gi dgos ched dang /
NK075(bu)003:495: rjes 'jug gis yi ge ris su bkod pa'i dgos ched do //
NK075(bu)003:497: ston pa la dbang mi za zhing rtogs nas brtsam
NK075(bu)003:498: pa byin rlabs su snang ba'i brdar ston pa dang
NK075(bu)003:499: / chos nyid mnyam pa nyid la khungs dbyung zhing chos kyi grub tshul mi nyams pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:500: tshogs gnyis rdzogs shing sgrib gnyis sbyang bas bar chad kyi rkyen bgegs nye bar zhi ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:501: brtsam pa mthar dbyung ba'i dgos ched yod do //
NK075(bu)003:503: bdag nyid ya rabs su shes pa'i dang /
NK075(bu)003:504: nyan bshad mthar phyin pa'i dgos ched yod do //
NK075(bu)003:506: phyag 'tshal ba'i yul rgyal ba rigs lnga la khyad par yod dam med /
NK075(bu)003:508: sangs rgyas rigs lnga bzang ngan can du 'gyur /
NK075(bu)003:509: med na rdo rje sems dpa' la sgos su phyag 'tshal ba 'gal lo zhe na /
NK075(bu)003:511: spyir sangs rgyas rigs lnga'i dgongs pa la mtho dman dang bzang ngan med kyang /
NK075(bu)003:512: bye brag tu gdul bya'i mos pa'i dbang gis 'dir
NK075(bu)003:513: thugs sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i skabs su 'chad pa'i skyes
NK075(bu)003:514: bu dang dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo yin pa'i phyir
NK075(bu)003:515: rdo rje sems dpa' la phyag 'tshal ba ste /
NK075(bu)003:517: rdo rje sems pa dkyil yin te //
NK075(bu)003:518: rigs bzhi lha dang lha mo'i 'khor //
NK075(bu)003:520: dkyil 'khor gtso bo skyes bu mchog /
NK075(bu)003:522: rdo rje sems dpa'i bkas bshad pa'i //
NK075(bu)003:524: mi bskyod rgyal po mdun na gnas //
NK075(bu)003:526: slob dpon nyid kyi thugs dam gyi gtso bo yin pa'i phyir na /
NK075(bu)003:527: rdo rje sems dpa' kho na la phyag 'tshal ba yin te /
NK075(bu)003:529: dam pa'i lha phyir phyag 'tshal lo //
NK075(bu)003:531: gsum pa bshad bshad par dam bca' ba la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:533: dang po dam bca' ba dngos dang /
NK075(bu)003:535: de yang phyag 'tshal nas ci byed na /
NK075(bu)003:537: gang bstan na rin chen bcud thugsa /
NK075(bu)003:538: gang gi don du bstan na skal ldan phyir /
NK075(bu)003:539: 'o na rang bzo ma yin nam zhe na sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba rdo rje semas /
NK075(bu)003:540: gsang ba' snying po'i rgyud dag la brten nasa /
NK075(bu)003:541: bldab par mi 'gyur ram zhe na bsdus te /
NK075(bu)003:542: 'o na lhag chad can du ma song ngam zhe
NK075(bu)003:543: na legsa par ces pa ni khog bsdebs nas bsdus
NK075(bu)003:544: don ltar bshad pa yin la /
NK075(bu)003:545: de nyid rgyas par bshad na /
NK075(bu)003:546: de'ang 'bru'i 'dug sa bsgyur don gyi go rim bsdeb ste /
NK075(bu)003:547: ston pa rdo rje sems dpa' des gsungs pa'i bstan pa ni /
NK075(bu)003:548: dpe don rtags gsum gyis 'chad de /
NK075(bu)003:550: don ni thabs shes rab dbyer med pa /
NK075(bu)003:551: rtags lha yab yum 'khri la sbyor yin te /
NK075(bu)003:552: de yang 'khrul pa phyi nang gi dngos po thams
NK075(bu)003:553: cad rang bzhin rang rgyud can du ma grub pa
NK075(bu)003:554: sgyu ma ste / don ni shes rab rang bzhin med pa /
NK075(bu)003:556: 'phrul ye shes kyi snang ba cir yang 'char ba thabs 'gag med /
NK075(bu)003:557: rtags lha yab d+r+wa ba mdo mdud gcig nas gnyis
NK075(bu)003:558: su 'brel pa ltar don thabs shes rab gnyis med
NK075(bu)003:560: de ltar bden gsum dbyer med de nyid zab cing
NK075(bu)003:561: rtogs dka' zhing don gyi bcud 'dus pas na gsang
NK075(bu)003:562: ba'i snying po'i rgyud daga la brten nas /
NK075(bu)003:563: dgos 'dod thams cad 'byung bas nor bu rin po
NK075(bu)003:564: che dang 'dra ba'i rgyud dbu zhabs kyi don bcud
NK075(bu)003:565: kyi yon tan thams cad 'dus pa'i thugs kyi thigs
NK075(bu)003:566: pa 'di nyid / dngos 'khor dang ma 'ongs pa'i
NK075(bu)003:567: gang zag 'dir 'jug cing go rtogs kyi skal ba
NK075(bu)003:568: dang ldan pa rnams kyi don bya ba'i phyir du
NK075(bu)003:569: pa 'di nyid / / rgyud don nor 'khrul lhag chad med par legsa par rgyal ba'i bka' dang /
NK075(bu)003:570: bla ma dam pa'i man ngag dang /
NK075(bu)003:571: rang gi rig pa tshad ma gsum dang mi 'gal bar byas nas /
NK075(bu)003:572: gang zag gzu lums dang ras gcod can rnams dgag
NK075(bu)003:573: par bya ba'i phyir du rgyud stod smad du 'thor
NK075(bu)003:574: ba rnams slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba'i nyer len
NK075(bu)003:575: gyi shes rab kyis bsdus te thugs kyi dgongs pa
NK075(bu)003:576: zhal du phyung nas gzhan don du bstan par bya
NK075(bu)003:577: ste zhes bshad par dam bca' ba'o //
NK075(bu)003:578: de'ang rgyud la brten nas brtsam tshul du dam bca' /
NK075(bu)003:579: dgos ched dang ldan par dam bca' /
NK075(bu)003:581: khengs skyungs dang ldan par dam bca' ba dang bzhi yod pa las /
NK075(bu)003:582: 'dir snga ma gsum du shes par bya'o //
NK075(bu)003:583: de yang 'grel pa tshig gsal las /
NK075(bu)003:584: gzhan don brtsam pa can rnams srog phyir yang //
NK075(bu)003:585: rang gi nus pa lhod par mi byed de //
NK075(bu)003:586: skyes bu dam pas khur ci khur ba dag /
NK075(bu)003:587: nyam nga'i lam du nam yang dor mi bya //
NK075(bu)003:589: gnyis pa man ngag brtsam tshul dang spyir bstan gyi
NK075(bu)003:590: sgo nas bshad pa dam bca' ba dang 'brel tshul
NK075(bu)003:592: phyi'i rgya mtsho chen po las ni chu thigs pa
NK075(bu)003:593: gcig blang ba la chu'i mtshan nyid tshang ba bzhin
NK075(bu)003:594: du / sems ye shes rang snang du ston pa'i
NK075(bu)003:595: rgyud sde rgya mtsho dang 'dra ba'i thugs kyi rgyud
NK075(bu)003:596: kyi nang nas thugs kyi thigs pa 'di nyid bsdus
NK075(bu)003:597: pa la rgyud kyi don 'dus shing ma tshang ba
NK075(bu)003:598: du / med de / dper na mi 'jigsa pa
NK075(bu)003:599: seng ge'i phung po la gcan gzan gzhan gyi gnod
NK075(bu)003:600: pas mi tshugs pa ci lta ba bzhina tu /
NK075(bu)003:601: thugs thigs kyi tshig don 'di la sgro skur lung ma bstan gyi skyon gsum dang bral bas /
NK075(bu)003:602: sems ye shes rang snang du ston pa'i thugs kyi bcud bsdus na gsum po 'di nyid yin te /
NK075(bu)003:603: gang zhe na gzhi rang bzhin gyi snang ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:604: 'bras bu bde bar gshegs pa'i snang ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:605: gdul bya yi lam gyi snang ba /
NK075(bu)003:606: gsum gyi ngo bo yin pa la /
NK075(bu)003:607: mtshon byed tshig gi rgyud kyi dbye ba ni gsum du rnam par bzhag nas gtan la phab pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:608: de yang mtshon bya don gyi ngo bo gcig yin
NK075(bu)003:609: pa la 'o na gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum gyi
NK075(bu)003:610: ngo bo tha dad byung ba de yang gang gis
NK075(bu)003:612: gang dag rang ngo ma shes pa blo 'khrul pa'i
NK075(bu)003:613: snang bas phye bas gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum du
NK075(bu)003:614: 'gyur te / de yang gzhi rang la gnas kyang
NK075(bu)003:615: blo 'khrul pas ngo ma shes pas de nyid gab
NK075(bu)003:616: 'gyur te / pa dang / 'khrul pa de'i gnyen por lam bgrod pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:617: 'khrul pa de sangs pa'i tshe 'bras bu thob pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:618: gtan tshigs des na gzhi lam 'bras bu 'khrul pa'i
NK075(bu)003:619: snang ba dang bzhi po dag tu khog dbub pa
NK075(bu)003:620: ni / rgyal bas gsungs pa'i rgyud lung dang rigas
NK075(bu)003:621: pa'i man ngag gi bstan chos kun la gsungs pas
NK075(bu)003:622: bdag gis kyang gsal bar bshad do zhes bya'o //
NK075(bu)003:623: gnyis pa gzhung la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:627: gsang sngags rdo rje'i theg pa gtan la dbab par
NK075(bu)003:628: byed pa la rtogs ma rtogs phyogs rtogs kyi yan
NK075(bu)003:629: lag snang ba rnam pa bzhi po gsal bar bshad
NK075(bu)003:631: de yang snang ba bzhi dang rgyud gsum gyi spyi'i go don bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:633: brgal lan gyi sgo nas mtha' yongs su chod par bya'o //
NK075(bu)003:635: gzhi rang bzhin gyi snang ba'i rgyud ces bya ste /
NK075(bu)003:636: gzhi ni 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad kyi 'byung gzhi /
NK075(bu)003:637: rang bzhin ni dbyer med bcos slad dang bral ba /
NK075(bu)003:638: snang ba ni rang rig pa thams cad du rtsal ma 'gags par snang ba'o //
NK075(bu)003:639: de ka la skabs kyis rgyud ces kyang bya ste /
NK075(bu)003:640: gang zhig dgos pa tshang zhing 'brel pa dang ldan pas na rgyud do //
NK075(bu)003:641: de yang gzhi dang lam dang 'bras bu'i yon tan gyi dgos pa tshang zhing /
NK075(bu)003:642: gzhi dang 'bras bu gnyis ngo bo nyid gcig tu 'brel bas na rgyud de /
NK075(bu)003:644: 'brel dang ma tshangs med pa dang //
NK075(bu)003:645: dgos pa tshang bas rgyud ces bya //
NK075(bu)003:647: gdul bya lam gyi snang ba'i rgyud ni /
NK075(bu)003:648: sbyangs pa dang rang bzhin gyis thun mong dang mchog gi sems lnga skyes sam /
NK075(bu)003:650: 'jug cing bgrod par byed pas lam /
NK075(bu)003:651: bstan pa blo dang 'tshams par snang bas snang ba /
NK075(bu)003:652: de ka la rgyud ces bya ste /
NK075(bu)003:653: lam gyis gzhi gtan la phab cing 'bras bu mngon
NK075(bu)003:654: sum du byed pa'i cha nas lam la gzhi 'bras
NK075(bu)003:655: kyi yon tan gyi dgos pa tshang ba des na
NK075(bu)003:656: gzhi 'bras gnyis dang 'brel pas na rgyud ces bya'o
NK075(bu)003:657: // 'bras bu bde bar gshegs pa'i snang ba'i rgyud ni /
NK075(bu)003:658: gang zhig smin pa zhig 'bras bu /
NK075(bu)003:659: zug rngu med cing nar son pas na bde bar gshegs /
NK075(bu)003:660: rtogs pa'i rig pa la sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du snang bas na snang ba'o //
NK075(bu)003:661: de ka la rgyud ces bya ste /
NK075(bu)003:662: 'bras bu la yon tan yar ldan du lam mthar
NK075(bu)003:663: phyin cing gzhi mngon du byas pa'i cha nas gzhi
NK075(bu)003:664: lam gyi yon tan gyi dgos pa thams cad tshang
NK075(bu)003:665: ste / des na 'bras bu dang gzhi lam gnyis
NK075(bu)003:666: ngo bo nyid du ma 'dres yongs rdzogs su 'brel
NK075(bu)003:668: log rtog 'khrul pa'i snang ba ni /
NK075(bu)003:669: gnyis med la log cing gnyis su rtog pas na log rtog /
NK075(bu)003:670: de ma yin la der 'dzin pas 'khrul pa /
NK075(bu)003:671: las dang log rtog gi blo ngor snang bas snang ba /
NK075(bu)003:672: de la 'brel pa dang dgos pa med pas na snang ba yin kyang rgyud ma yin no //
NK075(bu)003:674: rig rtsal 'gag med du snang ba gzhi snang yin nam ma yin /
NK075(bu)003:676: rang rig pa thams cad du rtsal ma 'gags par snang ba ni rang bzhin gyi snang ba'o //
NK075(bu)003:678: yin na de'i steng na snang ba gsum po snang ngam mi snang /
NK075(bu)003:679: mi snang na rig rtsal 'gag med du snang ba dang 'gal /
NK075(bu)003:680: snang na gsum du dbye ba dgos med du thal /
NK075(bu)003:683: lan ni spyir gzhi snang ye shes sgron ma'i ngo bor la bzla ba'i dbang du /
NK075(bu)003:684: snang ba gsum rig rtsal 'gag med du gcig gis
NK075(bu)003:685: gcig mi sgrib par ma 'dres yongs rdzogs su snang
NK075(bu)003:686: ba yin te / grub thob nyi ma'i snying po'i zhal nas /
NK075(bu)003:687: snang ba bzhi'i me long du 'khor 'das kyi chos
NK075(bu)003:688: kyi gzugs brnyan shar nas yod pas lta na de
NK075(bu)003:689: la ltos / stong pa bzhi'i nam mkha' la 'khor
NK075(bu)003:690: 'das kyi chos kyi gnas pa yod pas sdod sa
NK075(bu)003:691: la ltos / de la gyis / dbyer med bzhi'i
NK075(bu)003:692: nor bu la dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas kyi dgongs
NK075(bu)003:693: pa'i gter mdzod yod kyis blo gtad de la gyis
NK075(bu)003:694: la ltos / de la gyis / zhes gsungs so
NK075(bu)003:695: // bye brag tu shag 'byed pa'i dbang du snang
NK075(bu)003:696: ba gsum bzang ngan tha dad kyi snang ba med
NK075(bu)003:697: pas de'i skyon las grol lo //
NK075(bu)003:698: blo dang 'tsham par snang ba gdul bya'i snang ba yin nam ma yin ma yin na /
NK075(bu)003:699: rgyas pa'i rigs brgyad dbye ba las /
NK075(bu)003:700: chos kyi dbyings kyis kun la khyab pa yi //
NK075(bu)003:701: bla med theg pa bsam yas gsungs pa yang //
NK075(bu)003:702: so sor rang rig blo la snang bar zad //
NK075(bu)003:705: de nyams su blangs pas sngags mthar thug gi 'bras bu thob bam mi thob /
NK075(bu)003:706: mi thob na lam rnams nyams su blangs pa don med du thal /
NK075(bu)003:708: thos bsam sgom pa'i rnal 'byor gyis //
NK075(bu)003:709: rang byung kun ngam lhun gyis grub //
NK075(bu)003:711: thob na mu stegs rtag chad kyis kyang thob par thal /
NK075(bu)003:713: rtag chad gnyis su gang gis blo zhen pa //
NK075(bu)003:714: don gyi snying po nyid las gol bar gsungs //
NK075(bu)003:715: ces gsungs pas gsal lo zhe na /
NK075(bu)003:716: bstan pa blo dang 'tshams pa lam snang yin pas 'bras bu thob kyang /
NK075(bu)003:717: mu stegs rtag chad ni sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa
NK075(bu)003:718: la gol zhing log pa'i lta bar song ba yin
NK075(bu)003:720: rtogs pa'i rig pa la sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du snang ba /
NK075(bu)003:721: 'bras bu'i snang ba yin nam ma yin /
NK075(bu)003:724: sku mchog rdo rje 'od snang ba //
NK075(bu)003:725: mthun pa'i ye shes rang snang ngo //
NK075(bu)003:727: yin na lhun grub rig 'dzin chos can /
NK075(bu)003:728: mthar thug gi 'bras bu yin par thal /
NK075(bu)003:730: yi ge 'khor lo mngon gzigs pa //
NK075(bu)003:732: 'dod na lam pa ba yin pa gsal lo zhe na /
NK075(bu)003:733: mthar lam pa dang mthar thug gi 'bras bu gnyis
NK075(bu)003:734: sku dang ye shes kyi snang ba tsam la gcig
NK075(bu)003:735: kyang / lhun grub rig 'dzin ni lam pa yin
NK075(bu)003:736: pas da rung bag nyal gyi sgrib pa yod pas
NK075(bu)003:737: kyang / / sangs rgyas dang khyad yod pa yin te /
NK075(bu)003:739: kun mkhyen me long tshul gzigs pa //
NK075(bu)003:740: yul dang mkhyen tshad rgyal ba dang //
NK075(bu)003:741: 'dra la bag la nyal gyis phye //
NK075(bu)003:742: zhes gsungs pas de'i skyon las grol lo //
NK075(bu)003:743: gnyis med las log cing gnyis su 'dzin pas 'khrul snang yin nam ma yin /
NK075(bu)003:747: ma rig rtog pa'i gzung 'dzin gyis //
NK075(bu)003:749: mi mthun bde sdug myong bar 'gyur //
NK075(bu)003:751: yin na 'gro la shes rgyud gnyis 'chang du thal /
NK075(bu)003:755: zhes pas gsal lo zhe na /
NK075(bu)003:757: skad cig dang po gnyis med las log cing /
NK075(bu)003:758: skad cig gnyis par gnyis can du 'dzin zhing 'khrul pa yin pas na /
NK075(bu)003:759: 'gro la shes rgyud gnyis 'chang du 'gro ba'i skyon med do //
NK075(bu)003:760: yang snang ba bzhi gcig gam tha dad ce na /
NK075(bu)003:762: snang bzhi ngo bo bder gshegs snying po las ma g.yos par gcig la /
NK075(bu)003:764: gzhi ni ma rtogs la ma 'khrul ba yin la /
NK075(bu)003:765: 'khrul pa ni ma rtogs la 'khrul pa yin la lam pa ni rtogs bzhin 'khrul pa yin la /
NK075(bu)003:766: 'bras bu ni rtogs la ma 'khrul ba yin pas ldog pa tha dad do //
NK075(bu)003:767: de ltar snang ba bzhir grangs nges pa'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK075(bu)003:768: snang ba bzhi las grangs mang na lhag ste /
NK075(bu)003:769: shes bya'i chos thams cad snang ba bzhir ma 'dus shing ma tshang ba med pa'i phyir ro //
NK075(bu)003:770: yang snang ba bzhi las grangs nyung na mi chog ste /
NK075(bu)003:771: rang bzhin gyi snang ba med na /
NK075(bu)003:772: 'khrul grol gnyis kyi spyi gzhi'i gnas lugs med pa'i skyon yod do //
NK075(bu)003:773: gdul bya'i snang ba med na /
NK075(bu)003:774: sems can la khams dang cha med cing chos kyi snang ba mi 'char ba'i skyon yod la /
NK075(bu)003:776: gdul bya'i lam bgrod pa don med du 'gyur ba'i skyon yod 'khrul pa'i snang ba med na /
NK075(bu)003:777: 'khor ba'i chos gting nas med pa'i phyir ro //
NK075(bu)003:778: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la bzhi ste /
NK075(bu)003:779: rang bzhin gyi snang ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:782: bde bar gshegs pa'i snang ba'o //
NK075(bu)003:788: dang po ngo bo lhun grub tu bstan pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:789: drang snang ba bzhi'i thog mar bstan pa'i gzhi rang
NK075(bu)003:790: bzhin gyi snang ba'i don ni byang ba stong pa'i
NK075(bu)003:791: rang bzhin don dam bden pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:792: chub pa snang ba'i rang bzhin kun rdzob bden pa sgyu ma lta bu dang /
NK075(bu)003:793: sems dbyer med kyi rang bzhin de nyid gang la gnas na /
NK075(bu)003:794: rgyud drag las kyi 'gro ba mang po'i ste kun gyi sems rgyud la gnas te /
NK075(bu)003:795: de yang gar gnas na log rtog gi ngo bor
NK075(bu)003:796: snang ba 'di dang lhan cig tu gnas kyang rgyu
NK075(bu)003:797: ma rig pas ngo ma shes rkyen las nyon gyis
NK075(bu)003:798: mtshams sbyar nas 'bras bu rigs drug dang 'khor 'das
NK075(bu)003:799: tha dad du snang ba'i dus nyid na'ang dper na
NK075(bu)003:800: gser las byas pa'i gzugs ci ltar snang yang ngo
NK075(bu)003:801: gser la gcig pa bzhin du dbyer med kyi don
NK075(bu)003:802: de rgyu rkyen dang bral ba'i rang byung sgrib g.yogs
NK075(bu)003:803: dang bral bas ye shes kyi ngo bo la 'khor
NK075(bu)003:804: 'das kyi chos thams cad gzhi la rig rtsal du
NK075(bu)003:805: snang bas na tha dad med par gcig pa ste
NK075(bu)003:807: ngo bo thams cad sems yin te //
NK075(bu)003:808: gser gyi dpe bzhin gnyis su med //
NK075(bu)003:810: don rang byung gi ye shes de yang 'khor ba
NK075(bu)003:811: dang grol ba myang 'das gnyis ka'i bdag nyid yin
NK075(bu)003:812: pa'i phyir / dper na me long grub pa dang
NK075(bu)003:813: ni g.ya' grub pa tha dad med pa bzhin tu
NK075(bu)003:814: pa'i phyir / / 'khor 'das ma rig ye shes
NK075(bu)003:815: phana tshun rig rtsal 'gag med kyi snang bar spang
NK075(bu)003:816: ba dang blang ba meda pa la /
NK075(bu)003:817: gsang sngags kyi don la blo shed ma phye bas
NK075(bu)003:818: byis sba rgyu mtshan nyid pa'i theg pas ma rig
NK075(bu)003:819: pa 'di 'khor gzhi dang myang 'das kyi rten tsam
NK075(bu)003:820: yin zhes tha dad du smra na'ang /
NK075(bu)003:821: dbyer med kyi don la mkhas pa gsang sngags pas
NK075(bu)003:822: 'khor 'das ye nas ka dag lhun grub dbyer med
NK075(bu)003:823: kyi don de nyid smra ba'i tshig dang bsam pa'i
NK075(bu)003:825: gnyis pa de la 'khor 'das snang tshul la bzhi ste /
NK075(bu)003:827: dang po sems rigs rgyud med pa la 'khor 'das
NK075(bu)003:828: su snang zhing ngo bo lhun grub tu bstan pa
NK075(bu)003:830: 'di skad du gsang ba'i snying po sgyu 'phrul rgyas pa'i rgyud nyid las gsungs pa ni /
NK075(bu)003:831: bde bar gshegs pa'i sku ye shes sgyu ma'i rang mdangs gzugs skur snang ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:832: log rtog gi bsam gzugs la rigs drug gi lus
NK075(bu)003:833: sgyu mar snang ba gnyis ni ye shes sgyu ma'i
NK075(bu)003:834: ngo bor dbyer med gcig pa des na 'khor 'das
NK075(bu)003:835: kyi rigsa tha dad dang rgyud tha dad du blos
NK075(bu)003:836: brtag tu med de ci'i phyir na 'khor ba bskyed
NK075(bu)003:837: pa'i gzhi dang myang 'das brten pa'i rtsa ba rang
NK075(bu)003:838: rgyud du grub pa med de rang bzhin gyis stong
NK075(bu)003:839: pa de la / pho mo ma ning gi rigs
NK075(bu)003:840: tha dad dang dkar ser la sogs pa'i kha dog
NK075(bu)003:841: pa de la / dang / zlum po gru bzhi
NK075(bu)003:842: la sogs pa'i dbyibsa phyogs gcig tu grub pa med
NK075(bu)003:843: pa de la / dang / pa las / med
NK075(bu)003:844: bzhin du rig rtsal 'gag med tu phyi nang snod
NK075(bu)003:845: bcud thams cad du rang snang ba'o //
NK075(bu)003:846: yang ngo bo lhun grub tu bstan pa ni sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba rtsa rgyud gsang snying las /
NK075(bu)003:847: 'khor ba'i dus su gzung 'dzin bcings pa med /
NK075(bu)003:848: 'das pa'i dus su med pa las rnam par grol
NK075(bu)003:849: ba po yang med pa'i ka dag gi ngo bo
NK075(bu)003:850: la / ye gdod ma nyid nas sku dang ye
NK075(bu)003:851: shes su lhun gyis grub cing rdzogs pa ni 'gyur
NK075(bu)003:852: ba med pa'i sangas rgyas yin la /
NK075(bu)003:853: dar nub med pa'i chos kyang de yin par gsungs
NK075(bu)003:854: pa des na gzhi rang bzhin gyi rgyud de nyid
NK075(bu)003:856: ma rig pa dang rig pa ye shes gnyis gzhi snang tsam la tha dad med de /
NK075(bu)003:857: dper na nam mkha' dwangs pa ste stong pa la
NK075(bu)003:858: sprin gyi gnas bca' nas snang dus nam mkha' la
NK075(bu)003:859: ma g.yos pa'o // gnyis pa tha dad lhun grub
NK075(bu)003:860: tu gcig pa'i sems nyid mtha' thug med du cir
NK075(bu)003:861: yang snang du rung ba'i dpe don /
NK075(bu)003:863: dpe shel dwangs pa'i rigsa cana de la kha dog
NK075(bu)003:864: gang bstan gyi kha dog tu 'gro yang ngo bo
NK075(bu)003:865: shel la 'gyur ba med pa ltar /
NK075(bu)003:866: rnam rtog bzang ngan gyi semsa dang gzung 'dzin mi
NK075(bu)003:867: mthun pa mang po snang yang byang chub kyi semsa
NK075(bu)003:868: de nyid du ngo bo gcig yin pa las rang
NK075(bu)003:869: gi sems bzang ngan gyi bsam gzugs la mtha' thug
NK075(bu)003:870: pa med par kun la shar ba yin te /
NK075(bu)003:871: dgongs pa tshigs pa'i rgyud las /
NK075(bu)003:872: shel sgong dri ma med pa la //
NK075(bu)003:873: gang 'phrad rgyan gyis de ltar snang //
NK075(bu)003:874: de bzhin sems nyid dag pa yang //
NK075(bu)003:875: dge sdig gos pa ltar snang ngo //
NK075(bu)003:877: gsum pa cir yang snang ba yang rkyen gyis bsgyur bas snang du rung ba'i dpe don dngos dang /
NK075(bu)003:879: de yang dper na ar+ya ste 'phags pa rdo rje
NK075(bu)003:880: sems dpa' de nyid nor lha dzam b+ha la'i skur
NK075(bu)003:881: snang nas / phyag g.yon pas ne'u le'i rkyal pa
NK075(bu)003:882: rin po ches bkang ba bsnams nas rin chena gyi
NK075(bu)003:883: char phyogs med du phab pa las /
NK075(bu)003:884: 'khor los bsgyur ba'i rgyal po de'i chos lugs yang
NK075(bu)003:885: dag pa pa dang ldan zhing dge bcu spyod pa'i
NK075(bu)003:887: rgyal srid rin po che sna bdun babs pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:888: bram ze dam pa ste ya rabs pa de'i gnas
NK075(bu)003:889: su sna tshogsa rina chena gser dngul la sogs phal
NK075(bu)003:891: tsi bi ra ste yi dwags kyi gnas su bye tshuba dang gram par mthong ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:892: dbul ba tan tra ste dbul po'i rigs rgyud kyi
NK075(bu)003:893: grong khyer du zas kyi lhada ma dang ras ma
NK075(bu)003:894: gos hrul por shar ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:895: rigs ngan bshan pa dang shan ta rak+sha ste srin
NK075(bu)003:896: pa'i gnas su sha dang khrag dang rus pa'i char
NK075(bu)003:897: dang / gdol pa zhing las pa'i grong du 'bru rin chen sil mi'i char 'bab pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:898: de ltar rin po che'i char gcig la bsod nams
NK075(bu)003:899: che chung gi dbang gis so sor snang ba bzhin
NK075(bu)003:900: du / 'gro drug gi spyod yul bde sdug mi mthun pa tha dad du snang ba de yang /
NK075(bu)003:901: rang gi sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes de
NK075(bu)003:902: rtogs ma rtogs phyogs rtogs kyi rkyen gyis bsgyur nas
NK075(bu)003:904: don gyi ngo bo la 'khor 'das so so'i rigs
NK075(bu)003:905: rgyud dang phyogs cha tha dad du grub pa med
NK075(bu)003:906: pa las thams cad snang bas sems nyid de la
NK075(bu)003:907: rkyen bzang ngan des bsgyur cing cir yang snang du
NK075(bu)003:908: btub bo // de yang klong drug pa las /
NK075(bu)003:909: bsgyur du btub par gnas pa las //
NK075(bu)003:910: 'bad med blo yi snang bar snang //
NK075(bu)003:912: de ltar na lam bgrod pa don med cing /
NK075(bu)003:913: 'bras bu'ang slar sems can du log par 'gyur te /
NK075(bu)003:915: rang gi gnas lugs bsgyur btub na //
NK075(bu)003:916: 'bras bu nyid ni rgyur ldog phyir //
NK075(bu)003:917: 'bad pa rnams la goms med pas //
NK075(bu)003:918: yang dang yang du ldog pas na //
NK075(bu)003:919: bems po rnams ni rig bcas su //
NK075(bu)003:920: 'gro bar gtub pa ma yin bzhin //
NK075(bu)003:921: zhes gsungs pa'i phyir ro zhe na /
NK075(bu)003:922: don gnas lugs la 'gyur ba med cing bsgyur du mi btub kyang /
NK075(bu)003:923: de nyid ngo ma shes pa'i blo la 'khrul par
NK075(bu)003:924: shar ba la bsgyur ba ltar snang ba'i phyir 'gal
NK075(bu)003:925: ba med de / rgyas pa las /
NK075(bu)003:926: ngan song 'gro drug sna tshogs rgyu ba yang //
NK075(bu)003:927: 'khrul pa'i log rtog blo nyid snang ba ste //
NK075(bu)003:928: de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings las 'gyur ba med //
NK075(bu)003:930: bzhi pa log rtog gi snang ba don la rang rgyud du med pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:932: spyir bsdus te bstan pa ni ma rig pas bskyed
NK075(bu)003:933: pa'i sems can gyi gzung 'dzin gyi snang ba thams
NK075(bu)003:935: de la bden par 'dzin pa ni rtog pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:936: de nyid 'gro ba rigs drug gi dbang gis yul sems na rnam grangs bsam yas pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:937: dus kyang thog mtha' med par bsam yas pa ste /
NK075(bu)003:938: de dag nam mkha' gzugs su grub ma myongs pa bzhin /
NK075(bu)003:939: ye'am gdod ma nyid nas gzhi sems nyid kyi ngang
NK075(bu)003:940: la rang rgyud du grub nas yod pa ma yin
NK075(bu)003:941: te / de yang sten kyang gsum skyon dang bstan bya lhag ma can gnyis las /
NK075(bu)003:943: de dag rang rgyud du ma grub kyang 'gro drug
NK075(bu)003:944: so so'i gzung 'dzin gyi rtog pa dge sdig lung
NK075(bu)003:945: ma bstan gyi bag chags bzang ngan dang phra rags
NK075(bu)003:946: bsogs sad kyi rim pa rnams ther slong gi drag
NK075(bu)003:947: pa bzhin tu kun gzhi la bsogs pas /
NK075(bu)003:948: dper na chu rnyog ma la gzugs brnyan mi 'char ba ltar /
NK075(bu)003:949: sems kyi 'gyu mthas rang gi mtshan nyid rang gis
NK075(bu)003:950: bsgribsa shing dus mtha' med par rtag tu khams gsum
NK075(bu)003:951: du 'khor ba'o // de'i don ni 'di skad du
NK075(bu)003:952: rgyas pa'i rgyud las gsungs pas dus thog ma med
NK075(bu)003:954: sems nyid rang byung ye shes las logs su ste
NK075(bu)003:955: gud du ma 'gyur cing mkha' sprin ltar dbyer med
NK075(bu)003:956: do // 'o na ci'i phyir 'khrul zhe na /
NK075(bu)003:957: rgyud lhan skyes ma rig pa dang kun brtags ma rig gnyis dang /
NK075(bu)003:958: rkyen las nyon gyis 'khrul par snang ste /
NK075(bu)003:959: de yang gshis la ma grub cing dwangs ba dang
NK075(bu)003:960: sang rgyu yod pa'i phyir glo bur ba zhes bya
NK075(bu)003:961: ste / des na 'khrul pa'i spyod yul tha dad
NK075(bu)003:962: par snang ba'i dus la thog ma 'di nas byung
NK075(bu)003:963: ba dang mtha' ma 'dir thal med par snang ba'o
NK075(bu)003:964: ste / // gsum pa don rtogs par bya ba'i
NK075(bu)003:965: phyir 'khrul pa dang ma nor ba'i mtshan nyid la
NK075(bu)003:967: dang po gnyis su 'dod pa lhun grub la skyon brjod pa nyid 'khrul pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:969: gzhi don byang chub semsa kyi rgyud la 'khor 'das
NK075(bu)003:970: gnyis kyis bsdus pa'i chos kun rtsal 'gag med du
NK075(bu)003:971: lhun gyis grub par gnas pa ste /
NK075(bu)003:972: dper na nor bu rin chen la dgos 'dod lhun
NK075(bu)003:973: grub tu 'byung ba ltar bu gcig pa yin pa
NK075(bu)003:974: de la / 'khor 'das snang stong tha dad 'gal ba yin pas /
NK075(bu)003:975: skyon du ma 'dus pa yin zhes theg pa dman pa mtshan nyid las brjod na'ang /
NK075(bu)003:976: 'o na gzhi snang btags pa'i 'khor 'das gnyis la
NK075(bu)003:977: phan tshun spang blang du byed par gang zag gang
NK075(bu)003:979: dpe dred mos rtsi thog gi 'bras bu zos kyang khong par mi sdod nas byaba pa ltar /
NK075(bu)003:980: gzhi don la 'khor 'das tha dad du 'dod na
NK075(bu)003:981: gsang ba bla na med pa'i don mchog ga la
NK075(bu)003:983: gnyis pa 'khor 'das tha dad la skyon brjod de tha mi dad du bstan pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:985: kun gzhi'i thog nas bag chags sad pa nyon mongs gzung 'dzin 'khor ba'i chos dang /
NK075(bu)003:986: de dag rnam par byang ba mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos gnyis rgyu mtshan nyid theg pa ltar /
NK075(bu)003:987: ye gdod ma nyid nas 'khor 'das gnyis kyi ngo
NK075(bu)003:988: bo bde sdug tha dad du yod pa yin zhe
NK075(bu)003:989: na / gzung 'dzin nyon mongs 'khor ba'i chos spang
NK075(bu)003:990: zhing thob bya 'bras bu byang chub bsgrub tu med
NK075(bu)003:992: yang dag gshegs dang log rtogs gnyis //
NK075(bu)003:993: ngo bo nyid du gnas gyur na //
NK075(bu)003:994: de la bcos shing bsgyur du med //
NK075(bu)003:995: mching bu rin chen bzhin mi rigs //
NK075(bu)003:997: 'khor 'das gnyis so so'i rang bzhin snang ba dang
NK075(bu)003:998: stong pa tha dad du nges pa yin zhe na
NK075(bu)003:999: / yang dag pa bla med kyi lam thos bsam
NK075(bu)003:1000: bsgom pa'i bskyed rdzogs kyi sgo nas 'khor ba myang
NK075(bu)003:1001: 'das su bcos su med de sol ba dkar por
NK075(bu)003:1004: byang chub mchog gi ngo bo la //
NK075(bu)003:1005: so sor rang bzhin nges she na //
NK075(bu)003:1006: yang dag lam gyis bcos su med //
NK075(bu)003:1008: gang du de ltar 'khor 'das tha dad na skyon
NK075(bu)003:1009: yod par rgyud las gsungs pa'i phyir na gsang sngags
NK075(bu)003:1010: bla med kyi gzhi snang du 'khor 'das kyi chos
NK075(bu)003:1011: thams cad ngo bo nyid kyi rgyur lhun gyis grub
NK075(bu)003:1013: de ltar ngo ma shes pa rgyu'i theg pas shes
NK075(bu)003:1014: byed kyi blo dang shes bya'i gzhi gnyis blo can
NK075(bu)003:1015: blo 'das zhes tha dad gnyis su smra na'ang /
NK075(bu)003:1016: bla med rang gzhung gi dgongs pa ni bsam pa'i
NK075(bu)003:1017: blo de ka rang gzhi chos nyid de bzhin nyid
NK075(bu)003:1019: gzhan gyis 'o na blo de la 'khrul rtog yoda
NK075(bu)003:1020: pa de gzhi de la med par 'dod pa des
NK075(bu)003:1021: na / gzhi dang blo gnyis phyogs ris su rtogs nas tha dad par bden pa yin zhe na /
NK075(bu)003:1022: 'o na blo de dang gzhi de gnyis la 'brel
NK075(bu)003:1023: pa med pas gzhi rtogs su mi btub pa'i skyon
NK075(bu)003:1025: dus nama yang sngon gong du ngo bo dang rang
NK075(bu)003:1026: bzhin tha dad la skyon yod pa bzhin du don
NK075(bu)003:1027: la bden cing 'thad pa min no //
NK075(bu)003:1029: chos nyid rnam par mi rtog pa'i gzhi don de
NK075(bu)003:1030: nyid rtog pa blo'i sems rgyud la dbyer med du
NK075(bu)003:1032: gsum pa log rtog spang du med pa'i dpe don dang /
NK075(bu)003:1034: snod bcud rgyud rnams thamsa cad rigs lnga yab yum
NK075(bu)003:1035: dang ye shes su rnam par dag ces bya ba'am
NK075(bu)003:1038: ka dag chen po bya ba de yang /
NK075(bu)003:1039: dang po dngos po ma dag pa gcig bsal nas
NK075(bu)003:1040: gsar du dag par 'dod pa ni ma yin te
NK075(bu)003:1041: / snang ba bde ba dang spyod pa bde ba'i dus nyid na gzhi snang du rnam par dag /
NK075(bu)003:1042: ces rgyas pa'i rgyud las gsungsa pas na log rtog
NK075(bu)003:1043: gi shes pa 'di nyid gzhi ye shes rang snang
NK075(bu)003:1044: las ma g.yos pa'i phyir spang du med de /
NK075(bu)003:1045: dper na nam mkha' stong pa la sprin dang 'ja' tshon sna tshogs su snang ba'i tshe na /
NK075(bu)003:1046: rang bzhin nam mkha' stong par ngang ngam shugs gis gnas pa ltar ro //
NK075(bu)003:1048: chos can mtshan mar snang ba'i rang bzhin rnams //
NK075(bu)003:1049: chos nyid mtshan ma med pa'i ngang du gnas //
NK075(bu)003:1051: bzhi pa blo dngos su 'byed pa'i skyon dang /
NK075(bu)003:1053: gsang sngags la dgar bas gang zag dag rgyu yi theg pa mtshan nyid pas /
NK075(bu)003:1054: yul yul can kun tu gzung 'dzin gyi rtog pa
NK075(bu)003:1055: kun rdzob 'khrul snang 'di nyid don dam gyi ngo
NK075(bu)003:1056: bo la bden par yod na /
NK075(bu)003:1057: don dam spros bral gyi nges tshig med par 'dogs pas bden pa gnyis su dbye ste /
NK075(bu)003:1058: klu sgrub kyis 'jig rten kun rdzob bden pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:1059: dam pa'i don du bden pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:1061: don dam gyi mtshan nyid ni /
NK075(bu)003:1062: kun rdzob gzhig cing ma grub pas dwangs zhing blo'i
NK075(bu)003:1063: spros pa dang bral bas gsal ba snang ba rnam
NK075(bu)003:1064: par dag pa gang yin pa don dam du 'dod
NK075(bu)003:1065: pa'o // bsam pa'i blo dag la kun rdzob kyi snang ba de dag yod ces smra na /
NK075(bu)003:1066: bden gnyis so sor dgag bsgrub can du bstan pa
NK075(bu)003:1067: ni rnam par rtog pa'i blos brtag dpyad byas pa
NK075(bu)003:1068: yin pas chos nyid mtha' bral blo las 'das pa'i
NK075(bu)003:1069: don rtogs pa ni ma yin no //
NK075(bu)003:1070: lnga pa sgra ci bzhin tu 'dzin pa 'khrul zhing mi 'dzin pa 'khrul pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:1072: gsang sngags kyi don la blo shed ma bye ba'i tshig phyir blo 'brang ba dag gis /
NK075(bu)003:1073: gsang sngags kyi rgyud gzhung du snod bcud rgyud rnams
NK075(bu)003:1074: rigs lnga yab yum ye shes su dag pa gsum
NK075(bu)003:1075: dang / lhag pa'i mnyam pa gnyis dang 'khor 'das
NK075(bu)003:1076: sam bden gnyis gnyis med kyi don de dag tshig
NK075(bu)003:1078: ma dag pa gsum ldog pas dag pa gsum dang /
NK075(bu)003:1079: mi mnyam pa gnyis ldog pas stong par 'dod pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:1080: gnyis can ldog pas gnyis med stong par 'dod pa
NK075(bu)003:1081: dang gsum gyis phye bas gzhi ci bzhin pa'i don
NK075(bu)003:1082: sgrub byed kyi gtan tshigs sgra gang cir zhen cing
NK075(bu)003:1083: bsgrub pa grub mtha'i phyogs su 'dod pa ni /
NK075(bu)003:1084: yul gang ga dar ci'i mi yi dwags bzhiin du /
NK075(bu)003:1085: bsod nams chung bas spos dri mi gtsang ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:1086: dar zab tsher ma ru mthong nas zas gos longs
NK075(bu)003:1087: spyod kyi spyod yul bral ba ste bza' btung gi
NK075(bu)003:1088: 'dod pas ni gdung ba bzhin du /
NK075(bu)003:1089: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad rang byung ye shes
NK075(bu)003:1090: kyi ngang yin pa la bzang ngan dgag bsgrub gnyis
NK075(bu)003:1091: kyi rtog pas bsdus pas dbyer med kyi don dang
NK075(bu)003:1092: bral ba dang / gzhi 'bras dbyer med lhun grub kyi ngang yin pa la /
NK075(bu)003:1093: the tshom ye rngam za ba ste tha dad 'dod pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:1094: 'khor 'das dbyer med kyi don gang zag gang gis shes pa ni /
NK075(bu)003:1095: gang ga dar tsi'i mi gtsang bar mthong ba de
NK075(bu)003:1096: mi bsod nams can gyis spos drir mthong ba dang
NK075(bu)003:1097: / tsher ma'i nang na 'dug pa de bsod nams can des na bzar mthong ba bzhin du /
NK075(bu)003:1098: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad rang rig pa gzhi
NK075(bu)003:1099: don byang chub kyi sems su dbyer med pa de
NK075(bu)003:1100: ni sgro skur lung ma bstan gyi skyon dang bral
NK075(bu)003:1101: bas lung gi tshad mar bzhag pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:1102: drug pa brtsal thabs yod med gnyis kar tshol ba 'khrul ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:1104: gzhi don byang chub sems phyogs med kyi ngo bo la snang stong phyogs rer gzung ba ste /
NK075(bu)003:1105: de yang gzhi'i ngo bo yod pa snang ba phyogs
NK075(bu)003:1106: gcig las brtsal na byang ba stong pa'i rang bzhin
NK075(bu)003:1107: la sgro btags pa yin te /
NK075(bu)003:1108: de ltar med pa stong pa phyogs gcig las brtsal
NK075(bu)003:1109: na rig rtsal 'gag med chub pa snang ba'i rang
NK075(bu)003:1110: bzhin la skur pa btab par 'gyur ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:1111: yang yod pa snang ba dang med pa stong pa gnyis tha dad las btsal bar byas na /
NK075(bu)003:1112: de ni lung ma bstan te dbyer med mnyam pa nyid lung ma bstan du 'gyur ba yin no //
NK075(bu)003:1113: rgyas pa las de skad gsungs pa'i phyir na rang rig pa byang chub sems dbyer med la /
NK075(bu)003:1114: yod pa bsgrub cing med pa dgag pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:1115: med pa bsgrub cing yod pa dgag pas phyogs rer
NK075(bu)003:1116: gzung ba ni 'du shes phyogs gcig pa ste blun
NK075(bu)003:1118: bdun pa don dbyer med la lhun grub phyogs gcig par 'dzin pa 'khrul pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:1120: dgag bsgrub byas na skyon 'dug pa de bas na
NK075(bu)003:1121: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad gzhi don semas kyi
NK075(bu)003:1122: de kho na nyid du lhun gyis grub pa yin
NK075(bu)003:1123: pa la / rgyu'i theg pa sems tsam pas yul yul can kun tu blos brtagsa pa ste /
NK075(bu)003:1124: mtshan nyid rgya chad pa'i dang /
NK075(bu)003:1126: ltos pa'i kun brtags dang gsum po de nyid /
NK075(bu)003:1127: dag ma dag gyi rgyu rkyen gzhan gyi dbang gis byas pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:1128: don la 'gyur ba med pa'i yongs su grub pa gzhi don dang /
NK075(bu)003:1129: phyin ci ma log pa'i yongs grub lta ba dang gsum gyi bye brag tu phyes te /
NK075(bu)003:1130: spang blang dgag bsgrub byed nas rang rig rang gsal
NK075(bu)003:1131: stong thog tu lhun gyis grub par 'dod pa dang
NK075(bu)003:1132: / gsang sngags phyogs med kyi lhun grub 'dra'am zhe na mi 'dra ste /
NK075(bu)003:1134: sems tsam ltar kun brtags gzhan dbang yongs grub gsum
NK075(bu)003:1135: gyis dgag sgrub can gyi gtan tshigs kyi bya ba
NK075(bu)003:1136: de dang grub mtha' rang rig rang gsal du 'dod
NK075(bu)003:1137: pa de dag grub pa med do //
NK075(bu)003:1138: 'dod pa des ni sngags kyi smra bsam brjod du
NK075(bu)003:1139: med pa'i gzhi don phyogs med lhun grub kyi don
NK075(bu)003:1140: la mi 'jog ste mi bzhag go //
NK075(bu)003:1142: gzhan gyi dam pa'i don de nyid //
NK075(bu)003:1143: phyogs gcig la gnas yang dag min //
NK075(bu)003:1144: rkyen snang se gol cha yi phyir //
NK075(bu)003:1145: gnyis bral smra ba'i rig pas 'gal //
NK075(bu)003:1147: 'o na gzhi'i ngo bo gang zhe na /
NK075(bu)003:1148: sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes kyis shes bya'i
NK075(bu)003:1149: chos kun la bgos pa med par khyab pas rgyas
NK075(bu)003:1150: btab cing lhun gyis grub pas na /
NK075(bu)003:1151: sems nyid kyi rang bzhin 'khor 'das kyi chos kun
NK075(bu)003:1152: dang dbyer med kyi ngang du gnas pa yin pa
NK075(bu)003:1154: med pa 'ba' zhig gi phyogs ma yin te /
NK075(bu)003:1156: dper na rgyal pos rgyas btab na //
NK075(bu)003:1157: sems can kun gyi yongs mi 'da' //
NK075(bu)003:1158: de bzhin mnyam nyid phyag rgya yis //
NK075(bu)003:1159: kun la khyab cing thams cad snang //
NK075(bu)003:1160: sku gsung thugs kyis rgyas btab na //
NK075(bu)003:1162: 'o na dbu ma'i lta ba dang 'dra'am zhe na ma yin te /
NK075(bu)003:1163: med par 'dod pa'i dpe mi srid pa'i chos bzhi ste /
NK075(bu)003:1164: gling bzhi gcig la 'khor lo bsgyur rgyal gnyis mi srid /
NK075(bu)003:1165: bstan pa gcig la ston pa gnyis /
NK075(bu)003:1166: gling bzhi gcig la nyi zla phrugs gnyis /
NK075(bu)003:1167: bud med la rang sangs rgyas mi srid pa ltar
NK075(bu)003:1168: stong nyid spros bral dbyer med phyogs gcig tsam du
NK075(bu)003:1171: mnyam rdzogs bdag nyid chen po'i phyir //
NK075(bu)003:1172: bden pa gnyis kyi skad las 'das //
NK075(bu)003:1175: yod mthong grags pa'i chos rnams dang //
NK075(bu)003:1176: med snang brtags pa'i chos rnams kun //
NK075(bu)003:1177: rang la tha dad med pas na //
NK075(bu)003:1178: gnyis su med par ye gnas gsal //
NK075(bu)003:1179: ltos pa med par rang sar grol //
NK075(bu)003:1181: brgyad pa bden pa dbyer med kyi dpe don sgra ci bzhin du rtog pa 'khrul pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:1183: 'o na sngags kyi dbyer med gang zhe na /
NK075(bu)003:1184: chu dang gzugs brnyan ltar don dam dang kun rdzob
NK075(bu)003:1185: kyi bden pa rnam pa gnyis po ye nas snga
NK075(bu)003:1186: phyi dang bzang ngan tha dad med par dbyer med
NK075(bu)003:1188: des na gzhi'i ngo bo la kun rdzob dgag nas don dam phyogs gcig sgrub pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:1189: yang don dam dgag nas kun rdzob bsgrub tu med
NK075(bu)003:1190: pa'i phyir ye nas gnyis med kyi ngo bo smra
NK075(bu)003:1191: ba'i tshig dang bsam pa'i blo las grola ba yin
NK075(bu)003:1192: te / de yang 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad
NK075(bu)003:1193: rang byung gi ye shes su rig pa rang snang
NK075(bu)003:1194: te / ba'i phyir / gong ltar 'khor 'das sam
NK075(bu)003:1195: bden gnyis mi mthun pa gnyis lhan cig tu 'dus
NK075(bu)003:1196: par blos brtag tu med de /
NK075(bu)003:1197: dper na yid bzhin gyi nor bu dang dpag bsam
NK075(bu)003:1198: gyi ljon shing la rtog med du dgos 'dod lhun
NK075(bu)003:1199: gyis grub pa ltar byed pa po med par bden
NK075(bu)003:1200: gnyis dbyer med du gnas pa yin pa la /
NK075(bu)003:1201: bden gnyis tshig gis tha dad du sgra ci bzhin
NK075(bu)003:1202: pa ru so sor bzang ngan tha dad du rtog
NK075(bu)003:1203: pa ni bla med kyi gzhi don dbyer med lhun
NK075(bu)003:1204: grub kyi don la 'khrul te mi rtogs pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:1205: bzhi pa nges tshig la gsum ste /
NK075(bu)003:1206: gzhi'i snang ba'i nges tshig dang /
NK075(bu)003:1207: de ltar snang dus 'khor 'das gnyis med du la bzla ba'i dpe don bstan pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:1210: dang po snang ba'i nges tshig dang /
NK075(bu)003:1212: de ltar don dam dang kun rdzob bden pa gnyis gzhi don la gnyis su med pa de yang /
NK075(bu)003:1213: don dam nam mkha' stong pa dang 'dra ba'i ngang
NK075(bu)003:1214: du kun rdzob bden pa 'ja' tshon dang sprin ltar
NK075(bu)003:1215: dbyer med par snang ba bzhin du /
NK075(bu)003:1216: snang ba kun rdzob dang stong pa don dam gnyis
NK075(bu)003:1217: dus dang rnam pa kun tu sems nyid dbyer med
NK075(bu)003:1218: rang du gsal ba de bas na /
NK075(bu)003:1219: rang bzhin ngam ngam shugs kyi rang snang ba'o //
NK075(bu)003:1220: gnyis pa de nyid ngang snang yin tshul lung gis gsal ba'o //
NK075(bu)003:1222: de la bdag sems ngang gzhan yul du blos tha dad du ma rtags par /
NK075(bu)003:1223: shes bya ma 'dres par so sor rang snang zhing
NK075(bu)003:1224: mthun pa'i gzugs su rig rtsal 'gag med du shar
NK075(bu)003:1225: ba dpe de lta bu don de yi ngang du
NK075(bu)003:1226: rang snang ba'o // zhes rgyas pa las de skad
NK075(bu)003:1227: gsungs pa'i lung gis don 'dir drang zhing bgrod dang
NK075(bu)003:1228: go ba dang rtogs par yang sla'o //
NK075(bu)003:1229: gnyis pa de ltar du snang dus 'khor 'das gnyis
NK075(bu)003:1230: med du la bzla ba'i dpe don bstan pa dang
NK075(bu)003:1232: gzung 'dzin phyin ci log pa de nyid yang dag pa'i gnas lugs su la bzla ba yin te /
NK075(bu)003:1234: khams gsum gyi rgyu ma rig pa de nyid rang
NK075(bu)003:1235: rig pa'i ye shes su sgrib g.yogs med par gsal
NK075(bu)003:1236: zhing / rkyen nyon mongas lnga dang las gsum 'bras
NK075(bu)003:1237: bu sdug bsngal dang bcas pa byang chub mchog sangs
NK075(bu)003:1238: rgyas kyi dgongs pa yin par ye nas gnas pa'i
NK075(bu)003:1239: zhing / don de nyid / rgyas pa las de
NK075(bu)003:1240: skad gsungs pa'i don gyis na de dag tha dad
NK075(bu)003:1241: du byas nas gzung 'dzin de 'phos nas yang dag
NK075(bu)003:1242: zhing / don de nyid / dang / ma rig pa de 'phos nas ye shes dang /
NK075(bu)003:1243: nyon mongs sdug bsngal 'phos nas byang chub mchog tu bsgrub tu med pa ni /
NK075(bu)003:1244: dper na mar me gsal ba'i dus na mun pa
NK075(bu)003:1245: ma spangs kyang mun pa ngo bo nyid kyis mi
NK075(bu)003:1247: blun po mtshan nyid pas mun pa ste 'khor ba snang ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:1248: snang ba ste 'das pa stong pa gnyis res mos tha dad du mthonga ba'o //
NK075(bu)003:1249: dbyer med kyi don la mkhas pa gsang sngags pas ni /
NK075(bu)003:1250: gzhi snang la 'khor 'das kyi ngo bo bzang ngan tha dad kyi ris su mi lta ste /
NK075(bu)003:1251: 'khor ba'i chos thams cad gzhi chos nyid de bzhin
NK075(bu)003:1252: nyid kyi ngang du rtsal ma 'gags par rang snang
NK075(bu)003:1253: ba yin no // gzhi snang du 'khor ba btags
NK075(bu)003:1254: pa ba spangs pa med par 'khor ba rang rgyud
NK075(bu)003:1255: kyi skyon kun dang bral ba ni /
NK075(bu)003:1256: dper na me tog pun+da ri ka dkar po la
NK075(bu)003:1257: nag po'i skyon med pa lta bu'i gzhi don yin
NK075(bu)003:1259: 'khor ba ka dag rin chen gling //
NK075(bu)003:1262: ye nas chos skur sangs rgyas te //
NK075(bu)003:1263: rgyu gzhi rang byung ye shes pas //
NK075(bu)003:1264: rgyu yi ngo bo gdod nas dag /
NK075(bu)003:1265: ma rig pa nyid ye shes phyir //
NK075(bu)003:1266: 'khor rgyu ma bcos rang bzhin mnyam //
NK075(bu)003:1267: phral du chags sdang ye shes lhar //
NK075(bu)003:1268: ye nas ma bcos ma gsal ste //
NK075(bu)003:1269: nyon mongs rang spyi sku gsung thugs //
NK075(bu)003:1270: yin phyir rkyen yang sangs rgyas so //
NK075(bu)003:1271: rgyu rkyen 'bras bu'i rang bzhin bas //
NK075(bu)003:1272: ma spang 'bras bu sangs rgyas te //
NK075(bu)003:1273: rdo rje phung sogs sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:1274: nyi ma'i snying po mun pa bzhin //
NK075(bu)003:1275: rang bzhin ngang la 'khor ba med //
NK075(bu)003:1277: gsum pa rgyud kyi nges tshig go //
NK075(bu)003:1279: gzhi don de la lam gyi chos rnams dang 'bras
NK075(bu)003:1280: bu'i chos kyi che yon thams cad lhun gyis grub
NK075(bu)003:1281: cing tshang bar gnas pas na /
NK075(bu)003:1284: gzhi 'bras gnyis ngo bo bdag nyid gcig par 'brel pa dang gsum gyi tan+t+ra ste rgyud ces bya'o //
NK075(bu)003:1286: de las gzhan pa'i thob bya med //
NK075(bu)003:1287: kun kyang smin zin bgrod pa med //
NK075(bu)003:1288: de nyid lam gyi ngo bo yin //
NK075(bu)003:1291: phun sum tshogs pa lnga tshogs shing //
NK075(bu)003:1292: 'brel dang ma tshang med pa dang //
NK075(bu)003:1293: yongs su rdzogs pas rgyud ces bya //
NK075(bu)003:1295: spyir gzhi lam 'bras bu'i gnas skabs su 'khrul pa yod med kyi brtags pa la gsum las /
NK075(bu)003:1296: dang po gzhi'i ngo bo la 'khrul pa med de /
NK075(bu)003:1297: gzhi don byang chub kyi sems rang byung gi ye shes la /
NK075(bu)003:1298: las nyon shes bya'i sgrib pa ka nas dag pa yin pa'i phyir te /
NK075(bu)003:1300: bcings med rnam par grol med pas //
NK075(bu)003:1301: ye nas lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas chos //
NK075(bu)003:1303: nam mkha' mtha' mnyam gyi rgyud las /
NK075(bu)003:1304: thag pa'i rang bzhin sbrul med kyang //
NK075(bu)003:1305: 'khrul pa'i ngo la sbrul du snang //
NK075(bu)003:1306: rang sems ma bcos ci bzhin la //
NK075(bu)003:1307: 'khrul pa'i gnyis su rtog pas bzung //
NK075(bu)003:1310: tho mi thag sbrul smig rgyu ltar //
NK075(bu)003:1311: log pa'i kun rdzob 'khrul gsum yon //
NK075(bu)003:1314: spyir ni log rtog bsam yas pa //
NK075(bu)003:1315: ye nas yod pa ma yin te //
NK075(bu)003:1316: zhes sogs du ma gsungs so //
NK075(bu)003:1318: sems can rnams ni sangs rgyas nyid //
NK075(bu)003:1319: 'on kyang glo bur dri mas bsgribs //
NK075(bu)003:1320: dri ma de bsal sangs rgyas nyid //
NK075(bu)003:1324: nam mkha' la me 'bar yang nam mkha' tshig par mi nus te /
NK075(bu)003:1325: de bzhin sems nyid rang bzhin gyi 'od gsal ba la glo bur gyi dri ma byung yang /
NK075(bu)003:1326: rang bzhin gyi 'od gsal ba de glo bur gyi
NK075(bu)003:1327: dri mas kun nas nyon mongs pa can du byas
NK075(bu)003:1331: sems nyid rang bzhin 'od gsal ba /
NK075(bu)003:1332: nyon mongs can ni glo bur ba /
NK075(bu)003:1335: 'khrul pa gzhi la med de glo bur pa //
NK075(bu)003:1336: mtshan nyid go bas chog go ding ri ba //
NK075(bu)003:1340: sems can sangs rgyas mi srid pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:1341: lam thos bsam sgom gsum gyis 'khrul pa mi sel ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:1342: gzhi la dri ma yod pa'i phyir /
NK075(bu)003:1343: sol ba la dung mi 'byung ba bzhin no //
NK075(bu)003:1344: gnyis pa la lam gyi gnas skabs su 'khrul ma 'khrul yod de /
NK075(bu)003:1345: de yang mnyam gzhag chos nyid kyi ngo bo la 'khrul pa med de /
NK075(bu)003:1346: 'on kyang rjes shes la mthar lam gyi bar du 'khrul pa'i tha snyad yod pa yin te /
NK075(bu)003:1348: ma rtogs sems can thams cad la //
NK075(bu)003:1349: 'khrul pa zang ma gnas pa yin //
NK075(bu)003:1350: lam la gnas pa'i rnal 'byor la //
NK075(bu)003:1351: 'khrul dang ye shes dum bur gnas //
NK075(bu)003:1352: dum bur gnas shing dum bur mthud //
NK075(bu)003:1354: gal te lam gyi ngo bo 'khrul na /
NK075(bu)003:1356: 'khrul pa mthar phyin pa la sogs pa'i skyon du ma yod do //
NK075(bu)003:1357: gsum pa 'bras bu'i dus su 'khrul pa ka nas dag ste /
NK075(bu)003:1358: sgrib pa thams cad sangs shing ye shes kyi yon tan thams cad rgyas pa'i phyir te /
NK075(bu)003:1360: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad la //
NK075(bu)003:1361: ye shes zang mar gnas pa yin //
NK075(bu)003:1364: rang byung ye shes spros dang bral bas sangs //
NK075(bu)003:1365: spros bral rtogs pa'i ring du chub pas rgyas //
NK075(bu)003:1368: sangs pas ye shes phyogs bral rgyas //
NK075(bu)003:1373: mtshan don dang 'bru mthun pa las rang bzhin dbyer med bcos slad dang bral ba las /
NK075(bu)003:1374: dgos pa tshang zhing 'brel pa dang ldan pas na
NK075(bu)003:1375: rgyud de nyid du rig rtsal 'gag med du snang
NK075(bu)003:1376: ba'i gzhung don gcod cing mtshams 'dzin par byed pas
NK075(bu)003:1378: yas bgrang dang po'i don du gada'o //
NK075(bu)003:1380: // gnyis pa 'khrul snang la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:1384: dang po mdor bstan pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:1386: 'khrul pa'i gzhi ni gzhi ngo bo nyid sems kyi chos nyid dang /
NK075(bu)003:1388: ma rig pa las byung ba'i khams gsum gyi 'khrul
NK075(bu)003:1389: pa'i ngo bo dus thog mtha' yang dag pa'i spyan
NK075(bu)003:1390: dang bral ba / rang bzhin ni 'khrul pa'i dus
NK075(bu)003:1391: nyid na'ang gzhi don las ma g.yos pa gsum gyi
NK075(bu)003:1392: sdom tshig de'i nang du 'khrul pa'i chos rnams nges
NK075(bu)003:1394: gnyis pa rgyas bshad de la gsum ste /
NK075(bu)003:1400: dang po gzhi sgro skur dang bral bar bstan pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:1402: rgyud drug las kyi dbang gis 'gro ba'i mtho ris
NK075(bu)003:1403: gnas gsum ngan song gnas gsum dang drug gi sems
NK075(bu)003:1405: semsa kyi gnas lugs nyid ni dper na yid bzhin
NK075(bu)003:1406: gyi nor bu rin po che la rtog pa med
NK075(bu)003:1407: kyang / dgos 'dod skong ba'i yon tan zad 'phel med pa de bzhin tu /
NK075(bu)003:1408: sems nyid ci ltar rang gis bsam pa ltar rig rtsal 'gag med du snang ba'i gzhi don la /
NK075(bu)003:1409: 'khrul gzhi ma rig pa dngos po rang kha mar yod par sgro 'dogs pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:1410: rang bzhin stong pa phyogs gcig gi ngo bo la /
NK075(bu)003:1411: rig rtsal 'gag med snang ba med par skur pa
NK075(bu)003:1412: btab pa'i mtha' gnyis dang bral zhing sems nyid ma
NK075(bu)003:1413: 'dres yongs rdzogs su gnas pa de la /
NK075(bu)003:1414: gnyis pa 'khrul gzhi yod pa la 'khrul pa'i skyon dang /
NK075(bu)003:1417: gzhi lhun grub kyi ye shes la rmongs pas /
NK075(bu)003:1418: 'khrul gzhi ma rig pa rang rgyud du yod par
NK075(bu)003:1419: sgro 'dogs pa des dbang bsgyur nas 'khrul pa 'byung
NK075(bu)003:1420: bar 'dod pa'i gang zag phyogs gcig pa rnams kyis
NK075(bu)003:1421: / gang la sgro 'dogs na de rnams kyis /
NK075(bu)003:1422: byang chub sems kyi chos nyid kyi ngo bo la
NK075(bu)003:1423: ma rig pa rang kha la dmigs su med pa
NK075(bu)003:1424: yin pa la sgro 'dogs tshul ci ltar na ma
NK075(bu)003:1425: rig pa'i dngos po ste ngo bo rang rgyud can
NK075(bu)003:1426: cig gzhi'i ngo bor yod par smra ba'i skyon rnams
NK075(bu)003:1427: ni / gang zag de yi lta ba 'dzin pa'i
NK075(bu)003:1428: rigs rgyud thams cad mu stegs rtaga par lta ba
NK075(bu)003:1430: sol ba la dung mi 'byung ba ltar /
NK075(bu)003:1431: sems can la sangs rgyas mi 'byung ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:1432: gzhi 'khor ba'i mthar ltung ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:1433: lam thos bsam sgom gsum gyis 'khrul pa mi sel ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:1434: gzhi la 'khor 'das tha dad du thal ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:1435: gal chung na theg dman nyan rang du gol ba
NK075(bu)003:1436: la sogs pa'i skyon du ma yod pa yin te
NK075(bu)003:1438: chos dang sems gnyis so sor mi 'gyur bas //
NK075(bu)003:1439: de ni rtag pa'i mtha' stong grol ba med //
NK075(bu)003:1442: rang sems rgyun gyi rtag par 'dod //
NK075(bu)003:1443: bdag tu khas len mu stegs dang //
NK075(bu)003:1444: tshig la khyad yod don la med //
NK075(bu)003:1445: ces pa dang ye shes gsang ba las /
NK075(bu)003:1446: lta spyod log pa'i nga rgyal can //
NK075(bu)003:1447: ma bcos rang gar rol pa dang //
NK075(bu)003:1448: rnam rtog zhen pas brtags pa dag /
NK075(bu)003:1449: bye brag ma phyed rmongs pa'i blo //
NK075(bu)003:1450: rdo la gser du 'dzin pa bzhin //
NK075(bu)003:1451: 'od gsal lhun grub rang snang de //
NK075(bu)003:1452: brtags pa'i zhen pa bsres nas smra //
NK075(bu)003:1453: ma bcos rig pa grangs med par //
NK075(bu)003:1454: lta ba ya rabs mtho 'dod pa //
NK075(bu)003:1455: bab chol 'dod lnga spyod pas log /
NK075(bu)003:1456: de yi dus kyi gang zag rnams //
NK075(bu)003:1457: sbrel ma g.yang du lhung ba bzhin //
NK075(bu)003:1458: rdo rje khab tu ltung gyur nas //
NK075(bu)003:1459: byang chub sems kyi rigs dang bral //
NK075(bu)003:1461: gsum pa med pa 'khrul pa'i skyon dang drang /
NK075(bu)003:1462: gang gis skur bas btab na /
NK075(bu)003:1463: gang zag 'ga' zhig gis chub pa snang ba'i rang
NK075(bu)003:1464: bzhin la skur pa btab pa ni 'di lta ste
NK075(bu)003:1465: / gang la btab na gzhi snang 'khor 'das lhun gyis grub pa la btab /
NK075(bu)003:1467: gzhi stong par 'dod pa de dang /
NK075(bu)003:1468: bsam pa'i blo snang gnyis yod med so sor rtog nas /
NK075(bu)003:1469: 'das pa stong pa de la 'khor ba snang ba de ni dbyer med du mi srid de /
NK075(bu)003:1470: dper na ri bong la rwa med pa bzhin du /
NK075(bu)003:1471: gzhi stong pa'i ngo bo la ye gdod ma nas
NK075(bu)003:1472: rig rtsal 'gag med kyi snang ba med ces smras
NK075(bu)003:1473: nas / zhen pa'i blo'i ngo bo la gzhi stong pa med do zhes smra na skyon rnams ni /
NK075(bu)003:1474: gzhi ye shes rang snang la skur pa btab pa'i
NK075(bu)003:1475: gang zag gang yin pa de phugs stong pa cang
NK075(bu)003:1476: med du 'dod pa ni mu stegs chad lta ru
NK075(bu)003:1477: ltung ba dang / gzhi stong pa de dang blo
NK075(bu)003:1478: snang ba de gnyis tha dad cing snang stong snga
NK075(bu)003:1479: phyi can du thal ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:1480: mi srid pa'i dpe bzhin du kun 'byung 'khor ba'i chos la thog ma byung ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:1481: 'ang gi sgras 'khor ba la tha ma 'byung ba'i skyon dang /
NK075(bu)003:1482: gol chung na dbu ma la ltung ba'i skyon yod de /
NK075(bu)003:1484: stong par btags pa don las 'khrul //
NK075(bu)003:1485: mu stegs chad par lta ba dang //
NK075(bu)003:1486: tshig la chad yod don la med //
NK075(bu)003:1489: stong pa nyid du mu chad pas //
NK075(bu)003:1490: chad pa'i khams chen nyid du 'gyur //
NK075(bu)003:1491: des nas slar yang 'phos pa yis //
NK075(bu)003:1492: grol thar lam ni chad par 'gyur //
NK075(bu)003:1495: thams cad gdod nas dag pas blo yul min //
NK075(bu)003:1496: de ni chad pa'i mtha' ste grol ba med //
NK075(bu)003:1498: gang yang yod pa ma yin te //
NK075(bu)003:1499: ci skad smras kyang sgro btags yin //
NK075(bu)003:1500: don gyi ngo bo ci yang med //
NK075(bu)003:1501: ci med skye med phyal bar chad //
NK075(bu)003:1503: bzhi pa gnyis med phyogs gcig las 'khrul pa'i skyon dang /
NK075(bu)003:1505: gang zag la la ste 'ga' zhig gis gzhi snang
NK075(bu)003:1506: la ma rig pa la sogs ma dag pa'i snang
NK075(bu)003:1507: ba ldog nas dag pa'i snang bar gnyis su med
NK075(bu)003:1508: pa'i gzhi don de ngo ma shes pa las 'khor
NK075(bu)003:1509: bar snang zhes smra na'ang rgyud lhan cig skyes pa'i
NK075(bu)003:1510: ma rig pa de rig pa de rig rtsal 'gag
NK075(bu)003:1511: med du med pa dag pa'i snang ba phyogs gcig
NK075(bu)003:1513: gzhi lam rig pa rig rtsal 'gag med kyi snang
NK075(bu)003:1514: ba med na rnam byang gi rten pa'i cha mi
NK075(bu)003:1515: dgos te med par thal ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:1516: 'khor ba'i 'khrul gzhir brgyud rgyur mi btub pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:1517: gzhi 'khor 'das dbyer med ma yin par thal ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:1518: gol che na mu rtug tu gol ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:1519: gol chung na sngags phyi rgyud la gol ba la sogs pa'i skyon yod pa yin te /
NK075(bu)003:1520: gzhi snang la rgyu ma rig pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:1521: rkyen las nyon spang ste bral ba des na 'bras
NK075(bu)003:1522: bu khams gsum 'khor ba dang bcas pa gzhi snang
NK075(bu)003:1523: ba med na / gnyis med phyogs cig de nyid
NK075(bu)003:1524: 'khor 'das kyi spyi gzhir rigsa shing 'thad pa min
NK075(bu)003:1525: ba med na / no // de yang rgyas pa las /
NK075(bu)003:1526: thabs kyi theg pa chen po ni //
NK075(bu)003:1527: rnam par byang dang sdug bsngal dag /
NK075(bu)003:1528: kun rdzob tu yang dbyer med de //
NK075(bu)003:1529: lta ba mthon dman de tsam mo //
NK075(bu)003:1532: thams cad ma lus chos so cog /
NK075(bu)003:1533: sems nyid las ni gzhan med de //
NK075(bu)003:1534: 'di ltar snang ba'i chos rnams kun //
NK075(bu)003:1535: gdos po can gyi chos min te //
NK075(bu)003:1536: rtog med rang rig 'od gsal ba'i //
NK075(bu)003:1537: shes pa 'ba' zhig kho na'i phyir //
NK075(bu)003:1538: 'jig rten brten g.yo la sogs pa'i //
NK075(bu)003:1539: snang ba nyid na ngo bo med //
NK075(bu)003:1540: de nyid chos sku chen po yin //
NK075(bu)003:1542: lnga pa thun mong ma yin pa'i thun mong las 'khrul ba'o //
NK075(bu)003:1544: gzhi don 'khor 'das dbyer med mnyam pa nyid la yod pa snang ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:1545: med pa stong pa phyogs gcig gi rigs tha dad du grub pa med pa las /
NK075(bu)003:1546: rig ma rig la 'khor 'das gnyis su byung yang
NK075(bu)003:1547: 'khor ba de yi rgyu ma rig pa dang rkyen
NK075(bu)003:1548: las nyon dang bcas pa thams cad snang la rang
NK075(bu)003:1550: dpe sman ga pur gyis tsha nad can la phan grang nad can la gnod kyang /
NK075(bu)003:1551: ga pur la phan gnod ma grub pa ci lta ba bzhin tu /
NK075(bu)003:1552: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad lhag ma ma lus
NK075(bu)003:1553: pa kun byang chub sems su rgyu gcig pa yin
NK075(bu)003:1554: pa las / rig ma rig gi dbang gis 'khor
NK075(bu)003:1555: 'das mi mthun pa'i bde sdug gi khyad par so
NK075(bu)003:1557: rgyas pa las gsungsa pa'i phyir na rig ma rig gi rkyen gyis 'khor 'das gnyis su phye ba'o //
NK075(bu)003:1558: yang rgyas pa'i lung las kyang ni 'og nas 'byung ba 'di skad du gsung ste /
NK075(bu)003:1559: nyon mongs pa rgyud drug gi 'gro ba rigs drug
NK075(bu)003:1560: gi 'khor ba'i lus sna tshogs su snang ba ni
NK075(bu)003:1561: / sems 'khrul pa'i rnam rtog bzang ngan dang mthun
NK075(bu)003:1562: pa'i las sna tshogs bsags pa'i dbang gis tha dad
NK075(bu)003:1563: / par snang ngo // sku lnga lhun grub mchog
NK075(bu)003:1564: gi sku rdo rje 'dzin pa ye shes sgyu ma'i
NK075(bu)003:1566: rtogs pa'i ngo ka dang mthun pa'i ye shes lnga'i rang 'od las snang ngo //
NK075(bu)003:1567: gtan tshigs de bas na 'a khor 'das kyi chos
NK075(bu)003:1568: kun sems kyi de kho na nyid du gcig kyang
NK075(bu)003:1569: / rang gi snang ba mthong ba dag pa dang ma dag pa'i dbang gis phye bas /
NK075(bu)003:1570: 'khor 'das kyi spyod yul bzang ngan so sor snang
NK075(bu)003:1571: yang gnas lugs kyi ngo bo de la 'khor 'das
NK075(bu)003:1572: gzhi snang du ma spangs kyang 'khrul snang rang rgyud
NK075(bu)003:1574: 'khrul gzhi'i mtshan ma rang rgyud can du yod pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:1575: gzhi snang med pa'i dgos pa'ang 'dir med pa des na /
NK075(bu)003:1576: 'khor ba'i kun rdzob ched du dgag pa med pas
NK075(bu)003:1577: myang 'das sam don dam du blang du med pa'i
NK075(bu)003:1578: phyir ro // 'o na 'khrul gzhi yod med dbyer med gang las 'khrul zhe na /
NK075(bu)003:1579: de yang gzhi rang snang lhun grub ngo ma shes pa las 'khrul pa 'byung ba yin te /
NK075(bu)003:1580: thag pa la sbrul 'dzin 'byung ba lta bu ste /
NK075(bu)003:1581: de yang a ro'i thig le skor las /
NK075(bu)003:1584: lhun grub de nyid kyi ngo bor 'khrul gzhi rang
NK075(bu)003:1585: rgyud can du grub pa med par ka nas dag
NK075(bu)003:1586: pa yin te / nam mkha' la skra shad ltar ro //
NK075(bu)003:1588: nyi ma'i dkyil na mun med ltar //
NK075(bu)003:1589: ye shes rang snang ma rtog pa //
NK075(bu)003:1590: nyon mongs 'khor ba ngang gis med //
NK075(bu)003:1592: de ltar ka dag lhun grub ngo shes ma shes pa las 'khor 'das 'byung ba yin te /
NK075(bu)003:1595: sman gyi phan gnod ci bzhin du //
NK075(bu)003:1596: thams cad ma lus rgyu gcig las //
NK075(bu)003:1597: mi mthun khyad par so sor snang //
NK075(bu)003:1600: 'khrul gzhi yod med sgro skur bral //
