NK075(bu)003:1602: 'o na 'khrul gzhi zhes bya ba de /
NK075(bu)003:1603: bder gshegs snying po la 'dod dam /
NK075(bu)003:1606: 'khrul pa'i ngo bo mi rnyed par thal te /
NK075(bu)003:1607: gzhi la ltos na rang grol 'gyur //
NK075(bu)003:1610: sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa mi rnyed par thal te /
NK075(bu)003:1613: zhes gsungs pa'i phyir ro zhe na /
NK075(bu)003:1614: brgyud pa'i rgyu bde gshegs snying po yin te /
NK075(bu)003:1616: bcings med rnam par grol med pa'i //
NK075(bu)003:1617: ye nas lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas chos //
NK075(bu)003:1619: e ma'o bde gshegs snying po las /
NK075(bu)003:1621: dngos rgyu lhan skyes ma rig pa yin te /
NK075(bu)003:1623: ma rig rtog pa'i gzung 'dzin gyis //
NK075(bu)003:1625: de ltar theg pa 'og mas snang ba dang stong
NK075(bu)003:1626: pa gnyis tha dad phyogs re'i grub mtha' yi gzhung
NK075(bu)003:1627: ltar du 'khor 'das sam bden gnyis dgag bsgrub can
NK075(bu)003:1628: du byed kyang / 'dir gsang sngags 'khor 'das dbyer
NK075(bu)003:1629: med kyi gzhi don la de ltar mi dgos te
NK075(bu)003:1630: phyogs ris kyi dgag sgrub dang bral ba'i phyir ro
NK075(bu)003:1631: du byed kyang / // gnyis pa 'khrul tshul la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:1633: dang po ma rig pas ngo ma shes te 'khrul pa spyir bstan pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:1635: gong ltar ma rig pa dang rig pa'i ye shes
NK075(bu)003:1636: gnyis dus dang gnas skabs kun tu mtshungs par ldan
NK075(bu)003:1638: de yang 'das ma 'ongs pa da ltar dus gsum dang /
NK075(bu)003:1639: spyod lam bzhir rang byung ye shes de dang 'grogs
NK075(bu)003:1640: kyang rgyun du ye shes de'i don mthong zhing grol
NK075(bu)003:1641: ba med de / bka' brgyad las /
NK075(bu)003:1642: ye nas rang dang 'grogs kyang zhal ma mthong //
NK075(bu)003:1644: dper na mig rang gis mig rang mi mthong ba
NK075(bu)003:1645: bzhin du sems kyang de ltar bur rang gis rang
NK075(bu)003:1646: mi mthong bas / gzung 'dzin gnyis su snang ba
NK075(bu)003:1647: ni snga ma nas phyi mar long btags shing nor
NK075(bu)003:1648: pa'i spyod yul sna tshogs su rgyun mi 'chad pa'o
NK075(bu)003:1649: mi mthong bas / // gnyis pa bye brag phyes ste bstan pa la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:1653: 'khrul pa de'i sdom tshig ni 'khrul pa 'byung ba'i dus dang /
NK075(bu)003:1660: gnyis pa bshad pa de la bdun te /
NK075(bu)003:1664: tan+t+ra ste rgyas pa nyid las gsungs pa'i dus ni 'di lta ste /
NK075(bu)003:1665: thog ma med pa'i dus nas sems rang ngo ma shes te rgya yan tu btang bas /
NK075(bu)003:1666: gzung 'dzin phyin ci log la 'jol nyog tu spyan cing 'khrul lo //
NK075(bu)003:1667: gal te dus thog med nas ma byung ste 'khrul pa gsar du 'byung bar 'gyur zhe na /
NK075(bu)003:1668: 'jiga rten 'khor ba la thog ma byung ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:1669: 'ang gi sgras 'khor ba la tha ma 'byung bar 'gyur ba'i skyon yod do //
NK075(bu)003:1671: thog ma med pa'i dus nas //
NK075(bu)003:1672: yang dag don ma rtogs pas nyams //
NK075(bu)003:1675: yin par gnas dang ma shes pas //
NK075(bu)003:1676: snga phyi mi gnas thog ma med //
NK075(bu)003:1677: tshad las 'das pas tha ma bral //
NK075(bu)003:1678: rgyun du mi sdod 'khor lo'ang bskor //
NK075(bu)003:1681: 'khor ba thog ma tha ma med pa'i khams su /
NK075(bu)003:1683: gnyis pa rgyu la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:1687: ngo bo nyid kyi rgyu bder gshegs snying po dang mtshungs par ldan pa'i rgyu ma rig pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:1688: lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu gzung 'dzin dug gsum dang /
NK075(bu)003:1689: nye bar len pa'i rgyu nyon mongs kyi bag chags brtas bslang dang /
NK075(bu)003:1690: 'phen pa'i rgyu las gsum bsags par mdo bcad pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:1691: gnyis pa bshad pa de la lnga ste /
NK075(bu)003:1693: dang po ngo bo nyid kyi rgyu dang /
NK075(bu)003:1695: sems nyid rgyu rkyen med par rang byung gi ye shes la 'khor 'das kyi rigs tha dad dang /
NK075(bu)003:1696: rgyu snga phyi bzang ngan tha dad kyi ngo bo grub pa med pa'i don nyid /
NK075(bu)003:1697: ngo ma shes pa'i rkyen gyis cir yang snang ba na /
NK075(bu)003:1698: gzhi don de nyid 'khor ba 'khrul pa'i chos su snang ba'i phyir tan+t+ra ste rgyud rgyas pa las /
NK075(bu)003:1699: sngar thun mong ma yin pa'i 'khrul gzhi'i skabs su /
NK075(bu)003:1701: don nyid yod med ris med las //
NK075(bu)003:1702: de yi rgyu rkyen rang bzhin bas //
NK075(bu)003:1703: sman gyi phan gnod ci bzhin du //
NK075(bu)003:1704: thams cad ma lus rgyu gcig las //
NK075(bu)003:1705: mi mthun khyad par so sor snang //
NK075(bu)003:1706: zhes gsungsa pa'i don gyi na /
NK075(bu)003:1708: dang po'i ngo bo nyid kyi rgyu zhes gsungs te /
NK075(bu)003:1709: ngo bo nyid kyi rgyud de nyid kyang 'khor ba
NK075(bu)003:1710: las gzhan du yod pa min te chu dang gsher
NK075(bu)003:1712: gnyis pa mtshungs pa'i rgyu dang /
NK075(bu)003:1714: sngon gzhi don gyi skabs su me long dang ni g.ya' /
NK075(bu)003:1715: nam mkha' dang ni sprin gyi dpe rnam pa gnyis po ltar du /
NK075(bu)003:1716: ye shes grub pas ma rig pa grub ste /
NK075(bu)003:1717: ye shes med na ma rig pa zhes bya ba'i nges tshig med pa des na /
NK075(bu)003:1718: ye gdoda ma nas rang byung gi ye shes yod pa ltar /
NK075(bu)003:1719: lhan skyes ma rig kyang ye nas dus dang ltos
NK075(bu)003:1720: pa 'go mnyam du mtshungs par ldan pas des na
NK075(bu)003:1721: gnyis med ni dbyer med pa ste rtogs ma rtogs
NK075(bu)003:1722: tsam yin pa'o // gsum pa lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu dang /
NK075(bu)003:1724: kun brtags ma rig gis yul yul can kun tu
NK075(bu)003:1725: rtog pa'i gzung 'dzin rnam pa gnyis po me long
NK075(bu)003:1726: gi gzugs brnyan yul du bzung ba ltar /
NK075(bu)003:1727: gzung 'dzin snga ma la goms pa stobs su gyur
NK075(bu)003:1728: pas phyi ma rgyun chags pas na dus mnyam du
NK075(bu)003:1729: 'byung ba'i yul bzang po la brtag dpyad byas pas
NK075(bu)003:1730: 'dod chags / ngan pa la zhe sdang /
NK075(bu)003:1731: bzang ngan mi 'byed pa la gti mug dang gsum gyi 'dzin pa des /
NK075(bu)003:1732: 'khor ba'i chos de las snang zhing bskyed pas na lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu zhes bya'o //
NK075(bu)003:1733: bzhi pa nye bar len pa'i rgyu dang /
NK075(bu)003:1735: sngar gyi dug gsum de yi rkyen gyis phyi ma'i
NK075(bu)003:1736: bag chags kyi mthu brtas nye bar bslang bas stobs
NK075(bu)003:1737: bskyed de snga ma'i bag chags phyi mas nye bar
NK075(bu)003:1738: len pa'o // lnga pa 'phen pa'i pa'i rgyu dang /
NK075(bu)003:1740: 'od ma'i gzhu bzang po la skyes bu mtheb brag
NK075(bu)003:1741: gis mda' 'phangs nas 'ben la tshegs med par phog
NK075(bu)003:1742: pa lta bur / las dkar nag gang yin pa
NK075(bu)003:1743: bsags pa mdo bcad nas phyi mar 'phen pa'i rgyu
NK075(bu)003:1745: gnyis pa rkyen la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:1749: 'dod khams gzugs khams gzugs med khams gsum gyi 'bras
NK075(bu)003:1750: bu 'di na gnas pa kun tu skye ba'i rkyen
NK075(bu)003:1751: ni / las dkar po dge ba bcus mtho ris kyi gnas bcu dang /
NK075(bu)003:1752: nag po mi dge ba bcu yis ngan song gnas bcu'o //
NK075(bu)003:1753: des khamas gsum gyi dang po'i 'dod khams gnas ris nyi shu skye ba yin te /
NK075(bu)003:1754: dge bcu'i steng du tshangs pa'i gnas te tshad med bzhi dang /
NK075(bu)003:1755: gsal thog gi mi g.yo ba'i las bsam gtan bzhi bsgom pa la /
NK075(bu)003:1756: dang po rtogs dpyod dang ldan pa'i dga' bde'i ting nge 'dzin gyi bsam gtan dang po gsum dang /
NK075(bu)003:1757: gnyis pa rtog dpyod dang bral ba'i dga' bde'i gnyis pa'i gsum dang /
NK075(bu)003:1758: gsum pa bde ba'i sa ma d+his gsum pa'i gsum dang /
NK075(bu)003:1759: bzhi pa la rtog dpyod gnyis /
NK075(bu)003:1762: bde sdug gnyis te skyon brgyad dang bral ba'i ting
NK075(bu)003:1763: nge 'dzin gyis so so'i skye bo'i gnas gsum dang
NK075(bu)003:1764: / lhag mthong nges 'byed cha bzhi'i ting nge 'dzin
NK075(bu)003:1765: bsgoms pa'i las rnams kyis 'phags pa'i gnas lnga la
NK075(bu)003:1766: / skye ba ste / de ltar gzugs khams gnas
NK075(bu)003:1767: risa bcu bdun gyi zhing khams la longs spyod pa'i
NK075(bu)003:1769: rig thog gis mi g.yo ba'i ting nge 'dzin bsgom
NK075(bu)003:1770: pa'i las kyi gzugs med pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa
NK075(bu)003:1771: bzhi'i ting nge 'dzin mthu dang ldan pa'i stobs kyis
NK075(bu)003:1772: smin na khams gsum las shes pa zab pa'i srid
NK075(bu)003:1777: yod min med min gyi skye mched dang bzhi yi gnas la longs spyod pa'i yul du snang ngo //
NK075(bu)003:1781: 'bras bu spyir btang na lha ma yin mi brtsi bas 'gro ba lnga'am /
NK075(bu)003:1782: yang na lha mi gnyis ngan song gsum dang lam rgyud lnga'i sems can du skye ba'i rkyen ni /
NK075(bu)003:1783: 'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug nga rgyal phrag dog gnyis dang dug lnga yin te /
NK075(bu)003:1784: de ni tan+t+ra ste rgyas pa'i le'u don gsum pa
NK075(bu)003:1785: sa ma ya dam tshig gi le'u las byung ba
NK075(bu)003:1786: ltar bshad de / de nyid las /
NK075(bu)003:1787: thams cad mnyam par ma shes nas //
NK075(bu)003:1788: ma lus kun la zhe sdang zhing //
NK075(bu)003:1789: snying rje yang dag mang gyur na //
NK075(bu)003:1790: 'di ni mi zad chen po yi //
NK075(bu)003:1791: dmyal khams bcu drug gnas pa yin //
NK075(bu)003:1792: chags bde dngos po mi shes nas //
NK075(bu)003:1793: thams cad kun la 'dod chags shing //
NK075(bu)003:1794: lus kyi sgrib dang zas kyi sgrib //
NK075(bu)003:1795: yi dwags chen po'i gnas su bskyed //
NK075(bu)003:1796: nga dang bdag med mi shes shing //
NK075(bu)003:1797: chos rnams kun la rmongs byas nas //
NK075(bu)003:1798: shes rab gsal don mi shes pas //
NK075(bu)003:1799: dge sdig gnyis kyi don ma rtogs //
NK075(bu)003:1800: 'di ni byol song gnas su skye //
NK075(bu)003:1801: shin tu nga rgyal cher bskyed de //
NK075(bu)003:1802: thams cad bdag gir bzung bas na //
NK075(bu)003:1803: kun la gsod pa'i las byed cing //
NK075(bu)003:1804: lha ma yin gyi gnas su skye //
NK075(bu)003:1807: phyi snod kyi 'jig rten rgyu 'bras kyi tshul ste /
NK075(bu)003:1808: de yang rgyu dang 'brel ba drug /
NK075(bu)003:1809: 'bras bu dang 'brel pa drug dang bcu gnyis /
NK075(bu)003:1810: nang bcud kyi sems can rten 'brel bcu gnyis kyi 'khor lo'i tshul du /
NK075(bu)003:1811: gnas khams gsum du bcud 'gro ba rigs drug las nyon gyi thog mtha' med pa bkod pa'ang /
NK075(bu)003:1812: khams gsum gyi lus yod med kyi cha yis phye
NK075(bu)003:1813: bas gcig tu nges pa med par lus can rnams
NK075(bu)003:1814: la dngos dang / lus med rnams la bag chags kyi tshul du 'khor ba'am /
NK075(bu)003:1815: yang na khams gsum gyi cha yis rten 'brel bcu gnyis grangs mnyam pa'i nges pa med de /
NK075(bu)003:1816: 'dod khams pa la dbang yul du g.yeng ba'i cha
NK075(bu)003:1817: yis phyi nang gi bcu gnyis kun tshang bar yod
NK075(bu)003:1818: / gzugs khams pa la yul la g.yeng ba med pa'i dbang gis bdun yod de /
NK075(bu)003:1819: ma rig pa 'khrul rgyu yin pas yod pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:1820: mi g.yo ba'i 'du byed dang gnyis yod /
NK075(bu)003:1821: rnam par shes pas skye gnas su khrid pa med pas /
NK075(bu)003:1823: skye mched drug gi lus rdzogs par byed pa'i tha snyad de gsum med /
NK075(bu)003:1824: reg pas gsum gyi yul yongs su gcod par byed pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:1825: tshor bas yul la longs spyod par byed pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:1826: sred pas yul bde ba la chags pa tsam dang gsum yod /
NK075(bu)003:1827: len pas skye ba dang mthun 'byed /
NK075(bu)003:1828: srid pas las nus pa thogs med du gyur pa de gnyis med /
NK075(bu)003:1829: skye 'chi 'khor ba'i thog mtha' yin pas yod do //
NK075(bu)003:1830: des na lnga ni med do //
NK075(bu)003:1831: gzugs med la skye shi dang /
NK075(bu)003:1832: ma rig pa'i thog tu 'gog pas de gsum yod do //
NK075(bu)003:1833: gzhan dgu po mngon gyur med do //
NK075(bu)003:1836: 'khrul pa'i rnam par rtog pa shin tu brtan pa'i
NK075(bu)003:1837: 'khrul snang gi spyod yul bzang ngan sna tshogs su
NK075(bu)003:1839: spyir 'gro drug so so'i phyi snod kyi 'jig rten dang /
NK075(bu)003:1840: nang bcud kyi sems can sna tshogs mtha' yas par snang ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:1841: bye brag tu rigs drug gi sems can re re la'ang lus bzang ngan dang /
NK075(bu)003:1846: ngan song gi sdug bsngal dang /
NK075(bu)003:1847: bar ma ste btang snyoms tha dad par snang ngo /
NK075(bu)003:1850: dper na sgyu ma mkhan gyi 'khrul 'khor gyis bslus
NK075(bu)003:1851: pa'i ltad mo ba'i mis sgyu ma la bden par
NK075(bu)003:1853: 'khor ba'i rgyu rkyen gyi nor ba'i 'khrul snang la
NK075(bu)003:1854: longs spyod pa'i yul gyi rang bzhin du de ma
NK075(bu)003:1855: yin la der 'dzin du snang ba'o //
NK075(bu)003:1856: 'o na sngar gzhi'i skabs su 'khor 'das gnyis kyi
NK075(bu)003:1857: ngo bo dang rang bzhin tha dad na skyon yod
NK075(bu)003:1859: gong gi gzhi'i skabs su ye shes rang snang gi
NK075(bu)003:1860: cha nas btags pa yin pas tha dad pa min
NK075(bu)003:1861: la / 'dir 'khor ba'i 'khrul snang rang rgyud pa'i mtshan nyid kyi ngo bo dang /
NK075(bu)003:1863: gzhi snang tha dad pas 'gal ba med do //
NK075(bu)003:1866: srid pa gsum gyi rtsa ba'i nyes dmigs ni ma
NK075(bu)003:1867: rig pa las byung bas bdag 'dzin las snang ba'i
NK075(bu)003:1868: phyir / de'i dbang gis 'gro drug gis sdug bsngal
NK075(bu)003:1869: sna tshogs myong zhing yang dag pa'i lam dang bral
NK075(bu)003:1870: phyir / ba'i nyes pa'o // spyi don gsum pa rang bzhin la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:1872: dang po de kho na nyid kyi rang bzhin dang /
NK075(bu)003:1874: gong du bstan pa'i 'khor bar 'khyams shing sdug bsngal
NK075(bu)003:1875: myong ba de yi dus na gzhi don la ma
NK075(bu)003:1877: rgyud rgyas pa nyid las gsungs pa ni 'di lta ste /
NK075(bu)003:1878: dpe nam mkha' stong pa'i dbyings kyi ngang la ni
NK075(bu)003:1879: bsam yas par snang ba'i nyi zla gza' skar dang
NK075(bu)003:1880: / mtshan mo'i ltas glog 'gyu ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:1882: sprin gyi kha dog mang po dang /
NK075(bu)003:1883: de ltar bzang ngan 'bring gsum sna tshogs su 'khrugsa par 'gyur na yang /
NK075(bu)003:1884: nam mkha' stong pa'i dbyings las gzhan du 'gyur zhing ngo bo la nyams pa med pa bzhin du /
NK075(bu)003:1885: don sems nyid snang stong phyogs re'i mtha' gang du
NK075(bu)003:1886: yang mi dmigsa pa chos kyi dbyings la ni bsam
NK075(bu)003:1887: yas par snang ba'i sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin
NK075(bu)003:1888: las lnga'am / nyer lnga rmad du byung ba 'bras bu'i che yon rnams dang /
NK075(bu)003:1889: 'jig rten gyi gtso bo'i mchog tshangs pa brgya byin
NK075(bu)003:1890: la sogs dang 'khor ba sems can 'gro drug sna
NK075(bu)003:1891: tshogs pa dang / de ltar rnam pa bye brag mang por snang ba de yang /
NK075(bu)003:1892: sems nyid chos kyi dbyings las gzhan du 'gyur zhing ngo bo la nyamsa pa med do //
NK075(bu)003:1894: phyogs med lhun grub sdong po la //
NK075(bu)003:1896: bya bral 'dzin med nam mkha' la //
NK075(bu)003:1897: sku gsum snying po'i nyi zla shar //
NK075(bu)003:1899: bde chen sangs rgyas zhing khams yin //
NK075(bu)003:1900: gzung 'dzin mtshan ma'i myu gu la //
NK075(bu)003:1901: bde chen chos sku'i 'bras bu smin //
NK075(bu)003:1903: gnyis pa rgyu yi theg pas ngo ma shes pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:1905: gong gi 'khor 'das dbyer med kyi don de dang
NK075(bu)003:1906: bral ba'i spyan bzang ste long ba dang 'dra ba'i
NK075(bu)003:1907: rgyu mtshan nyid pa rnams kyis 'khor ba de dang
NK075(bu)003:1908: 'das pa de ni tha dad pa yin te /
NK075(bu)003:1909: 'khor ba de nyid 'das pa min par 'dod pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:1910: de las gzhan du 'das pa brjod du med ces tha dad du smra ba de ltar yin na /
NK075(bu)003:1911: sems can sangs mi srid pa'i skyon yod do //
NK075(bu)003:1913: gsang sngags kyi 'khor 'das gnyis su med par dus
NK075(bu)003:1914: dang rnam pa kun tu ngo bo bdag nyid gcig
NK075(bu)003:1918: thugsa kyi thigs pa 'bru mthun pa las /
NK075(bu)003:1919: de ma yin pa der 'dzin pas 'khrul pa'i las
NK075(bu)003:1920: dang log rtog gi blo ngor snang ba'i gzhung don
NK075(bu)003:1921: gcod cing mtshams 'dzin par byed pas na le'u zhes
NK075(bu)003:1922: bya ste / yas bgrang gnyis pa'i don du gada'o //
NK075(bu)003:1924: // gsum pa gdul bya'i snang ba la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:1928: gdul bya'i snang ba spyir bstan pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:1929: mchog gi theg pa bkar te bstan pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:1932: dang po ngo bo'am nges tshig dang /
NK075(bu)003:1934: rang bzhin gyi dbang rnon dang /
NK075(bu)003:1935: theg 'og las rims kyis sbyangs pa'i dbang rtul gnyis
NK075(bu)003:1936: kyis phye ba yi dbang gis theg pa sna tshogs
NK075(bu)003:1937: 'byung ste / de yang rang bzhin dbang rnon des
NK075(bu)003:1938: thog ma nas sngags la 'jug nas chos nyid mngon
NK075(bu)003:1939: 'byung ste / du byed la / sbyang ba'i gang
NK075(bu)003:1940: zag gi dang po theg 'og las lta ba blo
NK075(bu)003:1941: ngor ma 'phrod kyi bar du sbyangs pa'i bya ba
NK075(bu)003:1942: byed nas mthar sngags la 'jug nas chos nyid rig
NK075(bu)003:1944: de ltar gdul bya gang mos kyi snod blo rno rtul dang /
NK075(bu)003:1945: bcud theg pa mthon dman mtshams par sbyar ba'i gdul
NK075(bu)003:1946: bya 'dul byed bsam yas pa gcig yod na'ang gdul
NK075(bu)003:1947: bya'i snang ba zhes tshigs su brjod do //
NK075(bu)003:1948: de yang dbang po rno rtul gyi sgrub byed la gsum las /
NK075(bu)003:1951: sems can rnams kyi shes pa'i rgyud la rno rtul rang bzhin gyis med pa ni ma yin no //
NK075(bu)003:1954: rdo rje sems dpa' zhing khams na 'khor ba'i sems
NK075(bu)003:1955: can chen po de dag gi sems rang bzhin sna
NK075(bu)003:1956: tshogs pa'i phyir / blo shin tu zab pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:1966: gsang sngags kyi ngo bo nyid kyi gtam rim gyis pa dang cig char bas thos nas /
NK075(bu)003:1967: de gang la yang mi skrag mi sngang gi dga' zhing mgu ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:1968: rangs sar 'gyur ba'i phyir sna tshogs su snang ngo //
NK075(bu)003:1971: lha mi sems can dbang po mi mthun te /
NK075(bu)003:1972: la la sbyangs pa'i dbang pa 'phro can dang /
NK075(bu)003:1973: la la ye nas dbang po gcig chod yod /
NK075(bu)003:1975: ye shes rjogs pa'i rgyud las /
NK075(bu)003:1976: rigs drug dbang po gcig chod dam /
NK075(bu)003:1977: kha cig sbyangs pa'i 'phro can no //
NK075(bu)003:1980: sems can dang po'i las can la //
NK075(bu)003:1981: cig char ba ni bstan par bya //
NK075(bu)003:1982: de nas sbyangs pa'i 'phro can la //
NK075(bu)003:1983: rim gyis pa ni bstan par bya //
NK075(bu)003:1987: kha cig thog ma nas de'i rigs //
NK075(bu)003:1988: kha cig sbyangs pa las gyur pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:1991: gzhi don ngo ma shes pa'i 'dzin stang phra rags mthug srab kyi khyad par las /
NK075(bu)003:1992: khams dang dbang po rno rdul gyi bye brag sna tshogs pa snang ste /
NK075(bu)003:1994: rang bzhin gcig tu ma nges pas //
NK075(bu)003:1995: rdzas snang rnam pa gcig la yang //
NK075(bu)003:1996: log mthong drug dang yang dag dgu //
NK075(bu)003:1997: cir yang 'gyur ba'i ngo bo nyid //
NK075(bu)003:1999: rgyas par ni lam rim du snod kyi skabs su shes par bya'o //
NK075(bu)003:2000: gnyis pa theg pa'i khyad par dang /
NK075(bu)003:2002: bcud theg mchog de dang theg dman de dag 'byung
NK075(bu)003:2003: ba'i rkyen ni snod rang bzhin gyis dbang rnon de
NK075(bu)003:2004: dang sbyangs pa'i dbang rnon de gnyis po yis phye
NK075(bu)003:2005: bas rang bzhin gyi dbang rnon gyis dang nas bla
NK075(bu)003:2006: med la 'jug nas sngags ci bzhin pa'i don mngon
NK075(bu)003:2007: du byed la / sbyangs rnon gyis mthar sngags la
NK075(bu)003:2008: 'jug nas chos nyid de bzhin mngon du byed dgos
NK075(bu)003:2009: du byed la / pa la'ang / rim pa bzhin
NK075(bu)003:2010: du lha mi nyan thos rang rgyal byang chub sems
NK075(bu)003:2011: dpa'i theg pa dang bzhi la bgrod pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:2012: mthar lnga pa gsang sngags 'bras bu yi theg par
NK075(bu)003:2013: 'jug pa la nges 'byung gi theg pa bzhi la
NK075(bu)003:2015: lta ba blo ngor ma 'phrod kyi bar du sbyangs
NK075(bu)003:2016: nas sngags kyi lam stegs sa bgrod cing mthar bla
NK075(bu)003:2017: na med pa'i theg pa nyid du sbyor dgos pa'i
NK075(bu)003:2018: phyir / 'di skad du gsang ba'i snying po'i rgyud las gsungs pa ni /
NK075(bu)003:2019: lha mi nyan thos rang rgyal byang chub sems dpa'i
NK075(bu)003:2020: theg pa dang bzhi yi sgo nas rang rang gi
NK075(bu)003:2021: gzhung lugs ma nor bar spyod na /
NK075(bu)003:2022: go rim bzhin du ngan song gsum dang /
NK075(bu)003:2024: mtha' gnyis las nges par 'byung la /
NK075(bu)003:2025: mthar thug gsang sngags kyi theg pa gcig ni gong
NK075(bu)003:2026: gi theg pa de dag gi 'bras bu gnas pa'o
NK075(bu)003:2027: // de ltar gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa gciga
NK075(bu)003:2028: la'ang dbang po rno rtul gyis phye bas phyi nang
NK075(bu)003:2029: gnyis gsungs pa yin pa dang gnyis po re re
NK075(bu)003:2030: la blo rab 'bring tha ma gsum gyis phye bas
NK075(bu)003:2031: phyi pa la bya ba spyod pa rnal 'byor gsum
NK075(bu)003:2032: // / nang pa la ma h+aa a nu a ti gsum ste drug tu phyes pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:2033: gsum pa gdul bya'i snang ba bsam yas pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:2035: mdo'i dgongs pa ltar bsdus na gzung 'dzin phyin ci log la mos pa'i gdul bya dang /
NK075(bu)003:2036: sogs kyi sgras rnal ma la mos pa'i gdul bya gnyis so //
NK075(bu)003:2037: dang po la rang bzhin gyis log pa phyal rgyang dang /
NK075(bu)003:2039: tha ma grub mthar 'jug pa la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:2040: log pa mu rtug mu stegs dang /
NK075(bu)003:2041: mu stegs la ltos na ma log pa nyan rang ngo //
NK075(bu)003:2042: bye brag tu rgyud kyi dgongs pa ltar phye na /
NK075(bu)003:2043: las rgyu 'bras la sogs pa ci yang ma rtogs
NK075(bu)003:2044: pa ni 'jig rten phyal ba rgyang 'phen te gzhi
NK075(bu)003:2045: don ngo ma shes pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:2047: snang ba dang po las ma gos mod kyang /
NK075(bu)003:2050: log par rtogsa pa ni gzhi'i don snang stong phyogs re las gol ba ste /
NK075(bu)003:2051: mu rtug dang mu stegs gnyis mu stegs la rtag chad gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:2053: mu stegs ni phyogs las gol ba'o //
NK075(bu)003:2055: rags pa gang zag gi bdag phyogs tsam stong par rtogs pa nyan rang /
NK075(bu)003:2056: bden gnyis dbyer med kyi gnas lugs yang dag pa'i
NK075(bu)003:2057: don nyid ma rtogs pa dbu ma dang sems tsam
NK075(bu)003:2058: mo // lus ngag gi spyod pa 'dul ba kri ya dang /
NK075(bu)003:2059: dgongs pa ting nge 'dzin dang spyod pa gnyis ka gtso bor byed pa u pa ya dang /
NK075(bu)003:2060: ting nge 'dzin gtso bo byed pa de nyid rtogs dka' bas gsang ba ste yo ga dang /
NK075(bu)003:2061: bskyed rim gtso bor byed pa'am spyod pa gtso bor byed pa sku'i rgyud ma h+aa yo ga dang /
NK075(bu)003:2062: rdzogs rim gtso bor byed cing don gsal ba'am sgom
NK075(bu)003:2063: pa gtso bor byed pa gsung gi rgyud a nu
NK075(bu)003:2064: yo ga dang / bskyed rdzogs zung 'jug gtso bor
NK075(bu)003:2065: byed pa'am dbyer med kyi lta ba gtso bor byed
NK075(bu)003:2066: pa thugs kyi rgyud a ti yo ga rnams su
NK075(bu)003:2067: snang ba zhes gsang snying las gsungs pas na sangs
NK075(bu)003:2068: rgyas kyi thugs rje skye ba'i yul dang sar ma
NK075(bu)003:2069: gyur pa'i gdul bya ni gang yang med de /
NK075(bu)003:2070: de bas na theg pa so sora gdul bya rang
NK075(bu)003:2071: rang gi blo dang 'tshams par snang ba'i rkyen gyi
NK075(bu)003:2072: thig pa bsam yas pa snang na'ang 'dir da res
NK075(bu)003:2073: ma h+aa'i theg pa bshad pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:2074: gnyis pa theg pa mchog la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:2076: dang po theg mchog rgyud kyi rnam grangs bstan pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:2078: gdul bya shes rab kyi dbang po mchog grol bar
NK075(bu)003:2079: byed pa'i rkyen ma h+aa yo ga'i rgyud ni rnam
NK075(bu)003:2080: pa gsum ste / gang zhe na /
NK075(bu)003:2081: rtsa rlung thig le sems dang bzhi ka yod kyang rlung gtso bor byed pa pha rgyud /
NK075(bu)003:2082: rtsa dang thig le gtso bor ston pa ma rgyud
NK075(bu)003:2083: sems sam ye shes rang snang du ston pa gnyis
NK075(bu)003:2085: de yang gzhi sems can nam gdul bya dang sbyar na /
NK075(bu)003:2087: skyes pa rnams ni gdul ba'i phyir //
NK075(bu)003:2088: rnal 'byor pha yi rgyud ces bshad //
NK075(bu)003:2089: bud med rnams ni gdul ba'i phyir //
NK075(bu)003:2090: rnal 'byor ma yi rgyud ces bshad //
NK075(bu)003:2092: lam rtsa thig rlung gsum dang sbyar na /
NK075(bu)003:2094: rtsa yi de nyid rtogs gyur pa //
NK075(bu)003:2095: de nyid ma yi rgyud ces bya //
NK075(bu)003:2096: rlung gi de nyid rtogs gyur pa //
NK075(bu)003:2097: de nyid rnal 'byor pha yi rgyud //
NK075(bu)003:2099: mthar thug gi 'bras bu'am brjod bya'i gtso bo dang sbyar na /
NK075(bu)003:2100: ma rgyud ye shes mkha' 'gro ma las /
NK075(bu)003:2101: pha rgyud ye shes chen po ste /
NK075(bu)003:2102: ma rgyud stong pa chen po yin /
NK075(bu)003:2105: dpal sangs rgyas 'byung ba la sogs ma ning gi rgyud dang /
NK075(bu)003:2108: thabs dang shes rab ma ning rgyud /
NK075(bu)003:2110: 'dir sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba gsang ba'i snying po ni
NK075(bu)003:2111: gnyis med ma ning lta bu zung 'jug gi rgyud
NK075(bu)003:2112: do // de nyid gtan la phab pa ni 'di lta ste /
NK075(bu)003:2113: gnyis pa de nyid gtan la phab pa ni 'di lta ste /
NK075(bu)003:2114: gnyis pa de nyid gtan la phab tshul bstan pa de la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:2116: dang po lam rkyen gyi rgyud gdul bya'i dbang po'i
NK075(bu)003:2117: bye brag gis phye bas gtan la dbab pa mdor
NK075(bu)003:2119: ston pa rdo rje sems dpa' des gsungs pa'i bstan
NK075(bu)003:2120: pa thugs sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba gsang ba snying po'i
NK075(bu)003:2121: rgyud dbu zhabs kyi spyi don thams cad gcod cing
NK075(bu)003:2123: sngon mdor bstan du bshad pa bzhin snang ba bzhir
NK075(bu)003:2124: bstan pa la gzhi dang grub pa'i snang ba gnyis
NK075(bu)003:2126: 'dir gsum pa gdul bya lam gyi snang ba ni /
NK075(bu)003:2127: lam gyi rkyen 'di yi ge'i rgyud dang sbyar nas gtan la dbab pa la /
NK075(bu)003:2128: gang rung gis 'jug nus pa ma yin te /
NK075(bu)003:2129: las dag pa blo mchog gi skal ba bcud theg mchog ma h+aa dang /
NK075(bu)003:2130: snod gang zag dbang rnon gyi shes rab gnyis la
NK075(bu)003:2131: shes bya shes byed dam snod bcud dam blo dang
NK075(bu)003:2132: theg par 'brel pa'i gzhi ma yod pa'i phyir rgyud
NK075(bu)003:2133: kyi don khong du chud pa yin no //
NK075(bu)003:2134: dbang rnon de la yang dbang po rab 'bring tha
NK075(bu)003:2135: ma gsum gyi blos phye bas gsang ba'i snying po'i
NK075(bu)003:2136: don bshad thabs la thugsa thigsa 'di ltar du rab
NK075(bu)003:2137: la mtshan bstan / 'bring la don rnam par dbye /
NK075(bu)003:2138: tha ma 'bru gnyer ba dang gsum mo //
NK075(bu)003:2140: rab la mtshan bstan 'bring la dbye //
NK075(bu)003:2143: gnyis pa yan lag rgyas par bshad pa de la gsum ste /
NK075(bu)003:2144: rab la mtshan bstan pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:2145: 'bring la don rnam par dbye ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:2146: tha ma lam gyi thob par byed ba shes rgyu 'bru re nas bstan pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:2149: gdul bya'i dbang gis thabs lam grol lam du bstan pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:2155: rab mtshan tha snyad gsum du grags //
NK075(bu)003:2156: sgyu 'phrul snying po lung gi spyi //
NK075(bu)003:2157: lag gi rtsa bzhin dbu zhabs rtogs //
NK075(bu)003:2158: skal ba can gyi ched phyir ro //
NK075(bu)003:2160: dang po dbang po rab la mtshan bstan pa tsam
NK075(bu)003:2161: gyis don mtshon pa'i gsang ba'i snying po la ming
NK075(bu)003:2162: gi 'dogs lugs gsum dang ldan no //
NK075(bu)003:2163: gnyis pa bshad pa de la gsum ste /
NK075(bu)003:2165: dang po rgyud dang ston pa'i mtshan thun mong du bstan pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:2167: theg 'og ni drang lung yin la /
NK075(bu)003:2168: 'dir nges pa'i lung ni gsang sngags yin te /
NK075(bu)003:2169: de yang chos thams cad snang bzhin ngo bo rang
NK075(bu)003:2170: rgyud du ma grub pas sgyu ma dang 'dra ba'i
NK075(bu)003:2171: phyir don shes rab rang bzhin med brtags lha yum
NK075(bu)003:2172: / de nyid 'khor 'das kyi dngos po gnyis su
NK075(bu)003:2173: shar ba la rig pa dang snang ba'i rtsal du
NK075(bu)003:2174: legsa par snang ba ni 'phrul te /
NK075(bu)003:2175: don med la cir yang 'char ba 'gag pa med pa ste rtags lha yab /
NK075(bu)003:2176: de ltar kun rdzob don dam gyi bden pa gnyis
NK075(bu)003:2177: po'i don d+r+wa ba ltar 'brel bas na thabs shes
NK075(bu)003:2179: rtags lha yab yum 'khril sbyor ro //
NK075(bu)003:2180: de nyid rang bzhin gnyis su med cing mtshan nyid
NK075(bu)003:2181: 'dus ma byas shing skye 'jigs dang bral bas na
NK075(bu)003:2182: rdo rje / dbyer med kyi don de sgrib g.yogs med par gsal bas na sems /
NK075(bu)003:2183: de nyid brtan cing tshur la dngos po gang gis
NK075(bu)003:2184: kyang mi tshugs shing phar la thams cad 'joms pas
NK075(bu)003:2185: na dpa' bo / ston pa des bstan pa thugs
NK075(bu)003:2186: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i byed las kyi rim pa sna
NK075(bu)003:2187: tshogs gsungs pas lha yi ming la rdo rje sems
NK075(bu)003:2188: na dpa' bo / dpa' zhes bya'o // gnyis pa che ba'i mtshan dang /
NK075(bu)003:2190: ston pa'i dgongs pa de ni bstan pa tha dag 'byung ba'i rgyu dang /
NK075(bu)003:2191: 'bras bu'i dngos gzhi yin pas na /
NK075(bu)003:2192: theg pa kun gyi spyi lung du nges pas na
NK075(bu)003:2193: bstan pas dang ston pa'i mtshan thun mong du bstan
NK075(bu)003:2194: pa song nas / gnyis pa che ba'i mtshan yin te /
NK075(bu)003:2196: sa rnams khyad par bkod pa yang //
NK075(bu)003:2197: gsang ba'i snying po 'gro ba'i lam //
NK075(bu)003:2200: 'dul ba mdo sde chos mngon dang //
NK075(bu)003:2204: gsum pa don rang gi ngo bo'i mtshan no //
NK075(bu)003:2206: gzhan la snang stong phyogs re'i sgo nas bstan par
NK075(bu)003:2207: dka' zhing rang gis kyang brtag par dka' bas na
NK075(bu)003:2208: gsang ba'i man ngag ces bya ste /
NK075(bu)003:2209: de yang rang bzhin gyi gsang ba bzhi yis chod pa yin te /
NK075(bu)003:2212: e ma'o ye nas gsang ba'i chos //
NK075(bu)003:2213: sna tshogs snang la rang bzhin gsang //
NK075(bu)003:2214: ngo bo nyid kyis rab tu gsang //
NK075(bu)003:2215: gzhan du min la shin tu gsang //
NK075(bu)003:2217: dang po ye nas gsang ba ni /
NK075(bu)003:2218: ye nas 'khor 'das gnyis su med pa'i rig pa
NK075(bu)003:2219: rang byung gi ye shes la che ba'i yon tan
NK075(bu)003:2220: thams cad lhun gyis grub pa'i don de rang la
NK075(bu)003:2221: rang chas su yod kyang ngo ma shes te /
NK075(bu)003:2222: gang gis ma shes na lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pas ngo ma shes te /
NK075(bu)003:2224: gnyis su med pa'i rang byung gi ye shes la
NK075(bu)003:2225: yon tan ril lhun gyis grub pa de rang chas
NK075(bu)003:2226: su yod kyang ngo ma shes pa kho na la
NK075(bu)003:2228: gnyis pa rang bzhin gyi gsang ba ni /
NK075(bu)003:2229: de nyid rang snang ba'i 'bras bu sku dang ye
NK075(bu)003:2230: shes kyi dkyil 'khor rang bzhin gyis gnas kyang ngo
NK075(bu)003:2231: ma shes te / gang gis ma shes na kun
NK075(bu)003:2232: tu brtags pa'i ma rig pas rang snang la mtshan
NK075(bu)003:2233: ma shes te / mar bzung nas / phyin ci log tu 'khrul pas gsang ngo //
NK075(bu)003:2235: de nyid rang snang ba'i dngos po ril mi zad
NK075(bu)003:2236: pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo rang rgyud du gnas pa
NK075(bu)003:2239: gsum pa ngo bo nyid kyi gsang ba ni /
NK075(bu)003:2240: rgyu 'bras dbyer med kyi bden pa rang chas su gnas kyang ngo ma shes te /
NK075(bu)003:2241: gang gis ma shes na snang stong tha dad du bzung bas so //
NK075(bu)003:2243: rang bzhin gyi rgyud kyi ngo bo nyid yul sems
NK075(bu)003:2244: dang rgyu 'bras dang bden pa gnyis las grol ba
NK075(bu)003:2245: ste / rang snang ba'i phyir rang gi ngo bo nyid yul du byar ma dmigs pa kho na'o //
NK075(bu)003:2247: bzhi pa shin tu gsang ba ni /
NK075(bu)003:2248: dbyer med dang bral ba'i don ye nas rang chas su gnas kyang ngo ma shes pa ste /
NK075(bu)003:2249: gang gis ma shes na yul yul can du bzung bas gsang ste /
NK075(bu)003:2251: 'bras pa'i rgyud bsgrub par bya ba de gud na med kyang /
NK075(bu)003:2254: lta ba'i sgrib pas gzhan du tshol yang /
NK075(bu)003:2255: rang rig pa la mi snang ba kho na'o //
NK075(bu)003:2257: rgyud dbus zhabs kyi don gyi bcud 'dus pas na snying po ste /
NK075(bu)003:2259: dang po rgyu'i snying po ni /
NK075(bu)003:2260: gdul bya las tha ma'i don du rgyud pa 'di bstan pa'i byin brlabs kyis /
NK075(bu)003:2261: go phye nas bstan pa thams cad 'byung ba yin te /
NK075(bu)003:2263: 'dul ba mdo sde chos mngon dang //
NK075(bu)003:2264: dam tshig bsgrub dang sgrub pa dang //
NK075(bu)003:2265: sku dang gsung dang thugs kyi rgyud //
NK075(bu)003:2266: phyogs bcu kun tu rab grags pa //
NK075(bu)003:2267: gsang ba'i snying po las 'phros te //
NK075(bu)003:2268: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po 'di //
NK075(bu)003:2269: sde snod kun dang rgyud kun gyi //
NK075(bu)003:2272: gnyis pa 'bras bu'i snying po ni /
NK075(bu)003:2273: theg pa'i sgo kun nas bsgrub pa'i mthar thug pa
NK075(bu)003:2274: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po 'di nyid mngon tu
NK075(bu)003:2276: de nyid kyi tha ma las /
NK075(bu)003:2277: sa rnams khyad par bkod pa yang //
NK075(bu)003:2278: gsang ba'i snying po 'gro ba'i lam //
NK075(bu)003:2281: theg pa bzhi yis nges 'byung la //
NK075(bu)003:2282: theg pa gcig gi 'bras bur gnas //
NK075(bu)003:2284: gsum pa bcud 'dus pa don gyi snying po ni /
NK075(bu)003:2285: gtan tshigs kyis sgo gang nas smal yang mthar thug
NK075(bu)003:2286: de bzhin gshegs pa'i spyod yul rtog tshogs thams cad
NK075(bu)003:2287: sku dang ye shes bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi dkyil
NK075(bu)003:2288: 'khor du sangs rgyas pas 'khor ba kar dag pa
NK075(bu)003:2290: don bsdus gsung rab bzhi bcu gnyis //
NK075(bu)003:2291: de las lhag pa'i don smra ba //
NK075(bu)003:2292: de ni rnam dag lam min te //
NK075(bu)003:2293: rang blo bsam pas 'khrul pa yin //
NK075(bu)003:2295: gsang snying gi bcu gsum pa las /
NK075(bu)003:2296: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad la //
NK075(bu)003:2297: gsang ba 'di las gzhan mi mnga' //
NK075(bu)003:2299: de kho na nyid kyi don ni /
NK075(bu)003:2301: rgyu 'bras gnyis su med pa yi //
NK075(bu)003:2302: de nyid ngo bo skabs kyis gsum //
NK075(bu)003:2304: dang po ma bcos pa'i de kho na nyid ni /
NK075(bu)003:2305: rtog tshogs thams cad rang rig pa las mi gzhan pa'i phyir /
NK075(bu)003:2306: snang stong gnyis su med pa'i ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor la blo ma bcos par bzhag pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:2307: de la skabs kyis rgyu'i de kho na nyid ces kyang tha snyad du 'dogs so //
NK075(bu)003:2308: gnyis pa ma nor ba'i de kho na nyid ni /
NK075(bu)003:2309: de nyid sku dang ye shes kyi phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor mang por mngon sum du snang ba'o //
NK075(bu)003:2310: de la 'bras bu'i tha snyad du 'dogs so //
NK075(bu)003:2311: gsum pa gzhan ma yin pa'i de kho na nyid ni /
NK075(bu)003:2312: rgyu 'bras gnyis la snga phyi bzang ngan tha dad med pa yin no //
NK075(bu)003:2313: de la rgyu 'bras gnyis su med pa'i tha snyad
NK075(bu)003:2314: du 'dogs pas de kho na nyid gsum dang ldan
NK075(bu)003:2315: pa'o // de nyid bden pa gsum dbyer med pa'i phyir nges pa ste /
NK075(bu)003:2317: gzhi dang lam dang 'bras bu yis //
NK075(bu)003:2318: nges pa rnam pa gsum du bshad //
NK075(bu)003:2320: dang po gzhir nges pa ni /
NK075(bu)003:2321: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po ste /
NK075(bu)003:2322: rang bzhin gyi sgro skur dang bral bar nges pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:2323: de 'dir nges par ston pa'i phyir ro //
NK075(bu)003:2324: de yang rgyud kyi tha ma las /
NK075(bu)003:2325: sgro dang skur pa zhi ba yin //
NK075(bu)003:2326: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na //
NK075(bu)003:2327: nyid de nges pa'i dbyings nas phyung //
NK075(bu)003:2329: gnyis pa lam du nges pa ni /
NK075(bu)003:2330: rgyud 'di nyid kyi lugs la 'bras bu nyid la nges pa'i lam du byed pa'i phyir te /
NK075(bu)003:2331: 'di nyid kyi bcu gsum pa las /
NK075(bu)003:2332: 'di ni gsang chen nges pa yi //
NK075(bu)003:2333: 'bras bu lam du gyur pa yin //
NK075(bu)003:2336: 'bras bu lam du gyur nas dus gcig mnyam par sbyor /
NK075(bu)003:2338: gsum pa 'bras bur nges pa ni /
NK075(bu)003:2339: rgyud 'di'i rang gi ngo bos de bzhin gshegs pa'i dgongs pa mngon du ston pa'i phyir te /
NK075(bu)003:2341: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus la //
NK075(bu)003:2342: 'di las gsang ba'i nges don med //
NK075(bu)003:2344: de lta bu'i don mtshon byed kyi ming gis mtshon bya'i don mtshon pa la /
NK075(bu)003:2345: gang gi bstan pa dang ston pa'i mtshan dang /
NK075(bu)003:2346: che ba'i mtshan gnyis kyis don phyogs re las mi mtshon la /
NK075(bu)003:2347: 'di ni de gnyis las lhag pa ste snang ba
NK075(bu)003:2348: bzhi gzhi lam 'bras gsum la sogs pa phyogs med
NK075(bu)003:2349: thams cad gtan la dbab pa'i don mtshon pa'i phyir
NK075(bu)003:2350: lhag pa'o // yang mtshan 'dogs lugs la /
NK075(bu)003:2356: 'dir ni don rang gi ngo bo'i mtshan yin pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:2359: blo 'bring dang tha ma ltar gzhung tshig rgyas pa'i
NK075(bu)003:2360: sa bcad 'bru gnur gyis kyang blo rab la don
NK075(bu)003:2361: mtshon nas khong du chud mi nus te tshig mthas
NK075(bu)003:2363: dper na sman pa 'tsho byed gzhon nus lus mgo
NK075(bu)003:2364: mjug gi nad thams cad lag ngar gyi rtsa gcig
NK075(bu)003:2365: pu'i nang du rtog pa bzhin du blo rab la
NK075(bu)003:2366: yi ge bsdus pa mtshan don tsam gyis rgyud dbu
NK075(bu)003:2367: zhabs kyi don rgyas par bshad cing brda 'phrad pa
NK075(bu)003:2368: de bas na tha snyad kyi tshig rnams ni 'dir
NK075(bu)003:2370: gnyis pa gdul bya'i dbang gis thabs lam grol lam du bstan pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:2373: gsum pa don rang gi ngo bo'i ming gis don
NK075(bu)003:2374: mtshon pa la gdul bya mos pa'i blo so sor
NK075(bu)003:2376: shes rab can la grol lam phyi ltar bshad pa ni gong du song nas /
NK075(bu)003:2377: chags pa can la thabs lam dang sbyar nas bshad de /
NK075(bu)003:2378: de yang steng sgo dang sbyar te nang ltar bshad pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:2379: 'og sgo dang sbyar te gsang ba ltar bshad pa dang gnyis ni gzhan du shes so //
NK075(bu)003:2380: gnyis pa 'bring la don rnam par dbye ba la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:2382: dang po dpe don gyis blo 'bring gi lam bgrod tshul spyir bstan pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:2384: rin po che la dang po nas 'od yod kyang
NK075(bu)003:2385: nyi ma'i 'od phog pas sngar bas mdzes pa'i 'od
NK075(bu)003:2386: dang ldan zhing rin chen cher gsal ba ltar /
NK075(bu)003:2387: tshig gi rnam par dbye ba ni sgron ma dang 'dra bas blo'i shes rab phye bas /
NK075(bu)003:2388: dbang po 'bring gi shes bya gsang ba'i snying po la snang ba mched par bya ba'i phyir /
NK075(bu)003:2389: rnam dbye 'di nyid mtshan bstan la ltos na rgyas
NK075(bu)003:2390: pa'i tshig don gyi bye brag 'bru gnyer la ltos
NK075(bu)003:2391: na nyung ste thigs par shar ba tsam las min
NK075(bu)003:2392: / de nyid kyi snod ni rang bzhin gyi dbang
NK075(bu)003:2393: rnon dang nas ma h+aa yo gar 'jug pa dang
NK075(bu)003:2394: / / theg 'og las rim gyis sbyangs rnon mthar
NK075(bu)003:2395: ma h+aa'i snod du gyur nas 'jug pa yin te
NK075(bu)003:2396: / / / de nas lam bgroda pa'i thabs la
NK075(bu)003:2397: rim dang cig char gnyis su bshad cing de'i yan
NK075(bu)003:2398: lag gi cha rkyen la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:2400: de rkyen yan lag rnam gnyis te //
NK075(bu)003:2401: shes byed rkyen dang sgrub byed rkyen //
NK075(bu)003:2403: shes bya lam gyi cha rkyen dang /
NK075(bu)003:2404: bsgrub bya lam gyi cha rkyen gnyis ni 'di lta ste /
NK075(bu)003:2405: gnyis pa bye brag rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:2407: dang po mdor bstan pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:2409: 'di la 'bru'i 'dug sa bsgyur nas don gyi go rim bsdeb dgos te /
NK075(bu)003:2410: dang po shes bya lam gyi yan lag ni /
NK075(bu)003:2411: thog mar shes par bya ba'i yul lnga dang /
NK075(bu)003:2412: bar du thun mong dang mchog gi lam gnyis nyams su blang ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:2413: tha ma thabs grol gnyis la brtan pa thob ba'i
NK075(bu)003:2414: drod tshad rtags dang ldan pas 'bras bu mthong lam
NK075(bu)003:2416: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa de la gsum ste /
NK075(bu)003:2417: thog mar shes par bya ba'i yul lnga dang /
NK075(bu)003:2418: bar du thun mong du mchog gi lam nyams su blang ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:2419: tha ma tshogs sgrub la drod tshad rtags tshad rtags
NK075(bu)003:2420: dang ldan nas 'bras bu mthong lam la sbyor ba'o
NK075(bu)003:2425: dang po shes par bya ba'i yul la lnga ste /
NK075(bu)003:2429: bshad thabs 'dren pa'i tshig gi dpe bcu dang rgyud
NK075(bu)003:2430: gdams shing gtad pa dang lngas rgyud shes thabs kyi
NK075(bu)003:2431: yan lag de rdzogsa pa yina no //
NK075(bu)003:2432: gnyis pa de la lnga ste /
NK075(bu)003:2442: thabs lam gyi rgyu gleng gzhi dang /
NK075(bu)003:2443: shes rab grol lam gyi rgyu gleng gzhi'i don yang rgyas par bstan pa ni 'di lta ste /
NK075(bu)003:2444: gnyis pa bshad pa de la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:2446: dang po thabs lam gyi gleng gzhi dang /
NK075(bu)003:2448: mdor bstan gyi snga ma thabs lam bstan pa'i gleng gzhi ni /
NK075(bu)003:2449: ston pa phun sum tshogs pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:2454: bstan pa phun sum tshogs pa dang drug go //
NK075(bu)003:2456: steng sgo snying kha chos kyi 'khor lo ni yon
NK075(bu)003:2457: tan thams cad kyi 'byung khungs yin pas rin po
NK075(bu)003:2458: che'am / rin chen zur brgyad dang 'dra ba rtsa brgyad 'dus pa'i sgrom dkyil 'khor /
NK075(bu)003:2459: 'og sgo'i gnas ni bde stong gnyis med kyi ye
NK075(bu)003:2460: shes de yo ga man chad kyis mi shes pas
NK075(bu)003:2461: gsang ba'i don de shes bya gang gi 'og tu
NK075(bu)003:2462: song ba min pa ni yum gyi mkha'o //
NK075(bu)003:2463: gnas de gnyis kyis phye bas ston 'khor phun sum
NK075(bu)003:2464: tshogs pa de yi ge e wam ma ya bzhi
NK075(bu)003:2465: yi sgo nas bsgrub ste shes par bya ba ni
NK075(bu)003:2466: / gsang ba bla na med pa'i theg pa sgyu 'phrul rgya mtsho'i rgyud dang /
NK075(bu)003:2467: thal ba'i rgyud kyi lung tshad ma gnyis dang sbrel nas gtan la phab dgos te /
NK075(bu)003:2468: de yang thabs lam steng 'og gi gleng gzhi gnyis las /
NK075(bu)003:2469: dang po rgya mtsho dang sbyar nas nang ltar thabs lam steng sgo ltar bshad na /
NK075(bu)003:2470: 'di zhes pa gnas phun sum tshogs pa ste /
NK075(bu)003:2473: 'og gzhi e sogs dbyibs su gnas //
NK075(bu)003:2475: d+harma tsakra ni chos kyi 'khor lo ste /
NK075(bu)003:2476: snying kha chos kyi 'khor lo don dam 'od gsal gyi gnas te /
NK075(bu)003:2479: las bzhi'i kha dog dang dbyibs su gnas te /
NK075(bu)003:2480: de la g.yas chos nyid kyi rtsa zlum po dkar po zhi ba'i gnas /
NK075(bu)003:2481: rgyab ye shes kyi rtsa gru bzhi ser po rgyas pa'i gnas /
NK075(bu)003:2482: g.yon yon tan gyi rtsa zla gam dmar po dbang gi gnas /
NK075(bu)003:2483: mdun las rang rgyud kyi rtsa dbyibs gru gsum 'od dmar nag drag po'i gnas so //
NK075(bu)003:2484: de ltar las bzhi'i 'od dbyibs su gnas pa de la gnas phun sum tshogs pa zhes bya'o //
NK075(bu)003:2485: skad ces pa ston pa phun sum tshogs pa ste /
NK075(bu)003:2487: mi shig thig le wam gyi dbyibs can /
NK075(bu)003:2488: rang la bde ba gsal byed dag /
NK075(bu)003:2490: srog mi shigs pa'i thig le dwangs ma lnga 'dus
NK075(bu)003:2491: kyi ngo bo dbyibs zlum po yi ge wam gyi
NK075(bu)003:2492: dbyibs can de mar me rang gis rang gsal bar
NK075(bu)003:2493: byed pa ltar / thig le de nyid rang gis
NK075(bu)003:2494: rang la bde ba gsal bar ston pa'i phyir ston
NK075(bu)003:2496: bshad ces pa 'khor phun sum tshogs pa ste /
NK075(bu)003:2497: de nyid las ma nu rnam shes yid sogs bzhi /
NK075(bu)003:2498: ye shes myong ba sdud par bshad //
NK075(bu)003:2500: yid shes la sogs pa'i sems rnam par shes pa
NK075(bu)003:2501: tshogs brgyad bde ba'i ye shes lngar gsal bar nyams
NK075(bu)003:2502: su myong bas bshad pa dang 'dra bas 'khor ro
NK075(bu)003:2503: // sdud pa po ni yid kyi shes pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:2504: pa'i zhes pa bstan pa phun sum tshogs pa ste /
NK075(bu)003:2506: ye shes nam mkha'i gzugs skyes pa //
NK075(bu)003:2507: pa ra m+aar+tha don zab mo //
NK075(bu)003:2509: pa ra m+aar+tha'i sgra las drangs na don dam pa byang chub kyi sems so //
NK075(bu)003:2510: y+aa na ni theg pa chen po ste /
NK075(bu)003:2511: bde gsal mi rtog pa'i ye shes nam mkha'i gzugs ltar skyes pa ni don zab mo ste /
NK075(bu)003:2512: bstan pa phun sum tshogs pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:2513: dus na zhes pa dus phun sum tshogs pa ste /
NK075(bu)003:2515: bde ba'i dus nyid snga phyi bral //
NK075(bu)003:2516: dus gsum kun gyi ngo bor gnas //
NK075(bu)003:2518: bde ba'i ye shes skyes pa'i dus su dus gsum
NK075(bu)003:2519: tha dad du 'dzin pa med cing mnyam pa nyid
NK075(bu)003:2520: du gyur pa ni dus so //
NK075(bu)003:2521: gnyis pa sgyu 'phrul thal pa'i rgyud dang sbyar te thabs lam 'og sgo ltar bshad pa ni /
NK075(bu)003:2522: sam skri ta'i skad du e wam ma ya /
NK075(bu)003:2523: bod skad du 'di skad bshad pa'i dus na zhes bya ste /
NK075(bu)003:2524: de yang 'di zhes pa gnas phun sum tshogs pa ste /
NK075(bu)003:2526: 'di zhes nye bar mtshon pa ni //
NK075(bu)003:2527: e sogs rnam bzhi'i dbyibs can gnas //
NK075(bu)003:2529: de la nye bar mtshan pa ni gnas te /
NK075(bu)003:2530: yum gyi mkha' phyi khyams gru gsum drag po'i gnas /
NK075(bu)003:2531: bar khyams gru bzhi rgyas pa'i /
NK075(bu)003:2532: skye gnas zla gam dbang gi /
NK075(bu)003:2533: dbyings phyug gi sna rtse zlum po zhi ba'i gnas so //
NK075(bu)003:2534: de na dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas gsang ba'i sku thams cad kyi bzhugs pa'i gnas su gsungs so //
NK075(bu)003:2535: skad ces pa ston pa phun sum tshogs pa ste /
NK075(bu)003:2537: skad ces pa gsal byed las ming can /
NK075(bu)003:2538: wam dbyibs thig le bcas ston pa /
NK075(bu)003:2540: yab yum rol pa'i dus na /
NK075(bu)003:2541: yab kyi gsang ba rdo rje'i dbu la rtsa sa
NK075(bu)003:2542: ya phrag bcu gsum gyi bcud 'dus pa'i kun rdzob
NK075(bu)003:2543: ye shes kyi thig le wa gyi dbyibs su rdzogs
NK075(bu)003:2544: pas / rtogs ma rtogs kyi dbang gis 'khor 'das
NK075(bu)003:2545: gnyis kyi byed pa so so'i phyir ston pa yin
NK075(bu)003:2546: pas / te / skabs 'dir bde ba ma lus
NK075(bu)003:2547: pa'i sku dang ye shes rdzogs par byed pa'i phyir
NK075(bu)003:2548: pas / te / ston pa'o // bshad ces pa 'khor phun sum tshogs pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:2550: ma da ma nu sdom byed yin //
NK075(bu)003:2551: las can rnam shes de dag la //
NK075(bu)003:2552: gsal bar go bas bshad par 'dod //
NK075(bu)003:2556: nyon yid la sogs pa'i rnam par shes pa tshogs
NK075(bu)003:2557: brgyad la sogs sku dang ye shes kyi ngo bor
NK075(bu)003:2558: rdo rje mthong ba la sogs pas phyin ci ma
NK075(bu)003:2560: 'khor la bshad de go bar tha snyad du 'dogs so //
NK075(bu)003:2561: pa'i zhes pa bstan pa phun sum tshogs pa ste /
NK075(bu)003:2563: pa sgra don dam nges pa'i rgyud //
NK075(bu)003:2564: y+aa na theg chen 'di yin te //
NK075(bu)003:2566: pa ra m+aar+tha na don dam pa zab mo'i /
NK075(bu)003:2567: y+aa na ni theg pa chen po /
NK075(bu)003:2568: dga' ba bcu drug gi mtha' mar rang bzhin lhan
NK075(bu)003:2569: cig skyes pa'i ye shes lhangs kyis nyams su myong
NK075(bu)003:2570: ba ni / rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po'i don yin te /
NK075(bu)003:2572: dus zhes pa dus phun sum tshogs pa ste /
NK075(bu)003:2574: dus ni bsam gyis mi khyab dus //
NK075(bu)003:2576: de nyid mngon du gyur pa'i dus su phyogs gcig
NK075(bu)003:2577: tu brjod du med pas bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i
NK075(bu)003:2578: dus so // na zhes pa zhes bya ba ste /
NK075(bu)003:2580: n+aa ma de ming zhes gsungs so //
NK075(bu)003:2581: zhes pas kun la 'jug pa ste /
NK075(bu)003:2587: de dag thun mong ma yin pa'i gleng gzhir 'jog pa'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK075(bu)003:2588: gdul bya las tha ma pa rnams te /
NK075(bu)003:2590: kun tu 'od rnams kyi phyir te /
NK075(bu)003:2592: de ni gdul bya las tha ma pa rnams kyi
NK075(bu)003:2593: don gyi phyir thun mong ma yin pa'i gleng gazhi'o
NK075(bu)003:2597: 'gro ba chags chen spang med pa'i //
NK075(bu)003:2598: longs spyod rdzogs sku btsun mo dang //
NK075(bu)003:2599: gnyis med rol sogs bstan pa ste //
NK075(bu)003:2600: mthun pas mthun par grol ba'i phyir ro //
NK075(bu)003:2601: skye bo chags sogs yongs 'dul ba //
NK075(bu)003:2603: gnyis pa shes rab grol lam gyi gleng gzhi de la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:2607: blo gros te shes rab grol lam gyi rgyu gleng gzhi la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:2608: theg 'og dang mthun mong gzugs sku rtags kyi gleng gzhi dang /
NK075(bu)003:2609: mchog ste khyad par chos sku don gyi gleng gazhi'o //
NK075(bu)003:2610: gnyis pa bshad pa de la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:2612: dang po khyad par don gyi gleng gzhi dang /
NK075(bu)003:2614: shes bya kun gyi blar gyur cing yon tan thams cad kyi 'byung khungs su gyur pas na ma /
NK075(bu)003:2615: de'ang rang gi sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes chen po de /
NK075(bu)003:2616: gdod ma nas rang la gnas pa'i gzhi don rtogs pa'i cha nas gnas phun sum tshogs pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:2617: de nyid byed las kyi sna tshogs su 'char ba ni ston pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:2618: de la ye shes kyi bye brag lnga'am bzhi bcu
NK075(bu)003:2619: rtsa gnyis la sogs pa mang pora shar ba ni
NK075(bu)003:2620: 'khor / de ltar mang por shar yang ye shes
NK075(bu)003:2621: thams cad dbyer med pa'i bdag nyid rang byung gi
NK075(bu)003:2623: bstan pa'i ngo bo ni thams cad kyi bcud thugs
NK075(bu)003:2624: rang byung gi ye shes su bsdus pa'i dngos po
NK075(bu)003:2625: de bstan pa'o // chos thams cad yongs rdzogs la
NK075(bu)003:2626: ma g.yos bzhin du shes bya ma 'dres par bkra
NK075(bu)003:2628: sgro skur gyi mtha' dang bral bas lung la dus bzhi mnyam pa ni dus phun sum tshogs pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:2629: 'khor de la khyad par chos sku'i gleng gzhi de
NK075(bu)003:2630: gnas nas yod pa de mthar mngon sum du rtogs
NK075(bu)003:2632: de'i don ni gsang snying le'u dang po'i bsdu ba'i don dang mthun pa yin te /
NK075(bu)003:2634: gnas kyang nga la ston pa nga //
NK075(bu)003:2635: 'khor kyang nga la dus kyang nga //
NK075(bu)003:2638: rang rig pa nyid kyi khyad par du snang ba la ngom pa gsum mo //
NK075(bu)003:2640: gnyis pa thun mong rtags kyi gleng gzhi de la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:2644: theg 'og gi gdul bya dang thun mong du gyur
NK075(bu)003:2645: pa la mdo sngags kyi gzugs sku rtags kyi gleng
NK075(bu)003:2647: gdul bya lugs 'byung zlog gis phye bas mtshan mi
NK075(bu)003:2648: 'dra ba gnyis kyi gzugs su shar nas snang ba'o
NK075(bu)003:2649: // gnyis pa bshad pa de la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:2651: khro bo gang mos su snang ba'o //
NK075(bu)003:2656: ston pa'i rnam grangs ni rgyu rkyen dang bral bas
NK075(bu)003:2657: don rang byung gi ye shes kyi rtags su rigs
NK075(bu)003:2658: lnga dbyer mi phyed pas rdo rje ste /
NK075(bu)003:2659: drug pa rdo rje 'chang chen kyang phyag dang pos rdo rje 'dzin pa ste /
NK075(bu)003:2661: ye shes rgya mtsho 'og min gyi //
NK075(bu)003:2663: bdag po kun bzang 'khor lo bskor //
NK075(bu)003:2664: bka' sdod skyes bu mdun na gnas //
NK075(bu)003:2665: brjod pa med bzhin go bar mdzad //
NK075(bu)003:2666: dpag med ye shes yongs rdzogs pas //
NK075(bu)003:2667: zhing 'khor longs spyod phun sum ldan //
NK075(bu)003:2669: ston pa de'i rgyal tshab 'dzin cing sku gsung thugs
NK075(bu)003:2670: yon tan 'phrin las kyi rgyud sna tshogs ston pa
NK075(bu)003:2671: ni 'chad pa'i skyes bu rigs lnga dang /
NK075(bu)003:2672: byin rlabs kyi ston pa sdud pa po dang gnyis so //
NK075(bu)003:2673: bye brag tu sa nang tshigs su bcad na gnyis las /
NK075(bu)003:2674: dang po ston pa'i rang bzhin ni 'das ma 'ongs
NK075(bu)003:2675: da lta dus gsum gyi chos lasa gud du min
NK075(bu)003:2676: te 'khor 'das dbyer med pa'i rang bzhin no //
NK075(bu)003:2678: bcom ldan 'das zhes pa nas rdo rje'i bdag nyid
NK075(bu)003:2679: ces pa'i bar myang 'das dang dbyer med ston la
NK075(bu)003:2681: dbyer med pa'i rang bzhin te zhes pa'i bar ston pa 'khor ba dang dbyer med ston no //
NK075(bu)003:2682: gnyis pa ston pa'i ngo bo ni chags rtogs ma
NK075(bu)003:2683: spangs bde stong gi ye shes su rdzogs pa'i rtags
NK075(bu)003:2684: su longas spyod rdzogsa pa chena po'i sku don rang
NK075(bu)003:2685: byung gi ye shes kho na nyid yin pa'i phyir
NK075(bu)003:2686: rtags su sku mdun rgyab med pa kun tu zhal
NK075(bu)003:2688: gdul bya rang rang gang la mos pa'i snang ngor
NK075(bu)003:2689: theg pa sna tshogs kyi ston pa longs sprul bsam
NK075(bu)003:2690: gyis mi khyab pa ston pa'i mtshan gyi rnam grangs
NK075(bu)003:2691: rdul snyed du grags pa la /
NK075(bu)003:2692: 'dir sku gsung thugs bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i rnam thar gsum dang ldan pa'i rtags su dbu gsum /
NK075(bu)003:2693: ye shes drug mtshon pa'i rtags su phyag drug /
NK075(bu)003:2694: dgongs pa mnyam pa nyid las ma g.yos pa'i rtags
NK075(bu)003:2695: su phyag mnyam par bzhag cing longs spyod rdzogs sku'i
NK075(bu)003:2696: mtshan phyi nang gsang gsum dang ldan zhing gzhan don
NK075(bu)003:2697: du brda'i sgo nas chos ston par mdzad pa /
NK075(bu)003:2698: yab kyi zhabs mthil gnyis barla'i steng du byas shing
NK075(bu)003:2699: sor mo rnams rdo rje'i rwa'i tshul du byas pa
NK075(bu)003:2700: ni rdo rje skyil krung dang /
NK075(bu)003:2701: de la yum gyi zhabs gnyis kyis 'khyud de nyon
NK075(bu)003:2702: mongs pa brtul zhing bde ba chen po'i ye shes
NK075(bu)003:2703: kyi ngang du zhugs pas brtul zhugs dang /
NK075(bu)003:2704: yab yum gyi mkha' gsang rdo rje dang pad+mo'i rtse
NK075(bu)003:2705: mo'i rtsa gnyis sprad pa'i bde stong gi ye shes
NK075(bu)003:2706: la / rgyu 'bras kyi chos thams cad kyi yon
NK075(bu)003:2707: tan mnyam par rdzogs pa'i phyir mnyam pa dang rdzogs
NK075(bu)003:2708: pa'i ming bzhi dang ldan pa'i skyil mo krung gis
NK075(bu)003:2711: sku mdun dang rgyab med pa zhes pa nas dbu
NK075(bu)003:2712: gsum dang ldan pa zhes pa'i bar gyi don no
NK075(bu)003:2715: ston pa de yi rten pa'i gnas la gnyis las /
NK075(bu)003:2716: dang po gnas kyi rang bzhin gzhi //
NK075(bu)003:2717: de'i shugs la 'og min gyi rnam grangs bdun yang 'chad de /
NK075(bu)003:2718: de yang rgyas pa'i thugs rang rig pa'i ye shes
NK075(bu)003:2719: kyi gong gang gis kyang mchod pa ni rig pa'i
NK075(bu)003:2720: 'og min dang / don chos nyid kyi gong gis kyang chod pa ni don gyi dang /
NK075(bu)003:2721: lha rtog dbyer med kyi gong gang gis kyang ma chod pa ni rtog pa'i dang /
NK075(bu)003:2722: yab yum gyi mkha' gsang la bde ba skye ba'i
NK075(bu)003:2723: gong gang gis kyang ma chod pa ni gsang ba'i
NK075(bu)003:2724: dang / yod min med min gyi skye mched ni bgrangs pa'i dang /
NK075(bu)003:2725: gzugs khams kun gyi gong na gnas pa ni 'jig rten gnas kyi 'og min dang drug go //
NK075(bu)003:2726: de la 'dir 'jig rten gnas kyi 'og min de las gnyis 'gyur gyis dpags pa ste /
NK075(bu)003:2727: dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas kun gyi bzhugs gnas su
NK075(bu)003:2728: grags pa chos nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyingsa kyi
NK075(bu)003:2729: gong gang gis ma chod pa /
NK075(bu)003:2730: ma spangs rgyan rdzogs kyi gzhal yas khang longs spyod
NK075(bu)003:2731: chen po'o 'og min de nyid sangs rgyas kho na'i
NK075(bu)003:2733: lam pa'i spyod yul du gyur pa min pas na gsang ba'i gnas yin te /
NK075(bu)003:2735: 'og min gyi gnas mtha' dang dbus med pa na /
NK075(bu)003:2737: de na ston pa gang bzhugs she na /
NK075(bu)003:2740: gtsang ma'i rigs dag spangs pa yi //
NK075(bu)003:2741: 'og min chen po'i gnas mchog na //
NK075(bu)003:2742: rig bdag phyag rgya lhun grub sku //
NK075(bu)003:2743: gcig dang du ma rnam spangs pa'i //
NK075(bu)003:2744: sangs rgyas kun gyi spyi gzugs te //
NK075(bu)003:2745: gdod nas theg mchog mdzod nyid phyir //
NK075(bu)003:2746: sgrib pa mtha' spangs gdul bya la //
NK075(bu)003:2747: skad cig gcig gis snang bar mdzad //
NK075(bu)003:2749: gnyis pa gnas kyi ngo bo ni /
NK075(bu)003:2750: lha'i sku dang lhan cig tu 'dus pa'i gzhal yas
NK075(bu)003:2751: khang de'i rgyu ni ye shes nyid dbyibs kha dog
NK075(bu)003:2753: de'ang gdul bya'i dgos 'dod skong ba don yin la /
NK075(bu)003:2754: rtags rin po che 'od 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang /
NK075(bu)003:2755: 'khor ba'i chos thams cad ma spangs par 'bras bu'i
NK075(bu)003:2756: ngo bor lhun gyis grub cing yon tan dpag tu
NK075(bu)003:2757: med pa rdzogsa pa don yin pa'i phyir /
NK075(bu)003:2758: rtags gzhal yas khang gi dbyibsa gru bzhir gyur pa /
NK075(bu)003:2759: de'ang chos kyi dbyings la mtha' thug pa med pa don yin la /
NK075(bu)003:2760: rtags bum pa'i mtho dman la tshad dpag tu med de de bzhin gshegs pa'i gtsug tor lta bu'o //
NK075(bu)003:2761: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dgongs pa rang rig pa'i
NK075(bu)003:2762: ye shes su gcig pa don yin la rtags gzhal
NK075(bu)003:2763: yas khang gi rtse mo gur lta bur kun 'khyil
NK075(bu)003:2765: gcig dang du ma bral ba'i phyir //
NK075(bu)003:2766: dkyil 'khor spros med zlum po'i tshul //
NK075(bu)003:2768: rnam par thar pa bzhi dang ldan pa'i rtags su sgo bzhi glo 'bur du yod pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:2771: de phyir ye shes sgo bzhir bshad //
NK075(bu)003:2773: ye shes re re'ang ye shes bzhi bzhi dang ldan pa'i rtags su glo 'bur mkhar thabs bzhi'o //
NK075(bu)003:2774: bla med kyi theg pa ni theg pa gzhan las
NK075(bu)003:2775: 'phags pa'i rtags su gzhal yas khang gi 'og gzhi'i
NK075(bu)003:2777: rnam thar brgyad kyi theg pa'i 'jug pa mtshon pa'i
NK075(bu)003:2778: rtags su them skam rta bab phyi bzhi nang bzhi'o
NK075(bu)003:2780: der 'gro lam stegs brgyad dang ldan //
NK075(bu)003:2782: rang sa'i 'bras bu brgyad thob pa'i rtags su rgyan rta bab brgyad dang ldan pa ni /
NK075(bu)003:2784: rta rkang chu skyes rin chen sgrom //
NK075(bu)003:2785: ma skyes thabs kyi za rar tshags //
NK075(bu)003:2787: sna tshogs khyung mgo rim par 'khrigs //
NK075(bu)003:2789: yul sems dbyer med bdag nyid chen po'i don mngon
NK075(bu)003:2790: du byas pa'i lha yab de dang ni yum rnams
NK075(bu)003:2791: kyis bdag po byed pa'i gnas ni /
NK075(bu)003:2793: dkyil 'khor bzhi bcu gnyis kyis brgyan //
NK075(bu)003:2795: lha'i sprul pa'i 'phro 'dus kyi gdan bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis brgyan pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:2804: tha ma'i 'dab mas kun g.yogs pas //
NK075(bu)003:2805: ye shes rtsig stong seng mgo gtams //
NK075(bu)003:2806: mi 'jig kha na mu tig tar //
NK075(bu)003:2807: pha gu mdzes pa'i bad dang ldan //
NK075(bu)003:2808: d+r+wa ba d+r+wa phyed mgul 'khor ldan //
NK075(bu)003:2809: gzugs sogs lha mo 'khrigs pa ste //
NK075(bu)003:2810: sna tshogs mchod byed rol mo yis //
NK075(bu)003:2811: bar snang khams kun sprin phung bzhin //
NK075(bu)003:2813: thugs rje dang sprul pa'i 'phro 'du rgyun mi 'chad pa dang ldan pa'i rtags la phreng ba /
NK075(bu)003:2814: bden pa gnyis dbyer med pa'i rtags su rin po che'i chun 'phyang /
NK075(bu)003:2815: thabs sna tshogs ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa'i
NK075(bu)003:2816: rtags la mdzes gdung la rin po che'i shar bu
NK075(bu)003:2817: / 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga ma spangs rnam dag
NK075(bu)003:2818: rgyan du rdzogs pa'i rtags su 'dod yon lnga lha
NK075(bu)003:2819: mo dpag tu med pa phyogs bcur 'khrigs shing rgyun
NK075(bu)003:2822: sgo khang nang gi rgyan dgu dang /
NK075(bu)003:2823: bcu gcig rdo rje'i 'breng ra la sogs pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:2826: ye nas mi nyid mi 'ad'i phyir //
NK075(bu)003:2827: ta la'i ljon shing rang bzhin gnas //
NK075(bu)003:2828: re ba yid bzhin skong ba'i phyir //
NK075(bu)003:2829: dpag bsam shing ni rin chen 'bar //
NK075(bu)003:2830: yid bzhin rin chen rgyan gyis bskor //
NK075(bu)003:2831: thams cad la ni dbang bskur phyir //
NK075(bu)003:2832: 'jig rten lha chen rnams kyis bskor //
NK075(bu)003:2834: ye nas mnyam pa nyid la mi 'da' bas nyon
NK075(bu)003:2835: mongs gtan nas mi skye ba'i rtags su ta la'i
NK075(bu)003:2836: ljon shing bcad zin brgyad dam bcu drug /
NK075(bu)003:2837: man ngag ltar na mkha' 'gro sum cu gnyis kyi gnas yin pas so gnyis su 'dod skad do //
NK075(bu)003:2838: gdul bya'i re ba yid la bsam pa bzhin du
NK075(bu)003:2839: skong ba'i rtags su dpag bsam shing la rin po
NK075(bu)003:2840: che'i tshong tshong gis spras pa la dril bu g.yer
NK075(bu)003:2841: khas brgyan pa ta la'i grangs dang mthun pa /
NK075(bu)003:2842: de dag gi bar bar du rin po che'i phung po dang /
NK075(bu)003:2843: khrus kyi rdzing bu yang ta la dang /
NK075(bu)003:2844: dpag bsam shing gi grangs ltar yod do //
NK075(bu)003:2845: 'khor ba'i chos la dbang bsgyur ba'i rtags su 'jig
NK075(bu)003:2846: rten gyi lha chen po la sogs pa rnams kyis
NK075(bu)003:2850: de'i steng na me tog ldem gzing dkar po'i tshal yod do //
NK075(bu)003:2851: de lta bu'i gzhal yas khang gi rgyan du mar snang ba yang /
NK075(bu)003:2852: dpe dri za kho rang gar bsdad pa'i sar gnas khang rang shugs kyis grub pa bzhin du /
NK075(bu)003:2853: ston pa longs sku'i dgongas pa ye shes kyi rtsal
NK075(bu)003:2854: las gzhal yas khang gi dbyibs kha dog rgyan du
NK075(bu)003:2855: mar snang ba'o // de yang gsang snying las /
NK075(bu)003:2856: ye shes rin po che 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang
NK075(bu)003:2857: zhes pa nas rnam par thar pa brgyad kyi rta
NK075(bu)003:2859: zhes gsungs pa'i bar gyi don no //
NK075(bu)003:2860: rang rig pa'i ye shes rgya khyon phyogs re'i tshad bzungs du dka' ba ni /
NK075(bu)003:2861: thams cad ye shes kho na yin pa la blo'i
NK075(bu)003:2862: spyod yul dang bral ba yin pa'i phyir de nyid
NK075(bu)003:2863: las / rgya phyogs bcur yongs su ma chad pa /
NK075(bu)003:2865: de bas na dus dang gnas skabs kun tu ye shes ma gtogs pa phyi rol gyi yul dang /
NK075(bu)003:2866: nang gi sems tha dad pa ni rang rig pa'i
NK075(bu)003:2867: ye shes de la med de kun tu yang nang
NK075(bu)003:2868: du gyur pa'o // de nyid las /
NK075(bu)003:2869: phyi dang nang med pa kun tu yang nang du gyur pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:2871: gdan gyi nang mtshan la lnga ste /
NK075(bu)003:2872: 'og gzhi chos kyi 'khor lo bskor pa'i gdan dang /
NK075(bu)003:2873: yon tan gyi che bas nyes tshogs bcom pa'i dang /
NK075(bu)003:2875: thugs rig pa rang snang gi gdan dang /
NK075(bu)003:2876: smon lam gus pa'i gdan no //
NK075(bu)003:2878: de yang ston pas gdul bya bsam gyis mi khyab
NK075(bu)003:2879: pa la chos kyi 'khor lo rgyun chad med par
NK075(bu)003:2880: bskor ba'i rtags su 'khor lo rtsib bzhi lte ba
NK075(bu)003:2883: gzhi tshad med pa ye shes kyi 'khor lo gsal ba la /
NK075(bu)003:2886: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes skus //
NK075(bu)003:2887: chos kyi 'khor lo yongs su bskor //
NK075(bu)003:2890: shes rab rang bzhin med pa don yin la rtags nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK075(bu)003:2891: thabsa 'gag pa med pa don yin la rtags zla ba'i dkyil 'khor dang de nyid las /
NK075(bu)003:2892: rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba'i nyi zla'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK075(bu)003:2895: rang bzhin ye nas 'od gsal phyir //
NK075(bu)003:2896: nyi zla brtsegs pa'i gdan khri 'bar //
NK075(bu)003:2898: thabs shes rab gnyis med la nyes pa'i skyon gyis ma chagas pa don yin la /
NK075(bu)003:2904: ye nas rnam par dag pa'i phyir //
NK075(bu)003:2907: gsum pa ni gdul bya'i re ba skong zhing dgos 'dod lhun gyis grub pa don yin la /
NK075(bu)003:2908: rtags rin po che'i khri ste /
NK075(bu)003:2909: de yang dkar po bdun ngo bo nyid lhun gyis grub pa don yin la /
NK075(bu)003:2910: rtags khri rkang re re la yang mdzod mig bdun bdun dang ldan pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:2915: zad med ye shes gter gyur pas //
NK075(bu)003:2916: yid bzhin rin chen 'bar ba'i gdan //
NK075(bu)003:2919: ston pa'i dgongs pa la 'bras bu'i che yon thams cad lhun gyis grub cing /
NK075(bu)003:2921: rtags sems can lnga'i gdan du snang ba yin te /
NK075(bu)003:2923: mi 'jigs pa seng ge zhes pa nas /
NK075(bu)003:2924: nam mkha' lding gi khri dang zhes pa'i bar dang /
NK075(bu)003:2925: dbang bskur rgyal po'i rgyud las /
NK075(bu)003:2926: thugs ni mi 'jigs bzhi yis bdud bzhi 'joms //
NK075(bu)003:2927: de grub rtags su seng ge'i khri la bzhugs //
NK075(bu)003:2928: sku ni stobs bcus mi dge bcu rnams 'joms //
NK075(bu)003:2929: de grub rtags su glang chen khri la bzhugs //
NK075(bu)003:2930: yon tan rdzu 'phrul rkang bzhis chags med sgrol //
NK075(bu)003:2931: de grub rtags su rta mchog khri la bzhugs //
NK075(bu)003:2932: gsung ni dbang bcu mthar phyin rgyas pa'i gsung //
NK075(bu)003:2933: de grub rtags su rma bya'i khri la bzhugs //
NK075(bu)003:2934: las ni 'phrin las bzhi yis thogs med sgrol //
NK075(bu)003:2935: de grub rtags su shang shang khri la bzhugs //
NK075(bu)003:2937: lnga pa smon lam gus pa'i gdan ni /
NK075(bu)003:2938: 'bras bu'i gdan gyi zhor la bshad de /
NK075(bu)003:2939: de yang sa mtha'i byang chub sems dpa' smon lam
NK075(bu)003:2940: gyi dbang gis lus seng ge la sogs par sprul
NK075(bu)003:2941: te / ston pa'i gdan du phul nas nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa sbyangs /
NK075(bu)003:2942: rna bas chos nyan pas shes bya'i sgrib pa sbyangs te /
NK075(bu)003:2944: byang chub sems dpa' smon lam dbang //
NK075(bu)003:2945: thos pa rgya mtsho bsags pa'i phyir //
NK075(bu)003:2946: lus ni seng ge'i gdan du phul //
NK075(bu)003:2949: seng ge la sogs pa smon lam gyi byang chub sems dpa' gcig brgyad do //
NK075(bu)003:2951: de la gdan gyi rim pa ni /
NK075(bu)003:2953: skyes bu lnga la lnga brtsegs te /
NK075(bu)003:2955: sgo ba yab yum la nyi ma dang pad+ma gnyis brtsegs /
NK075(bu)003:2956: kun bzang yab yum la dkyil 'khor la 'god pa'i tshe sum brtsegs dang /
NK075(bu)003:2957: chos 'chad pa'i tshe lnga brtsegs su bshad do //
NK075(bu)003:2958: de yang gdan gyi steng du zla ba 'ong ba'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK075(bu)003:2960: thig le chen po dang sa bon ni thams cad
NK075(bu)003:2961: kyi byed pa po'i phyir bdag po dang rdo rje
NK075(bu)003:2962: ste / dbus na zla ba blar gnas so //
NK075(bu)003:2965: snying ga chos kyi 'khor lo na srog mi shigs pa'i thig le dang /
NK075(bu)003:2966: klad pa bde chen gyi 'khor lo na srog mi shigs pa'i thig le yod pas /
NK075(bu)003:2967: thabs kyis zin ma zin gyi chas thig le gnyis
NK075(bu)003:2968: po de 'khor 'das thams cad kyi byed pa po'i
NK075(bu)003:2971: rgyud kyi bdag po rgyal ba drug pa kun tu bzang po dang /
NK075(bu)003:2972: dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo rdo rje sems dpa' gnyis
NK075(bu)003:2973: la gdan zla ba steng du yod pa'i rgyu mtshan
NK075(bu)003:2976: gtso bo ni shes rab la spyod pa'i phyir /
NK075(bu)003:2977: nang gi chu skyes kyi lte ba la nyi ma brtan pa'i phyir /
NK075(bu)003:2978: ri bong can steng na gnas so //
NK075(bu)003:2979: yum rnams de las zlog go //
NK075(bu)003:2981: lha 'khril sbyor rnams la gdan gcig pas mi 'gal lo //
NK075(bu)003:2983: zhi ba'i lha kun la zla ba steng du 'ong la /
NK075(bu)003:2984: khro bo'i lha kun la nyi ma steng du 'ong bar gsungs so //
NK075(bu)003:2985: de ltar ye shes kyis rtsal las gzhal yas khang gi gdan dang /
NK075(bu)003:2986: rgyan du mar snang bas dbyings phyogs gcig gi mtha' dang bral bas na /
NK075(bu)003:2987: gcig ma yin la ye shes sna tshogs su snang
NK075(bu)003:2988: ba'i dus la rang bzhin med de dbyings las ma
NK075(bu)003:2989: g.yos pas du ma'i mtha' dang bral ba'o //
NK075(bu)003:2994: don la gtso 'khor gyi dgongs pa dbyer med yin kyang /
NK075(bu)003:2995: gdul bya'i snang ngo la gtso 'khor gyi tshul du snang ste /
NK075(bu)003:2996: de yang gnas de na ston pa de la 'khor de gus pa'i tshul du snang ste /
NK075(bu)003:2997: ston pa kun bzang gi rgyal tshab kyi tshul 'dzin
NK075(bu)003:2998: cing rgyud 'chad byed kyi skyes bu rgyal ba rigs
NK075(bu)003:3000: rgyal sras byang chub sems dpa'i tshul 'dzin pa'i 'khor sems dpa' yab yum bcu drug dang /
NK075(bu)003:3001: gdug pa can 'jigs par byed pa khro bo'i tshul 'dzin pa'i 'khor khro bo yab yum brgyad dang /
NK075(bu)003:3002: thugs rje'i sprul pa'i 'khor thub pa drug gi tshul 'dzin pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:3003: dad pa can gtam nyan pa'i 'khor sangs rgyas kyi
NK075(bu)003:3004: thugs rje dang gdul bya'i smon lam 'brel ba'i stobs
NK075(bu)003:3005: kyis lha chen po brgyad dang /
NK075(bu)003:3006: sogsa kyi sgras dpal mgon bdun cu rtsa lnga'i tshul 'dzin pa /
NK075(bu)003:3007: gzhal yas khang gi rgyab rdo rje rwa ba'i nang /
NK075(bu)003:3008: me tog ldom gzing dkar po'i steng na bzhugs pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:3011: 'khor de rnams kyi bzhugs tshul ni /
NK075(bu)003:3012: rigs lnga yab yum bcu ni ston pa kun bzang
NK075(bu)003:3013: yab yum dang dgongs pa dbyer med pas bzhugs tshul
NK075(bu)003:3014: gcig go // sems dpa' rnams ni lam mthar ma
NK075(bu)003:3015: phyin gyi bar du bdag gzhan gyi don bsgrub pa
NK075(bu)003:3016: la mnyam rjes kyi tshul du /
NK075(bu)003:3017: g.yon bskum g.yas pa gdan la 'bab pa'i tshul dang /
NK075(bu)003:3018: khro bo rnams ni sgo bsrung ba'i tshul du zur gyis blta ba'am /
NK075(bu)003:3019: phyir bltas pa'i zhabs gyad bkyag thabs su dang /
NK075(bu)003:3020: thub pa rnams ni 'gro ba'i don rgyun chad med par mdzad pa'i phyir zhabs 'greng bar bzhugs pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:3022: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa rnam par shes pa'i rgyal po dang /
NK075(bu)003:3024: mtshan mar ma yin pa zhes pa'i bar gyis don no //
NK075(bu)003:3025: 'o na gong du rigs lnga dang sems dpa' ston par mdzad pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:3026: 'dir 'khor du bshad pa gnyis 'gal lo zhe na /
NK075(bu)003:3027: 'gal ba ma yin te gong du thams cad ston par bshad pa ni /
NK075(bu)003:3028: gdul bya lha mi'i snang ngo la /
NK075(bu)003:3029: lam rkyen yi ge'i rgyud kyi ston pa 'byung bar byed pa la /
NK075(bu)003:3030: chos sku kun bzang gi rgyal ba dgongs brgyud /
NK075(bu)003:3031: longs sku rigs lngas rig 'dzin brda' brgyud /
NK075(bu)003:3032: sprul sku phyag rdor gyis dam pa'i rigs can lnga la tshig brda'i sgo nas gsungs te /
NK075(bu)003:3033: de nas rgyal po dzahmana chad du gang zag snyan brgyud du bstan pa dar ba la /
NK075(bu)003:3034: de ltar rgyal ba sku gsum du brgyud dgongs pa yin te /
NK075(bu)003:3036: ston pa'i rang bzhin brgyad dang ldan //
NK075(bu)003:3037: bdag nyid byed pa kun tu bzang //
NK075(bu)003:3038: 'chad pa'i skyes bu rigs lnga ste //
NK075(bu)003:3039: mtshungs pa'i gzhi dang ldan pa'i phyir //
NK075(bu)003:3040: lngas kyang bstan pa gsungs mi 'gal //
NK075(bu)003:3041: gsang bdag phyag na rdo rje yis //
NK075(bu)003:3042: thun mong ma yin nges pa'i rgyud //
NK075(bu)003:3043: dris lan mi mngon tshul gyis bsdus //
NK075(bu)003:3044: byin rlabs mi yul grags pa yin //
NK075(bu)003:3046: 'dir 'khor du bshad pa'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK075(bu)003:3047: spyi'i rgyud kyi chos 'chad pa'i ston pa ni /
NK075(bu)003:3048: kun bzang nyag gcig gis gsungs pa yin pas /
NK075(bu)003:3049: de la ltos nas rigs lnga man chad 'khor du bshad pa la 'gal ba med do //
NK075(bu)003:3050: gsum pa tshad gnyis bstan pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:3052: de lta bu'i sprul pa rang rgyud pa'i tshogs ni
NK075(bu)003:3053: grangs tshad las 'das pa'i don gyi grangs brjod kyi
NK075(bu)003:3054: mi lang yang / cha lugs kyi rnam grangs ni gang gi bzhi bcu la 'dus pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:3055: de'ang yab yum gtso 'khor du bzhugs shing chos kyi dbyings mu mtha' med par khyab pa ni /
NK075(bu)003:3056: rang bzhin mngon du byas pa'i rtags su gzhal yas
NK075(bu)003:3057: khang lhas gang nas kun tu khyab par bzhugs so
NK075(bu)003:3059: de lta bu'i tshogs brjod kyis mi lang ba dang gnyis su med par bzhugs so //
NK075(bu)003:3061: bzhi pa sdud pa po dang /
NK075(bu)003:3063: dper na nor bu rin po che la gdul bya
NK075(bu)003:3064: rang rang gi bsam pa bzhin du dgos 'dod 'byung
NK075(bu)003:3065: ba ltar / sdud pa po yang gdul bya rang
NK075(bu)003:3066: rang gi mos pa bzhin du sku mnga' ba'i gsang
NK075(bu)003:3067: bdag ni snyan cha lnga ldan du yod pas rgyud
NK075(bu)003:3068: de yi bdag po yin pa'i phyir /
NK075(bu)003:3069: sdud pa po yang gsang ba bdag rang yin kyang /
NK075(bu)003:3070: tan+t+ra ste rgyud thugs sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba de'i don
NK075(bu)003:3071: sdud pa pos bsdus nas mi dang mi ma yin
NK075(bu)003:3072: pa la sogs pa la brgyud pa'ang /
NK075(bu)003:3073: rang rang gi mos pa bzhin du /
NK075(bu)003:3074: lha la ku ma ra ste 'jam dpal du snang ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:3075: klu la spyan tshor te spyan ras gzigs su snang ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:3076: mi dang mi min gnyis ka la gsang bdag tu
NK075(bu)003:3077: snang ba de ni ston pa kun bzang de yi
NK075(bu)003:3079: rgyud de yi don ni gsang bdag des bsdus nas dam pa'i rigsa can lnga dang /
NK075(bu)003:3080: rgyal po dzahl sogs pa'i skal ldan rnams la gsungs pa ni rigs te 'thad pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:3082: rang gi lus ngag yid rdo rje //
NK075(bu)003:3083: mi phyed pa yi ngo bo nyid //
NK075(bu)003:3084: rig pa bcas par ldan pa nyid //
NK075(bu)003:3085: rig pa'i skyes bu zhes su brjod //
NK075(bu)003:3092: mngon par byang chub pa'i sku dang lnga ni /
NK075(bu)003:3093: lam pa'i sa tshod mtho na dman gyi blo yis phye bas ye shes rgya mtsho'i 'khor dang /
NK075(bu)003:3097: rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i 'khor dang lnga po rnams la /
NK075(bu)003:3098: so sor rang rang gi blo dang 'tshams par chos
NK075(bu)003:3099: bstan cing brda' sprad pa'i dus tha dad du snang
NK075(bu)003:3100: na yang / gdul bya go phye ba'i 'khor gyi snang ngor rkyang bkar du bshad pa yin la /
NK075(bu)003:3101: 'dir ni ston pa sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa'i
NK075(bu)003:3102: drug pa des lhan cig pa yi 'khor rnams la
NK075(bu)003:3103: bstan pa gsung lnga lhun grub dus gcig tu snang
NK075(bu)003:3104: ste / de yang tshul ci ltar du snang na /
NK075(bu)003:3105: mthar lam pa'i 'khor gang gis ston pa drug pa'i
NK075(bu)003:3106: zhal mthong ba dang bstan pa gsung lnga lhun grub
NK075(bu)003:3107: kyi don rtogsa nas sangs rgyas pa de'i tshe na
NK075(bu)003:3108: yang / dus bzhi mnyam pa nyid las ma g.yos pa yin te /
NK075(bu)003:3109: de yang dus bzhi ni dpe me shing dang 'dra ste /
NK075(bu)003:3110: rgyu rkyen 'dzom pa de bral ba ni 'das pa /
NK075(bu)003:3111: rgyu rkyen 'tshogs bdo ba ni da lta ba /
NK075(bu)003:3112: rgyu rkyen 'dzom pa'i tshe 'bras bu gcig 'byung la ma rag pa ni ma 'ongs pa /
NK075(bu)003:3113: rgyu rkyen so sor yod kyang lhan cig tu ma 'tshogs pa ni 'byung bar ma nges pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:3114: de yang kun rdzob kyi bden pa'i cha nas dus bzhir snang la ma 'gags la /
NK075(bu)003:3115: don dam gyi bden pa'i cha nas dus bzhir snang ba ma dmigs te /
NK075(bu)003:3116: dbyer med kyi bden pa'i cha nas dus bzhi ma
NK075(bu)003:3117: 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pas mnyam pa nyid ces
NK075(bu)003:3119: ma bcos de bzhin nyid 'di la //
NK075(bu)003:3120: dus gsum dus bzhi ma dmigs te //
NK075(bu)003:3121: ye shes rig pa'i yul can la //
NK075(bu)003:3122: skad cig bskal pa de skad cig /
NK075(bu)003:3127: ye shes rtogs pa'i khyad par gyis //
NK075(bu)003:3128: dus bzhi snga phyi med pa yi //
NK075(bu)003:3129: mnyam pa nyid de lhan ner sbyor //
NK075(bu)003:3131: de yang gsang ba'i snying po 'khor 'das rang bzhin
NK075(bu)003:3132: mnyam pa nyid rtogs pa'i ngang du dus bzhi ma
NK075(bu)003:3133: 'dres la yongs su rdzogs par brda 'phrod pa'i 'khor
NK075(bu)003:3134: rnams la / rtag par rgyun du bstan pa gsung
NK075(bu)003:3135: lnga lhun grub tu brda mjal bas na thugsa rje
NK075(bu)003:3136: rnams la / 'dzom pa'o // dus nam 'dzom zhe
NK075(bu)003:3137: na mthar phyin nas shes bya bag la nyal gyi
NK075(bu)003:3138: dri ma dag pa yi dus la mngon sum du
NK075(bu)003:3142: lam mthar phyin pa de'i tshe gang snang na rang
NK075(bu)003:3143: bzhin gsang ba'i snying po 'bras bu'i rgyud nges pa'i
NK075(bu)003:3144: lung de mngon sum du snang /
NK075(bu)003:3145: tshul ci ltar du snang na gsung lnga lhun gyis grub pa'i tshul gyisa snang /
NK075(bu)003:3146: gang la snang na lhan gcig pa'i 'khor la 'char nas snang ba'o //
NK075(bu)003:3147: 'o na yi ge'i rgyud 'di nges lung ma yin nam snyam na /
NK075(bu)003:3148: mtshon byed tshig gis bstan par snang ba'i rgyud de nyid kyi don brjod pa yin te /
NK075(bu)003:3149: 'o na tshig kho na dngos su brjod dam zhe na /
NK075(bu)003:3150: ma yin te mtshon byed tshig de dag mtshon bya mtshon byed med par rang sgra ste /
NK075(bu)003:3151: dper na chu zla'i gzugs brnyan bzhin du ston 'khor
NK075(bu)003:3152: gyi dgongs pa la gsung lnga lhun grub mtshon bya
NK075(bu)003:3154: gnyis pa khro bo gang mos su snang ba'o //
NK075(bu)003:3156: dper na 'gro ba mi la sogs pa gang dag
NK075(bu)003:3157: gi mig gi gzugs su snang ba'i yul la rang
NK075(bu)003:3158: rang gi rigs mthun snang na gcig la gcig dga'
NK075(bu)003:3159: bar byed la / mi mthun pa'i dgra la ni
NK075(bu)003:3160: dga' ba de las sgyur bar byed pa 'jigs pa'i
NK075(bu)003:3162: rgyal ba drug pa'i gleng gzhi'ang de bzhin du lugs 'byung rnams la zhi ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:3163: lugs ldog rnams la khro bo'i gleng gzhir bsgyur ba de bzhin no //
NK075(bu)003:3164: de nyid rgyas par bshad pa ni /
NK075(bu)003:3165: gsang snying le'u bco lnga pa ltar shes par bya'o //
NK075(bu)003:3166: gnyis pa rkyen gyi gleng bslang ba la gsum ste /
NK075(bu)003:3170: gong gi gleng gzhi de rnams kyi rjes su rkyen
NK075(bu)003:3171: gyis gleng bslang ba la gsum ste thun mong ma
NK075(bu)003:3172: yin pa'i gleng bslang ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:3173: thun mong gi gleng bslang ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:3176: gong du bshad pa ltar thabs lam gyi gleng gzhi
NK075(bu)003:3177: tshogs nas 'bras bu rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po
NK075(bu)003:3178: 'di nyid shin tu zab pas na /
NK075(bu)003:3179: 'khor gyis i yod mi shes te ston pas mdun
NK075(bu)003:3180: bsus te gnang bar zhal gyis bzhes nas gleng bslang
NK075(bu)003:3181: ba ste / 'bras bu'i rgyud 'di nyid dang /
NK075(bu)003:3183: de nas rang bzhin lhan cig pa'i 'khor gyis gus
NK075(bu)003:3184: pas gsang ba bzhis chod tshul zhus te gleng bslang
NK075(bu)003:3185: ba dang / rgyud de'i zhor la mtshan nyid kyi bka' pha rol tu phyin pa yang /
NK075(bu)003:3186: chos zab pas 'khor gyis i yod mi shes pa ston pa'i thugs rjes gnang ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:3187: 'khor gyis shes nas zhus pa mdo rgyud gzhan rnams lta bu'o //
NK075(bu)003:3189: bstan pa snang bdo ba'i bar skabs dkyus la zhus pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:3190: lan gyi bye brag ste gleng du lang ba dang gsum mo //
NK075(bu)003:3193: ston pas gnang ba dang 'khor gyis dri ba gnyis ni /
NK075(bu)003:3194: rgyud don bstan pa 'byung ba'i rkyen du gang dang
NK075(bu)003:3195: gang gyur pa'i bstan pa de ston pa des gsung
NK075(bu)003:3196: la ma rag pa ni rkyen gleng bslang zhes bya
NK075(bu)003:3197: ba'i nges pa'i tshig kyang de ltar du 'grub la
NK075(bu)003:3198: / gleng bslang gi ngo bo yang de yin no //
NK075(bu)003:3199: gnas skabs kyi 'khor gyis dris pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:3200: ston pas lan gnang ba rnams kyang gleng lang yin par smos ci dgos te /
NK075(bu)003:3201: ston 'khor gyi dris lan byed bdo ba des ni
NK075(bu)003:3202: gleng lang zhes pa'i nges tshig de nges par 'grub
NK075(bu)003:3203: pa yin no // gsum pa dgos ched do //
NK075(bu)003:3206: don gyi go rim sdeb dgos pa yin te /
NK075(bu)003:3207: de yang gong gi dang po thun mong ma yin
NK075(bu)003:3208: pa thabs lam spyod pa'i gleng gzhi gang 'tshogs pa'i
NK075(bu)003:3209: tshe na yang / sngon byung gi rgyud don sems
NK075(bu)003:3210: lnga 'byung ba'i rkyen byed cing bstan pa 'byung la
NK075(bu)003:3212: sngon byung lhan cig pa'i 'khor gyi don bya ba'i phyir du /
NK075(bu)003:3213: thabs lam gyi rgyud gleng gzhi 'tshogsa nas ston pas
NK075(bu)003:3214: byang sems gnang ba'i thugs rjes rkyen gleng bslang ste
NK075(bu)003:3215: ston 'khor dgongs pa dbyer med du sangs rgyas par
NK075(bu)003:3217: e ma'o rdo rje phung po'i yan lag ni //
NK075(bu)003:3219: mnyes par khyab par gyur to //
NK075(bu)003:3220: zhes pa'i bar gyi don yin te /
NK075(bu)003:3222: dkyil 'khor bzhi bcu rtsa lnga dang //
NK075(bu)003:3223: phun sum tshogs pa lhun grub rnams //
NK075(bu)003:3224: gsang dbang mchog gis 'byin par byed //
NK075(bu)003:3227: thun mong ma yin ston pa nyid //
NK075(bu)003:3228: yab yum chags bskul rol pa dang //
NK075(bu)003:3229: dgyes gtad 'khor la dbang bskur bas //
NK075(bu)003:3230: rgyud don 'byung phyir bslang zhes bya //
NK075(bu)003:3232: gnyis pa rgyud khyad par can shes rab grol lam
NK075(bu)003:3233: gyi rgyud gleng gzhi 'tshogs pa gang gi tshe na
NK075(bu)003:3234: yang / rjes 'jug gi rgyud don 'byung ba'i rkyen
NK075(bu)003:3235: byed cing bstan pa 'byung la ma rag pa de
NK075(bu)003:3236: yang / / gzhan go phye ba'i 'khor gyi don bya ba'i phyir du /
NK075(bu)003:3237: grol lam gyi rgyu gleng gzhi 'tshogsa nas 'khor gyi
NK075(bu)003:3238: thugs rjes gsang ba bzhis chod tshul gyi dri ba'i
NK075(bu)003:3240: gdul bya tha dag gi don du lam rkyen yi
NK075(bu)003:3241: ge'i rgyud kyi bstan pa thams cad 'byung bar 'gyur
NK075(bu)003:3242: ba'i gzhi byas pa yin te /
NK075(bu)003:3244: e ma'o ye nas gsang ba'i chos //
NK075(bu)003:3246: gzhan du min la shin tu gsang //
NK075(bu)003:3247: zhes pa'i bar gyi don no //
NK075(bu)003:3249: thun mong gleng bslang ston dang 'khor //
NK075(bu)003:3250: tha dad snang nas dbang thob 'khor //
NK075(bu)003:3251: nyid kyi rtogs nas 'gro don du //
NK075(bu)003:3252: bka' stsal don gyi zhus dang lan //
NK075(bu)003:3253: gnang bar don gyi tshig tu phyung //
NK075(bu)003:3254: sku gsung thugs kyis spro ba mdzad //
NK075(bu)003:3255: de nyid skye bo phal pa'i don //
NK075(bu)003:3256: ngo bo don bslang tshig phyung ba'o //
NK075(bu)003:3260: 'di la sngon gyi bshad srol la dgos 'brel bzhi ltar gsungs pa yod kyang /
NK075(bu)003:3261: gzhung tshig rang la dngos su brtags na /
NK075(bu)003:3262: brjod 'brel bzhi bas mi gda' bas //
NK075(bu)003:3264: dang po brjod bya ni rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying
NK075(bu)003:3265: po'i gzhi 'bras kyi rgyud kyi don de nyid ci
