NK075(bu)003:3267: mtshon byed lam rkyen yi ge'i rgyu rjod par byed
NK075(bu)003:3268: pa'i bdag po ston pa rgyal ba drug pas gsungs
NK075(bu)003:3269: pa'i rgyud kyi don de nyid /
NK075(bu)003:3270: lam rkyen yi ge'i rgyud dang tshig tshogs su snang ba ni rjod byed yin te /
NK075(bu)003:3271: 'di la brtsegs sdeb gcig bya ste /
NK075(bu)003:3272: de yang gang zag gzu lums ras chod can dgag par bya ba'i phyir du /
NK075(bu)003:3273: rgyud de nyid 'chol zhing 'khrugs nas yod pa la /
NK075(bu)003:3274: las 'phro skal ba dang ldan pa la bshad pa'i tshe /
NK075(bu)003:3275: de nyid 'brel pa rim bzhi dang sbyar dgos te /
NK075(bu)003:3276: de yang thabs grol gyi rgyu gleng gzhi 'tshogs nas
NK075(bu)003:3277: rkyen gleng bslang ba ni rgyud don 'byung ba'i thabs
NK075(bu)003:3278: yin pa dang / thabs de las rgyud don 'di
NK075(bu)003:3279: nyid 'byung ba ni thabs dang thabs byung 'brel pa
NK075(bu)003:3280: yin pa dang / yin la / de ltar rgyud
NK075(bu)003:3281: don gtan la phab cing nyams su len pa ni
NK075(bu)003:3282: yin pa dang / yin la / rgyu / mi
NK075(bu)003:3283: zad rgyun gyi 'khor lo thob pa ni 'bras bu
NK075(bu)003:3284: yin pa dang / yin la / rgyu / ste / de ni rgyu dang 'bras bu'i 'brel pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:3285: de yang gleng gzhi la thabs grol gnyis byung ba
NK075(bu)003:3286: de'i rjes su brjod 'brel bzhi yang thabs grol gnyis
NK075(bu)003:3287: su bshad pa nges par 'gro ba yin te /
NK075(bu)003:3288: de yang grol lam gyi gzhi ni gong du song la /
NK075(bu)003:3289: thabs lam gyi brjod 'brel bzhi ni /
NK075(bu)003:3290: gsang ba rdo rje'i rtse mor byang sems thig le
NK075(bu)003:3291: chen po dbab bzung gi thabs dang bcas pa ni
NK075(bu)003:3292: brjod byed / thig le dga' ba bcu drug gi bde ba'i ye shes ni brjod bya /
NK075(bu)003:3293: bde ba myong bar byed pa'i thig le rlung dang bcas pa ni thabs /
NK075(bu)003:3294: des rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po bde ba'i ye shes myong ba ni thabs byung /
NK075(bu)003:3295: thig le bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis ni rgyu /
NK075(bu)003:3296: ye shes bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis ni 'bras bu'o //
NK075(bu)003:3297: de yang rgyud 'chol zhing 'khrugs nas yod pa la
NK075(bu)003:3298: rgol ba byung na lan de ltar du 'debs pa
NK075(bu)003:3300: rgol ba po dag tshar gcod phyir //
NK075(bu)003:3303: rgyud la ldan phyir rgol ba bzlog /
NK075(bu)003:3305: bzhi pa 'dren pa'i tshig gi dpe la gsum ste /
NK075(bu)003:3309: tan+t+ra ste rgyud gsang ba'i snying po'i dbu nas zhabs
NK075(bu)003:3310: kyi le'u'i grangs rnams kyi bshad thabs mdor bsdus pa'i
NK075(bu)003:3311: sgo nas dmigs ngos bzung na /
NK075(bu)003:3312: dper na me long la gzugs brnyan gsal ba ltar
NK075(bu)003:3313: bshad thabs 'dren pa'i tshig bcu po yi rgyud kyi
NK075(bu)003:3314: don mtshon nus pas na bshad thabs bcu po dang
NK075(bu)003:3316: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:3318: bcu po de gang zhe na /
NK075(bu)003:3319: spyi don sdud pa'i tshig seng ge mchongs pa ltar bshad pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:3320: rnam par dbye ba'i tshig stag gi mchongs pa ltar /
NK075(bu)003:3321: rang bzhin lta ba'i tshig khyung nam mkha' la lding ba /
NK075(bu)003:3322: rang rkyen gnyer ba'i tshig rus sbal gnur 'gros tshad ma bka' gzhung gi tshig dus kyi 'brug sgra /
NK075(bu)003:3323: gtar kha gegs sel gyi tshig glag mo gzan la 'dzum pa /
NK075(bu)003:3324: ldem dgongs man ngag gi tshig gna' phrug brag la 'dzeg pa /
NK075(bu)003:3325: 'brel mtshams sbyar ba'i tshig bya ngang mo'i 'gros /
NK075(bu)003:3326: mtshon pa dpe'i tshig me long g.ya' dag pa /
NK075(bu)003:3327: bsnol mtshams 'phen sdud kyi tshig seng ge'i phru gu
NK075(bu)003:3328: rtsal sbyangs pa ltar du bshad pa dang bcu yis
NK075(bu)003:3329: tshig thog tu rgyud don 'dren par bshad par gyis
NK075(bu)003:3330: la / bshad thabs bsdus pa bcu po de dag la'ang /
NK075(bu)003:3331: rgyud don gyi bye brag mi 'dra bas phye bas
NK075(bu)003:3332: le'u rim pa bzhin du bdag po rang rang gtso
NK075(bu)003:3333: gang dang gang che ba ma gtogs pa bcu po
NK075(bu)003:3334: gzhan rnams dgos pa'i nges pa med de /
NK075(bu)003:3335: de'ang lta ba mi ston na rang bzhin lta ba'i tshig mi dgos pa dang 'dra'o //
NK075(bu)003:3338: rnam par dbye ba spyi 'gro gsum ni le'u kun la shes par 'gyur ba yin no //
NK075(bu)003:3340: seng ge mchongs pa'i chos gcig gi kha 'og tu tshigs du ma chud pa ltar du /
NK075(bu)003:3341: spyi don sdud pa'i tshig gis rnam grangs kyi tshig
NK075(bu)003:3342: mang po yang lam don gyi ngo bo gcig tu
NK075(bu)003:3343: khog dbub nas sdud par byed do //
NK075(bu)003:3344: gnyis pa ni b+y+aa kri ste stag mo mchongas pa'i
NK075(bu)003:3345: tshe seng ge mchongs pa de bzhin du bgrod par
NK075(bu)003:3346: bya ba'i sa tshig dum bur bcad nas mchongs pa
NK075(bu)003:3347: bzhin du / rnam par dbye ba'i tshig gis tan+t+ra
NK075(bu)003:3348: ste rgyud gsang ba'i snying po'i tshig dang don gyi
NK075(bu)003:3349: dmigs so sor phye ba'i thabas su sa gcod nas
NK075(bu)003:3352: ka la ping+ka ste bya khyung lding ba'i dus su chos bzhi pos mtshon te /
NK075(bu)003:3354: mig gong 'og tu mi lta ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:3355: gshog pa rlob pa'i rtsol ba med pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:3356: ngam 'grog dang g.yang za la nyam mi nga ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:3357: bya lam la rjes med pa bzhin du /
NK075(bu)003:3358: rang bzhin lta ba'i tshig gis rnal 'byor spyan gyi
NK075(bu)003:3359: 'phang gcod pa'i theg pa thams cad lta ba'i 'og
NK075(bu)003:3360: tu tshud pa / lam bgrod pa'i rtsol ba med pa /
NK075(bu)003:3361: srid zhi la nyam nga med pa /
NK075(bu)003:3362: blta bya lta byed kyi spyod yul med do //
NK075(bu)003:3364: rus sbal 'gros kyi chos gnyis yod de /
NK075(bu)003:3366: g.yo 'gul mi mngon par shugs kyis 'gro zhing sa stong mi lus par khyab pa bzhin du /
NK075(bu)003:3367: rang rkyen gnyer ba'i tshig gis 'bru stong mi bzhag
NK075(bu)003:3368: par tshig la don gyi gzer bus gdab cing don
NK075(bu)003:3369: brda' sprod par byed cing gzhung don mthar phyin par
NK075(bu)003:3371: dus min par mi 'byung dbyar gyi dus su 'brug sgra dang char pa 'byung ste /
NK075(bu)003:3372: de byung ba dang skye bo rnams kyis de ring
NK075(bu)003:3373: nas dbyar dgun gyi shan phrag bye'o zhes dus tshod
NK075(bu)003:3374: kyi spros pa chod pa'i chos gsum pa des yid
NK075(bu)003:3375: ches pa bzhin du tshad ma bka' gzhug gi tshig
NK075(bu)003:3376: gis gsang sngags bla med kyi don gtan la dbab
NK075(bu)003:3377: par byed pa yi tshad ma la dag pa gsum
NK075(bu)003:3379: rtogs pa bzhi dang gsum gyi don rang rang gi skabs dang sbyar ces pa'am /
NK075(bu)003:3380: yang na tshad ma bka' gzhung gi tshig gis bka'
NK075(bu)003:3381: lung man ngag rigs pa yi tshad ma gsum gyi
NK075(bu)003:3383: bden gsum dbyer med kyi don la sgro 'dogs chod nas grub mtha' mngon sum du snang ba ni /
NK075(bu)003:3384: theg 'og gi skabs su mi 'byung rang gzhung gi skabs su 'byung /
NK075(bu)003:3385: des the tshom chod nas yid ches pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:3387: glag gi gzan la zhugs pa'i tshe mchu sder gyis
NK075(bu)003:3388: phyi'i sha dang pags pa la mi lta nas nang
NK075(bu)003:3389: gi don snying 'byin par byed pa'i chos gnyis dang
NK075(bu)003:3391: gtar kha gegs sel gyi tshig gis tshig dang blo
NK075(bu)003:3392: la mi lta nas grub mtha'i don gyi dmigs ngos
NK075(bu)003:3393: bzung nas don gang mi gsal ba'i gegsa rnams bsal
NK075(bu)003:3394: lo // bdun pa ni gna' ba'i phru gu brag
NK075(bu)003:3395: ri nyi ma shar ba thams cad la 'dzeg pa'i
NK075(bu)003:3396: tshe ri dwags gzhan la mi 'tsham yang /
NK075(bu)003:3397: gna' phrug rang la 'tshams pa'i chos gnyis dang ldan pa ltar /
NK075(bu)003:3398: de yang ldem dgongs man ngag gi tshig gis gsang
NK075(bu)003:3399: ba bla med kyi don rnams dgongs pa bzhi dang
NK075(bu)003:3400: / ldem po bzhi dang brgyad kyi don dang sbyar ba ni 'di lta ste /
NK075(bu)003:3401: de la dang po dgongs pa bzhi ni /
NK075(bu)003:3402: mnyam pa nyid la dgongs pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:3405: gang zag gi bsam pa la dgongs pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:3406: theg pa 'og ma pa rgyu 'bras snga phyi tha
NK075(bu)003:3407: dad du zhen pa rnams kyis sangs rgyas dang sems
NK075(bu)003:3408: can bzang ngan tha dad du 'dzin pa'i zhen pa
NK075(bu)003:3410: chos nyid mnyam pa nyid la dgongs te bzang ngan med par ston pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:3412: gdul bya bzhi dang theg pa bzhi po rnams //
NK075(bu)003:3413: bzang ngan 'dzin pa gsang sgor drang ba'i phyir //
NK075(bu)003:3414: thams cad mnyam pa'i don la rab dgongs te //
NK075(bu)003:3415: thams cad bzang ngan blang dor med par bstan //
NK075(bu)003:3418: dus yun ring po dang byang chub kyi spyod pa rgya chen pos sgyid lug pa dag la /
NK075(bu)003:3419: sngags la mos pa tsam gyis kyang 'bras bu 'grub la /
NK075(bu)003:3420: dus kyang yi dam gyi lha dran pa tsam gyis kyang tshe 'di nyid la 'grub par bstan te /
NK075(bu)003:3421: de nyid las dus dang las kyi sgyid lug gdul bya rnams /
NK075(bu)003:3422: spros pa bskyed cing 'bras bur drang ba'i phyir //
NK075(bu)003:3423: brgyud nas 'grub pa'i don la dgongs pa dang //
NK075(bu)003:3424: gsang ba mos pa tsam gyis 'grub par bstan //
NK075(bu)003:3426: de yang gsang snying le'u bcu gsum pa las /
NK075(bu)003:3427: gang zhig 'di la mos gyur pa //
NK075(bu)003:3428: sangs rgyas dkyil 'khor thams cad kyis //
NK075(bu)003:3429: phyogs dus kun na thams cad du //
NK075(bu)003:3430: dkyil 'khor ma lus bsnyen pa yi //
NK075(bu)003:3431: nye ba'i sras su dgongs par 'gyur //
NK075(bu)003:3433: yang de nyid kyi dgu pa las /
NK075(bu)003:3434: ma nyams 'jug la rab brtson na //
NK075(bu)003:3435: zhag ni sum cu phrag drug nam //
NK075(bu)003:3436: bcu gnyis bcu bzhi bcu drug gis //
NK075(bu)003:3437: dbang bsgyur rigs kyi dam par 'grub //
NK075(bu)003:3440: brtson 'grus drag po'i sgo nas yun ring por thos
NK075(bu)003:3441: bsam sgom pa'i shes rab gsum la blo sbyangs ma
NK075(bu)003:3442: byas par / kha 'byams tshig gi lta ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:3443: shes bya 'ga' zhig shes pa'i yon tan sna re khong du chud pa'i yon tan rloms sems dang /
NK075(bu)003:3444: nga rgyal byed pa dag gis bden pa ma mthong ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:3445: 'bras bu ma thob pa la dgongs nas /
NK075(bu)003:3446: de dag gsang sngags nang pa'i theg pa la drang zhing don rtogs pa la bskul ba'i phyir /
NK075(bu)003:3447: byang sems gnyis ni bskal pa grangs med par sbyangs shing /
NK075(bu)003:3448: sangs rgyas mang po la bsnyen bskur byas shing sbyangs
NK075(bu)003:3449: pa 'ga' zhig gis 'grub par bstan pa rnams yin
NK075(bu)003:3451: shes bya 'ga' la rloms sems byed pa dag /
NK075(bu)003:3452: zhen pa bsal zhing theg chen sgor drang phyir //
NK075(bu)003:3453: bden pa ma mthong 'bras bu ma thob par //
NK075(bu)003:3454: dgongs nas bskal par sbyangs pa tsam las 'grub //
NK075(bu)003:3457: gang zag 'ga' zhig gis yi dam sna 'gas 'bras bu thob par 'dod pa dag la /
NK075(bu)003:3458: brjod pa'i dge ba de gcig pus 'bras bu mi 'grub par /
NK075(bu)003:3459: dge ba'i phyogs gzhan thams cad tshang bar bsgrubs na yon tan rgya chen po thob par brjod de /
NK075(bu)003:3461: kha cig mos pa'i blo bzhin du 'tshams par bstan pa ste /
NK075(bu)003:3463: chos 'gas chog par 'dzin pa'i gang zag rnams //
NK075(bu)003:3464: theg chen brjod pa rgya chen bskul ba'i phyir //
NK075(bu)003:3465: bsgrub pa'i yan lag tshang bar spyod na 'grub //
NK075(bu)003:3466: rgya chen spyod dang mos dang 'tshams par bstan //
NK075(bu)003:3468: gnyis pa ldem po la bzhi ste /
NK075(bu)003:3469: gzhugs pa la ldem pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:3474: theg 'og gi gdul bya rnams gsang sngags kyi don la skrag pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:3475: rang gi gzhug la spyod kyang don mi 'grub pas tshi chad pa'i rtsol ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:3476: de la mngon par zhen pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:3477: ci la'ang mi 'jug pa dag drang ba'i phyir /
NK075(bu)003:3478: lta ba dang spyod pa mthun par bstan te /
NK075(bu)003:3480: skrag cing basngangasa la tshi chad tshol //
NK075(bu)003:3481: mngon zhen ci la'ang mi 'jug rnams //
NK075(bu)003:3482: nges pa'i don la gzhug pa'i phyir //
NK075(bu)003:3483: lta spyod mthun bstan 'di ru bzhugs //
NK075(bu)003:3485: de ni gsang snying le'u tha ma las /
NK075(bu)003:3486: sa rnams khyad par bkod pa yang //
NK075(bu)003:3487: gsang ba'i snying por 'gro ba'i lam //
NK075(bu)003:3490: gdul bya blo gang la mos pa ltar drang ba'i
NK075(bu)003:3491: phyir kun brtags kyi 'khrul snang thams cad med pa
NK075(bu)003:3492: dang / gzhan dbang gi rgyu rkyen rten 'brel tsam yod pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:3493: 'gyur ba med pa'i yongs grub sogs rtag par 'dod pa ston pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:3495: gang la mos pa'i gdul bya dag /
NK075(bu)003:3496: mtshan nyid gsum gyi mthun drang phyir //
NK075(bu)003:3497: med pa kun brtags med par bstan //
NK075(bu)003:3499: rtag la yongs su grub par bstan //
NK075(bu)003:3502: skye ba med las thams cad skyes //
NK075(bu)003:3505: sems can 'ga' zhig gis rang rang gi gzugs dang /
NK075(bu)003:3509: mi'i yon tan chung ngu de dag gi gnyen por /
NK075(bu)003:3510: sangs rgyas longs sku'i yon tan rgya chen po bshad pa des nga rgyal zhi bar bya ste /
NK075(bu)003:3512: yon tan phyogs kyis dregs pa dag /
NK075(bu)003:3513: zil gyis mnan pa drang ba'i phyir //
NK075(bu)003:3514: gnyen por gyur pa'i yon tan rnams //
NK075(bu)003:3515: brjod bya zhi bya gsang sgor bya //
NK075(bu)003:3517: de'ang le'u gsum pa'i stod bstan pa 'byung ba spyi'i gleng gzhi dang /
NK075(bu)003:3518: bcu gsum pa'i rgyud kyi yon tan dang /
NK075(bu)003:3519: bcu bzhi pa glu drug gi yon tan rnams kyis ston no //
NK075(bu)003:3521: gsang sngags la blo ma mos pa'i gang zag kha
NK075(bu)003:3522: cig brtul zhugs kyi spyod pa la dga' ba rnams
NK075(bu)003:3523: / de dag sngags la gzhug cing 'bras bu thob pa'i thabs kyis 'du shes bsgyur ba ste /
NK075(bu)003:3524: lta sgom rlang po'i tshig dang /
NK075(bu)003:3525: sbyor sgrol la sogs pa'i spyod pa rang kha ma
NK075(bu)003:3526: de nyid kyis grol ba'i thabs yod pa skad kyi
NK075(bu)003:3529: 'du shes log pas log pa rnams //
NK075(bu)003:3530: sbas pa'i thabs kyis 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK075(bu)003:3531: brda dang gcus tshig sna tshogs kyis //
NK075(bu)003:3532: zab mo'i don la gzud par bya //
NK075(bu)003:3534: de ltar sngags nang gi ldem dgongs zab mo'i don rnams /
NK075(bu)003:3535: yo ga man chad kyi gdul bya blo dman la mi 'tshams kyang /
NK075(bu)003:3536: bla med rang gi gdul bya blo mchog la 'tshams pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:3538: bya ngang mo la sa la 'gro ba'i tshe snga
NK075(bu)003:3539: rjes dang phyi rjes dang 'brel ba'i chos rnam pa
NK075(bu)003:3540: gnyis dang ldan pa ltar du /
NK075(bu)003:3541: 'brel mtshams sbyor ba'i tshig gis gzhan slob ma'i don
NK075(bu)003:3542: byed pa'i tshe bya ngang mo 'gros pa'i chos gnyis
NK075(bu)003:3543: ltar / le'u gong 'og gi mtshamsa sbrel ba ni 'khrugs yod na 'khrugs ltar sbrel /
NK075(bu)003:3544: 'khrugs med na gzhung ltar tshig don sbrel nas drang por bshad do //
NK075(bu)003:3546: me long gi chos la gzugs brnyan 'char bas bzhin
NK075(bu)003:3547: gyi skyon ngos zin pa ltar mtshon pa'i dpe gtan
NK075(bu)003:3548: tshigs kyisa / gzhi lam 'bras bu'i don kun dang /
NK075(bu)003:3549: lam la rgyud don dngos po bcu la sogs pa rnams gtan la phab par byed pa la /
NK075(bu)003:3555: don gyi phyogs gcig dper blang ba'i dang /
NK075(bu)003:3556: shin tu lkog gyur gyi dpe dang bdun po de rnams kyis gang la gang 'os su sbyor nas /
NK075(bu)003:3557: dpe gtan tshigs kyis mtshon pa'i thog tu don de
NK075(bu)003:3558: gtan la dbab nas mi gsal ba gsal bar byed
NK075(bu)003:3560: mi 'jigs pa seng ge'i phru gus rtsal sbyangsa pa'i tshe /
NK075(bu)003:3561: pha'i yar mar phar tshur la mchongs nas drang por 'gro ba ltar du /
NK075(bu)003:3562: bsnol mtshams 'phen sdud kyi tshigs gis 'bru dang tshig gi 'dug sa bsgyur /
NK075(bu)003:3563: don gyi 'khrugs rnams go rim bsdebsa nas rgyud kyi
NK075(bu)003:3564: don phyi ci ma log par ston de bshad pa'o
NK075(bu)003:3565: // gsum pa dgos ched kyi mjug bsdu ba'o //
NK075(bu)003:3567: rgyud kyi tshig gis mtshon par byas nas thabs grol
NK075(bu)003:3568: gnyis kyi don de mngon sum du snang bar byed
NK075(bu)003:3569: do // lnga pa rgyud gdams shing gtad pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:3571: rgyud gdams shing gtad pa la bzhi ste /
NK075(bu)003:3574: gdams shing gtad pa'i ngo bo bstan pa gang yin
NK075(bu)003:3575: pa de dgos ched ci yi phyir gtad ce na
NK075(bu)003:3576: / de la ston pa ni rgyal ba drug pa kun tu bzang po des /
NK075(bu)003:3577: 'khor ni rgyal sras sdud pa po mdzad pa'i phyag
NK075(bu)003:3578: na rdo rje lhan cig pa'i 'khor la gtad de
NK075(bu)003:3580: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad la //
NK075(bu)003:3581: gsang ba 'di las gzhan mi mnga' //
NK075(bu)003:3582: sgro dang skur pa zhi ba yi //
NK075(bu)003:3583: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na //
NK075(bu)003:3584: nyid de nges pa'i dbyings nas phyung //
NK075(bu)003:3586: go phye ba'i 'khor ma 'ongs pa'i gang zag chos kyi mig can la gtad /
NK075(bu)003:3588: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi //
NK075(bu)003:3589: phyag rgya gsang chen snying po 'di //
NK075(bu)003:3590: rtogs smra bar gang byed pa //
NK075(bu)003:3591: de nyid nga yin dbang yang rdzogs //
NK075(bu)003:3592: de ni nges par lung bstan te //
NK075(bu)003:3593: sras ni thugs las skyes pa yin //
NK075(bu)003:3594: sa rab rig pa 'dzin la gnas //
NK075(bu)003:3597: rang rig ye shes rgyud don phyir //
NK075(bu)003:3598: rang snang rig pa mngon byas pas //
NK075(bu)003:3599: rig 'dzin mchog de lhun grub pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:3600: ting 'dzin nus pa'i mthu med kyang //
NK075(bu)003:3601: sa sbyangs sems dpa' bskyed du med //
NK075(bu)003:3602: bder gshegs nyid dang spyod yul gcig /
NK075(bu)003:3603: rig pa'i skyes bu lung thob pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:3606: de lta bu yi rang bzhin de //
NK075(bu)003:3607: gzhan la ma brtan mi 'gal bar //
NK075(bu)003:3608: mngon sum rig pa thag chod na //
NK075(bu)003:3609: rnal 'byor pa la slob pa yin //
NK075(bu)003:3612: rnam dag lam chen kun sgrol 'dir //
NK075(bu)003:3613: skal ldan gang zhig su zhugs pa //
NK075(bu)003:3615: nges par 'char gyi brtson par gyis //
NK075(bu)003:3616: de nyid sems kyi me long de //
NK075(bu)003:3617: mngon sum gsal bar rtogs ma thag /
NK075(bu)003:3618: 'gro ba'i lus la sangs rgyas yin //
NK075(bu)003:3620: sogs kyi sgras ma mo dang mkha' 'gro dang /
NK075(bu)003:3621: tshangs pa brgya byin phyogs skyong la sogs te /
NK075(bu)003:3622: sgyu 'phrul rgyas pa'i le'u zhe dgu pa las /
NK075(bu)003:3623: gsang ba'i snying po nges pa 'di //
NK075(bu)003:3624: gsang sngags kun gyi rgyal ba yin //
NK075(bu)003:3625: thabs chen mtshon pa'i shes rab yin //
NK075(bu)003:3626: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i snying po dang //
NK075(bu)003:3627: gsang ba'i rgyud chen mang po rnams //
NK075(bu)003:3628: nga yi thugs las sprul pa rnams //
NK075(bu)003:3629: tshangs pa dang ni brgya byin dang //
NK075(bu)003:3630: dbang phyug chen po la sogs pa //
NK075(bu)003:3631: ded dpon 'phrog ma'i bu rnams dang //
NK075(bu)003:3632: lus dang ba glang spyod pa dang //
NK075(bu)003:3633: sgra mi snyan dang 'dzam gling du //
NK075(bu)003:3634: nga yi thugs kyi snying po 'di //
NK075(bu)003:3635: phyogs bcu kun tu 'phel ba dang //
NK075(bu)003:3636: de yi gzugs la gtad pa ni //
NK075(bu)003:3637: yid bzhin mdzod 'byor bka' yi gnas //
NK075(bu)003:3638: bstan pa 'dzin par nus pa la //
NK075(bu)003:3639: gsang ba'i snying po shin tu gtad //
NK075(bu)003:3641: gdam shing gtad pa'i ngo bo la gnyis las /
NK075(bu)003:3643: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po ni rtsol sgrub ril dang bral bar gdams pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:3645: kye phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i rang bzhin 'di //
NK075(bu)003:3646: de bzhin gshegs pa'i ngo bo nyid //
NK075(bu)003:3649: lam rkyen yi ge'i rgyud rnams gsungs pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:3651: bstan pa mi nub par bya ba'i phyir sdud pa po la gtad /
NK075(bu)003:3652: bstan pa dar zhing rgyas par bya ba'i phyir gang zag chos kyi mig can la gtad /
NK075(bu)003:3653: bstan pa bsrung zhing thams cad du 'phel bar bya ba'i phyir ma dang /
NK075(bu)003:3654: mkha' 'gro la sogs la gtad pa'a //
NK075(bu)003:3655: gsum pa lam dang 'bras bu'i chos rnams rang gi
NK075(bu)003:3656: skabs su 'byung bas 'dir ma bstan pa'i 'thad pa'o
NK075(bu)003:3658: shes par bya ba'i yul lnga po de nyid rgyud gsang snying gi shes bya'i yan lag yin te /
NK075(bu)003:3659: de nyid bsgom par bya ba'i thabs mina no //
NK075(bu)003:3660: 'o na nyams len sgom thabs dang 'bras bu gar bshad ce na /
NK075(bu)003:3661: shes bya lnga po de yi phyi ma thun mong
NK075(bu)003:3662: dang mchog gi lam thabs grol gyi skabs dang 'bras
NK075(bu)003:3663: bu'i skabs su shes dgos mod /
NK075(bu)003:3664: de yang lam bsgrub pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:3665: 'bras bu thob pa gnyis ni 'og tu 'chad de /
NK075(bu)003:3666: rang rang gi skabs su rgyas par 'byung ba de
NK075(bu)003:3667: bas na 'dir shes bya yul lnga'i skabs su bsgom
NK075(bu)003:3668: bya bshad pa ma yin te ma dgos pa'i phyir
NK075(bu)003:3669: ro // gnyis pa bar du thun mong dang mchog gi lam bgrod tshul gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:3671: dang po spyir bstan pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:3673: shes bya lnga po gong du song nas bar du
NK075(bu)003:3674: bsgom bya la blo mosa pa des lam gzhol te
NK075(bu)003:3675: bgrod pa'i sdom tshig ni 'di lta ste /
NK075(bu)003:3676: lam stegs su thun mong bgrod tshul ni /
NK075(bu)003:3677: lha mi'i theg pas dge bcu la spyod tshul dang /
NK075(bu)003:3678: nyan thos kyis lam lnga sa brgyad bgrod tshul dang /
NK075(bu)003:3679: rang sangs rgyas kyis lam lnga bgrod tshul dang /
NK075(bu)003:3680: byang chub sems dpa' lam lnga sa brgyad bgrod tshul dang /
NK075(bu)003:3681: gsang sngags phyi rgyud sde gsum gyis bskyed rdzogs kyi sgo nas lam bgrod tshul rnams /
NK075(bu)003:3682: rang rang gi gzhung lugs su shes par bya'o //
NK075(bu)003:3683: khyad par du theg mchog ma h+aa'i lam bgrod tshul ste gnyis so //
NK075(bu)003:3684: gnyis pa theg mchog gi lam khyad par du bstan pa de la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:3688: tha ma theg mchog ma h+aa la yang gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:3689: so so skye bos 'dod yon lnga la dngos su
NK075(bu)003:3690: spyod pa de dang rjes su mthun par thabs lam
NK075(bu)003:3691: gyi lam la gzhol ba ste bgrod pa'i tshul dang
NK075(bu)003:3692: / rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa'i pha rol tu
NK075(bu)003:3693: phyin pa'i lam dang rjes su mthun par shes ra
NK075(bu)003:3694: ba grol lam la gzhol te bgrod pa'i tshul dang
NK075(bu)003:3695: / gnyis so // de yang thabs lam de dang grol lam de gnyis po re re la'ang /
NK075(bu)003:3696: gdul bya dbang po rno rtul gyis phye bas cig
NK075(bu)003:3697: char pa dang rim gyis pas sbyor bar byed pa
NK075(bu)003:3698: la thabs grol gyi lam rang rang dang rjes su
NK075(bu)003:3699: mthun par lung nas bshad pa bzhin du 'og rgyas
NK075(bu)003:3700: bshad kyi skabs su ston pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:3701: de yang bde ba che chung gi sgo nas thabs lam dang grol lam gnyis su dbye ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:3702: blo che chung gi sgo nas rim dang cig char gnyis su dbye ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:3703: mtshan ma che chung gi sgo nas lha dang mi rtog pa gnyis su dbye ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:3704: gdul bya rgyud drag zhan gyi sgo nas zhi khro gnyis su dbye ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:3705: rim pa 'dor mi 'dor gyi sgo nas thod rgal mthar chags gnyis su dbye ba las /
NK075(bu)003:3707: bshad pa de la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:3714: so so skye bos 'dod yon lnga yi bde ba
NK075(bu)003:3715: dngos su spyod pa de'i rjes su 'brang ba thabs
NK075(bu)003:3716: lam gyi lam bgrod pa la'ang /
NK075(bu)003:3717: sbyangs pa'i las 'phro che chung ngam /
NK075(bu)003:3718: snod kyi dbang po rno rtul dang /
NK075(bu)003:3719: bcud kyi skal ba yod med kyi dbang gis phye ba las /
NK075(bu)003:3720: gdul bya rang rang gi blo dang 'tshams para thabs
NK075(bu)003:3721: lam steng 'og gi gdams ngag gis lus sems grol
NK075(bu)003:3723: spyi bo bde chen gyi 'khor lo dang /
NK075(bu)003:3724: mgrin pa longs spyod kyi dang /
NK075(bu)003:3726: lte ba sprul pa'i 'khor lo dang bzhi la rang gnas kyi thig le byang sems yod pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:3727: rang gi thig le byed pa sdom pa'i thabs 'khrul
NK075(bu)003:3728: 'khor dang bcas pa bsgoms pa'i stobs las bde stong
NK075(bu)003:3729: gi ye shes byung ba de la dper na /
NK075(bu)003:3730: khams gnyis kyi lus grub lugs kyi spyod pa mi
NK075(bu)003:3731: 'dra ba yis phye bas dang po 'dod khams pa'i
NK075(bu)003:3732: lus lhur len nas gnas pa la /
NK075(bu)003:3733: mngal nas ming gzugs skye mched drug rim par skye ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:3734: gzugs khams bardzusa skyes dang nas skye mched drug rdzogs par smin pa'i tshul du /
NK075(bu)003:3735: steng sgo rim gyis pa dang 'og sgo cig char du snang ba ni 'di lta ste /
NK075(bu)003:3736: gnyis pa bshad pa de la gsum ste /
NK075(bu)003:3738: dang po rim gyis pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:3740: shira ni rtsa tsakra ni 'khor lo a sha dang /
NK075(bu)003:3741: ya mo cha ni drug ste /
NK075(bu)003:3743: rkyen 'khor lo gnyis dang drug go //
NK075(bu)003:3745: lte ba sprul pa'i 'khor lo rtsa 'dab drug cu rtsa gnyis dbus na /
NK075(bu)003:3746: thig le a thung shad kyi dbyibs su gnas pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:3747: snying kha chos kyi 'khor lo rtsa 'dab brgyad kyi dbus na /
NK075(bu)003:3748: thig le wa gi dbyibs su dang /
NK075(bu)003:3749: mgrin pa longs spyod kyi 'khor lo rtsa 'dab bcu drug gi dbus na /
NK075(bu)003:3750: thig le +aa gi dbyibs su dang /
NK075(bu)003:3751: klad pa bde chen gyi 'khor lo rtsa 'dabs sum cu rtsa gnyis kyi dbus na /
NK075(bu)003:3752: thig le ha gi dbyibs su gnas so //
NK075(bu)003:3754: sum mdo me'i 'khor lo na ra dang /
NK075(bu)003:3755: sgrom mado'am gshang kha rlung gi 'khor lo na ya gnas pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:3756: de lam pas bsgom pa'i dus na /
NK075(bu)003:3757: 'og rlung bsdoms pa las rang gnas kyi yi ge
NK075(bu)003:3758: ya las sgrol ma ste rlung gyen du 'gro bas
NK075(bu)003:3760: des a thung gi me sbar bas /
NK075(bu)003:3761: rtsa a ba d+hu ti'i nang du me sna zhugs
NK075(bu)003:3762: de la brten pa'i lte ba'i thig le de rtog
NK075(bu)003:3764: de nas rim pa ru snying kha dang /
NK075(bu)003:3766: spyi bo'i 'khor lo rnams kyi thig le rtog pas 'khyags pa rnams bzhus nas /
NK075(bu)003:3767: thig le'i 'od zer spyi bo nas 'thon te /
NK075(bu)003:3768: phyogs bcu'i de bzhin gshegs pa rnams la bde stong gi mchod pa phul bas /
NK075(bu)003:3769: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyis sbyor ba mdzad pa'i
NK075(bu)003:3770: byang sems ye shes kyii bdud rtsi'i chu rgyun tshur
NK075(bu)003:3771: 'dus spyi bo'i thig le la phog /
NK075(bu)003:3772: 'od du zhu bas lus kun khyab ste /
NK075(bu)003:3773: rkyal pa zhos bkang ba lta bur gyur par bsgoms pa yisa /
NK075(bu)003:3774: dga' ba bzhi bye brag tu bskyed pa'i cha'am 'og sgo'i sngon 'agro'am cha lag yin no //
NK075(bu)003:3775: gnyis pa cig char ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:3777: steng sgo rim gyis pa de sngon du song nas phyi ma 'og sgo cig char ba ni /
NK075(bu)003:3778: yab kyi gsang ba'i dbang po dang yum gyi gsang ba'i yul gnyis 'dzom pa ste /
NK075(bu)003:3779: de yang yab kyi rdo rje nor bu'i dbyibs sam /
NK075(bu)003:3780: yang na rdo rje thig le la bde ba kun 'byung bas nora bu /
NK075(bu)003:3781: yum gyi mkha' pad+ma'i dbyibs sam /
NK075(bu)003:3782: yang na bde ba skye dus nyon mongs pa'i dri mas ma gos pas chu skyes te pad+ma dang /
NK075(bu)003:3783: de gnyis las su rung ba dang ldan par gyur pas /
NK075(bu)003:3784: rig ma lo bcu drug lon pa de la /
NK075(bu)003:3788: spyod lam gyi yon tan dang bzhi rgyud lung man ngag nas bshad pa bzhin rdzogs pa la /
NK075(bu)003:3789: yab yum gyi mkha' gsang bsnol mar byin gyis brlab cing /
NK075(bu)003:3790: sbyor ba'i brdas bsnol mar bskul na /
NK075(bu)003:3795: de ltar phyag rgya bzhis rol nas /
NK075(bu)003:3796: yab yum gyi dbang po kha sbyor bas bde ba g.yo ba'i tshul ni /
NK075(bu)003:3797: rten yab yum gnyis de las yas 'bab dang mas brten gyi dga' bzhi skyes pa de yang /
NK075(bu)003:3798: rten yab thabs kyi cha yin pas bde ba dang tshul mthun /
NK075(bu)003:3799: yum shes rab kyi cha yin pas stong pa dang
NK075(bu)003:3800: tshul mthun pa'i yab yum kha sbyor bas thabs dang
NK075(bu)003:3801: shes rab dbyer med pa'i bde stong gi don rang
NK075(bu)003:3802: rig pa'i mngon sum du mthong ba yin no //
NK075(bu)003:3803: de yang dga' ba bzhi'i skye tshul rgyas par bshad na /
NK075(bu)003:3804: dang po yas 'bab kyi dga' ba ste /
NK075(bu)003:3805: de yang byang sems kyi bde ba'i chu rgyun spyi
NK075(bu)003:3806: bo bde chen gyi 'khor lo nas mgrin par babs
NK075(bu)003:3807: pas dga' ba / snying gar mchog dga' /
NK075(bu)003:3808: lte ba dga' bral gsang ba rdo rje'i lam nas byung ba'i tshe /
NK075(bu)003:3809: dga' bzhi'i mthar thug lhan cig skyes pa'i dga' ba bzhi'i mthar thug nyams su myong zhing /
NK075(bu)003:3810: rten byang chub sems kyi thig le yum gyi pad+ma
NK075(bu)003:3811: reg pa'i gnas su 'khyil ba yum gyi nyi ma
NK075(bu)003:3812: byang chub sems dang rtse 'phrad nas thig le phyed
NK075(bu)003:3814: yab yum gnyis kyi gsang rtsar phan tshun 'dres pa ni /
NK075(bu)003:3815: nyon mongs rang sar grol nas kun rdzob bde stong gi ye shes mngon du gyur pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:3816: de nas lhan cig skyes pa'i dga' ba'i ye shes
NK075(bu)003:3817: kyi bdag nyid thig le nyi zla gnyis 'dres te
NK075(bu)003:3818: 'gro 'ong byang chub kyi sems tshur log nas gsang
NK075(bu)003:3819: ba rdo rje'i bu gur bstim zhing /
NK075(bu)003:3820: thig le rdo rje'i lam nas yar log pa ni mas brtan zag med kyi dga' ba ste /
NK075(bu)003:3821: lte bar brtan pa dga' ba /
NK075(bu)003:3824: spyi bor brtan pa ni lhan cig skyes pa'i dga' ba'o //
NK075(bu)003:3825: de tsam na bcu gcig kun tu 'od kyi sa rdzogs shing /
NK075(bu)003:3826: de'i yon tan gyis thig les lus thams cad du
NK075(bu)003:3827: khyab cing brtan pas 'khor ba'i skyon gyis ma gos
NK075(bu)003:3828: pas / bcu gnyis pad+ma spyan gyis dang /
NK075(bu)003:3829: rtog tshogs thams cad sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil
NK075(bu)003:3830: 'khor du snang bas bcu gsum yi ge 'khor lo
NK075(bu)003:3834: thabs lam 'di skabs gar bshad na /
NK075(bu)003:3835: mchod pa la phyi nang gsang gsum las gsum pa gsang mchod kyi skabs su bshad /
NK075(bu)003:3837: gsal ldan ma 'am byin rlabs la //
NK075(bu)003:3838: stong gsum yungs 'brur gzhug tshul du //
NK075(bu)003:3840: mnyes nas grub pa'i dam tshig mchog /
NK075(bu)003:3841: bdag nyid chen po mchod pa yis //
NK075(bu)003:3842: sangs rgyas dkyil 'khor ma lus mnyes //
NK075(bu)003:3843: srid gsum 'gro ba thams cad la //
NK075(bu)003:3844: dga' ba chen pos khyab par 'gyur //
NK075(bu)003:3846: dkyil 'khora drug pa byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor gyi skabs su bshad de /
NK075(bu)003:3848: shin tu phra ba'i dam tshig mchog /
NK075(bu)003:3849: phyag rgya chen po'i phyag mthil du //
NK075(bu)003:3850: thugs kyi dkyil 'khor dam pa de //
NK075(bu)003:3851: sor ni bzhi yi tshad du bya //
NK075(bu)003:3855: de'ang chags pa can la thabs lam de nyid ma
NK075(bu)003:3856: gtogs pa grol lam gyi thos bsam sgom pa'i shes
NK075(bu)003:3857: rab gsum gyis nyon mongs pa chags rtog gi blo
NK075(bu)003:3858: de nyid mi 'byang ba yin te /
NK075(bu)003:3859: de bas na dang nas bde ba la sems bde
NK075(bu)003:3860: ba ma spangs nyon mongs pa ma spangs nyon mongs
NK075(bu)003:3861: pa chags rtog rang dag tu song nas mthar bde
NK075(bu)003:3862: stong gi ye shes mngon sum du rdzogsa pa'i phyir
NK075(bu)003:3863: thabs lam zhes bya ba'i nges tshig gi ming thob
NK075(bu)003:3864: pa'o // de yang khog gzhung las /
NK075(bu)003:3865: 'jug dang thob phyir lam brjod de //
NK075(bu)003:3866: skye bo gnyis sgrol phyir bzhag pa //
NK075(bu)003:3867: las su rung ba lam mthar phyir //
NK075(bu)003:3869: gnyis pa grol lam la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:3873: shesa raba kyi pha rola tu phyin pa'i lam gyi rjes su sbyor ba grol lam pa de'nga /
NK075(bu)003:3874: lam gyi gtso bo dang de sgrub thabs kyi yan lag cha rkyen du /
NK075(bu)003:3882: mchod pa ste rgyud don rnam pa bcu po yin te /
NK075(bu)003:3883: de yang gtso bo dang cha rkyen gyi khyad par ni /
NK075(bu)003:3885: skabs kyi gtso dang grogs kyi tshul //
NK075(bu)003:3887: gnas skabs kyi gtso bor gyur pa gcig lam gyi ngo bo /
NK075(bu)003:3888: de'i grogs byed pa'i ngos nas cha rkyen yin par gsungs so //
NK075(bu)003:3889: 'on kyang lam gyi gtso bo ngo bo'i 'dod lugs la mang ste /
NK075(bu)003:3891: rtogs nas 'dris par gang byed pa //
NK075(bu)003:3892: lam gyi ngo bo byang chub sems //
NK075(bu)003:3893: zhes pas lam gyi ngo bo byang chub sems bzhag /
NK075(bu)003:3895: kun kyang smin zin bgrod pa med //
NK075(bu)003:3896: de nyid lam gyi ngo bo ste //
NK075(bu)003:3898: bgrod bya'i don gnas pa'i ngos nas lam gyi ngo bor bzhag /
NK075(bu)003:3900: ngo bo shes rab rnam gsum ste //
NK075(bu)003:3901: sems bzhi shes par bstan pa ste //
NK075(bu)003:3902: zhes pas bgrod tshul gyi ngos nas lam gyi ngo bor bzhag /
NK075(bu)003:3904: ngo bo thabs dang shes rab ste //
NK075(bu)003:3906: dbye ba'i rnam grangs kyi ngos nas lam gyi ngo bor bzhag /
NK075(bu)003:3908: ngo bo sems lnga skyes pa ste //
NK075(bu)003:3911: 'jig ldang la sogs byang sems lnga //
NK075(bu)003:3912: nges par skye ba'i ngo bor 'dod //
NK075(bu)003:3914: lam gyi ngo bo sems lnga la bzhag ste /
NK075(bu)003:3916: thun mong sems lnga ni sbyangs pa'i gang zag gi skabs su skye bas zhor la bshad do //
NK075(bu)003:3917: 'dir mchog gi sems lnga la gnyis las /
NK075(bu)003:3918: dang po grol lam gyi sems lnga ni /
NK075(bu)003:3919: skye bo dang mu stegs can theg pa 'og ma pa rnams kyi zhe 'dod las grol nas /
NK075(bu)003:3920: gsang sngags su 'go g.yo ba ni /
NK075(bu)003:3921: g.yo ldan byang chub kyi sems te /
NK075(bu)003:3925: gzhi des dbyer med kyi don khong du chud par smon pa ni /
NK075(bu)003:3926: smon pa byang chub kyi sems te /
NK075(bu)003:3928: gzhi dpe khong du chud smon pa //
NK075(bu)003:3930: de nas dkyil 'khor la 'jug pa ni 'jug pa'i sems te /
NK075(bu)003:3932: lhag pa gzugs brnyan 'jug pa ste //
NK075(bu)003:3934: de nas dbang zhus shing bslab bya la gnas pa
NK075(bu)003:3935: dang thos bsam gnas pa ni gnas pa'i sems te
NK075(bu)003:3937: rigs nges 'gyur la phan pa bcu //
NK075(bu)003:3938: nus pa gnyis kyi byin brlabs bzhag /
NK075(bu)003:3939: rang gi spyan mchog 'byed la brtson //
NK075(bu)003:3940: thos bsam dam pa len par byed //
NK075(bu)003:3942: thos bsam mthar phyin nas go rtogs kyi don dang ldan pa ni /
NK075(bu)003:3943: mthar phyin pa'i byang chub sems te /
NK075(bu)003:3945: thos bsam brten pas lta mthar phyin //
NK075(bu)003:3947: gnyis pa thabs lam gyi sems lnga ni /
NK075(bu)003:3949: 'jig dang ldang dang gnas pa dang //
NK075(bu)003:3950: smon pa byang chub sems yin no //
NK075(bu)003:3951: g.yo dang bskyed dang ldang dang gnas //
NK075(bu)003:3952: zhes gsungs pa'i don gyi lnga las /
NK075(bu)003:3954: lam thabs lam nyams su len pa'i dus su /
NK075(bu)003:3955: rtsa gnas nas thig le 'go g.yo tsam na /
NK075(bu)003:3956: bde ba 'go ldang ba'i tshul du 'dug pas na /
NK075(bu)003:3957: g.yo ldang byang chub kyi sems so //
NK075(bu)003:3959: bde ba snga ma 'jig tsam na phyi ma la 'jug pa ni /
NK075(bu)003:3962: lus kyi rtsa dang thig le rnams rang sar gnas pas /
NK075(bu)003:3963: bde ba yang rang sar gnas pa ni /
NK075(bu)003:3964: gnas pa byang chub kyi sems so //
NK075(bu)003:3966: snga ma'i bde ba la dmigs shing phyii ma'i bde
NK075(bu)003:3967: ba la smon pa ni smon pa byang chub kyi
NK075(bu)003:3969: thig le rdo rje'i rtse nas phar 'gro ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:3970: pad+ma'i ze 'bru nas tshur 'ong ba ni /
NK075(bu)003:3972: 'o na lam gyi ngo bo sems lnga yin na /
NK075(bu)003:3973: lam pa rang gang gis byed ce na /
NK075(bu)003:3974: sems lnga skye ba'i gzhi ma'i ngos nas lam pa yin la /
NK075(bu)003:3975: skyes pa rang gi ngos nas lam gyi ngo bo yin no //
NK075(bu)003:3976: de nas phyag rgya spros pa mthar phyin pa'i tshe /
NK075(bu)003:3977: thabs grol gyi sems lnga dbyer med du nyams su blangs nas lam mthar phyin par byed do //
NK075(bu)003:3978: gnyis pa bshad pa de la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:3985: 'dir slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang bas ting nge 'dzin gtso bor bzhag ste /
NK075(bu)003:3986: de yang gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga grol lam
NK075(bu)003:3987: gyi sgor 'jug pa kun gyi don du gnyer bar
NK075(bu)003:3988: bya ba la'ang / lam gyi gtso bo'am mchog tu
NK075(bu)003:3989: gyur pa ting nge 'dzin bsgom par bya ba la'ang
NK075(bu)003:3990: sngon thabs lam la rim cig char gnyis su 'byung
NK075(bu)003:3991: bya ba la'ang / ba bzhin du / 'dir grol
NK075(bu)003:3992: lam gyi ting nge 'dzin la'ang rim cig char gnyis
NK075(bu)003:3994: gnyis pa bshad pa de la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:3996: dang po la cig char ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:3998: cig char ba'i gang zag ni blo'i mchog ste ma
NK075(bu)003:3999: h+aa rtogs pa'i skal ba dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor
NK075(bu)003:4000: ba rnams kyis / gdod ma nas bden gsum dbyer
NK075(bu)003:4001: med kyi lta ba cig char du blo la nges
NK075(bu)003:4002: par chud par rtogs nas ting nge 'dzin yang der
NK075(bu)003:4003: ba rnams kyis / gnas pa la / 'khor 'das gnyis su med par byang ba stong ba /
NK075(bu)003:4005: sems dbyer med pa'i don de la rim gyis pa'i de ting /
NK075(bu)003:4007: rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin gyi byang chub kyi semsa bsgom
NK075(bu)003:4008: pa rnam pa gsum dus gcig tu rdzogs te cig
NK075(bu)003:4009: char sgom pa'o // de yang gsang snying las /
NK075(bu)003:4010: ye shes phyogs bzhi dbus brtags te //
NK075(bu)003:4011: dkyil 'khor bsam yas lhun grub ni //
NK075(bu)003:4012: rdzogs chen rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK075(bu)003:4016: thig le chen po'i rang bzhin la //
NK075(bu)003:4017: sgom pa rnam gsum dus gcig rdzogs //
NK075(bu)003:4018: de ni de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings //
NK075(bu)003:4019: de ni kun tu snang gi ngang //
NK075(bu)003:4020: de ni rgyu yi rim par ldan //
NK075(bu)003:4023: sgom pa rnam bzhi zung ldan pa //
NK075(bu)003:4024: gdod ma nyid nas goms par byed //
NK075(bu)003:4028: blo chung ba'i gang zag ni cig char ba de las bzlog pa ste /
NK075(bu)003:4029: dper na rgyud snga ma las 'bras bu phyi ma 'byung ba'i rten 'brel bzhin du /
NK075(bu)003:4030: lta ba bden pa dbyer med kyi go ba yod kyang /
NK075(bu)003:4032: kun ting phyag rgya gcig pa la phra rags gnyis /
NK075(bu)003:4034: tshogs sgrub dang lnga yi lam la rim pa ltar
NK075(bu)003:4035: brten nas dona du gnyer bas mthar zag bcas bden
NK075(bu)003:4036: mthong ngam / zag med kyi bden pa mngon du byed de /
NK075(bu)003:4037: de nyid rgyas par ni 'og nas 'chad do //
NK075(bu)003:4038: gnyis pa cha rkyen la dgu ste /
NK075(bu)003:4039: lta sgom thun mong du bstan pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:4050: de'i rjes su sgom pa ting nge 'dzin no //
NK075(bu)003:4055: bgrod bya lam gyi gtso bo ting nge 'dzin gyi
NK075(bu)003:4056: sngon du lam gyi yan lag rgyud don bcu'i dang
NK075(bu)003:4057: po lta ba de'i sdom tshig ni /
NK075(bu)003:4059: rtogs par byed pa'i thabs dang /
NK075(bu)003:4062: rtogs pa'i yon tan dang lnga'i rim pas nang du ni /
NK075(bu)003:4063: shes rab kyi dbang po mchog gi spyod yul rnams
NK075(bu)003:4064: lta ba'i don rnams ni rdzogs par bshad pa ni
NK075(bu)003:4065: 'di lta ste / gnyis pa bshad pa de la lnga ste /
NK075(bu)003:4075: gsang sngags las gzhan pa'i theg 'og gi lta ba ngan pa'i mig de gsal ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:4076: theg mchog gsang sngags gang gi dgongs don spyan te
NK075(bu)003:4077: shes rab mchog lta ba'i don de mngon sum du
NK075(bu)003:4079: de'ang theg pa 'og ma'i lta ba ngan pa go
NK075(bu)003:4080: cha ngan pa dang 'dra ba ste rtol zhing 'bags
NK075(bu)003:4081: par byed pa'i thabs la gang gi bden pa dbyer
NK075(bu)003:4082: med kyi lta ba the tshom med pa'i don mdil
NK075(bu)003:4083: thung rnon po dang 'dra ba gcig rtogs par shin
NK075(bu)003:4085: gnyis pa bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:4089: phyogs 'dzin gyi lta bas phyogs med lhun grub mi rtogs pa'i dpe ni /
NK075(bu)003:4090: gling bzhi nas lta bas yul mthong rgya chung /
NK075(bu)003:4091: phal pa'i ri nag po dgu 'das nas de bas rgya che /
NK075(bu)003:4092: gser gyi ri bdun nas rim pa ltar de bas rgya che ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:4093: ri rab lhun po'i gnas nas lta bas thams cad
NK075(bu)003:4094: gsang ba'i rim pa pa de ltar yod pa bzhin
NK075(bu)003:4095: du / gnyis pa don de la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:4101: dang po lta bas gzhan sel lugs dang /
NK075(bu)003:4103: gnas skabs su sangs rgyas kyi rigsa ma sad pas med pa phyal rgyang gnyis dang /
NK075(bu)003:4104: rang bzhin gyis log pa mu rtug mu stegs dang /
NK075(bu)003:4105: phra ba chos bdag mchod pas phyi pa yin la /
NK075(bu)003:4106: rags pa gang zag gi bdag med par rtogs pas na nang pa ste /
NK075(bu)003:4107: de ltar phyi nang gnyis ltos pa nyan rang gnyis kyi lta ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:4108: snang ba'i gsal cha phyogs gcig sems yin par bsgrub ste /
NK075(bu)003:4109: sems rang rig rang gsal du 'dod pa sems tsam pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:4110: don dam stong pa dang kun rdzob snang ba gnyis
NK075(bu)003:4111: mi mthun pa tha dad du byas nas kun rdzob
NK075(bu)003:4112: 'gogsa pa dang don dam dag pa stong par 'dod
NK075(bu)003:4114: lta ba ngan pa de dag ni dper na zas
NK075(bu)003:4115: la dug btab pa'i cha yoda na zas dug can
NK075(bu)003:4116: de la gang gis mi reg ste mi za ba
NK075(bu)003:4117: bzhin du / gsang sngags kyi lta ba rtogs pa'i
NK075(bu)003:4118: gang zag gang gis snang stong phyogs 'dzin gyi lta
NK075(bu)003:4119: ba gol bar shes nas lta ngan der blo mi
NK075(bu)003:4121: gnyis pa sgom pa'i bsal bya'o //
NK075(bu)003:4123: chos nyid bsam gyis mi khyab pa gsang sngags bden gsum dbyer med kyi lta ba ma shes na /
NK075(bu)003:4124: sgom pa ni bsam pa'i 'gyu ba med par gnas pa zhi gnas tsam la brten pa des ni /
NK075(bu)003:4125: rnal 'byor bla med kyi dgongs pa gnyis med kyii
NK075(bu)003:4126: don nyams su myong zhing 'bras bu thob pa ni
NK075(bu)003:4127: ma yin no // de bas nam mkha' klong yangs las /
NK075(bu)003:4128: bde sdug ma dran btang snyoms ni //
NK075(bu)003:4129: zhi gnas ma rig gti mug de //
NK075(bu)003:4130: gang gi blo yang ma zhugs pas //
NK075(bu)003:4131: dge sdig gnyis su lung ma bstan //
NK075(bu)003:4133: gnyis pa don du gnyer ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:4135: gang zag gang gis lta sgom phyogs re ba la
NK075(bu)003:4136: skyon de ltar du yod par shes nas lta sgom
NK075(bu)003:4137: dbyer med rtogs pa'i thabs du ma'i sgo nas 'ub
NK075(bu)003:4139: snang stong dbyer med kyi don rtogs pas sgom pa la'ang /
NK075(bu)003:4140: rnal ma'i don la rang rig pa 'byor zhing tshogs
NK075(bu)003:4141: gnyis rdzogs shing sgrib gnyis byang sangs rgyas kyi sar
NK075(bu)003:4145: gsang sngags kyi rnal 'byor pa gang gis lam gyi
NK075(bu)003:4146: thog mar lta ba 'gro bas de'i don rang gi
NK075(bu)003:4147: rgyud la brten cing rtogs pa'i thabs la /
NK075(bu)003:4148: ting nge 'dzin gyi bye brag mi 'dra ba bskyed rim rnams dang /
NK075(bu)003:4149: rtsa thig rlung gsum du ma las spyod pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:4150: gzhan yang rtogs thabs kyi yan lag mang po ste /
NK075(bu)003:4153: slob grwa dang sgom grwa gtsug cing de la bkur ti bya ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:4154: nya stong dang brgyad gsum la sogs la dus mchod bya ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:4159: byams snying rje dga' ba btang snyoms te tshad med bzhi dang /
NK075(bu)003:4165: lha dang gsung rab bri ba /
NK075(bu)003:4166: dge ba'i dpung tshogs thams cad la 'bad par bya'o //
NK075(bu)003:4167: de dag ni brgyud pa yin la /
NK075(bu)003:4168: dngos su lta ba gtan la phab pa'i rgyu ni
NK075(bu)003:4169: lung rigs pa man ngag rnam par gsum gyi sgo
NK075(bu)003:4170: nas gtan la phab dgos pa yin te /
NK075(bu)003:4172: de bzhin bde bar gshegs pa'i rgyud //
NK075(bu)003:4173: bla ma mkhas pa'i man ngag dang //
NK075(bu)003:4174: rang gi nyams kyis bye brag rnams //
NK075(bu)003:4175: tshad ma gsum la brten nas ni //
NK075(bu)003:4178: lung dang man ngag rigs pa yi //
NK075(bu)003:4179: tshad ma dag gis gang gzhal ba //
NK075(bu)003:4180: gzhal byed de yang tshad mar 'gyur /
NK075(bu)003:4182: de yang gtan tshigs la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:4183: 'di la brtsegs sdeb gcig bya ste /
NK075(bu)003:4184: thun mong ma yin pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:4185: thun mong gi gtan tshigs so //
NK075(bu)003:4187: tshig don mi mthun pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:4189: dang po ni kun yin gang ma yin gyi gtan tshigs dang /
NK075(bu)003:4190: ma spangs mi ldan gyi gtan tshigs so //
NK075(bu)003:4191: gnyis pa tshig don mthun pa la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:4192: tshad ma bka' gzhung gi gtan tshigs dang /
NK075(bu)003:4193: sgra mthun don dpags kyi gtan tshigs so //
NK075(bu)003:4199: rang bzhin bden pa gsum gyi gtan tshigs so //
NK075(bu)003:4200: gnyis pa sgra mthun don dpags la bzhi ste /
NK075(bu)003:4204: mtshon pa dpe'i gtan tshigs rnams kyis gtan la phab lugs ni /
NK075(bu)003:4208: man ngag lam rim la sogs pa rnams las gragsa
NK075(bu)003:4209: pa rnams kyis lta ba rtogs pa'i rkyen byas te
NK075(bu)003:4210: / dper na ri rgyal lhun po'i kha nas thams
NK075(bu)003:4211: cad gsal ba lta bur 'khor 'das dbyer med ma
NK075(bu)003:4212: 'dres yongs rdzogs kyi don mthong ba gces so //
NK075(bu)003:4213: de yang mthong ba la rgyu rkyen 'tshogs dgos pas /
NK075(bu)003:4218: mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu ni ye gdod ma nas shes rab rang bzhin med pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:4219: thabs 'gag pa med pa gnyis dbyer med du rang la gnas pa yin te /
NK075(bu)003:4221: gdod nas shes rab lnga yin mtshungs //
NK075(bu)003:4223: gnyis pa lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu ni /
NK075(bu)003:4224: ye nas gnas pa'i don de nyid gong du bshad
NK075(bu)003:4225: pa'i gtan tshigs rnams kyis gtan la phab cing ngo
NK075(bu)003:4228: ces smos la sogs lhan cig byed //
NK075(bu)003:4230: gnyis pa rkyen la bzhi ste /
NK075(bu)003:4234: de ma thag pa'i rkyen no //
NK075(bu)003:4236: chos rang dang spyi'i mtshan nyid la brten nas rtogs dgos pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:4238: bla ma rdo rje slob dpon gyis gtan tshigs rim pas de dag ngo sprad pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:4240: rang bzhin gyi dbang rnon dang /
NK075(bu)003:4241: sbyangs pa'i dbang rnon gnyis kyis rtogs dgos pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:4245: rgyun rkyen dang gsum 'dzom pa'i de ma thag gi skad cig la ngo 'phrod dgos pa yin te /
NK075(bu)003:4247: des na rang spyi'i mtshan yul la //
NK075(bu)003:4248: bshes gnyen bdag po rim de dag /
NK075(bu)003:4249: dngas pa'i 'od dang bag chags rgyus //
NK075(bu)003:4251: yang rtogs thabs rgyu rkyen de dag bsdus na /
NK075(bu)003:4253: gang dag mnyan bsam shes rab tshe //
NK075(bu)003:4254: nyan cing thos 'dzin bsam pa dang //
NK075(bu)003:4255: bsam pa'i tshe na rtog dpyod pa //
NK075(bu)003:4256: gnyis po de dag shes pa'i rgyu //
NK075(bu)003:4257: mkhan po lung dang man ngag bcas //
NK075(bu)003:4258: lhan cig byed pa'i rkyen du 'dod //
NK075(bu)003:4259: rang bzhin bdun dang mtshungs ldan pa //
NK075(bu)003:4260: gcig shos rgyu ru nges pa yin //
NK075(bu)003:4262: de ltar gtan tshigs rgyu rkyen gang gi thog nas
NK075(bu)003:4263: grub mtha' bden pa dbyer med kyi nges shes skyes
NK075(bu)003:4264: pa'ang / bden gnyis dbyer med yin min gyi the
NK075(bu)003:4265: tshom za bas yin min la rtog dpyod byas pas
NK075(bu)003:4267: tha dad du byung bsam gyi som nyi za ba
NK075(bu)003:4268: de dag med pa la bden pa dbyer med kyi
NK075(bu)003:4270: de'ang bden pa dbyer med byung sems kyi nges 'jog gi blos rtog dpyod med pa yin te /
NK075(bu)003:4271: dper na gser gling rgyus bstan pa bzhin tu blo
NK075(bu)003:4272: de nyid rang rig pa'i ye shes su shar bas
NK075(bu)003:4273: 'khor 'das kyi chos gang yang dagga bsgrub dang spang
NK075(bu)003:4274: blang med pa'i rgyu gtan tshigs de las /
NK075(bu)003:4275: grub mtha'i ngo bo dgag bsgrub dang bral ba 'byung ba'i don yin te /
NK075(bu)003:4277: dgag pa med pas blang med phyir //
NK075(bu)003:4278: mtha' yi gzhung du bsgrub mi dgos //
NK075(bu)003:4281: lta ba phyogs ris mi phyed pa //
NK075(bu)003:4282: spyod pa blang dor mi bya'o //
NK075(bu)003:4283: zhes lta spyod 'brel pa'i phyir ro //
NK075(bu)003:4284: gsum pa ngo bo la bzhi ste /
NK075(bu)003:4286: dang po ngo bo dngos dang /
NK075(bu)003:4288: grub mtha' rtogs pa'i ngo bo ni /
NK075(bu)003:4289: mig la sogs pa'i dbang po drug gi yul drug
NK075(bu)003:4290: tu rnam shes drug 'char nas snang ba de yang
NK075(bu)003:4291: / lus snang sems gsum zung 'jug tu rtogs pa'i spyan lta ba la mchog tu brjod pa ni /
NK075(bu)003:4292: shes rab rang bzhin med pa don dam bden pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:4293: yul du shar ba'i shes pa dang bcas rang snang
NK075(bu)003:4294: 'gag pa med pa kun rdzob bden pa gnyis dbyer
NK075(bu)003:4295: med pa'i don mngon sum du rtogs pa ni /
NK075(bu)003:4296: rjes dpag gi rtogsa pa bas mchog gi don yin no //
NK075(bu)003:4297: de ltar mngon sum bzhi las /
NK075(bu)003:4298: rang rig pa'i mngon sum du rtogs pa'i yid rang byung gi ye shes mthong ba'i dus su /
NK075(bu)003:4299: mdud pa gcig grol bas do thag kun grol ba ltar /
NK075(bu)003:4300: tshogs brgyad tshogs drug rang snang gi ye shes gcig
NK075(bu)003:4301: po las ma g.yos shing ye shes lnga ma 'dres
NK075(bu)003:4302: la yongs su rdzogs par rtogs pa yin te /
NK075(bu)003:4304: snga ma kha cig mngon sum la //
NK075(bu)003:4305: drug gam brgyad nyid gnas gyur phyir //
NK075(bu)003:4306: shes rab dbang drug tshul gnas brjod //
NK075(bu)003:4307: nges par ma nor mthong ba yang //
NK075(bu)003:4308: ye shes lnga ru gsal ba'i phyir //
NK075(bu)003:4309: brgyad kyi ngo bo de nyid do //
NK075(bu)003:4311: de ltar shes rab kyi spyan gyi lta ba dam
NK075(bu)003:4312: pa'i ngo bo de kho na nyid rtogs pa yin
NK075(bu)003:4313: te bas na / de la phyi' yul dang nang
NK075(bu)003:4314: gi lus sems tha dad med par thams cad rig
NK075(bu)003:4315: pa rang snang ba'i phyir te /
NK075(bu)003:4317: lnga pa dmigs byed med phyir te //
NK075(bu)003:4318: de bas yul med rang gsal bas //
NK075(bu)003:4319: dbyings dang rig pa gnyis med par //
NK075(bu)003:4320: de bzhin nyid du rdo rje'i rigs //
NK075(bu)003:4321: gzung 'dzin bral ba'i rang rig nyid //
NK075(bu)003:4322: dmigs med tshul du rang snang ba //
NK075(bu)003:4324: gzhi mtha' bral lhun grub kyi don chos nyid spyi'i mtshan nyid dang /
NK075(bu)003:4325: khyad par rang gi mtshan nyid gnyis ma 'dres la
NK075(bu)003:4326: yongs su rdzogs par mthong ba med pa'i tshul du
NK075(bu)003:4327: mthong ba ste / thabs zhags las /
NK075(bu)003:4328: mthong ba med pa'i tshul du mthong ba'o //
NK075(bu)003:4331: nga dang bdag tu med pas na //
NK075(bu)003:4332: chos nyid ma dang 'phrad pa yin //
NK075(bu)003:4334: de la mngon sum dang rjes dpag gi go don ni /
NK075(bu)003:4335: spyir chos la tshad ma dang tshad min gnyis /
NK075(bu)003:4336: tshad min la 'gro ba rigs drug gi 'khrul snang /
NK075(bu)003:4347: sngar ma rtogs pa'i don la sgro 'dogs chod par byed pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:4349: gang zag gi gzhal bya bden rtogs dang ldan pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:4351: bslu ba med pa'i don de rgyud la nges par byas pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:4352: bzhi pa rnam grangs ni gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:4354: mngon sum dang ni rjes dpag gnyis /
NK075(bu)003:4363: ngo bo ni yul shes 'phrad pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:4364: mtshan ni rtog bral ma 'khrul ba'o //
NK075(bu)003:4365: nges tshig ni the tshom med par don nges pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:4370: rang rig pa'i mngon sum mo //
NK075(bu)003:4372: skad cig ma dang po la yul shes 'phrad pa tsam mo //
NK075(bu)003:4373: gnyis pa ni de'i rjes su zhugs pa'i shes pa
NK075(bu)003:4374: las nyid rang gi ngo bor the tshom chod pa'o
NK075(bu)003:4375: // gsum pa ni goms pa las byung ba ste
NK075(bu)003:4376: rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes gsal stong nyams
NK075(bu)003:4377: // su myong ba'o // de yang dag par 'jig rten pa'i mkhyen pa'i ye shes so //
NK075(bu)003:4379: bden gsum dbyer med rang rig pa'i mngon sum du rtogs pa ste /
NK075(bu)003:4380: dbye ba med pa'i ye shes so //
NK075(bu)003:4381: de ltar gsang sngags kyi lam gang zag blo rim gyis pas /
NK075(bu)003:4382: lta ba rtogs thabs kyi sgom pa'i skabs su mngon
NK075(bu)003:4383: sum bzhi rim gyis rtogs shing nyams su myong ba
NK075(bu)003:4384: yin no // lta ba rtogs pa ngo bo'i dus su /
NK075(bu)003:4385: mngon sum bzhi cig char du rtogs pa yin no //
NK075(bu)003:4386: dbang po'i mngon sum rig pa gcer 'phrad /
NK075(bu)003:4387: yid kyi mngon sum yid 'gyu ba rang grol /
NK075(bu)003:4388: rang rig mngon sum snang stong dbyer med /
NK075(bu)003:4389: rnal 'byor mngon sum chos kun ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa yin no //
NK075(bu)003:4390: de dag rgyas par gzhan du shes par bya'o //
NK075(bu)003:4391: gnyis pa rjes dpag la bzhi ste /
NK075(bu)003:4396: ngo bo ni shes pa gang zhig don dang 'brel zhing don gzhan mthong ba las byung ba'o //
NK075(bu)003:4397: mtshan nyid ni tshul gsum nges pa las skyes pa'i shes pa ma 'khrul ba'o //
NK075(bu)003:4398: nges tshig ni rtags gzung zhing 'brel pa dran pa'i rjes su dpag pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:4400: rang bzhin gyi gtan tshigs dang /
NK075(bu)003:4402: mi dmigs pa'i gtan tshigs so //
NK075(bu)003:4404: de la sbyor ba dgod na /
NK075(bu)003:4406: mi rtag pa ste zhes dam bca' /
NK075(bu)003:4407: skad cig ma'i skye 'gag dang bcas pa'i phyir /
NK075(bu)003:4408: dper na myu gu sngon po bzhin no //
NK075(bu)003:4411: me yod de zhes dam bca' /
NK075(bu)003:4412: rtags du ba mtshan nyid pa 'dug pa'i phyir dper na tshang khang bzhin no //
NK075(bu)003:4414: sa phyogs 'di chos bum pa med do zhes dam bca' /
NK075(bu)003:4415: yod na snang rung la mi dmigs pa'i phyir /
NK075(bu)003:4416: dper na ri bong rwa bzhin no //
NK075(bu)003:4417: de dag rgyas par gzhan du shes par bya'o //
NK075(bu)003:4418: gnyis pa mthong ba'i khyad par dang /
NK075(bu)003:4420: 'o na tshe dbang dang khyad med dam zhe na yod de /
NK075(bu)003:4421: zag bcas kyi mnyam gzhag tu chos nyid de ltar du mthong na'ang /
NK075(bu)003:4422: rjes thob tu log rtog ma zad pa'i stobs kyis /
NK075(bu)003:4423: dper na 'khor lo sgyur rgyal gyi bu chung de'i
NK075(bu)003:4424: sha khrag dang rigs ni rgyal po las 'gyur ba
NK075(bu)003:4425: med kyang / lus sems stobs ma rdzogs pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:4426: gdan sar ma bzhag pas rgyal po'i mnga' thang thams cad la dbang bsgyur mi nus pa bzhin du /
NK075(bu)003:4427: phyag rgya spros bcas kyi skabs su chos nyid rang
NK075(bu)003:4428: mtshan mthong yang rgyal bu stobs ma rdzogs pa de
NK075(bu)003:4429: lta bur / lta sgom stobs ma rdzogs pa de bas na mnyam rjes kyi rtsol ba yod la /
NK075(bu)003:4430: tshe la dbang bsgyur ba'i rig 'dzin ni mnyam rjes 'dres pas lta sgom stobs rdzogs pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:4431: spros pa ni lta sgom stobs ma rdzogs pas khyad par de ltar yod par 'gyur ba yin te /
NK075(bu)003:4433: gsum pa bden gnyis rang mtshan du //
NK075(bu)003:4434: 'go mthong gnyis med bzod ma thob //
NK075(bu)003:4438: gsang ba'i snying po sgyu 'phrul rgyas pa'i rgyud las 'di skad du gsung ste /
NK075(bu)003:4439: lus snang sems gsum zung 'jug gi ngo bo la
NK075(bu)003:4440: lta bar bya ba'i yul dang blta bar bya ba'i
NK075(bu)003:4441: mkhan po gnyis med pa'i ngang la /
NK075(bu)003:4442: thams cad gsal zhing sgrib g.yogs dang bral bas ye shes /
NK075(bu)003:4443: de ma 'dres par gsal bas na sgron ma /
NK075(bu)003:4444: de rgyun chad med par sbreng bar shar ba ni /
NK075(bu)003:4445: phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad steng 'og gnyis dang bcu'i zhing
NK075(bu)003:4446: khams dag ma dag thams cad kun ma 'dres yongs
NK075(bu)003:4448: yul yul can gang du yang mi mthong ba ni /
NK075(bu)003:4449: shes rab spyan gyi lta ba'i mchog go //
NK075(bu)003:4450: de yang rig par rang shar gyi rgyud las /
NK075(bu)003:4451: lta ba nyid la blta ru med //
NK075(bu)003:4452: lta ba sems kyi dri ma yin //
NK075(bu)003:4453: dri ma dag pa'i chos nyid la //
NK075(bu)003:4454: blta bya lta byed gnyis dang bral //
NK075(bu)003:4457: yul med gsal phyir ltar zhes bshad //
NK075(bu)003:4459: bzhi pa zhar la spyi'i mtshan nyid du 'dod pa nor ba de la gsum ste /
NK075(bu)003:4461: dang po spyi'i mtshan nyid du lta bas gsang sngags mi rtogs pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:4463: thams cad rang rig pa'i mngon sum du rtogs pa lta ba'i ngo bo yin pa de bas na /
NK075(bu)003:4464: spyi mtshan gyi go ba la lta ba'i ngor gang zag ganga zhig zhena te mi zhen no //
NK075(bu)003:4466: gsang sngags kyi don yid yul du byas pas lta ba'i ngo bo gang zag gang gisa rnyed de /
NK075(bu)003:4467: bden gsum dbyer med kyi don mi rnyed pa'i phyir ro //
NK075(bu)003:4468: gnyis pa yid kyi rtog pas gzung 'dzin du gol ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:4470: dbyer med skye 'jig dang bral ba rdo rje'i don
NK075(bu)003:4471: de nyid yiida kyi yul du byas nas sgra tsam
NK075(bu)003:4472: la brten pas gol ba yin pas /
NK075(bu)003:4473: gol tshul ni chos nyid 'dus ma byas pa stong
NK075(bu)003:4474: pa phyogs gcig tsam gyi ngo bo la gzugs dbyibs
NK075(bu)003:4475: kha dog dang / skye 'jug mi snang bsam nas
NK075(bu)003:4476: yul du dmigs pa dag la brten nas gsang sngags
NK075(bu)003:4478: nges par 'di kho na'o snyam nas lta ba de'i
NK075(bu)003:4479: rjes la rnal 'byor mi rtog pa'i don la bsgom
NK075(bu)003:4480: dgos ces rgyud gzhung nas bshad pa yang /
NK075(bu)003:4481: lta ba de dang phyogs nas mthun par skye bar
NK075(bu)003:4482: 'dod pa ni yid yul gyi blos nges par 'joga
NK075(bu)003:4483: pas chos nyid yul du rtog pa'i phyir gzung 'dzin
NK075(bu)003:4484: can du gyur bas mi grol ba'o //
NK075(bu)003:4486: nges pa'i shes pa ma skyes phyir //
NK075(bu)003:4487: rang rig tshad dang mi ldan te //
NK075(bu)003:4488: gzung 'dzin mtshan ma ma grol bas //
NK075(bu)003:4489: rang gis gar skyes mi shes pas //
NK075(bu)003:4490: 'ol phyir phyogs su gang bsgoms kyang //
NK075(bu)003:4491: long ba'i gom pa bzhin te phyal bar gol //
NK075(bu)003:4493: gsum pa sgra ci bzhin du ldog pa tshol bas lta ba dam pas dbul ba'o //
NK075(bu)003:4495: tshong pa yul kun tu rgyu bas thams cad shes pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:4496: byis pa gzhon nu ni gar yang ma phyin pas
NK075(bu)003:4497: ci yang mi shes pas de gnyis la shes rgya
NK075(bu)003:4498: che chung yod pa ltar du /
NK075(bu)003:4499: sgom pa ting nge 'dzin goms ma goms /
NK075(bu)003:4500: mchog lta ba rtogs ma rtogs /
NK075(bu)003:4501: gzhung las thos pa byas ma byas /
NK075(bu)003:4503: rigsa brgyad kyi dbye ba ston pa sgyu 'phrul brgyad
NK075(bu)003:4504: bcu pa'i le'u lnga pa lasa ni 'di lta ste
NK075(bu)003:4506: dang po chos nyid kyi rigs ni /
NK075(bu)003:4508: thams cad kun la yang khyab par yod de /
NK075(bu)003:4509: nam mkha' kun la khyab par yang gnas so //
NK075(bu)003:4510: de ltar chos nyid kyi rigs dang nam mkhas kun la khyab kyang /
NK075(bu)003:4511: mngon par thar pa'i don ma rtogs na /
NK075(bu)003:4512: me long g.yas g.yogs pa dang 'dra ste /
NK075(bu)003:4513: gzugs brnyan snang ba'i bya ba byed mi nus so //
NK075(bu)003:4515: gnyis pa bla na med pa'i theg pa'i rigs ni /
NK075(bu)003:4516: de nyid don rtogs rang rig rgyal po yi //
NK075(bu)003:4517: rgya mtsho chen por chu klung 'bab par ltar //
NK075(bu)003:4518: bla med don rtogs thabs chen 'di dag tu //
NK075(bu)003:4519: rnam thar theg pa bsam yas ma lus 'dus //
NK075(bu)003:4521: gsum pa byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa'i rigs ni /
NK075(bu)003:4523: bdag med gnyis rtogs pha rol phyin pa yi //
NK075(bu)003:4524: sa bcu rim gyis sgom pa'i rnal 'byor pa //
NK075(bu)003:4525: sangs rgyas sar bgrod go 'phang thob pa'i lam //
NK075(bu)003:4526: bden pa gnyis kyis rab tu thob par 'gyur //
NK075(bu)003:4528: bzhi pa rang rgyal gyi theg pa'i rigs ni /
NK075(bu)003:4530: phyi nang rten 'brel sgyu ma mig yor tshul shes pas //
NK075(bu)003:4531: dngos po'i gzugs la thogs med rab tu 'jug /
NK075(bu)003:4532: dge bshes mi slob rang gi rig pas rtogs //
NK075(bu)003:4533: byang chub sar bgrod yid bzhin bde ba'i mchog /
NK075(bu)003:4535: lnga pa nyan thos kyi theg pa'i rigs ni /
NK075(bu)003:4537: bden bzhi'i don rtogs rab tu spang ba yi //
NK075(bu)003:4538: ye shes bcu drug chas sbyangs rab zhi ba'i //
NK075(bu)003:4539: rgyun zhugs la sogs rim par sbyangs nas ni //
NK075(bu)003:4540: nyon mongs dgra rnams zhi ba'i sa ru 'gro //
NK075(bu)003:4542: drug pa rigs ma nges pa ni /
NK075(bu)003:4544: theg pa gang du bstan par ma nges pa'i //
NK075(bu)003:4545: yang na kun la mthun byas 'jam par 'jug /
NK075(bu)003:4546: yang na nges med 'di zhes bstan du med //
NK075(bu)003:4547: 'di ni ma nges rdo rje 'chang gis gsungs //
NK075(bu)003:4549: bdun pa lha dang mi'i theg pa'i rigs ni /
NK075(bu)003:4551: dge bcu spyod cing mi dge spang byed pa //
NK075(bu)003:4552: 'dod pa'i khams kyi lha mir skye ba'i rgyu //
NK075(bu)003:4553: tshad med bzhir spyod mi g.yo sgom byed pa //
NK075(bu)003:4554: tshangs gnas la sogs skye ba'i rgyu yin no //
NK075(bu)003:4556: brgyad pa rigs chad pa ni /
NK075(bu)003:4558: chos kyi dbyings kyis kun la khyab gyur kyang //
NK075(bu)003:4559: rang rigs rtogs pa'i skal dang mi ldan na //
NK075(bu)003:4560: ci ltar dmus longs mdun du mdog bstan bzhin //
NK075(bu)003:4561: 'di ni skal med rigs chad pa yin no //
NK075(bu)003:4562: zhes pas de rnams kyi lta ba'i khyad par gsungsa pa'i nang nas bla med mchog yin te /
NK075(bu)003:4563: de nyid kyi lta ba la dag pa gsum /
NK075(bu)003:4565: gnyis med la sogs pa'i tshig gi rnama grangsa tsam
NK075(bu)003:4566: shes pa la lta ba dam pa'i don yin par
NK075(bu)003:4567: 'dod nas sgra'i rjes su 'brang bas gsang sngagsa lhun
NK075(bu)003:4568: grub kyi lta ba las gol ba ste /
NK075(bu)003:4569: gol lugs ni dag mnyam la sogs pa de yi
NK075(bu)003:4570: sgra tsam la brten nas brtags dpyad byas pas ni
NK075(bu)003:4571: dper na mi dbul pos phyug po'i nor rdzas rnams
NK075(bu)003:4572: brjod shes kyang kho rang la ci yang med pa
NK075(bu)003:4573: bzhin du / gsang sngags kyi 'khor 'das dbyer med
NK075(bu)003:4574: pa'i lta ba'i don mi rtogs pas kha 'byams tshig
NK075(bu)003:4575: gi lta ba de nyid kho nar gol ba yin
NK075(bu)003:4576: bzhin du / te / lam rim las /
NK075(bu)003:4577: sems kyis mnyam pa ma rtogs na //
NK075(bu)003:4578: tshig gi mnyam pas 'tshang mi rgya //
NK075(bu)003:4580: smra bsam tshig la gang dga' ba //
NK075(bu)003:4581: gang gi dgongs pa dpog mi nus //
NK075(bu)003:4582: tshig tshogs rgya mtsho thob pa min //
NK075(bu)003:4583: tshig gcig thos na thos pa'i mchog /
NK075(bu)003:4586: gang zhig man ngag khungs chub cing //
NK075(bu)003:4587: sgra phyir khungs 'byin che ngag can //
NK075(bu)003:4588: bskal pa brgyad khrir sdug bsngal thob //
NK075(bu)003:4590: bzhi pa ma rtogs pa'i skyon dang /
NK075(bu)003:4592: bzhi pa skyon ni sgyu 'phrul rgyas pa'i lung las 'di skad gsungs te /
NK075(bu)003:4593: thabs spyod pa rnams la don la mkhas pa lta ba'i rtsis yi ma zin na /
NK075(bu)003:4594: lam gyi rten la dge ba bcu spyad cing bsgrubs nas stegs bcas kyang /
NK075(bu)003:4595: 'bras bu la mtho ris kyi lha dang mi ru skye la /
NK075(bu)003:4596: skye shi med pa'i sa mthar thug gi 'bras bu sangs rgyas mi thob pa yin no //
NK075(bu)003:4598: rang sems ma rtogs dge ba bcu la sogs //
NK075(bu)003:4599: bskal pa stong du tshogs bsags sgrib sbyangs kyang //
NK075(bu)003:4600: 'bras bu sku gsum sangs rgyas 'byung ba min //
NK075(bu)003:4602: lnga pa rtogs pa'i yon tan no //
NK075(bu)003:4604: grangs kyi lnga pa yon tan ni rgyud las ji skad 'byung ba ni gang zhe na /
NK075(bu)003:4605: thun mong gi dngos grub dang /
NK075(bu)003:4606: mchog gi dngos grub kyi snying po ni lta ba yin la /
NK075(bu)003:4607: dang po lta ba de'i don rtogsa nas mthar 'bras
NK075(bu)003:4608: bu ma thob kyi bar du lta ba de dang
NK075(bu)003:4609: ma bral na / bar du lta ba de dang ma bral na /
NK075(bu)003:4610: bar ma dor chud mi za ba'am ngan song dang 'khor bar mi gtong ba ste /
NK075(bu)003:4611: dpe chu srin gyi phyag rgya ste bzung nas phyir gtong ba med pa ci bzhin du'o //
NK075(bu)003:4612: gzhan yang phyi nang gi spyod yul thams cad kun
NK075(bu)003:4613: tu sku dang ye shes su shar ba'i yon tan
NK075(bu)003:4614: la tshad dpag tu med pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:4616: de'i rjes su sgom pa ting nge 'dzin la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:4620: lta ba spyi'i tshul du rtogs pa de'i rjes su
NK075(bu)003:4621: lam gyi gtso bo ting nge 'dzin des mchog lta
NK075(bu)003:4622: ba'i don de rim gyis goms par byas pa'i thabs
NK075(bu)003:4624: gnyis pa bshad de la drug ste /
NK075(bu)003:4626: dang po de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK075(bu)003:4628: 'byung ba sa chu me rlung dang /
NK075(bu)003:4629: sems 'du ba'i rten 'brel las lus grub pa'i skye gnas par do de nyid /
NK075(bu)003:4630: 'chi kha bar do'i skabs su lus sems 'bral ba'i tshul ni 'byung ba rim par 'gag ste /
NK075(bu)003:4631: de yang khams chu la thim /
NK075(bu)003:4634: nam mkha' kun gzhi'i rnam shes la thim ste /
NK075(bu)003:4635: chos nyid ngo ma shes pa'i bar do la rig pa rtog med bzhin du yin pa ste /
NK075(bu)003:4637: shi ba don dam bden pa ste //
NK075(bu)003:4642: de'ang blo rim gyis pas thog mar de bzhin nyid
NK075(bu)003:4643: kyi ting nge 'dzin rang sgom thabs gang gi yan
NK075(bu)003:4644: lag / lam rim nas bshad pa bzhin du don bco lnga ste /
NK075(bu)003:4645: sngon dgos thabs dang ngo bo dang /
NK075(bu)003:4646: mi mthun bcos nyams spyod dam tshig /
NK075(bu)003:4647: drod rtags mtshan yon 'da' ka ma /
NK075(bu)003:4648: rang gi 'bras bu rdzogs pa yi sgo nas nyams su len pa la /
NK075(bu)003:4649: khyad par du ting nge 'dzin rang gi ngo bo
NK075(bu)003:4650: ni tshogs drug gi snang ba la yul yul can
NK075(bu)003:4651: gang du'ang 'du shes med par rang rig par gsal
NK075(bu)003:4652: bzhin du stong pa'i don la ma yengs par sgom
NK075(bu)003:4653: dgos te / de yang sgom pa'i rnal 'byor pa gang yin pa de dag gi lam rim ltar /
NK075(bu)003:4654: nyams g.yo thob goms brtan mthar phyin pa lnga dang /
NK075(bu)003:4655: drod rtags mtshan ma me long rdzu 'phrul dang lnga
NK075(bu)003:4656: ste bcu mthar phyin pa dang ldan pa yi mthus
NK075(bu)003:4657: / snga ma de bzhin nyid sgom pa las kyang
NK075(bu)003:4658: phyi ma kun tu snang gi ting nge 'dzin la
NK075(bu)003:4660: de yang mdo ste rgyan las /
NK075(bu)003:4661: snga ma la brten phyi ma skye //
NK075(bu)003:4663: gnyis pa kun tu snang gi ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK075(bu)003:4665: dper na nyi ma las 'pho ba med par 'od du snang ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:4666: sa bon las myu gu dang /
NK075(bu)003:4667: sgyur la 'gram chu ldang ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:4668: sgra dang brag char grags pa dang bzhir snang ba bzhin du /
NK075(bu)003:4669: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin la 'pho ba
NK075(bu)003:4670: med par gdangs 'gag med du kun snang gi ting
NK075(bu)003:4672: dee yi yan lag la don bco lnga bstan pa
NK075(bu)003:4673: yang gong gi de bzhin nyid ltar du yin pas
NK075(bu)003:4674: na / rgyu de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin la brtan pa thob par byas nas /
NK075(bu)003:4675: de nyid kyi rtsal rang la gnas pa'i ye shes
NK075(bu)003:4676: 'gag pa med par snang ba kun tu khyab par
NK075(bu)003:4677: sgom pa ni ngo bo yin te /
NK075(bu)003:4678: de yang phyi snying rje dang /
NK075(bu)003:4680: nang skye byed kyi mkhan po tha dad med par
NK075(bu)003:4681: ye shes sgyu mar rang snang du sgom par byed
NK075(bu)003:4683: drod rtags rnams lam rim nas bshad pa bzhin du de'i nus mthu rnams rdzogs par bya'o //
NK075(bu)003:4684: gsum pa phyag rgya gcig pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK075(bu)003:4686: kun tu snang gi ting nge 'dzin mthar phyin pa
NK075(bu)003:4687: de yi stobs las phyag rgya gcig pa'i ting nge
NK075(bu)003:4688: 'dzin skyes pa la ni rim cig char gnyis las
NK075(bu)003:4689: / dang po mngal skyes ni dpe rten 'brel bcu gnyis yod pa la /
NK075(bu)003:4690: bzhi pa'i so nas ming gzugs de la sogs pa lus rim gyis 'byung ba'am /
NK075(bu)003:4691: gnyis pa gcig shos te bardzusa skyes ni skye mched
NK075(bu)003:4692: drug cig char du skye ba ci lta ba bzhin
NK075(bu)003:4693: du phyag rgya gcig pa sgom pa'ang /
NK075(bu)003:4694: zhi ba phyag rgya gcig pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:4695: khro bo phyag rgya gcig pa gnyis la gdul bya
NK075(bu)003:4696: rang rang gang la mos pa'i zhi khro gcig nyams
NK075(bu)003:4697: su len pa'ang / blo che chung gi dbang gis /
NK075(bu)003:4698: dang po phra ba yig 'bru la bslab cing /
NK075(bu)003:4699: de nas thugs phyag mtshan dang /
NK075(bu)003:4700: sku yongs rdzogs kyi bar du rim gyis bskyed pa rim gyis pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:4701: dang nas rags pa lha sku bsgom pa cig char
NK075(bu)003:4702: ba dang gnyis kyi tshul gyis lha bsgom pa la'ang
NK075(bu)003:4703: / sku phyag rgya chen po de'i thugs kar rigs
NK075(bu)003:4704: dang rang gi sa bon gang yin bsgom pa gsung
NK075(bu)003:4705: / chos rgya / thugs kar phyag mtshan bsgom pa
NK075(bu)003:4706: thugs phyag mtshan dam tshig gi phyag rgya 'od zer
NK075(bu)003:4707: spro bsdu bya ba la sogs 'phro 'du 'phrin las
NK075(bu)003:4708: kyi phyag rgya dang bzhi dang ldan pa'i sku la
NK075(bu)003:4709: / chos rgya / / dbu rgyan gyi lha lnga sku gsung thugs kyi lha gsum /
NK075(bu)003:4710: thugs kar ye shes sems dpa' ste lha dgu dang ldan par bsgom pa de la yang /
NK075(bu)003:4711: phyag rgya gcig pa rang gi cha rkyen la lam
NK075(bu)003:4712: rim nas bshad pa bzhin don bco lnga tshang ba
NK075(bu)003:4713: yi sgo nas nyams su len pa'i dgos ched ni
NK075(bu)003:4714: / de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin la stong zhen dang /
NK075(bu)003:4715: kun ting de la snang zhen yod pas de gnyis
NK075(bu)003:4716: grol bar 'gyur ba'i thabs la dbyer med phyag rgya
NK075(bu)003:4719: nyams g.yo thob goms brtan mthar phyin pa lnga dang
NK075(bu)003:4720: ldan par byas nas lam gong ma phyag rgya spros
NK075(bu)003:4721: pa'i ting nge 'dzin las ldang bar bya'o //
NK075(bu)003:4722: bzhi pa phyag rgya spros pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:4724: byis pa chung ngu gang yin pa de lo nyi
NK075(bu)003:4725: shu lon nas lus sems smin cing stobs rdzogs pas
NK075(bu)003:4726: rang dang rigs mthun pa'i khyims thabs gcig len pas
NK075(bu)003:4728: phyag rgya gcig pa de yi sgo nas zhi khro gang bsgom la gzhi blang ba las /
NK075(bu)003:4729: tshangs pa ste zhi ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:4730: ya ma ste khro bo'i lha rnams kyi gzugs can du shar ba bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis sam /
NK075(bu)003:4731: lnga bcu rtsa brgyad la sogs pa phyag rgya spros
NK075(bu)003:4732: par sgom pa de'ang med pa las yod par sgom
NK075(bu)003:4734: ye gdod ma nas rtog tshogs rang la gnas pa
NK075(bu)003:4735: lha dang lha mo'i dkyil 'khor du bsgom pa de
NK075(bu)003:4736: la bskyed sngags brjod pa tsam gyis cig char du
NK075(bu)003:4737: rgya mtsho'i nang du nyi zla gza' dang skar ma
NK075(bu)003:4738: shar ba bzhin rloms bskyed byed pa'am /
NK075(bu)003:4739: yang rgyu snga ma la brten cing 'bras bu phyi
NK075(bu)003:4740: ma dang 'brel ba bzhin tu rdo rje go cha
NK075(bu)003:4743: sku yongs rdzogs kyi cho ga gsum gyis bskyed pas sam /
NK075(bu)003:4744: gang yin na yang phyag rgya spros pa rang gi
NK075(bu)003:4745: bslab pa rang gi cha rkyen du don bco lnga
NK075(bu)003:4746: tshang ba'i sgo nas nyams su len pa mthar phyin
NK075(bu)003:4747: pa / blo che na zhi khro rgyas bsdus 'bring
NK075(bu)003:4748: gsum gang bsgom gyi lha rnams la lung gi lha
NK075(bu)003:4749: dgu nyid bcu dang ldan par byas nas de nas
NK075(bu)003:4750: lus dkyil du bkod nas sangs rgyas stong gi dkyil
NK075(bu)003:4751: pa / 'khor du spro / de nas nyi khri bzhi stong du spro /
NK075(bu)003:4752: de nas bsam yas lhun gyi grub pa'i bar du spro ste /
NK075(bu)003:4754: yan lag bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis ldan //
NK075(bu)003:4755: de nyid yan lag spros bdag ste //
NK075(bu)003:4757: de ltar ldan pa'i gtso mchog gis //
NK075(bu)003:4758: rgyal ba rgyal mchog de bzhin du //
NK075(bu)003:4760: de la sogs pa bsam mi khyab //
NK075(bu)003:4762: yang blo chung na lha dgu nyid bcu dang ldan pa de nas /
NK075(bu)003:4763: tshom bu gcig gsum lnga pa gang rung gi dkyil
NK075(bu)003:4764: 'khor bsgoms nas longs spyod de yo byad lnga la
NK075(bu)003:4765: spyod nas tshom bu tshogs sgrub pa la sbyar bar
NK075(bu)003:4766: bya'o // lnga pa bar chad med pa gnyis dang /
NK075(bu)003:4768: grangs kyi lnga pa tshogs sgrub kyi rnal 'byor pa
NK075(bu)003:4769: rab ni lung a nu yo ga dang lta sgom
NK075(bu)003:4770: mthun pa'i rnal 'byor ting nge 'dzin 'ba' zhig gi
NK075(bu)003:4772: dper na nyan thos la lhag bcas dang /
NK075(bu)003:4773: lhag med kyi mya ngan las 'das pa'i tshul gnyis yod pa bzhin du /
NK075(bu)003:4774: 'dir yang tshe rnam gnyis kyi rig 'dzin thob par 'gyur ba'ang gi sgras yod do //
NK075(bu)003:4775: ting nge 'dzin bar chad med pa de'i don dang
NK075(bu)003:4776: mi 'tshams pa'i blo chung ba des bza' btung la
NK075(bu)003:4777: sogs pa'i longs spyod lnga la spyod dgos te /
NK075(bu)003:4778: de yang tshom bu tshogs sgrub rang gi bsgrub gzhi phun sum tshogs pa bzhi yis gzhi bzung ste /
NK075(bu)003:4783: yo byad phun sum tshogs pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:4784: de rnams rgyas par lam rim du shes par bya'o //
NK075(bu)003:4785: sgrub thabs bsnyen bsgrub bzhi'i gzhung bsrang ba la bzhi gsum ste /
NK075(bu)003:4786: lam rim 'jug gi bsnyen bsgrub bzhi dang /
NK075(bu)003:4787: bsgrub pa'i bsnyen bsgrub bzhi dang /
NK075(bu)003:4790: de ting kun ting gnyis bsnyen pa /
NK075(bu)003:4791: phyag rgya gcig pa nye bsnyen /
NK075(bu)003:4792: longs spyod lngas tshogs sgrub pa ni bsgrub pa /
NK075(bu)003:4793: de yi dus +aa li k+aa li nyams su len pa ni bsgrub pa chen po ste bzhi'o //
NK075(bu)003:4795: grogs shom ra nas bzung ste dkyil 'khor bri zhing rdzas dgos pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:4796: phyi mchod bya zhing mtshams bcad pa rnams ni sngon du 'gro ba bya ba las kyis bsnyen pa /
NK075(bu)003:4797: sngon 'gro nas bzung ste rnal 'byor pho mo rnams kyi mi grangs sprad pa'am /
NK075(bu)003:4798: yang na rnal 'byor pa mi gcig gis lha kun
NK075(bu)003:4799: sgom par byed nas bsgrub pa ci tsam byed pa'i
NK075(bu)003:4800: zhag grangs phyed yan chad la 'od zer dkar po
NK075(bu)003:4801: spros pas ting nge 'dzin gyi snod dag par byed
NK075(bu)003:4803: phyed man chad la 'od zer dmar po 'phro 'dus
NK075(bu)003:4804: kyi ting nge 'dzin gyi bcud bsdus nas dngos grub
NK075(bu)003:4805: kyi snod du rung bar byed pa ni bsgrub pa
NK075(bu)003:4806: / nub tha ma'i zhag gcig la 'od zer mthing
NK075(bu)003:4807: ka phar mi spros bar tshur bsdu ba'i ting nge
NK075(bu)003:4808: 'dzin gyi dngos grub sdud pa ni bsgrub pa chen
NK075(bu)003:4809: / po dang bzhi'o // gsum pa ni /
NK075(bu)003:4811: de ltar bsnyen sgrub bzhi dang ldan pa'i sgo nas
NK075(bu)003:4812: zhag grangs kyi tshad dang bsnyen pa rnams rgyud nas
NK075(bu)003:4813: bshad pa ltar bsgrub cing rtagsa mar me rang 'bar
NK075(bu)003:4814: dang / bdud rtsi khol ba la sogs pa byung na /
NK075(bu)003:4815: dngos grub blang ba'i thabs la lha dang rjas gnyis so //
NK075(bu)003:4816: dang po ni sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga'i dkyil 'khor bsgrub pa'am /
NK075(bu)003:4819: rang rang mthun par sbyar te sku'i dkyil 'khor yin na /
NK075(bu)003:4820: spyi bo la bstim pa la sogs rang rang gi gnas su bstim zhing brtan par bya ba ste /
NK075(bu)003:4823: dkyil 'khor mthun pa nyid du sbyar //
NK075(bu)003:4824: gnas su bstim zhing brtan par bya //
NK075(bu)003:4826: gnyis pa rdzas kyi blang ba'i thabs la khyad par
NK075(bu)003:4827: du sbyor sgrol gnyis po'i sgo nas blang dgos te
NK075(bu)003:4828: / de'ang srod la rtogs pa nub pa'i dus su
NK075(bu)003:4829: thabs snying rje chen po'i rtsal rdzogs par byed pa
NK075(bu)003:4830: la sgrol ba mdzad pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:4831: tho rangs ye shes skye ba'i dus su thabs bde
NK075(bu)003:4832: ba'i ye shes rtsal rdzogs par byed pa la shes
NK075(bu)003:4833: rab yum la brten dgos pa yin te /
NK075(bu)003:4835: bsgrub pa'i brten mchog shes rab gzungs ma dang /
NK075(bu)003:4837: de la sbyor ba'i dus kyi bsnyen sgrub bzhi ni yum mtshan nyid dang ldan pa brtsal te /
NK075(bu)003:4839: chos bshad nas sta gon du byas pa bsnyen pa /
NK075(bu)003:4842: 'dod pa'i bstan chos kyis bde ba rgyas par byed pa nye bsnyen /
NK075(bu)003:4843: phyag rgya bzhi'i rol pa bsgrub pa /
NK075(bu)003:4844: nyi zla rdo rje'i lces blang ba ni bsgrub pa chen po /
NK075(bu)003:4845: nub tha ma la zag med mthong lam gyi ye
NK075(bu)003:4846: shes rgyud la skye bar byed pa dngos grub chen
NK075(bu)003:4847: po yum gyi mkha' la blang ba'i thabs te /
NK075(bu)003:4849: dngos su mchod pa rnam gnyis so //
NK075(bu)003:4850: gtso ru dgos pa gang yin pa //
NK075(bu)003:4852: de yi dus su gsang snying las /
NK075(bu)003:4853: cho ga lnga ni rdzogs byas shing //
NK075(bu)003:4854: sngags kyi yan lag lnga rdzogs pas //
NK075(bu)003:4855: yo byad lnga ni rdzogs par ldan //
NK075(bu)003:4857: lnga gsum bco lnga'i yan lag rnams tshang na lus
NK075(bu)003:4858: khams skye gnas kyi zag pa gsum med pa'i 'bras
NK075(bu)003:4859: bu rab kyis tshe la dbang bsgyur ba'i rig 'dzin
NK075(bu)003:4861: tha ma des rnams smin rig 'dzin thob par 'gyur ro //
NK075(bu)003:4862: gong gi de ltar tshang ba min te lta sgom stobs chung na skye ba phyi ma'am /
NK075(bu)003:4863: lan grangs bdun nam skye ba gzhan nyid du ste skal par mi 'gyang bar rig 'dzin thob pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:4864: drug pa mthar lam gyi ting nge 'dzin no //
NK075(bu)003:4866: dper na rgya mtsho'i nang du nyi 'od rin chen dang /
NK075(bu)003:4869: mthar thug pa'i rin chen dang bzhi yi 'od rgya
NK075(bu)003:4870: mtsho la phog pas rgya mtsho zho ru 'gyur ba
NK075(bu)003:4873: thams cad stongs par 'gyur ba ci bzhin du /
NK075(bu)003:4874: gnas skabs su rig 'dzin thob pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:4875: mthar thugs sangs rgyas su 'gyur ba la'ang tshogs sgrub
NK075(bu)003:4876: kyi lta spyod sgom gsum nus ldan 'dis ni zag
NK075(bu)003:4877: bcas mathara phyin pa 'bras bu mthong lam dang /
NK075(bu)003:4879: mthar lam gyi bar du rim par sbyar nas mthar
NK075(bu)003:4880: thug gi 'bras bu sangsa rgyas kyi sa thob pa
NK075(bu)003:4881: la gdon mi za ba yin te /
NK075(bu)003:4882: de yang tshogs sgrub kyi steng nas mthong lam tshe rnam gnyis thob pa ni /
NK075(bu)003:4883: nyi 'od kyis chu zhor 'gyur ba bzhin du /
NK075(bu)003:4884: zag bcas kyi nyon mongs pa de nyid zag med kyi ye shes su 'gyur la /
NK075(bu)003:4885: de nas sgom lam phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin
NK075(bu)003:4886: thob pa'i dus su lta sgom de bas stobs su
NK075(bu)003:4887: zhugs te / rlan med pa'i 'od phog pas mar du 'gro ba bzhin du /
NK075(bu)003:4888: mthong lam la da rung kun 'gro'i sgrib pa yod pa de /
NK075(bu)003:4889: 'dir ye shes su shar nas dgongs pa mi g.yo ba'i ting nge 'dzin du 'gyur ba'o //
NK075(bu)003:4890: mthar lam lhun grub rig 'dzin gyi skabs su de bas kyang stobs su gyur te /
NK075(bu)003:4891: me 'od kyi 'od phog pas me ru 'gyur ba bzhin du /
NK075(bu)003:4892: sgom lam la da rung lhan cig gnas pa'i dri
NK075(bu)003:4893: ma yod pa de 'dir ye shes rtsal rdzogs su
NK075(bu)003:4894: shar nas sku lnga lhun grub kyi rig 'dzin du
NK075(bu)003:4895: 'gyur ro // sangs rgyas pa'i dus su de bas kyang stobs su gyur te /
NK075(bu)003:4896: mthar thug pa'i 'od phog nas thams cad stong pa bzhin du /
NK075(bu)003:4897: mthar lam la da rung kun gzhi bag la nyal gyi dri ma yod pa de /
NK075(bu)003:4898: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes su shar nas gzung
NK075(bu)003:4899: 'dzin sa bon dang bcas pa brtsal bas mi rnyed
NK075(bu)003:4900: pas thams cad ye shes 'khor yug tu shar ba'o
NK075(bu)003:4904: rgya mtsho chen por 'dus pa'i chu'i phung po dag
NK075(bu)003:4905: kyang nor bu nyi ma'i snying po'i 'od phog nas
NK075(bu)003:4907: 'o ma dang zho ru 'gyur te 'dug go //
NK075(bu)003:4908: nor bu rin po che rlan med pa'i 'od phog
NK075(bu)003:4909: nas 'o ma dang zho'i rang bzhin spangs te mar
NK075(bu)003:4910: gyi snying khu lta bur 'gyur ro //
NK075(bu)003:4911: me'i 'od kyi nor bu rin po che'i 'od phog na /
NK075(bu)003:4912: mar gyi snying khu'i rang bzhin spangs te lta bur 'bar bar 'gyur ro //
NK075(bu)003:4913: nor bu rin po che ma lus pa mthar thug pa'i 'od phog na /
NK075(bu)003:4914: thams cad lhag ma med cing ma lus pa'i snang bar 'gyur ro //
NK075(bu)003:4916: gnyis pa spyod pa gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:4920: lam gyi yan lag la bcu yod pa'i gnyis pa
NK075(bu)003:4921: spyod pa ni lta don de nyid goms par byed
NK075(bu)003:4922: pa'i skabs 'dir spyod pa'i don rnams shes dgos te
NK075(bu)003:4923: / gong du bstan pa'i lta sgom de dag las su rung ba ste /
NK075(bu)003:4924: lta sgom sa bon dang 'dra ba nar son te
NK075(bu)003:4925: stobs su gyur te gong nas gong du 'phel bar
NK075(bu)003:4926: byed pa ni / spyod pa rlan dang 'dra bas
NK075(bu)003:4927: de nyid stobs su gyur nas 'bras bu la sbyor
NK075(bu)003:4928: byed pa ni / ba'o // de yang lta sgom gnyis ni spyod pa'i srog ste /
NK075(bu)003:4929: spyod pa gzung 'dzin du mi 'gro ba de nyid kyi mthu yin te /
NK075(bu)003:4930: bya lam la rjes med pa bzhin du /
NK075(bu)003:4931: spyod pa la chags zhen med pa'i gsang sngags kyi spyod pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:4935: spyod pa byed pa'i dus dang ni /
NK075(bu)003:4936: spyod pa ma byas pa'i skyon dang /
NK075(bu)003:4937: byas pa'i yon tan dang lnga po de nyid kyi
