NK075(bu)003:4938: nang du spyod pa'i don rgyas bshad de rdzogs pa
NK075(bu)003:4939: yin no // rgyas pa de la lnga ste /
NK075(bu)003:4943: rnal 'byor bdag nyid kyis gnas skabs dang mthar thug
NK075(bu)003:4944: gi 'bras bu la sbyor ba la spyod dgos pa
NK075(bu)003:4945: dang / gdul bya gzhan gyi don lhun gyis grub pa'i phyir /
NK075(bu)003:4947: spyod pa'i ngo bo'i dus su lta sgom gyis zin pa'i stobs kyis /
NK075(bu)003:4948: nam mkha' rdul mi chags pa bzhin du gnyis 'dzin
NK075(bu)003:4949: gyi sgrib pa dbri ba dang bsod nams dang ye
NK075(bu)003:4950: shes kyi tshogs gnyis sogsa te rdzogs pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:4951: thabs lam gyi spyod pa so so skye bo ltar
NK075(bu)003:4952: spyod kyang bag chags kyi dri mas mi gos pa
NK075(bu)003:4953: dang / grol lam gyi spyod pas ting nge 'dzin
NK075(bu)003:4954: goms par byed de gong nas gong du 'phel ba'i
NK075(bu)003:4955: phyir spyod pa gal che bas gces so //
NK075(bu)003:4957: mi rjes mthun pa'i spyod pa yang //
NK075(bu)003:4958: skabs kyi ting 'dzin stobs phyir spyad //
NK075(bu)003:4960: gnyis pa rnam grangs la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:4964: gsang ba'i snying po sgyu 'phrul rgyas pa'i rgyud de nyid las gsungs pa'i spyod pa rnams ni /
NK075(bu)003:4965: yo ga man chad blo dman rnams kyi spyod yul du ma gyur pa yin te /
NK075(bu)003:4967: so so skye bos barlada po rang kha ma dang tshul mthun par dri chen /
NK075(bu)003:4971: sha chen te dam rdzas lnga dang /
NK075(bu)003:4979: ngag barlanga po ste spyad par bya ba lnga la spyod pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:4980: gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya ste 'dod yon lnga dang /
NK075(bu)003:4985: phrag dog ste nyon mongs lnga dang /
NK075(bu)003:4986: de ltar nyi shu rtsa lnga ni 'khor ba nag po'i spyod pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:4988: khyad par gsang sngags kyi lta bas zin nas spyad
NK075(bu)003:4989: na nyon mongs pa de nyid kyi dri mas ma
NK075(bu)003:4990: gos nas 'dul ba'i thabs ci snyed pa gcig gsungs
NK075(bu)003:4991: pa ni / sngags phyi rgyud man chad dang thun
NK075(bu)003:4992: mong min pa ste thabs lam gyi spyod pa dang
NK075(bu)003:4993: de las bzlog pa dkar po'i spyod pa ni /
NK075(bu)003:4994: khyad par grol lam gyi ting nge 'dzin gyi spyod
NK075(bu)003:4995: pa de dang theg pa 'og ma'i sa dang lam
NK075(bu)003:4996: gyi skabs so sor spyod lugs dang mthun pa'o /
NK075(bu)003:4997: gnyis pa bshad pa de la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:4999: dang po thun mong ma yin pa thabs lam gyi spyod pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:5001: bde ba la zhen pa'i gang zag gis lam bgrod
NK075(bu)003:5002: pa la bde ba de nyid ma spangs lam du
NK075(bu)003:5003: khyer bas mthar chags rtog de nyid ye shes su
NK075(bu)003:5004: grol bas na / de ltar du dug nad can
NK075(bu)003:5005: la sman du dug kho rang bcud len du btang
NK075(bu)003:5006: bas dug nad la phan pa bzhin du /
NK075(bu)003:5007: zhen chags can gyi rnal 'byor pa bdag grol ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:5008: rang grol ba'i stobs kyis zhen chags can gyi gang
NK075(bu)003:5009: zag gzhan rnams kyi rgyud grol bar nus pa yin
NK075(bu)003:5010: te / des bdag gzhan gnyis ka'i don nyams su blang ba la /
NK075(bu)003:5011: bde ba de nyid spang mi dgos pas na thabs che ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:5012: de nyid kyi dri mas mi gos shing nyon mongs
NK075(bu)003:5013: ye shes su shar bas na thabs mkhas pa'i phyir
NK075(bu)003:5014: na thabs kyi spyod pa zhes bya'o //
NK075(bu)003:5016: ci ltar rna bar chu zhugs pa //
NK075(bu)003:5017: chu dag nyid kyis 'gugs par byed //
NK075(bu)003:5018: de bzhin dngos po rnam rtog yang //
NK075(bu)003:5019: rnam rtog nyid kyis dbyung bar byed //
NK075(bu)003:5021: gnyis pa grol lam gyi khyad par lam dang sar mthun par spyod pa de la gsum ste /
NK075(bu)003:5023: dang po dpe'i sgo nas mdor bstan pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:5025: gcig shos te grol lam pa'i spyod pa de'i dpe ni /
NK075(bu)003:5026: dmangs ni 'bang tha mal pa ste las dang po nam rtsol sgrub kyis 'tsho ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:5027: rje ni blon po yig tshang la sogs pa'i blo gros kyi thabs kyis 'tsho ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:5028: bram ze ni sngags kyi nus pas thams cad la longs spyod pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:5029: rgyal phran ni rin po che phal pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:5030: yo byad kyis phongs pa med de longs spyod 'dzoms pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:5031: 'khor lo sgyur ba'i rgyal po ni /
NK075(bu)003:5032: rgyal srid rin po che sna bdun la longs spyod
NK075(bu)003:5033: cing gling bzhi'i mi rnams kyis bkur sti phul ba
NK075(bu)003:5034: dang / lnga la mthon dman dang bsod nams che chung gi rim pa bzhin du /
NK075(bu)003:5035: gnyis pa don gyi sgo nas rgyas par bshad pa de la lnga ste /
NK075(bu)003:5037: dang po rgyu shes pa'i spyod pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:5039: bran gyis las sna tshogs byed pa bzhin du /
NK075(bu)003:5040: thos bsam gyis 'jig rten gyi snod bcud kyi rnam bzhag dang /
NK075(bu)003:5041: mu stegs kyi log lta dang /
NK075(bu)003:5042: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i theg pa rim pa dgu'i
NK075(bu)003:5043: lta ba thams cad shes par bya ba'i bslab bya
NK075(bu)003:5044: mang po de dag la bslab ste /
NK075(bu)003:5045: de nyid 'grub byed kyi grogs ni brtson 'grus yin pas na /
NK075(bu)003:5046: phyi nang gi theg pa gang la yang dor bar bya ba ni yod pa ma yina te /
NK075(bu)003:5047: kun la bslab par bya ste /
NK075(bu)003:5049: dper na bung ba tshong tshol ltar //
NK075(bu)003:5050: lta spyod sgo kun bsdur byas la //
NK075(bu)003:5051: ma nor don nyid rtogs bya'i phyir //
NK075(bu)003:5052: sgo rnams bsdur ba rab tu gces //
NK075(bu)003:5054: gnyis pa ting nge 'dzin gsum gyi spyod pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:5056: lta ba'i don de ting nge 'dzin gyis goms par
NK075(bu)003:5057: byed pa yang dpes don mtshon par byed pa gnyis
NK075(bu)003:5058: pa rje ste blon po'i spyod pa ltar du /
NK075(bu)003:5059: rkyen 'jug pa'i ting nge 'dzin la de ting kun
NK075(bu)003:5060: ting phyag rgya gcig pa gsum la blon po yig
NK075(bu)003:5061: tshang ste yon tan dang ldan pa des /
NK075(bu)003:5062: rgyal po'i mthun phyogs thams cad bsgrub /
NK075(bu)003:5063: mi mthun pa'i phyogs thams cad bsal ba'i thabs la brtson pa bzhin /
NK075(bu)003:5064: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin gyi ngo bo
NK075(bu)003:5065: shes rab rang bzhin med pa dang cha mthun par
NK075(bu)003:5066: don de dang ya mi bral ba'i spyod pa'i gdams
NK075(bu)003:5067: ngag gi sgo nas bying ba gsum dang /
NK075(bu)003:5068: rgod pa gsum gyi skyon de dag bsal nas gsal
NK075(bu)003:5069: stong dbyer med kyi don de dag nyams su blang
NK075(bu)003:5070: ba dang / kun ting gi ting nge 'dzin gyi
NK075(bu)003:5071: ngo bo thabs 'gag pa med pa dang cha mthun
NK075(bu)003:5072: par don de nyid dang ya mi bral bar spyod
NK075(bu)003:5073: pa'i gdams ngag gi sgo nas bying rgod kyi skyon
NK075(bu)003:5075: stong nyid snying rje dang 'gyu stong dbyer med ye shes sgyu ma'i don nyams su myong ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:5076: phyag rgya gcig pa'i rnal 'byor pa blo chung bas /
NK075(bu)003:5077: mnyam bzhag tu dang po yig 'bru gang ru sgom pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:5078: de nas sogs kyi sgras thugs phyag mtshan dang /
NK075(bu)003:5079: de nas sku yongs rdzogs kyi bar du rim gyis bskyed pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:5080: blo che bas de las bzlog nas dang la yi ge a la sems sbyangs /
NK075(bu)003:5081: de nas lha sku cig char du bskyed pa gnyis
NK075(bu)003:5082: la brten nas don de dang mthun par spyod par
NK075(bu)003:5083: bya'o // gsum pa spros pa'i spyod pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:5085: spros pa'i dus su bram ze gtsang ma rigs kyis
NK075(bu)003:5086: rdzas dang gang la spyod pa'i dus su sngags kyi
NK075(bu)003:5087: nus mthus sbyangs longs spyod du rung ba bzhin /
NK075(bu)003:5088: rim gyis pa'i dbang du thog mar bden pa dbyer med spyi'i tshul du mthong nas /
NK075(bu)003:5089: de nyid goms par byed pa la /
NK075(bu)003:5094: tshogs lam rnal 'byor bzhi rim par sbyangs nas 'dir
NK075(bu)003:5095: mthar phyin pa'i mthus rtog tshogs spyod yul thams cad
NK075(bu)003:5096: lha dang lha mor sbyangs nas spyod pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:5097: bzhi pa bar chad med pa'i spyod pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:5099: grangs kyi lnga pa bar chad med par tshogs sgrub pa'i dus su /
NK075(bu)003:5100: skye 'gro thams cad kyi sri zhu gus pa'i gnas ni rgyal po yin la /
NK075(bu)003:5101: rgyal po de'i chos lugs ni /
NK075(bu)003:5102: gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya lnga la dad cing longs spyod pa bzhin du /
NK075(bu)003:5103: 'dir yang longs spyod yo byad lnga la spyod cing
NK075(bu)003:5104: shin tu spros pa sna tshogs kyi spyod pa nyams
NK075(bu)003:5106: de yang grangs kyi lnga pa bar chad med par tshogs sgrub pa'i dus su /
NK075(bu)003:5107: bza' dang btung ba'i yo byad /
NK075(bu)003:5111: +aa li k+aa la'i yo byad dang lnga po ni
NK075(bu)003:5112: lta sgom spyod gsum dbyer med pa'i stobs kyis 'dir
NK075(bu)003:5113: spyod pa'i gtso bor nyams su blang ba yin no
NK075(bu)003:5114: // lnga pa rig 'dzin gyi spyod pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:5116: yo byad bzhi la spyod pa de nas bsnyen pa dang nye ba'i bsnyen pa /
NK075(bu)003:5117: sgrub pa dang sgrub pa chen po bzhi yi sgo
NK075(bu)003:5118: nas bsgrubs par byas pa'i 'bras bu lus khams skye
NK075(bu)003:5119: gnas kyi zag pa gsum dang bral nas rig 'dzin
NK075(bu)003:5121: dper na lcagsa 'khor can gling gcig dang /
NK075(bu)003:5124: dngul 'khor can gling gsum la dbang byed pa'i gdul
NK075(bu)003:5125: bya la rgya che chung gi go rim yod pa
NK075(bu)003:5126: bzhin du / rig 'dzin bzhi la yang bdag don ting nge 'dzin la stobs che chung dang /
NK075(bu)003:5127: gzhan don byed pa'i yul gdul bya la rgya che
NK075(bu)003:5128: chung gi khyad par yod par 'gyur ba yin te
NK075(bu)003:5129: / de yang lcags 'khor can gling gcig la dbyer
NK075(bu)003:5130: med pa bzhin du rnam smin rig 'dzin gyi bdag
NK075(bu)003:5132: spyod yul lha dang lha mor rol pa'i tshul du spyod la /
NK075(bu)003:5133: gzhan don du phrin las rnam bzhi'i sgo nas gling
NK075(bu)003:5134: bzhi drug tshun chad kyi gdul bya yang dag pa'i
NK075(bu)003:5136: zangs 'khor can de bas stobs che ba bzhin du /
NK075(bu)003:5137: tshe dbang rig 'dzin gyis rang don du lo stong
NK075(bu)003:5138: drug brgya'i bar du kun 'gro'i sgrib pa sbyang zhing
NK075(bu)003:5139: lam gong ma la spyor bar byed do //
NK075(bu)003:5140: gzhan don du stong gsum gyi stong chen po brgya
NK075(bu)003:5141: tshun tshad kyi gdul bya rnams la bskal par gnas
NK075(bu)003:5142: nas cho 'phrul bzhi'i sgo nas don byed do //
NK075(bu)003:5143: dngul 'khor can de bas kyang rgya che ba bzhin du /
NK075(bu)003:5144: phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin gyis nyi khri bzhi
NK075(bu)003:5145: stong la sogs grangs can gyi 'khor lo mngon sum
NK075(bu)003:5146: du snang zhing lhan gcig gnas pa'i dri ma dag
NK075(bu)003:5147: par byed la / gzhan don du stong gsum gyi
NK075(bu)003:5148: stong chen po brgya phrag stong de 'dra ba bcu'i
NK075(bu)003:5149: rdul snyed dang mnyam pa'i 'jig rten brgya phrag stong
NK075(bu)003:5150: de 'dra ba bcu'i rdul snyed kyi zhing khams su
NK075(bu)003:5151: rngon dang smad 'tshong la sogs pa sprul pa'i lus
NK075(bu)003:5152: kyi sgo nas cho 'phrul bzhi'i 'dul bar byed do
NK075(bu)003:5153: par byed la / // gser 'khor can de bas kyang stobs che ba bzhin du /
NK075(bu)003:5154: lhun grub rig 'dzin gyis rang don du bag la nyal phra ba sbyangs shing /
NK075(bu)003:5155: gzhan don du zhing khams mtha' yas par gdul bya
NK075(bu)003:5156: sna tshogs la sprul sku'i mdzad pa sna tshogs bstan
NK075(bu)003:5157: no // gsum pa lam rang gi spyod pa khyad par gyi spyod pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:5159: 'o na lam gong ma'i skabs su 'og ma'i spyod
NK075(bu)003:5160: pa dang gnyis ka la spyod dgos pas spyod pa
NK075(bu)003:5161: la khyad par med dam zhe na /
NK075(bu)003:5163: lam snga ma'i dus kyi spyod pa de /
NK075(bu)003:5164: lam phyi ma la 'jug pa'i gang zag gi rgyud
NK075(bu)003:5165: la rang shugs kyis ldan nas yod pas lam 'og
NK075(bu)003:5166: ma'i spyod pa de gong ma'i skabs su dngos su
NK075(bu)003:5167: spyod pa'i rtsol ba med cing /
NK075(bu)003:5168: de bas na lam rang rang gi spyod pa'i bslab pa gang yin pa de /
NK075(bu)003:5169: lam rang rang gi skabs su spyod pa shin tu gces pas na /
NK075(bu)003:5170: lam gyis tshod mthon dman gyis phye bas spyod pa la khyad par yod pa yin no //
NK075(bu)003:5173: de yang spyod pa dus tshod dang ldan dgos pas /
NK075(bu)003:5174: lam dang sa yi rim pa mtho dman gyi skabs dang sbyar nas /
NK075(bu)003:5175: spyod pa dgos par rgyud gzhung nas gragsa pa bzhin du byed dgos te /
NK075(bu)003:5176: de yang lam mthon dman gyi don go ba tsam gyis mi chog /
NK075(bu)003:5177: ting nge 'dzin gyi ro rang gis nyams su myong ba'i tshod rang gis bzung nas /
NK075(bu)003:5178: ting nge 'dzin dang mthun pa'i spyod pa dgos te /
NK075(bu)003:5179: de yang lam snga ma'i ting nge 'dzin la goms
NK075(bu)003:5180: pa mthar ma phyin gyi bar du lam snga ma'i
NK075(bu)003:5182: lam phyi ma la 'jug pa'i tshe de nas lam
NK075(bu)003:5183: phyi ma rang gi spyod yul rgyud gzhung nas ci
NK075(bu)003:5184: ltar bshad pa bzhin nyams su blang bar bya'o //
NK075(bu)003:5187: khyad par grol lam gyi rang rang gi skabs su
NK075(bu)003:5188: bshad pa'i spyod pa ma byas nas dor bar byas
NK075(bu)003:5189: na lam mthar phyin nas 'bras bu thob tu med
NK075(bu)003:5190: do // thabs lam gyi spyod pa nyi shu rtsa
NK075(bu)003:5191: lnga po rnams barlanga po rang kha mar spyod pa
NK075(bu)003:5192: do // ni / bdag don du mi 'gyur bas rang ngan song du 'gro /
NK075(bu)003:5193: gzhan don du mi 'gyur bas gzhan gyis theg chen
NK075(bu)003:5194: la mi mos mi dang nas skur bas btab pas
NK075(bu)003:5196: gnyis don du mi 'gyur bas don gnyis mi 'grub /
NK075(bu)003:5197: chos don du mi 'gyur bas chos chud gsan pa dang bzhii 'byung ba yin te /
NK075(bu)003:5199: nyon mongs pa lnga po rnams rang khar spyod pa'i
NK075(bu)003:5200: dbang du song bas nyon mongs pa lnga la sogs
NK075(bu)003:5201: pa'i sgo nas so so'i rnam smin tshad las 'das
NK075(bu)003:5203: 'bras bu ngan song gi sdug bsngal tshad las 'das pa zhig myong bar byed do //
NK075(bu)003:5204: gzhan yang byang chub sems dpas lta ba phyogs gcig
NK075(bu)003:5205: rtogs kyang spyod pa'i rtsal sprug ma nus pas bskal
NK075(bu)003:5206: pa grangs med gsum la sogs pa thogs /
NK075(bu)003:5207: mu stegs pas lta ba ma rtogs par spyod pa
NK075(bu)003:5208: byas pas ngan song la 'gro zhes sgyu 'phrul rgyas
NK075(bu)003:5212: gong gi grol lam de rnams rang rang gi skabs
NK075(bu)003:5213: la bdag gzhan gyi spyod pa de yi spyod na
NK075(bu)003:5214: dgos ched kyi skabs yon tan de dag yod pa'i
NK075(bu)003:5215: phyir na / bdag don gyi spyod pa de dang /
NK075(bu)003:5217: des bdag gzhan gnyis po 'khor mi ltung nas 'bras bu thob pa'i yon tan dang /
NK075(bu)003:5218: thabs lam gyi spyod pa nyi shu rtsa lnga po
NK075(bu)003:5219: so so rang kha ma'i spyod pa byas na ngan
NK075(bu)003:5221: lta bas zin nas spyod na 'bras bu sangs rgyas
NK075(bu)003:5222: thob pas byed ces rgyud gzhung las grags pa bzhin
NK075(bu)003:5223: yin la / gzhan yang bsagsa bya tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa 'gyur te /
NK075(bu)003:5224: nyon mongs la sogs pa ma spangs rang rig tu gsal ba lam du khyer bas bsod nams dang /
NK075(bu)003:5225: de'i dus su chos nyid rang las ma g.yos pas ye shes kyi tshogs rdzogs pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:5226: nyon mongs pa lnga la sogs pa nyi shu rtsa
NK075(bu)003:5227: lnga po la spyod kyang dri mas ma gos pas
NK075(bu)003:5228: na sgrib pa dbri ba ste dag par 'gyur ro
NK075(bu)003:5229: // gsum pa 'phrin las la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:5233: gsum pa 'phrin las bya ba'i sdom tshig ni /
NK075(bu)003:5234: 'phrin las bya ba'i dgos ched dang /
NK075(bu)003:5235: ngo bo ngos bzung ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:5237: rnam grangs du yod pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:5239: dus skabs gar mkho ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:5242: byas pa'i yon tan dang dgu yi nang 'phrin las kyi rgyas bshad de nges rdzogsa pa yin no //
NK075(bu)003:5243: gnyis pa bshad pa de la dgu ste /
NK075(bu)003:5247: rnal 'byor pa bdag don du bsgrub pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:5248: gdul bya gzhan don byed pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:5249: bdag gzhan gnyis ka'i don lhun grub tu bsgrub pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:5250: dam pa'i chos don du 'gyur ba'i phyir na zhi
NK075(bu)003:5251: rgyas dbang drag lhun gyis grub pa'i 'phrin las dang
NK075(bu)003:5252: rnam par lnga po de dper na zhing bzang po
NK075(bu)003:5253: la sa bon btab nas rkyen chu lud byas pa
NK075(bu)003:5254: chud mi za ba bzhin du /
NK075(bu)003:5255: bdag gzhan gyi don bsgrubs nas 'bras bu chud mi za bar 'byung bar byed pa la /
NK075(bu)003:5256: 'phrin las rnam pa lnga dang du blang dgos pa la /
NK075(bu)003:5257: de'ang dbang po rab ting nge 'dzin kho na /
NK075(bu)003:5258: 'bring gis ting nge 'dzin dang sngags gnyis /
NK075(bu)003:5259: tha mas mtshan bcas kyi sgo nas sngags rdzas ting
NK075(bu)003:5260: nge 'dzin gsum gyi sgo nas nus tshad dang sbyar
NK075(bu)003:5261: bar bya'o // gnyis pa ngo bo dang /
NK075(bu)003:5263: de yang 'phrin las rnam pa bzhi'i gdul bya la
NK075(bu)003:5264: phyi nang gnyis gnyis gcig tu brtsi bas zung bzhi
NK075(bu)003:5265: po de rnams 'dul bar byed pa'i mthu chen po
NK075(bu)003:5266: zhi rgyas dbang drag gi 'phrin las rnam pa bzhi
NK075(bu)003:5267: 'byung ba dang / lhun grub kyi phrin las gcig
NK075(bu)003:5268: gis gong gi gdul bya phyi nang zung bzhi po
NK075(bu)003:5269: kun 'dul nus pa'i mthu chen po yod pa dang
NK075(bu)003:5270: 'byung ba dang / / sogs kyi sgras 'das pa'i
NK075(bu)003:5271: byed las thams cad 'phrin las kyis bsdus pas de
NK075(bu)003:5272: ltar lnga po gdul bya 'dul byed gang yin pa
NK075(bu)003:5273: 'dzoms pa de phrin las kyi ngo bo yin no
NK075(bu)003:5274: 'byung ba dang / / // gsum pa nges tshig dang /
NK075(bu)003:5276: sdug bsngal gyi zug rngu ste phyi la nad bgegs dgra dang /
NK075(bu)003:5277: nang du nyon mongs rnam rtog zhi ba'i phyir na zhi ba'i 'phrin las kyi sgra 'jug pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:5278: rgyas par 'phel bar bya ba la phyi la sha ni lo thog gso ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:5279: tshe dang rigs rgyud la sogs 'phel ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:5280: nang du sku dang ye shes te /
NK075(bu)003:5281: de ltar gnyis po 'phel bar bya ba'i phyir rgyas pa'i sgra 'jug pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:5282: gzungs ma la sogs dgug pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:5283: dgra bgregs gnyis dbang po bsgyur ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:5284: 'bras bu sku lnga la sogs bzhi po dbang du
NK075(bu)003:5285: sdud pa'i phyir na dbang gi sgra 'jug pa dang
NK075(bu)003:5286: / phyi la dgra bgegs dang nang la nyon mongs
NK075(bu)003:5287: pa'i gdug pa rnam pa gnyis 'jomsa pa'i phyir na
NK075(bu)003:5289: lnga pa lhun grub ni sngon ngo bo'i dus su
NK075(bu)003:5290: bstan pa bzhin 'phrin las gcig gi kun 'dul ba'i
NK075(bu)003:5291: phyir na lhun gyis grub pa'i sgrar 'jug pa dang
NK075(bu)003:5292: / de bas na phrin las rnam pa lnga'i nges
NK075(bu)003:5293: tshig gam sgra don de nges par 'grub pa yin
NK075(bu)003:5294: / no // bzhi pa las bzhi'i rnam grangs la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:5296: dang po spyi'i rnam grangs dang /
NK075(bu)003:5298: 'phrin las kyi don gyi dmigs su ngos bzung ba'i phyir rnam par phye nas gsum ste /
NK075(bu)003:5303: gzhi gnas lugs byang chub sems kyi ngo bor zhi
NK075(bu)003:5304: rgyas dbang drag gi phrin las bzhi lhun grub tu
NK075(bu)003:5305: rang bzhin gyis gnas pa yin te /
NK075(bu)003:5307: don dam sems dngos po'i gnas lugs dang /
NK075(bu)003:5308: kun rdzob lus dngos po'i gnas lugs so //
NK075(bu)003:5310: byang ba stong pa'i rang bzhin la /
NK075(bu)003:5311: nyon shes bya'i sgrib pa ka nas dag pa'i ngo bo ni zhi ba'i 'phrin las rang gnas dang /
NK075(bu)003:5312: chub pa snang ba'i rang bzhin la sku dang ye
NK075(bu)003:5313: shes lhun gyis grub pa'i ngo bo ni rgyas pa'i
NK075(bu)003:5315: de ltar ka dag lhun grub dbyer med kyi ngo
NK075(bu)003:5316: bo la yod med tha dad kyi mtha' gnyis dang
NK075(bu)003:5317: bral ba'i gnyis med ni dbang gi 'phrin las rang
NK075(bu)003:5318: gnas dang / des yod med snang stong phyogs re'i
NK075(bu)003:5319: mtshan ma thams cad 'joms pa'i phyir drag po'i 'phrin
NK075(bu)003:5320: las dang bzhi lhun gyis grub cing gnas pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:5322: lus spyi la 'phrin las bzhi lhun gyis grub par gnas te /
NK075(bu)003:5324: spyi bor sa'i dkyil 'khor gru bzhi ser po rgyas pa'i 'phrin las dang /
NK075(bu)003:5325: mgrin par rlung gi dkyil 'khor zla gam dbang gi dang /
NK075(bu)003:5326: snying gar me'i dkyil 'khor gru gsum nag po'i dang /
NK075(bu)003:5327: lte bar chu'i dkyil 'khor zlum po zhi ba'i 'phrin
NK075(bu)003:5328: las dang bzhi rang la gnas pa yin par gsungs
NK075(bu)003:5330: gnas bzhi'i 'byung ba'ang las bzhi ste /
NK075(bu)003:5332: yang nang snying kha chos kyi 'khor lo la 'phrin las bzhi lhun gyi grub par gnas te /
NK075(bu)003:5336: gsang ba yum gyi mkha' la yang /
NK075(bu)003:5337: las bzhi lhun gyis grub par gnas te /
NK075(bu)003:5339: gsang ba'i mkha' la rang bzhin ldan //
NK075(bu)003:5342: thabs grol gyi lam nyams su len pa'i dus su
NK075(bu)003:5343: phrin las rnam pa bzhi las ma g.yos pa ni
NK075(bu)003:5346: mthar thug sangs rgyas rigs lnga'i thugs rjes sems can
NK075(bu)003:5347: gyi don byed pa de yang 'phrin las lnga'i sgo
NK075(bu)003:5349: de ltar gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum du phye ba'o //
NK075(bu)003:5351: bzhi phyir rnam bzhi dol ba rnams //
NK075(bu)003:5353: rnam bzhi'i bye brag tha dad pa //
NK075(bu)003:5354: re re'ang lnga lnga'i snang tshul gyis snang //
NK075(bu)003:5355: de rigs bzhi yi cha 'dzin pa //
NK075(bu)003:5356: las kyi rigs la lhun gyi grub //
NK075(bu)003:5357: rnam pa bzhi yis 'dul mdzad pa //
NK075(bu)003:5358: phyag rgya chen pos 'dul bas rigs ma yin //
NK075(bu)003:5360: gnyis pa bye brag lam gyi rnam grangs de la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:5362: las bzhi so so'i rnam grangs so //
NK075(bu)003:5367: 'dir bar lam gyi phrin las thabs lam dang shes rab grol lam gnyis yin pa las /
NK075(bu)003:5368: gnyis pa thabs dang shes rab kyi rnam grangs rgyas par bshad pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:5370: snga ma thabs lam la steng sgo dang 'og sgo gnyis kyang phrin las bzhi yin pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:5371: phyi ma grol lam la yang /
NK075(bu)003:5372: shes rab lta ba rtogs pa'i ngo bo dang /
NK075(bu)003:5373: sgom pa bskyed rdzogs kyi ting nge 'dzin rnam pa gnyis la yang /
NK075(bu)003:5374: gzhi la phrin las bzhi lhun gyis grub pa ltar /
NK075(bu)003:5375: lta ba rtogs pa dang ting nge 'dzin gyi ngo bo la las bzhi tshang ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:5376: za tshogs gtor lung ltar zas la langas spyod pa yang las bzhi yin pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:5377: las bzhi lhag pa gzugs brnyan mchod rten gyi sgo nas las bzhi byed pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:5378: me'i sgo nas las bzhi'i sbyin sreg byed thabs dang gnyis so //
NK075(bu)003:5379: de rnams zhor la sbyin sreg dang sbyar nas bshad na /
NK075(bu)003:5381: dang po lta ba la tshang tshul ni /
NK075(bu)003:5382: gzhi chos nyid rtogs pa'i ngo bo la don las bzhi tshang ba ni hom khung /
NK075(bu)003:5383: snang srid kyi chos ni bsreg rdzas de rnams gang la yang zhen pa med pa sbyin pa /
NK075(bu)003:5384: yid 'gyu ba rang sar grol nas ye shes su
NK075(bu)003:5385: shar ba'i me des nyon mongs pa dngos por 'dzin
NK075(bu)003:5387: gnyis pa ting nge 'dzin la tshang tshul ni /
NK075(bu)003:5388: sgom pa chos nyid kyi ngo bo la don la las bzhi tshang ba ni hom khung /
NK075(bu)003:5389: rnam shes phra rags ni bsreg rdzas /
NK075(bu)003:5390: gang shar chos nyid kyi ngo bor khyer bas sbyin pa /
NK075(bu)003:5391: zhen chags ye shes su shar ba'i me des 'dod
NK075(bu)003:5392: yon rang rgyud du zhen cing chags pa de bsregs
NK075(bu)003:5393: pa'o // gsum pa 'dod yon tshogs su rol ba la yang las bzhi tshang tshul ni /
NK075(bu)003:5397: 'dod yon zhen med lam du khyer ba sbyin pa /
NK075(bu)003:5398: zhen chags ye shes su shar ba'i me des 'dod
NK075(bu)003:5399: yon rang rgyud du zhen cing chags pa de bsregs
NK075(bu)003:5400: pa'o // lhag pa gzugs brnyan ni /
NK075(bu)003:5401: 'og bya thabs skabs su 'chad par 'gyur ro //
NK075(bu)003:5402: gsum pa mjug gsum du bsdu ba'o //
NK075(bu)003:5404: rnam grangs de dag tshur la bsdus na lhag pa gzugs brnyan ni phyi yin la /
NK075(bu)003:5408: longs spyod bzhi nang yin la /
NK075(bu)003:5409: 'og sgo gsang ba yin par bshad pa dang gsum du shes par bya'o //
NK075(bu)003:5410: gnyis pa las bzhi'i rnam grangs so //
NK075(bu)003:5412: gong gi ngo boo ngos bzung gi skabs dang rjes
NK075(bu)003:5413: su mthun par zhi ba'i rnam grangs phyi nang gnyis
NK075(bu)003:5414: te / phyi la nada kyi bye brag dang /
NK075(bu)003:5416: dgra rnams zhi bar byed pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:5417: nang la nyon mongsa pa rnam rtog gi bye brag zhi bar byed pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:5418: rgyas pa la phyi nang gnyis po ngos bzung na phyi la gso ba dang 'phel ba ste /
NK075(bu)003:5419: gso ba la yang na ba gso ba /
NK075(bu)003:5423: sogs khong du rta phyugs gso ba sogs pa rnams so //
NK075(bu)003:5424: 'phel ba la tshe 'phel ba ste ring ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:5425: rigs rgyud mang du 'phel ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:5426: longs spyod 'phel ba ste che ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:5428: bzhi bo ni phyi yin la /
NK075(bu)003:5429: nang la 'bras bu sku dang ye shes 'phel thabs so //
NK075(bu)003:5430: dbang la ni dgug pa dang bsdu ba gnyis yod de /
NK075(bu)003:5431: phyi rol la d+ha ra ste gzungs ma rigs lnga dang /
NK075(bu)003:5432: rigs bzhi'i rnam pa dgug par byed pa'i thabs dang /
NK075(bu)003:5433: rang dang mi mthun pa'i dgra bgegs rnam pa gnyis
NK075(bu)003:5434: dabnga po bsgyur nas ma dad pa dad par bya
NK075(bu)003:5435: ba dang / nang la rang gi semsa nyid kyi
NK075(bu)003:5436: ngo bo la 'bras bu sku gsung thugs yon tan
NK075(bu)003:5437: phrin las lnga dbang du bsdu bar bya ba'i thabs
NK075(bu)003:5438: ba dang / so // mngona spyod drag po la dgra bgegs yul gzhan du bskrad pa'i thabs dang /
NK075(bu)003:5439: gtan nas mi ldang bar bya ba'i phyir manna pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:5440: dran pa nyams nas smyo ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:5441: kha nas cal col du smra nas 'bogsa pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:5442: lus 'gul mi shes nas byad du bcug pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:5443: lus dang yan lag gi sha med nas bskomsa pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:5444: dran pa mi dran nas rmongs pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:5445: gtan nas gling khams gzhan du 'phangs nas spo ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:5446: lus sems phral nas rgyud gzhan gyi sems la zhugs pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:5447: de rnams kyi sgo nas rnal 'byor pa rang gi phyi'i dgra bgegs 'joms par byed la /
NK075(bu)003:5448: nang du nyon mongs pa'i dgra bgegs 'joms par byed pa'i thabs rnams so //
NK075(bu)003:5449: lnga pa bya thabs la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:5451: dang po thabs lam gyi bya thabs dang /
NK075(bu)003:5453: phrin las nyams su blang ba'i bya thabs ni 'di lta ste /
NK075(bu)003:5454: de la lha gsal ba'i ngang nas thabs lam gyi
NK075(bu)003:5455: bya thabs la yang gsang ba dang nang gnyis so
NK075(bu)003:5456: // nang ltar steng sgo'i rtsa khamsa kyi 'khor lo
NK075(bu)003:5457: bzhi'i gnas su byang sems thig le la rig pa
NK075(bu)003:5458: gtad nas nyams su len pa'i dus su /
NK075(bu)003:5459: bde stong gi ye shes la zhen chags kyi rtog
NK075(bu)003:5460: pa dang bral ba ni zhi ba'i 'phrin las yin
NK075(bu)003:5461: pa dang / de'i tshe rtsa dang rlung dga' bzhi'i ye shes skyel ba ni rgyas pa'i dang /
NK075(bu)003:5462: bde stong gnyis med kyi don nyams su myong ba ni dbang gi dang /
NK075(bu)003:5463: des 'gyu ba dang 'dzin zhen chags gsum gyi rtog
NK075(bu)003:5464: pa'i mtshan ma thams cad 'dzoms pa ni drag po'i
NK075(bu)003:5466: yang bla ma dam pa'i gsung sgros la sbyin sreg ltar zhor la bshad na /
NK075(bu)003:5467: rtsa 'khor gyi gnas su las bzhi'i dbyibs su dod nas yod pa hom khung /
NK075(bu)003:5468: ro rkyang gnyis dgang blug gzar /
NK075(bu)003:5469: sgrom mdo'i yam las rlung byung /
NK075(bu)003:5470: sum mdo'i ram la phog nas me sbar ba'i drod kyis /
NK075(bu)003:5471: bsreg rdzas rtsa gnas kyi thig le bzhu nas /
NK075(bu)003:5472: rtsa khams rnams su sbyin pas bde stong rtog med kyi ye shes skyes pas /
NK075(bu)003:5473: nyon mongs rnam rtog bsregs pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:5474: yang gsang ba 'og sgo ltar nyams su blangs na /
NK075(bu)003:5476: dbang po rdo rje rtse'i theg le dang /
NK075(bu)003:5477: dbang shes bde ba'i khams dang gsum la sbyor nas yab yum rol pa mdzad pa'i tshe //
NK075(bu)003:5478: nyi zla gnyis 'dres kyi dus su bde stong gnyis
NK075(bu)003:5479: med kyi ye shes nyams su myong ba'i ngo bo
NK075(bu)003:5480: la / nyon mongs chags rtog gi dri ma dang
NK075(bu)003:5481: bral ba ni zhi ba'i phrin las yin pa dang
NK075(bu)003:5482: la / / de'i tshe na phung khams skye mched kyi rtog tshogs dang /
NK075(bu)003:5483: gsang ba'i mkha' la lha'i dkyil 'khor du gsal zhing /
NK075(bu)003:5484: dga' ba bzhi dang ye shes lnga'i don sgrib g.yogs med par gsal ba ni rgyas pa'i dang /
NK075(bu)003:5485: de ltar bde stong gnyis med kyi don myong ba ni dbang gi dang /
NK075(bu)003:5486: des nyon mongs zhen chags kyi rtog pa thams cad
NK075(bu)003:5487: 'joms pa ni drag po'i phrin las dang bzhi zhes
NK075(bu)003:5488: bya'o // yang zhor la sbyin sreg ltar na /
NK075(bu)003:5489: yum gyi mkha' la las bzhi'i dbyibs su yod pa hom khung /
NK075(bu)003:5490: yab kyi rdo rje hom gzar /
NK075(bu)003:5491: yab kyi thig le bsreg rdzas de sbyin pas /
NK075(bu)003:5492: bde stong gi ye shes skyes pas nyon mongs chags rtog rang kha ma de bsregs pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:5493: gnyis pa grol lam gyi bya thabs de la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:5497: shes rab grol lam gyi sgo nas las bzhi'i bya thabs la /
NK075(bu)003:5498: lta ba'i rjes su sgom pas nyams su len thabs
NK075(bu)003:5499: la phyi nang gnyis kyi sgo nas shes dgos te
NK075(bu)003:5500: / de la nang ltar las bzhi bya thabs gong du song la /
NK075(bu)003:5501: gnyis pa bye brag tu phye ba'i thabs de la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:5503: dang po tshad med pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:5505: phyi rol rjes thob tu tshad meda pa nyid sgom pa la yang las bzhi tshang ste /
NK075(bu)003:5507: zhi ba snying rjes dbyings su 'gug pa'i phyir //
NK075(bu)003:5508: 'gugs byed chen po badz+ra am gu sha /
NK075(bu)003:5509: rgyas pa byams pas ye shes 'phel ba'i phyir //
NK075(bu)003:5510: 'phel byed chen mo badz+ra p+aa sha h'u //
NK075(bu)003:5511: dga' ba dbang gis mtha' gnyis bsdu ba'i phyir //
NK075(bu)003:5512: sdom byed chen mo badz+ra s+pho ta bam //
NK075(bu)003:5513: btang snyoms dril bus rdul du brlag pa'i phyir //
NK075(bu)003:5514: rlag byed chen mo badz+ra g+han+de to //
NK075(bu)003:5516: chos rje rin po che'i bzhed la /
NK075(bu)003:5520: btang snyoms dbang gi 'phrin las su 'dod do //
NK075(bu)003:5521: gnyis pa lhag pa gzugs brnyan la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:5525: lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi sgo nas las bzhi bya thabs la gnyisa te /
NK075(bu)003:5526: mchod rten gyi sgo nas las bzhi bya thabs dang /
NK075(bu)003:5527: sbyin sreg me'i sgo nas las bzhi bya thabs te /
NK075(bu)003:5528: de la mchod rten gyi sgo nas bya thabs ni /
NK075(bu)003:5529: sgyu 'phrul le'u lag gi nas las bzhi'i s+aats+tsha btab thabs dang /
NK075(bu)003:5530: rgyas pa'i le'u nyi shu pa las kyang /
NK075(bu)003:5532: bgegs kyi ling+ga mnan par bya //
NK075(bu)003:5534: gnyis pa bye brag tu bya thabs de la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:5538: phyi ma me'i sgo nas sbyin sreg bya thabs la /
NK075(bu)003:5540: gnas rdzas thabs kyi rnam pa dang //
NK075(bu)003:5541: gzungs dang gtso sems bsgrub bya dang //
NK075(bu)003:5542: phur pa lha sems dus rim dang //
NK075(bu)003:5543: lhag ma bcu gcig shes par bya //
NK075(bu)003:5544: zhes bcu gcig gi go rim de ltar gsungs kyang /
NK075(bu)003:5545: 'dir gzhung ltar rnam grangs bcu bzhi'am bco lnga'i go rim bsgrig par bya ste /
NK075(bu)003:5547: zhi ba la ri bo 'dus pa'i rtse /
NK075(bu)003:5548: rgyas pa la nags tshal dang /
NK075(bu)003:5552: drag po la dur khrod kyi gnas su bya ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:5553: de la zhi ba'i gnas ni /
NK075(bu)003:5555: ri bo 'dus pa'i rtse dag dang //
NK075(bu)003:5556: chu klung 'dzoms pa'i sa phyogs su //
NK075(bu)003:5557: dang bar byed pa'i las rnams brtsoms //
NK075(bu)003:5559: nags tshal sman ljongs me tog tshal //
NK075(bu)003:5560: lhun sdug ri bo rgyas pa bya //
NK075(bu)003:5562: sum mdo chu bo 'dus pa dang //
NK075(bu)003:5563: bzhi mdo khong stong sdud ces bya //
NK075(bu)003:5565: dur khrod ngan pa'i sa phyogs su //
NK075(bu)003:5566: lhag par brtsam na nges par 'grub //
NK075(bu)003:5568: las bzhi'i gnas de dag shin tu gal che bar bstan te /
NK075(bu)003:5570: rang bzhin nus mthu ldan pa'i phyir //
NK075(bu)003:5571: shin tu dgos par bsten pa yin //
NK075(bu)003:5573: gnyis pa sgrub pa po'i gang zag ni /
NK075(bu)003:5574: bden pa dbyer med kyi lta ba gting 'byin par rtogs pa /
NK075(bu)003:5575: ting nge 'dzin bskyed rdzogs zung 'jug gis sems kyi gnas rnyed pa /
NK075(bu)003:5576: spyod pa gnyis 'dzin gyi rtsol ba dang bral ba nyams su len pa /
NK075(bu)003:5577: phrin las chog 'grig gi lag len la mkhas pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:5578: gsum pa thabs kyi rnam pa ni /
NK075(bu)003:5580: sa bzhi legs par sbyangs byas nas //
NK075(bu)003:5582: sa gzhi rnams legs par sbyangs bar byas nas /
NK075(bu)003:5583: las bzhi'i thabs brtsegs pa la /
NK075(bu)003:5585: dkyil 'khor zlum po rim pa gsum //
NK075(bu)003:5587: zhi ba la zlum po 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi /
NK075(bu)003:5588: rgyas pa la gru bzhi'am rin chen zur brgyad /
NK075(bu)003:5589: dbang la zla gam mam pad+ma 'dab brgyad /
NK075(bu)003:5590: drag po la gru gsum khro zhal ste thabs brgyad /
NK075(bu)003:5592: rgyas pa la rin chen t+r+aa /
NK075(bu)003:5593: dbang la pad+ma h+r+aih drag po la rdo rje'am kha ta la h'u gis mtshan pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:5595: las bzhi'i thab kyi dbyibs bzhi po re re la bang rim gsum gsum ste /
NK075(bu)003:5596: zhi ba'i zlum po nang ma la khru gang /
NK075(bu)003:5597: rgyas pa'i gru bzhi la khru gang /
NK075(bu)003:5598: dbang yang dkyil na phar khru gang yod pa /
NK075(bu)003:5599: drag po yang ngos re la khru gang re yod pa /
NK075(bu)003:5600: bzhi ka zabs su khru phyed brus pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:5601: kha khyer phar sor bzhi bskyed /
NK075(bu)003:5605: yang sor bzhi bskyed pas kha khyer gsum gsum pa bzhi ka la mthun no //
NK075(bu)003:5606: zhi ba'i gsum la nang ma la rdo rje /
NK075(bu)003:5607: kha khyer mtho ba la 'khor lo /
NK075(bu)003:5608: phyi ta dma' ba la me 'od gtang /
NK075(bu)003:5609: rgyas pa'i gsum pa nang ma la rdo rje /
NK075(bu)003:5610: bar ma la rin po che /
NK075(bu)003:5611: phyi ta la zhags pa gtang /
NK075(bu)003:5612: dbang gi gsum la nang ma la rdo rje /
NK075(bu)003:5618: phyi ta la lcags kyu gtang ngo //
NK075(bu)003:5620: dkyil 'khor gsum po rim pa gsum //
NK075(bu)003:5621: khru gang dpangs dang zheng du yin //
NK075(bu)003:5622: zab dang gyen ni phyed du bshad //
NK075(bu)003:5625: mda' bzhi zhags pa dkar pos dkris //
NK075(bu)003:5626: gzhan yang 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi la //
NK075(bu)003:5627: rigs bzhi'i phyag rgya rab shes na //
NK075(bu)003:5628: dang seng mgo spel mar bri //
NK075(bu)003:5629: mu khyur bskor ba phyi ru bshad //
NK075(bu)003:5630: thams cad zhi byed dkyil 'khor yin //
NK075(bu)003:5631: gnyis pa rgyas pa'i thab ni /
NK075(bu)003:5633: gru chad la sogs rim rjes mthun //
NK075(bu)003:5634: rdo rje rin chen zhags pas bskor //
NK075(bu)003:5635: dbus su rin chen t+r+aa snying ldan //
NK075(bu)003:5636: gzhan yang rin chen dbyibs gnyis su //
NK075(bu)003:5637: rim pa la sogs rjes su mthun //
NK075(bu)003:5638: zhags pa ser po mda' bzhis bskor //
NK075(bu)003:5639: thams cad spel byed dkyil 'khor yin //
NK075(bu)003:5640: gsum pa dbang gi thab ni /
NK075(bu)003:5641: hom khung zla gam gdengs pa la //
NK075(bu)003:5643: lcags sgrog gtams pas mdzes par bya //
NK075(bu)003:5645: gzhan yang 'dab brgyad de bzhin du //
NK075(bu)003:5646: tha ma ljon shing mdzes pas bskor //
NK075(bu)003:5647: mda' bzhi zhags bsdus dbang gi yin //
NK075(bu)003:5648: bzhi pa drag po'i thab ni /
NK075(bu)003:5649: dkyil 'khor gru gsum gdeng pa la //
NK075(bu)003:5650: dur khrod sol bas khyab par sbyar //
NK075(bu)003:5651: rdo rje rtse gsum gdengs pa la //
NK075(bu)003:5652: thod pa lcags kyu gtam pas bskor //
NK075(bu)003:5653: h'u rdo rje snying por ldan //
NK075(bu)003:5654: mda' bzhi zhags pa nag pos bskor //
NK075(bu)003:5655: gzhan yang zhal gdangs spyan bgrad pa'i //
NK075(bu)003:5656: khro zhal shin tu 'jigs pa yis //
NK075(bu)003:5657: me dpung 'bar bas rab mdzes pa //
NK075(bu)003:5658: 'di ni gsod pa'i mchog tu gsungs //
NK075(bu)003:5661: thab khung de'i lho nub mtshams su las bzhi rang
NK075(bu)003:5662: rang gi dbyibs can gyi tshad mtho gang ba re
NK075(bu)003:5663: re dang bcas pa kha khyer gcig pa ste /
NK075(bu)003:5665: lnga pa sgrub pa po'i kha blta phyogs la gnyis te gdul bya dang 'dul byed do //
NK075(bu)003:5666: dang po yul gdul bya dang bstun na /
NK075(bu)003:5667: zhi ba la rang nub tu 'dug cing kha shar du blta /
NK075(bu)003:5668: gsum po de'i 'gres su shes so //
NK075(bu)003:5669: gnyis pa 'dul byed dam ye shes dang bstun na /
NK075(bu)003:5670: zhi ba la rang shar du 'dug cing kha nub tu blta /
NK075(bu)003:5671: gsum po de'i 'gres su shes so //
NK075(bu)003:5672: drug pa sgrub pa po'i chas gos dang /
NK075(bu)003:5673: thab khung gi kha dog ni /
NK075(bu)003:5677: drag po la mthing nag go //
NK075(bu)003:5679: dang po lo gcig la dbye na /
NK075(bu)003:5681: dbyar dgun ston dpyid las rim dang //
NK075(bu)003:5689: snga dro gung dgong nam phyed dus //
NK075(bu)003:5690: las rim brtsam na shis par bshad //
NK075(bu)003:5695: nam gung drag po'i sbyin sreg bya'o //
NK075(bu)003:5697: zhi ba la dngul lam shing dkar po'i phur pa dbal zlum por byas pa drug /
NK075(bu)003:5698: rgyas pa la gser ram shing ser po'i phur pa dbal gru bzhi byas pa bzhi /
NK075(bu)003:5699: dbang la zangs sam shing dmar po'i phur pa dbal zla gam du byas pa lnga /
NK075(bu)003:5700: drag po la lcags sam shing nag po'i phur pa dbal zur gsum byas pa gsum /
NK075(bu)003:5701: de dag kyang grub na las byed kyi phur pa nyi shu rtsa gcig re ste /
NK075(bu)003:5702: sras mchog nyi shu rtsa gcig tu gsal bar bsham mo //
NK075(bu)003:5703: de yang dang po zhi ba'i phur pa ni /
NK075(bu)003:5705: dngul lam dkar po'i shing rnams la //
NK075(bu)003:5706: mgo bo rgya mdud rtse zlum po //
NK075(bu)003:5707: steng 'og logs la khro bcu bsgom //
NK075(bu)003:5709: sngags dang phyag rgyas byin brlabs pas //
NK075(bu)003:5710: mtha' bskor yan lag snying la sbyar //
NK075(bu)003:5711: gnyis pa rgyas pa'i phur pa ni //
NK075(bu)003:5712: gser ram ser po'i shing rnams la //
NK075(bu)003:5713: mgo bo rgya mdud rtse zur bzhi //
NK075(bu)003:5714: lha rnams de bzhin rin chen 'phro //
NK075(bu)003:5715: zur bzhi gnas pa lus gnas bzhir //
NK075(bu)003:5716: btab pas yon tan 'du bar bsam //
NK075(bu)003:5717: gsum pa dbang gi phur pa ni //
NK075(bu)003:5719: zangs sam dmar po'i shing rnams la //
NK075(bu)003:5720: mgo bo rgya mdud rtse zla gam //
NK075(bu)003:5721: de bzhin chags pa'i phur bur shes //
NK075(bu)003:5722: zla gam mtha' skor dbang la sbyar //
NK075(bu)003:5723: de dag bsgyur te 'dus par bya //
NK075(bu)003:5724: bzhi pa drag po'i phur pa ni /
NK075(bu)003:5726: lcags sam nag po'i shing rnams la //
NK075(bu)003:5727: mgo bo rgya mdud rtse gsum pa //
NK075(bu)003:5728: de bzhin rdo rje phur brlab pa //
NK075(bu)003:5729: zur gsum lus ngag sems la sbyar //
NK075(bu)003:5731: las byed nyi shu gcig tu'ang gsungs //
NK075(bu)003:5734: las sbyor gyi lha zhi khro'i dkyil chog gzhung bzhin bsrang ngo //
NK075(bu)003:5737: sbyin dang bsreg pa'i lha gnyis te //
NK075(bu)003:5742: rigs bzhi sangs rgyas kyi sprul pa 'phrin las bzhi
NK075(bu)003:5743: gang la thogs pa med par 'jug pa'i sku mdog
NK075(bu)003:5745: de yang ra'i gdan thog na /
NK075(bu)003:5747: las sku mdog dkar po phyag g.yas na ril ba spyi blugs bsnams pa /
NK075(bu)003:5749: t+r+aa las ser po g.yas pas rin po che'i sgrom /
NK075(bu)003:5750: dbang ni h+r+aihls dmar po g.yas pas zhags pa /
NK075(bu)003:5751: drag po ni h'u las nag po g.yas pas tri shu la /
NK075(bu)003:5752: g.yon bzhi kas bgrangs phreng 'dzin pa /
NK075(bu)003:5753: drang srong gi cha byad can /
NK075(bu)003:5754: ra skyes la bcib pa ste /
NK075(bu)003:5756: sangs rgyas rigs kyi sprul pa'i phyir //
NK075(bu)003:5757: thams cad las la thogs med 'jug /
NK075(bu)003:5758: sku mdog cha lugs las bzhi mthun //
NK075(bu)003:5760: rigs kyi phyag rgyas gdab par bya //
NK075(bu)003:5762: ag+ne de wa las bzhi'i sngags //
NK075(bu)003:5764: zhal phyir sbyin pa'i lhar bshad do //
NK075(bu)003:5769: lnga bcu rtsa brgyad kyi dkyil 'khor bsgom ste /
NK075(bu)003:5770: de yang zhi ba'i 'phrin las la rnam snang dang /
NK075(bu)003:5771: bud+ha he ru kas gtsor byas pa'i zhi khro'i lha kun /
NK075(bu)003:5772: sku mdog dkar po 'od zer dkar po 'phro ba /
NK075(bu)003:5774: lha kun gyi g.yas dang pos 'khor lo 'dzin pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:5776: rat+na he ru kas gtsos byas pa'i lha kun ser po 'od zer ser po /
NK075(bu)003:5779: pad+ma he ru kas gtsor byas pa'i lha kun dmar po 'od zer dmar po /
NK075(bu)003:5781: drag po la rdo rje sems dpa' dang /
NK075(bu)003:5782: badz+ra he ru kas gtso byas pa'i lha kun mthing ka /
NK075(bu)003:5783: g.yas rdo rje 'dzin pa bskyed do //
NK075(bu)003:5785: gzugs brnyan lta bu'i gzhal yas ni //
NK075(bu)003:5788: rgyan rnams zhi la dkar ba dang //
NK075(bu)003:5790: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor ma lus pa //
NK075(bu)003:5791: kun kyang gti mug rdo rje'i tshul //
NK075(bu)003:5793: khams gsum thams cad khyab pa sbyar //
NK075(bu)003:5794: sa bon dang rang sngags ldan //
NK075(bu)003:5795: gzhan la'ang de bzhin shes par bya //
NK075(bu)003:5796: rin chen dga' 'phro ser skya ni //
NK075(bu)003:5798: sngags sogs gzhan ni snga ma'i tshul //
NK075(bu)003:5799: sprul pa'ang rjes su mthun pa ste //
NK075(bu)003:5800: dzahmh'u ba ho ldan par bya //
NK075(bu)003:5801: 'dod chags rdo rje lcags sgrog dang //
NK075(bu)003:5802: mdog ni dmar smug 'od po che //
NK075(bu)003:5803: sngags ni yi ge ra dang h+r+ai //
NK075(bu)003:5804: phyogs bcur khyab cing hri la bsdus //
NK075(bu)003:5805: zhe sdang rdo rje gtum chen 'bar //
NK075(bu)003:5806: dud ka nag po'i mdog 'dra ba //
NK075(bu)003:5808: nyi zla thod sbrul gdug pas brgyan //
NK075(bu)003:5809: seng ge glang chen stag rngam dang //
NK075(bu)003:5810: rbod gtong ldan pa'i phyag rgya ldan //
NK075(bu)003:5811: sgra skad drag pos khams gsum dkrugs //
NK075(bu)003:5812: bsgrub bya phyag rgya goms pa yis //
NK075(bu)003:5815: bcu pa sems la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:5816: don sems spyir bstan pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:5817: don sems bzhi dang gdung sems bzhi bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:5819: 'khor 'das kun gyi bdag nyid rang rig pa byang chub kyi sems mngon du byas pa yin te /
NK075(bu)003:5821: rang rig sangs rgyas kun gyi dngos //
NK075(bu)003:5822: thams cad rang dbang bdag bsgyur phyir //
NK075(bu)003:5823: bsgrub pa'i gtso bo 'di gsungs so //
NK075(bu)003:5825: gnyis pa bye brag tu bshad pa la zung bzhi las /
NK075(bu)003:5826: dang po zhi ba gnyis ni /
NK075(bu)003:5828: ma lus sems ni mtha' bral phyir //
NK075(bu)003:5829: rang bzhin rnam dag mngon du bya //
NK075(bu)003:5830: gnyis pa rgyas pa'i gnyis ni /
NK075(bu)003:5831: sems gter rtog tshogs dkyil 'khor phyir //
NK075(bu)003:5832: byin rlabs bsdus 'phel mngon du bsgom //
NK075(bu)003:5833: gsum pa dbang gi gnyis ni /
NK075(bu)003:5834: thams cad bdag phyir tha mi dad //
NK075(bu)003:5835: shin tu zhen pa nyid kyis 'grub //
NK075(bu)003:5836: chags pa chen po nyid du bshad //
NK075(bu)003:5837: bzhi pa drag po'i gnyis ni /
NK075(bu)003:5838: rang bzhin gcig phyir dngos med 'jigs //
NK075(bu)003:5839: log rtog khros pa'i sems kyis bskul //
NK075(bu)003:5840: yang dag zhe sdang chen por gsungs //
NK075(bu)003:5843: zhi ba la zhi zhing dwangsa pa /
NK075(bu)003:5844: rgyas pa la spro zhing dga' ba /
NK075(bu)003:5845: dbang la zhen cing chags pa /
NK075(bu)003:5846: drag po la khro zhing gtum pa'i sems kyis te /
NK075(bu)003:5848: dwangs pa dga' ba chags pa dang //
NK075(bu)003:5849: khros pas k+aa li rab tu bya //
NK075(bu)003:5852: zhi ba la bong chung ba /
NK075(bu)003:5857: sha dang nu ma rgyas shing rna ba 'phyang ba /
NK075(bu)003:5864: drag po la bzhin gru gsum /
NK075(bu)003:5865: sha nag la skra rtsub pa /
NK075(bu)003:5868: dang po zhi ba'i gzungs ma ni /
NK075(bu)003:5870: bong chung lus mdzes zla ba'i mdog /
NK075(bu)003:5871: g.yas 'khyil lus kyang de bzhin shes //
NK075(bu)003:5872: skad gsal sngags zlos yid mi skyo //
NK075(bu)003:5873: khro yang de bzhin zhi la sbyar //
NK075(bu)003:5876: ban glang ser mo gru bzhi ma //
NK075(bu)003:5877: rna ba 'gram zla ring sha rgyas //
NK075(bu)003:5878: yan lag zla mang las la mkhas //
NK075(bu)003:5879: dal zhing blo gros ldan pa ni //
NK075(bu)003:5882: bcu gnyis pa bsgrub bya ni /
NK075(bu)003:5884: bdag gzhan la gtum zhing rngam pa'i dgra bgegs dang /
NK075(bu)003:5885: rang gi sems kyi nyon mongs pa rnam rtog che ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:5886: gzhan gyi rbod gtong ngan pa la sogs pa rnams so //
NK075(bu)003:5888: tshe dang bsod nams dang longs spyod la sogs pa mi ldan pa de la /
NK075(bu)003:5889: gzhan tshe dang bsod nams longs spyod dang ldan pa gcig bkug nas /
NK075(bu)003:5892: bdag la pho mo dgra bgegs gang yin pa mi
NK075(bu)003:5893: mos shing mi 'dud pa de bkug ste dbang du
NK075(bu)003:5894: bsdu ba'o // drag po'i bsgrub bya ni /
NK075(bu)003:5895: bsgral ba'i zhing bcu po tshar bcad pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:5898: bdag gzhan gnod pa'i sems dang ni //
NK075(bu)003:5899: sbyor ba ngan pa'i rig sngags las //
NK075(bu)003:5900: khams rkyen las gyur gnod mang ba //
NK075(bu)003:5901: gsum pa'i las la sbyor bya zhing //
NK075(bu)003:5902: lha yang de bzhin shes par bya //
NK075(bu)003:5903: zhing bcur gyur pa'i sems can dang //
NK075(bu)003:5904: dam pa'i chos 'jig ma rung byed //
NK075(bu)003:5905: dpa' bos dgos pa yod pa'i phyir //
NK075(bu)003:5906: kun la phan phyir de bya'o //
NK075(bu)003:5908: bcu gsum pa las bzhi so so'i ling+ga'i rgyu ni /
NK075(bu)003:5909: bsgrub rgya gang yin pa'i dam rdzas /
NK075(bu)003:5912: gos la sogs pa zhi ba'i ling+ga'i rgyu dang /
NK075(bu)003:5913: rdzas de la gzhan gyi longs spyod rgyas pa'i thabs su bsdu ba ni rgyas pa'i rgyu dang /
NK075(bu)003:5914: dam rdzas kyi thog tu ro sgyur ba'i rdzas bsnan pa ni dbang gi rgyu dang /
NK075(bu)003:5915: de'i thog tu dug dang tsha ba gsum dang sha
NK075(bu)003:5916: chen dang ra dang ba glang gi sha bsnan pa
NK075(bu)003:5919: bdud rtsi lnga'am zas lnga la //
NK075(bu)003:5920: mtshan ma ming dang bcas par bya //
NK075(bu)003:5922: rgyu de las ling+ga byas te /
NK075(bu)003:5927: 'doms su las bzhi gang yin gyi sngags spu gri dang bcas pa bris la /
NK075(bu)003:5928: las bzhi gang byed kyi brub khung du bzhag go //
NK075(bu)003:5929: bcu bzhi pa me mchod kyi rdzas la yang /
NK075(bu)003:5931: gnyis pa rnam pa lngar bshad de //
NK075(bu)003:5932: zhes gsungs pas rdzas la lnga ste /
NK075(bu)003:5933: las bzhi gang byed kyi bsreg shing /
NK075(bu)003:5939: me yi rdzas gnyis bsreg shing dang /
NK075(bu)003:5943: zhi ba la rtse mo'i cha las byung ba'i sor bcu gnyis pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:5945: yal ga las byung ba'i sor bcu drug pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:5947: sdong po'i cha las byung ba sor bcu drug pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:5948: drag po la rtsa ba'i cha las byung ba'i sor bzhi pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:5950: rtse mo zhi byed yal ga rgyas //
NK075(bu)003:5951: sdong po rtsa ba mngon spyod de //
NK075(bu)003:5953: shing tha dad la byed na /
NK075(bu)003:5954: shing dkar ser 'jam po la zhi rgyas gnyis /
NK075(bu)003:5955: dmar nag tsher ma can la dbang drag gi bsreg shing bya ba ste /
NK075(bu)003:5957: kha dog las kyis sbyar ba'o //
NK075(bu)003:5961: shug pa tsan+dana dkar po dang /
NK075(bu)003:5962: u dum w+aa ra 'o ma'i shing /
NK075(bu)003:5963: zhi rgyas yam shing shes par bya /
NK075(bu)003:5964: dmar la dri zhim shing rnams dang /
NK075(bu)003:5965: dug shing tsher ma can dag la /
NK075(bu)003:5966: tshil byug dbang drag me sbar ro //
NK075(bu)003:5967: gsum pa ling+ga'i rgyu ni gong du song la /
NK075(bu)003:5968: bzhi pa gtor ma la'ang zhi ba'i gtor ma ni /
NK075(bu)003:5971: me tog dkar po'i gtor ma zhi //
NK075(bu)003:5974: ldong ros gro chan zho rgun 'bru //
NK075(bu)003:5975: me tog gser phye rgyas pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:5977: zangs phye nas ram 'bras chen dmar //
NK075(bu)003:5979: thams cad sdud pa'i gtor ma yin //
NK075(bu)003:5981: dug rnams lcags phye rdo phye dang //
NK075(bu)003:5982: ra khyi khrag dang sha chen dang //
NK075(bu)003:5983: dur sol dur kha'i chan rnams ni //
NK075(bu)003:5984: gsod par byed pa'i gtor ma yin //
NK075(bu)003:5988: mar dkar til dkar nas dkar chan //
NK075(bu)003:5989: dkar gsum tsan+dana dkar po'i shing //
NK075(bu)003:5990: thams cad ye shes bdud rtsi ste //
NK075(bu)003:5991: tha mas ye shes mes skyed do //
NK075(bu)003:5994: zho dang mar rnying bu ram sbrang //
NK075(bu)003:5995: rgun 'bru star rga shang tse dang //
NK075(bu)003:5996: dri zhim gser phye rgyas pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:5998: yang tan+ta li dang shang tse dang //
NK075(bu)003:5999: ke tshe tsha ba'i mar dag dang //
NK075(bu)003:6000: dmar po'i shing dang 'bras dag gis //
NK075(bu)003:6001: thams cad 'gug pa'i mchog tu gsungs //
NK075(bu)003:6004: dug dang tshil chen ske tshe'i mar //
NK075(bu)003:6005: sran chan khrag sna tshogs tshad dang //
NK075(bu)003:6006: tsher ma ba glang sha yis gsod //
NK075(bu)003:6007: 'bras bu gdon phyir tshogs par bya'o //
NK075(bu)003:6009: bco lnga pa cha rkyen ni /
NK075(bu)003:6010: gzhan yang rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor la mchod pa la
NK075(bu)003:6011: sogs pa'i yo byad gang mkho rnams tshang bar sbyar
NK075(bu)003:6012: bar bya'o // gnyis pa las kyi rim pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:6014: 'phrin las bya ba'i thabs kyi gtso bo ni sbyin bsreg yin pas /
NK075(bu)003:6015: de'i 'phrin las kyi rim pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:6016: phrin las kyi skabs su dgos pa'i brub khung gi
NK075(bu)003:6017: ling ga la las bzhi rang rang gi bsgrub par
NK075(bu)003:6018: bya ba de bkug cing bstims nas /
NK075(bu)003:6019: de la phur pa gdab pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:6020: phrin las kyi mtha' rdzogs par bya ba'i phyir bro
NK075(bu)003:6021: bstab pa dang bcas pa'i cha rkyen rnams tshang bar
NK075(bu)003:6023: bya thabs de dag rgyas par bshad na /
NK075(bu)003:6024: zhi khro gang yin gyi rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor sngon 'gro yan lag brgyad pa nas bzung ste /
NK075(bu)003:6025: mchod 'bul bstod pa bsnyen pa man chad tshang ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:6026: de nas ta na sgrol ba ste /
NK075(bu)003:6027: ling+ga la 'gugs gzhug la sogs pa bsgral las bya ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:6028: de nas g+ha na sbyor ba ste rnam shes spar chog bya /
NK075(bu)003:6029: de dag shin tu rgyas par na /
NK075(bu)003:6030: sbyin bsreg bya thabs kyi rim pa la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:6033: rdzas dang yo byad ldan byas la //
NK075(bu)003:6034: sa gzhi sbyangs te gzugs brnyan sbyar //
NK075(bu)003:6035: stong gyur mgon la las bcol zhing //
NK075(bu)003:6036: kun kyang 'tshams bya bgo ba bya'o //
NK075(bu)003:6037: shing gnyis mchod rdzas legs bkod de //
NK075(bu)003:6038: kha dog me dar legs par dgab //
NK075(bu)003:6039: ling+ga'i gnas ni gzugs brnyan tshul //
NK075(bu)003:6040: ming rus ldan pa'i phur pas bskor //
NK075(bu)003:6041: gnyis pa sngon 'gro'i cho ga dngos ni /
NK075(bu)003:6042: rdo rje'i gur gyis phyogs bcings zhing //
NK075(bu)003:6043: nyi ma zla ba las gnyis kyis //
NK075(bu)003:6044: gzhong pa snod kyi rdzas rnams la //
NK075(bu)003:6045: las kyi h'u la 'bru lnga dgod //
NK075(bu)003:6047: mang zhing sna tshogs ror ldan bya //
NK075(bu)003:6049: gnyis pa las rim dngos la gsum ste /
NK075(bu)003:6050: las sbyor gyi phrin las zhi khro gzhung bsrang ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:6052: sbyin sreg gi las rim bya'o //
NK075(bu)003:6054: dkyil 'khor las kyi gzhung bsrangs la //
NK075(bu)003:6055: sna tshogs mchod don rgyas par 'bul //
NK075(bu)003:6056: tshogs kyi 'khor lo legs par brtags //
NK075(bu)003:6057: mchod pa chen po'ang 'bul bar bya //
NK075(bu)003:6059: ye shes dkyil 'khor bskul bar bya //
NK075(bu)003:6060: khams gsum byin rlabs dag bsdus te //
NK075(bu)003:6061: bsgrub bya nye bar sbyar ba dang //
NK075(bu)003:6062: srog dang ldan pa'i bzlas pa ni //
NK075(bu)003:6063: zhal gyi rang sngags khri 'bum du //
NK075(bu)003:6064: rnam pa gsum gyi bya ba dag /
NK075(bu)003:6065: shin tu stongs gyur rgyas par bya //
NK075(bu)003:6068: khams gsum gang ba'i dkyil 'khor ni //
NK075(bu)003:6070: bdag nyid 'dzin pa'i phyag rgya ste //
NK075(bu)003:6071: mtshan la bzung nas rang sngags 'don //
NK075(bu)003:6072: rol pa'i pho nya bka' nyan tshogs //
NK075(bu)003:6073: phyag rgya bzhi ldan sgra skad grags //
NK075(bu)003:6074: khams gsum dkrugs te bral byas nas //
NK075(bu)003:6075: bsgrub bya mngon du sbyar bar bya //
NK075(bu)003:6077: tshogs tha ma la ling+ga byas pas brub khung nang du brub la dgug gzhug bya /
NK075(bu)003:6078: gtor bskul byas la gtor thun dbab //
NK075(bu)003:6079: phur bskul byas la phur pa gdab //
NK075(bu)003:6080: mtshon cha'i char dbab gris gtubs la //
NK075(bu)003:6081: bsreg rdzas dang bsre la bzhag go //
NK075(bu)003:6082: de nas me mchod sbyin sreg gi rim pa ni /
NK075(bu)003:6086: me mtshams bcad cing bgegs bskrad la sogs byas la /
NK075(bu)003:6087: me lha ni las bzhi gang byed kyi me lha'i dam tshig pa bskyed /
NK075(bu)003:6090: ye shes pa snyan gsan dbab /
NK075(bu)003:6091: spyan drangs nas dam tshig pa la bstim /
NK075(bu)003:6093: las bzhi gang byed kyi smon lam gdab bo //
NK075(bu)003:6095: las gzhi gang byed kyi dam tshig pa bskyed /
NK075(bu)003:6097: ye shes kyi lha dbab drang bstim /
NK075(bu)003:6099: de nas las bzhi gang byed kyi bsreg rdzas sngags kyis 'bul /
NK075(bu)003:6100: bden pa dang smon lam gdab nas bstod pa bya /
NK075(bu)003:6103: rjes su mthun pa'i gzhal yas su //
NK075(bu)003:6104: sbyin lha so so'i gdan ltar bsgom //
NK075(bu)003:6105: me dpung 'bar ba'i mtshan can du //
NK075(bu)003:6106: me lha ag+ne dzahs bkug nas //
NK075(bu)003:6107: phyag rgya bzhi yis nges bkug la //
NK075(bu)003:6108: ram zhes pa yis me sbar nas //
NK075(bu)003:6109: gzar bu rigs kyi mtshan bcas pa //
NK075(bu)003:6110: mchod pa bdud rtsi rgyas par 'bul //
NK075(bu)003:6111: de dbus 'khor lo gsal gdab ste //
NK075(bu)003:6112: gnyis pa'i lha rnams spyan drangs bstim //
NK075(bu)003:6113: mar dang shing bu chan la sogs //
NK075(bu)003:6115: gcig min thams cad bdud rtsi ste //
NK075(bu)003:6116: yang na lan gsum brgya rtsa brgyad //
NK075(bu)003:6118: dug gsum mchod pa de bzhin bya //
NK075(bu)003:6119: dbang med zhal du thim par 'bul //
NK075(bu)003:6120: ming dang las bzhi'i sngags kyis 'bul //
NK075(bu)003:6123: gzugs brnyan lu gu rgyud bskor la //
NK075(bu)003:6124: e la sogs pa'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK075(bu)003:6125: rjes su mthun pa'i lha bsgoms la //
NK075(bu)003:6126: slas dang byi mo'i tshogs kyis bskor //
NK075(bu)003:6127: khams gsum gang bar sbyar bar bya //
NK075(bu)003:6128: srog dang ldan pa'i bro stabs gar //
NK075(bu)003:6129: phyogs bcu ma lus kun nas ni //
NK075(bu)003:6130: bsgrub bya dbus su legs brtag ste //
NK075(bu)003:6131: sa bon 'od zer las bzhi kun //
NK075(bu)003:6132: bstims nas bsam pa 'grub par bya //
NK075(bu)003:6133: rjes su mthun pa'i smon lam gdab //
NK075(bu)003:6135: de nas lhag ma'i las dag ni /
NK075(bu)003:6137: bdag nyid 'dus pa'i dbang phyug tu //
NK075(bu)003:6138: las bzhin mnyam bzhag khro bo yis //
NK075(bu)003:6140: phra man tshogs rnams bskul bsdus te //
NK075(bu)003:6141: las bzhi'i dkyil 'khor de dag tu //
NK075(bu)003:6142: lhag ma kha chu'i bkod pa rnams //
NK075(bu)003:6146: yi ge brgya pas lhag chad kha bskangs /
NK075(bu)003:6147: bsreg lha dang me lha'i ye shes pa gshegs /
NK075(bu)003:6148: dam tshig pa rang la bsdu tshom bu dang dkyil 'khor bsdu la /
NK075(bu)003:6149: las kyi rjes mi mngon par bya zhing /
NK075(bu)003:6150: bkra shis kyi tshigs su bcad pa brjod pa yan chad kyis sbyin sreg gi las rdzogs so //
NK075(bu)003:6153: sbyin bsreg bya ba'i skabs nii dbang bskur ba'i dus
NK075(bu)003:6154: sa chog gi skabs la zhi ba'i sbyin sreg dang
NK075(bu)003:6155: / sta gon la drag po'i dang /
NK075(bu)003:6156: rab gnas kyi dus su rgyas pa'i dang /
NK075(bu)003:6157: dbang ngo bo'i dus su dbang ngo //
NK075(bu)003:6158: bsgrub pa'i dus su las sbyor la las bzhi bya ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:6159: mchod pa byed pa'i dus dang /
NK075(bu)003:6160: dam tshig chag nyams bshagsa pa'i tshe na dgos pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:6161: las bzhi rang rang gis gdul bya 'dul ba'i dus la bab pa'i tshe na dgos pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:6164: phrin las kyi rim pa mtho dman gyi khyad par
NK075(bu)003:6165: ni zag bcas tshogs lam rnal 'byor bzhi'i dus su
NK075(bu)003:6166: lhag pa gzugs brnyan la brten pas rgya chung /
NK075(bu)003:6167: bar chad med pa tshogs sgrub pa'i dus su ting nge 'dzin la brten pas 'bring /
NK075(bu)003:6168: de dag mthar phyin pa'i lam rig 'dzin gyi dus su las bzhi lhun gyis grub pas rgya che /
NK075(bu)003:6169: de ltar mtho dman dang rgya che chung gis phye ba'am /
NK075(bu)003:6170: yang na blo'i shes rab kyi dbang po rab 'bring tha ma rnam pa gsum gyi phye bas /
NK075(bu)003:6171: las bzhi la nus mthu che chung dang /
NK075(bu)003:6172: byin rlabs kyis yul gdul bya la don 'gyur che chung dang /
NK075(bu)003:6173: ngo bo la mos pa dang nus pa'i khyad par dang /
NK075(bu)003:6174: las bzhi bya thabs la sngags dang rdzas ting nge
NK075(bu)003:6175: 'dzin dgos mi dgos dang bzhi la khyad par yod
NK075(bu)003:6176: pa ni / dper na skan tsha'i gdong bu la mthon dman yod pa ci lta bu yin pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:6179: las bzhi nyams su ma blangs na dam tshig chag
NK075(bu)003:6180: nyams mi skong sgrib pa mi 'byong tshogs mi rdzogs
NK075(bu)003:6181: pa dang / bdag gzhan gyi don gnyis mi 'grub
NK075(bu)003:6182: pa rnams 'phrin las ma byas pa de'i skyon yin
NK075(bu)003:6183: pa dang / / dgu pa yon tan no //
NK075(bu)003:6185: gong gi las bzhi de ltar byas na skyon de
NK075(bu)003:6186: las bzlog pa'i yon tan gyi tshul dang ldan pa
NK075(bu)003:6190: bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs rdzogs /
NK075(bu)003:6191: bdag gzhan gyi don gnyis 'grub pa ste /
NK075(bu)003:6192: de ni yon tan nyid du yin par shes par bya'o //
NK075(bu)003:6193: bzhi pa dam tshig la gnyis /
NK075(bu)003:6197: yan lag bzhi pa lam dang 'bras bu'i gzhi dam
NK075(bu)003:6198: tshig gis bzung bas na sa gzhi gshin po dang
NK075(bu)003:6199: 'dra ba de'i sdom tshig ni 'di lta ste /
NK075(bu)003:6200: dam tshig gi ngo bo dang /
NK075(bu)003:6202: dam tshig bsrung ba'i dgos ched dang /
NK075(bu)003:6203: bsrung ba'i dus la rim pa yod tshul dang /
NK075(bu)003:6204: 'di la bsrung bya thams cad rdzogs pa'i che ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:6205: dam tshig bsrungs pa'i yon tan dang /
NK075(bu)003:6206: nyams na bskang ba'i thabs rnams dang /
NK075(bu)003:6207: ma bsrungs pa'i skyon dang brgyad po dag gis nang
NK075(bu)003:6208: du nges par ma nor bar 'og rgyas bshad kyi
NK075(bu)003:6209: dmigs rnams yongs su shes par bya'o //
NK075(bu)003:6210: gnyis pa bshad pa de la brgyad de /
NK075(bu)003:6214: gsang sngags bla med kyi sgor zhugsa pa'i gang zag thams cad kyi /
NK075(bu)003:6215: lus ngag yid gsum gyi sgo gsum gyi bla med
NK075(bu)003:6216: rang gzhung gi rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam
NK075(bu)003:6217: tshig bsrung bya thams cad la /
NK075(bu)003:6218: dper na rgyal po'i kha 'og gi mi rnams kyis
NK075(bu)003:6219: rgyal po'i bka' shog gi rtags snang na 'da' mi
NK075(bu)003:6220: phod pa ci lta bar nyams par mi byed cing
NK075(bu)003:6221: mi 'bral nas bsrung byar sdom pa de dam tshig
NK075(bu)003:6225: thun mong spyi'i rnam grangs ni /
NK075(bu)003:6228: byang sems kyi sems bskyed la sogs don 'gyur du
NK075(bu)003:6229: snang na nyams su blangs lugs thun mong gi gzhung
NK075(bu)003:6230: gzhan nas bshad pa'i bsrung bya rnams kyang 'gro ba
NK075(bu)003:6231: sems can drang ba'i don du bsrung dgos pa dang
NK075(bu)003:6232: / khyad par gsang sngags rang gzhung gi dam tshig
NK075(bu)003:6233: rtsa ba dang yan lag de dag gi bsrung bya'i
NK075(bu)003:6234: / rnam grangs ni / mdor bsdus pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:6237: srung mkhan gyi gang zag la blo rab 'bring tha ma gsum las /
NK075(bu)003:6238: dang po blo rab la don gyi mdo ni mnyam pa nyid kyi dam tshig yin te /
NK075(bu)003:6240: mnyam la mnyam par sbyor ba yis //
NK075(bu)003:6241: mnyam pa'i dam tshig la gnas na //
NK075(bu)003:6242: mnyam rdzogs chen po thob par 'gyur //
NK075(bu)003:6243: 'das na sangs rgyas ma yin no //
NK075(bu)003:6245: rnam grangs kyi mdo ni rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig bco lnga po yin te /
NK075(bu)003:6247: bla med mi spang bla ma bskur //
NK075(bu)003:6248: sngags dang phyag rgya rgyun mi gcad //
NK075(bu)003:6249: yang dag lam du zhugs la byams //
NK075(bu)003:6250: gsang ba'i don phyir smra mi bya //
NK075(bu)003:6251: gti mug chags dang zhe sdang dang //
NK075(bu)003:6252: nga rgyal phrag dog mi spang ngo //
NK075(bu)003:6253: dkar rtsi dmar rtsi dri sha chen //
NK075(bu)003:6254: dag pa'i snod bcud mi dor ro //
NK075(bu)003:6256: gnyis pa blo 'bring la dam tshig sum brgya drug cur dbye ba ste /
NK075(bu)003:6258: rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga la ni //
NK075(bu)003:6259: gcig la'ang gnyis dang bcu phrag gsum //
NK075(bu)003:6260: yan lag dam tshig lnga gnyis la //
NK075(bu)003:6261: gcig la'ang bcu phrag gnyis su dbye //
NK075(bu)003:6262: zhes gsungs pa'i rnam grangs kyi dbye ba ni /
NK075(bu)003:6264: phyi ma rtsa ba yan lag las //
NK075(bu)003:6265: lnga bcu brgya dang drug cu dang //
NK075(bu)003:6266: gnyis brgya'i bsrung bya ma lus pa //
NK075(bu)003:6267: bka' lung gnyis kyi rjes su zhugs //
NK075(bu)003:6268: pany+tsa'i snying lag shes bya ba //
NK075(bu)003:6269: dang po nyid las thabs spyod dang //
NK075(bu)003:6270: shes rab nyid kyis gnyis 'gyur yin //
NK075(bu)003:6271: re re'ang bsrung bya bcu gsum ste //
NK075(bu)003:6273: rtsa ba'i dam tshig gcig la yang /
NK075(bu)003:6274: shes rab rang bzhin med pa'i lta ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:6275: thabs ma 'gags par spyod pa gnyis su phye bas bcu dang /
NK075(bu)003:6276: de dag spyi ru bzhag nas /
NK075(bu)003:6277: bye brag tu rtsa ba lnga po re la yang sum cu re re ste /
NK075(bu)003:6279: yan lag gi dam tshig bcu po re re la nyi shu re re dbye bas gnyis brgya ste /
NK075(bu)003:6280: kun bsdoms na sum brgya drug cu'o //
NK075(bu)003:6281: gsum pa blo tha ma'i gdul bya'i snang ngor dam tshig gi rnam grangs mtha' yas pa gsung ste /
NK075(bu)003:6283: dam tshig rnams ni rmad po che //
NK075(bu)003:6284: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu na //
NK075(bu)003:6285: srid gsum 'gro ba ci snyed pa //
NK075(bu)003:6286: rtog 'dul dam tshig de snyed spro //
NK075(bu)003:6287: zhes gsungs pa rnams tan+t+ra ste rgyud gsang ba'i snying
NK075(bu)003:6288: po'i nang du gsungsa pas der snyigsa te shes par
NK075(bu)003:6289: bya ba rnams ni de lta bu la bya'o //
NK075(bu)003:6290: gzhan yang theg chena ma h+aa rang gzhung gi sa
NK075(bu)003:6291: lam gong 'og la bsrung bya'i khyad para yod pa'i
NK075(bu)003:6292: phyir / tshogs lam rnal 'byor bzhi dang /
NK075(bu)003:6293: sbyor lam tshogs sgrub dang lnga po rang rang gi
NK075(bu)003:6294: skabs kyi lam gyi ngo bo'i chos nyid mnyam bzhag
NK075(bu)003:6295: de dang mi mthun pa'i phyogs rnams bsrung bar bya'o
NK075(bu)003:6298: dam tshig de nyid bsrung ba yi dgos ched ni /
NK075(bu)003:6299: khyad par gsang sngags rang gi dam tshig dang /
NK075(bu)003:6300: thun mong spyi yi dam tshig ma bsrungs pa'i skyon cha'i ngan song dang 'khor bar ltung la /
NK075(bu)003:6301: der mi ltung ba la dam tshig dgos pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:6302: bsrung ba'i yon tan gyi cha yisa mtho ris dang
NK075(bu)003:6303: byang chub thob pa'i dgos ched che ba de bas
NK075(bu)003:6304: na / ma bsrungs na nyes che ba de dang
NK075(bu)003:6305: bsrungs na yon tan che ba de yis dam tshig
NK075(bu)003:6306: bsrung ba'i dgos ched kyi nges tshig de 'grub pa
NK075(bu)003:6307: na / yin te / lam rim las /
NK075(bu)003:6309: log na yod pa ma yin te //
NK075(bu)003:6310: rang gi lta ba dam tshig yin //
NK075(bu)003:6311: mi gtong phyir yang dam zhes bya //
NK075(bu)003:6312: gzungs su gyur kyang dam zhes bya //
NK075(bu)003:6313: de bzhin nyid las mi byed //
NK075(bu)003:6314: de bzhin nyid ldan dam pa ste //
NK075(bu)003:6317: dam zhes pa chos nyid la bya ste /
NK075(bu)003:6318: des khyab cing mi 'da' bas na dam /
NK075(bu)003:6319: de nyid lta sgom gyis nyams su len cing mi 'da' bar bsrungs na /
NK075(bu)003:6320: 'khor ba'i rgyu nyon mongs 'bras bu dang bcas pa thams cad tshig par 'gyur la /
NK075(bu)003:6321: de las 'das na mya ngan las 'das pa'i bde 'bras thams cad tshig par 'gyur ro //
NK075(bu)003:6322: gzhan yang khyad par gsang sngags rang gi dam tshig dang /
NK075(bu)003:6323: thun mong gi theg pa spyi'i dam tshig rnams bdag
NK075(bu)003:6324: gzhan gyi don du bsrung ba'i gdul bya gang yin
NK075(bu)003:6325: pa'i sgrib pa sbyangs ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:6326: tshogs bsags pa'i dgos ched yod pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:6329: thun mong dang khyad par gyi bsrung bya'i dam tshig
NK075(bu)003:6330: gi rnam grangs las lam mthon dman gyi rim pa
NK075(bu)003:6331: dang / drang nges kyi khyad par yada pa'i phyir
NK075(bu)003:6332: na las dang po pa'i dus su thun mong gi
NK075(bu)003:6333: dam tshig rnams rang don du bsrung ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:6334: khyad par gyi dam tshig rnams mos bsrung byed la /
NK075(bu)003:6335: ye shes dang ting nge 'dzin la dbang thob nas
NK075(bu)003:6336: thun mong gi dam tshig gzhan don du bsrung ba
NK075(bu)003:6337: dang / khyad par gyi dam tshig nus bsrung byed pa yin pa de bas na /
NK075(bu)003:6338: tshogs sbyor gyi sa lam gyi rim pa gang thob
NK075(bu)003:6339: pa de yi tshe de dus kyi mnyam bzhag chos
NK075(bu)003:6340: nyid de nyid ma yin mi 'da' ba'i thabs la
NK075(bu)003:6341: dam tshig de dgongs pa de bas na /
NK075(bu)003:6342: sa lam rang rang gi ting nge 'dzin dang mthun
NK075(bu)003:6343: pa'i dam tshig de bsrung bar byed pa'i thabs rnams
NK075(bu)003:6344: nyams su blang ba'i dus la bab pa yin no
NK075(bu)003:6345: // de ltar sa lam gang thob pa'i skabsa kyi
NK075(bu)003:6346: ting nge 'dzin de dang rang rang gi bsrung bya'i
NK075(bu)003:6347: dam tshig gnyis 'byor na phan yon la gnyis te
NK075(bu)003:6348: // / sgrib pa byang tshogs gnyis rdzogs nas lam nar son pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:6351: spyir theg pa 'og ma'i bsrung bya nyan thos kyi 'dul khrims dang /
NK075(bu)003:6352: byang sems kyi sdom pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:6353: sngags phyi rgyud kyi dam tshig rnams /
NK075(bu)003:6354: 'dir theg mchog ma h+aa yo ga'i bsrung bya'i dam
NK075(bu)003:6355: tshig la bskul zhing yon tan yar ldan du rdzogs
NK075(bu)003:6357: rgyud gsang snying la sogs pa'i nang nas smos pa'i
NK075(bu)003:6358: gsang sngags bla med kyi dam tshig rnams bsrung zhing
NK075(bu)003:6360: nyan thos kyi tshul khrims dang /
NK075(bu)003:6361: byang sems kyi sdom pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:6362: sngags phyi rgyud kyi dam tshig thams cad ngo bo nyid kyis rdzogs pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:6363: 'o na 'og ma'i 'dul sdom dam tshig rnams dngos su bsrung ngam zhe na ma yin te /
NK075(bu)003:6364: spang bya nyon mongs pa bdag 'dzin 'di /
NK075(bu)003:6365: nyan thos kyis spangs byang sems kyis sbyangs /
NK075(bu)003:6366: gsang sngags phyi rgyud kyis bsgyur nas dag par byed la /
NK075(bu)003:6367: 'dir gsang sngags bla med kyi spang bya nyon mongs
NK075(bu)003:6368: pa'i rang bzhin sku dang ye shes yin pa de
NK075(bu)003:6369: / lta sgom gyis nyams su len zhing mi 'da' ba'i ngo bo la /
NK075(bu)003:6370: spang gnyen shar grol du ro gcig par gyur pa'i dus su /
NK075(bu)003:6371: theg 'og ltar dam tshig bsrung bya dang srung byed
NK075(bu)003:6372: med par sdom pa'i ngo bo nyamsa pa'ang med do
NK075(bu)003:6373: // gang gi rgyud la smos pa zhes bya ba ni /
NK075(bu)003:6374: gsang snying le'u bcu dgu pa las /
NK075(bu)003:6375: bla med theg par rab nges na //
NK075(bu)003:6376: nyon mongs las rnams kun spyod kyang //
NK075(bu)003:6377: byas la mi sogs tshogs 'gyur te //
NK075(bu)003:6378: tshul khrims sdom pa phun sum tshogs //
NK075(bu)003:6379: bla med mchog gi dam tshig tu //
NK075(bu)003:6380: 'dul ba'i dbang gis tshul khrims dang //
NK075(bu)003:6381: ci snyed sdom pa bsam yas pa //
NK075(bu)003:6382: ma lus kun 'dus rnam par dag /
NK075(bu)003:6386: bla med 'di nyid kyi lta sgom la sogs pa
NK075(bu)003:6387: rnams ma nor ba'i don la mi 'da' ba'i dam
NK075(bu)003:6388: tshig la gnas pa'i phan yon ni rtsa ba dang
NK075(bu)003:6389: yan lag gi dam tshig gi rnam grangs rnams rjes
NK075(bu)003:6391: spyi'i phan yon ni rgyud gsang snying las gragsa pa ste gsungs pa ni /
NK075(bu)003:6392: gzhan yang rgyal mchog kun bzang gi //
NK075(bu)003:6393: thams cad ma lus phyag rgya yis //
NK075(bu)003:6394: bsgrub med dam pa ma lus 'grub //
NK075(bu)003:6395: de la sogs pa mtha' yas mchog /
NK075(bu)003:6396: rgyal ba'i rigs mchog 'dzin pa de //
NK075(bu)003:6398: dam pa mchog dang dam pa yis //
NK075(bu)003:6399: sras dang spun dgongs byin gyis rlob //
NK075(bu)003:6400: bder gshegs nyid kyi yul la zhugs //
NK075(bu)003:6401: 'jigs med kun tu bzang por sbyor //
NK075(bu)003:6402: ci bzhin nyid dpal 'dul ba'i thabs //
NK075(bu)003:6403: ci snyed sdom pa mtha' yas kyang //
NK075(bu)003:6404: ma lus rnam dag lhun gyis grub //
NK075(bu)003:6405: nyams na bskangs pas rdzogs pa dang //
NK075(bu)003:6406: de la sogs mtha' yas mchog /
NK075(bu)003:6408: gzhan yang dam tshig bsrungs na ngan song dang 'khor ba la mi ltung nas bzung ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:6409: 'bras bu sangs rgyas thob pa yin pas na de'i dbye ba'ang bya ste de dag yod pas na /
NK075(bu)003:6410: rnal 'byor pa bdag gi don dang gdul bya gzhan
NK075(bu)003:6411: gyi don gang la yang dam tshig bsrung dgos pa
NK075(bu)003:6412: de bas na dam tshig gi rnam grangs kyi yon
NK075(bu)003:6413: tan ma lus pa rdzogs pa' phyir byang pa'i lug
NK075(bu)003:6417: rtsa ba'i dam tshig de dang /
NK075(bu)003:6418: yan lag gi dam tshig de rtsa ba dang nas nyam pa zhig pa'am /
NK075(bu)003:6419: sna re nas nyams pas ral ba byung ba'i tshe /
NK075(bu)003:6420: gang nyams kyi dmigs de shes par byas la /
NK075(bu)003:6421: gso ba'i thabs la rtsa ba lnga ni /
NK075(bu)003:6423: las dang rdzas dang 'dun pa dang //
NK075(bu)003:6424: ting nge 'dzin dang de bzhin nyid //
NK075(bu)003:6426: dang po las kyi bskang ba ni /
NK075(bu)003:6428: rtsa ba nyams na khri tsho lnga dang stong tsho gsum blug /
NK075(bu)003:6429: yan lag nyams na stong tsho lnga dang brgya tsho gsum blug /
NK075(bu)003:6430: zlar nyams na brgya tsho lnga dang bcu tsho gsum blug /
NK075(bu)003:6431: zhar nyams la lnga bcu rtsa gsum blug go //
NK075(bu)003:6432: gnyis pa rdzas kyis bskang ba ni //
NK075(bu)003:6433: rigs gang nyams dang mthun pa'i nor 'bul la gaso'o //
NK075(bu)003:6434: gsum pa 'dun pas bskang ba la yig brgya dang bshags pa bya'o //
NK075(bu)003:6435: bzhi pa ting nge 'dzin gyis bskang ba la /
NK075(bu)003:6436: ram yam kham gsum gyis bsreg sbyang bkru gsum bya'o //
NK075(bu)003:6437: lnga pa de kho na nyid kyis bskang ba ni /
NK075(bu)003:6438: lta ba rtogs pas gso bar bya'o //
NK075(bu)003:6439: de ltar gso ba'i thabs gang la yang le lo
NK075(bu)003:6440: med par brtson 'grus kyi sgo nas mos 'dun dang
NK075(bu)003:6441: bcas pas rang rang gi blos lcogsa tshad sbyar bar
NK075(bu)003:6442: bya'o // des na chag nyams gso ba'i yon tan
NK075(bu)003:6443: gyis lam chud mi za bar nges par tshogs gnyis
NK075(bu)003:6444: rdzogs nas ngan song dang 'khor bar mi gtong nas
NK075(bu)003:6446: mchog thun mong gi 'bras bu rnams thob pa yin no //
NK075(bu)003:6447: brgyad pa nyams pa'i rgyu dang nyams pa'i skyon no //
NK075(bu)003:6449: bsrung bya'i dmigs mi shes pas phyal ba pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:6450: dmigs shes kyang brtson 'grus med nas le lo byed pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:6451: sngar dam tshig mnos kyang mi bsrung nas sdig pa byas pas loga pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:6452: grogs ngan gyi zlar nyams pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:6453: nyams pa can gyi grib phog pas zhar la nyams shor ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:6454: nyon mongsa pa che bas de'i dbang du song nas nyams pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:6455: dngos su bdud kyis bslus te de'i dbang du song nas nyams pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:6456: rang bzhin gyi gshis ngan pas slob dpon dang grogs mched la chag nyams khur ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:6457: brgyad po des dam tshig nyams pa'i rgyu byas nas
NK075(bu)003:6458: 'bras bu dka' thub sdom pa'i dam tshig nyams nas
NK075(bu)003:6459: ral pa dag gis gso ba la brtson na /
NK075(bu)003:6460: dus 'di nyid la nyams pa che chung gis phyi mar rnam smin myong ba la yang /
NK075(bu)003:6461: tshe 'dir nyams pa che na phyi mar sdug bsngal drag /
NK075(bu)003:6462: 'dir nyams pa chung na phyi mar sdug bsngal zhena pa yin gyis /
NK075(bu)003:6463: des na thun mong spyi'i dam tshig nyams pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:6464: sgos su gsang sngags rang gi dam tshig nyams pa'i skyon gyis bdag gzhan gnyis la gnod de /
NK075(bu)003:6465: ngan song du 'gro zhing mchog thun mong gi dngos grub mi myong ba'o //
NK075(bu)003:6466: 'o na dam tshig dang spyod pa la khyad par ci yod ce na /
NK075(bu)003:6467: dam tshig ni da nas bzung ste sangs ma rgyas
NK075(bu)003:6468: kyi bar du bsrung bya'i rnam grangs tshang dgos pa
NK075(bu)003:6469: yin la / spyod pa ni rang rang gi skabs
NK075(bu)003:6470: kyi spyod pa rnams ma gtogs pa gong 'og tu
NK075(bu)003:6472: yang na spyod pa ni lta sgom spyod gsum du bsres nas lam du khyer ba'i cha yin la /
NK075(bu)003:6473: dam tshig ni lta sgom la sogs spyi la 'jug ste /
NK075(bu)003:6474: rang rang gi don la mi 'da' bar bsrung ba'i phyir ro //
NK075(bu)003:6475: lnga pa dkyil 'khor la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:6479: yan lag lnga pa gtso 'khor du bkod pa'i thabs
NK075(bu)003:6480: dkyil 'khor la rgyud rgyas pa'i le'u dgu pa las
NK075(bu)003:6481: nang tshan bdun du gsungsa pa ni /
NK075(bu)003:6483: gzugs brnyan lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan dang //
NK075(bu)003:6485: byang chub sems dang tshogs mchog bstan //
NK075(bu)003:6487: de rnams kun gyi sdom tshig ni 'di lta ste /
NK075(bu)003:6488: dkyil 'khor gyi ngo bo dang dkyil 'khor gyi khyad par dang /
NK075(bu)003:6490: skabs gar dgos pa'i dus dang /
NK075(bu)003:6492: dkyil 'khor gyi nges tshig gam sgra don dang /
NK075(bu)003:6493: dkyil ched du gnyer ba'i yon tan dang /
NK075(bu)003:6494: ma gnyer ba'i skyon dang brgyad kyis nang du /
NK075(bu)003:6495: 'og dkyil 'khor gyi rgyas bshad 'byung ba'i gzhi ru bzhag pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:6496: gnyis pa bshad pa de la brgyad te /
NK075(bu)003:6500: dkyil 'khor rang rang gi gnas skabs kyi dkyil 'khor
NK075(bu)003:6501: bdun du snying po len pa ste dkyil yin la
NK075(bu)003:6502: / de'i 'khor du bkod pa gang dang gang du
NK075(bu)003:6503: rdzogs pa de dkyil 'khor gyi ngo bo yin no
NK075(bu)003:6504: / // de la dkyil 'khor gyi ngo bo dmigs ngos bzung /
NK075(bu)003:6505: dang po rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:6507: rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin no //
NK075(bu)003:6509: dang po rang bzhin don dam gyi dkyil ni /
NK075(bu)003:6510: rgyas pa'i don bzhi pa las /
NK075(bu)003:6511: rang bzhin dkyil 'khor yang dag ni //
NK075(bu)003:6512: chos dbyings b+ha ga dbyer med pas //
NK075(bu)003:6513: mnyam par sbyor zhing dag pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:6516: chos nyid rang bzhin spros bral te //
NK075(bu)003:6517: dngos po kun kyang de bzhin te //
NK075(bu)003:6518: rang bzhin nyid kyi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK075(bu)003:6520: gnyis pa kun rdzob kyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK075(bu)003:6522: phyi nang snod bcud bdag rnams la //
NK075(bu)003:6523: rang bzhin dkyil 'khor ye nas gnas //
NK075(bu)003:6526: dkyil 'khor bzhi bcu rtsa lnga nyid //
NK075(bu)003:6527: khams dang skyed mched la gnas pa //
NK075(bu)003:6528: lhun gyis grub par rgyal bas gsungs //
NK075(bu)003:6530: de'i dkyil ni rang rig pa'i ye shes /
NK075(bu)003:6531: 'khor ni ye shes bzhir shar ba'o //
NK075(bu)003:6532: gnyis pa rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin gyi dkyil 'khor la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:6536: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga lnga ste /
NK075(bu)003:6538: sku gsung thugs kyi rdzogs pa che //
NK075(bu)003:6539: yon tan phrin las kun tu rdzogs //
NK075(bu)003:6543: bzhugs pa'i dkyil dang 'khor gyi tshul //
NK075(bu)003:6544: de yang zhi khro rnam gnyis te //
NK075(bu)003:6545: nges par sku gsung thugs su 'gyur //
NK075(bu)003:6547: de'i dkyil ni 'das pa yin la /
NK075(bu)003:6548: 'khor ni 'jig rten pa'i tshul du snang ba'o //
NK075(bu)003:6549: gnyis pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK075(bu)003:6551: don dam pa'i gzugs brnyan kun rdzob lha'i dkyiil 'khor du byung ba la bzhed /
NK075(bu)003:6553: rtogs pa phra rags kyi lha yab yum mtshon pa la bzhed do //
NK075(bu)003:6554: gnyis ka mthun pa'i lung ni /
NK075(bu)003:6556: gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor yang dag ni //
NK075(bu)003:6557: chen po rags pa thabs su rtogs //
NK075(bu)003:6558: so so'i mtshan nyid shes rab rtogs //
NK075(bu)003:6559: gnyis med 'brel bas thabs chen yin //
NK075(bu)003:6561: de'i dkyil 'khor ni rang rig ye shes yin la /
NK075(bu)003:6563: gsum pa lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK075(bu)003:6564: las dang bya bas lhag pa ste /
NK075(bu)003:6566: sa gzhi mnyam dang tshad thig dang //
NK075(bu)003:6567: tshon dang bri ba'i rnam pa dang //
NK075(bu)003:6568: rab gnas sbyin sreg 'jug pa dang //
NK075(bu)003:6569: yon tan rnam bcu rgyas shes bya //
NK075(bu)003:6570: zhes gsungs pa bzhin yin la /
NK075(bu)003:6571: de'ang dgos ched kyi dbang gis skabs lngar dbye ste /
NK075(bu)003:6572: zhi khro'i lha tshogs bsgrub cing mchod pas mchod pa'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK075(bu)003:6573: dbang bskur ba dbang gi dang /
NK075(bu)003:6574: sku gsung thugs kyi rab gnas ni bsod nams rten gyi dang /
NK075(bu)003:6575: mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub bsgrub pa bsgrub pa'i dang /
NK075(bu)003:6576: zhi rgyas dbang drag gi phrin las bsgrub pa phrin las kyi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK075(bu)003:6577: de'i dkyil ni rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs pa rigs gtso bor gang bzhag pa de yin la /
NK075(bu)003:6578: 'khor ni rigs bzhi lha dang lha mo'i /
NK075(bu)003:6579: bzhi pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK075(bu)003:6580: bden gsum dbyer med lta sgom gyis nyams su len pa la bya ste /
NK075(bu)003:6582: ye shes phyogs bzhi dbus brtags te //
NK075(bu)003:6583: dkyil 'khor bsam yas lhun grub ni //
NK075(bu)003:6584: rdzogs chen rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK075(bu)003:6587: rgyas pa'i nyi shu pa las /
NK075(bu)003:6589: thams cad dbyings su bsdus nas ni //
NK075(bu)003:6590: nyid kyi thugs la thims byas te //
NK075(bu)003:6591: thams cad chos sku'i phyag rgya che //
NK075(bu)003:6593: dkyil ni rang rig pa'i ye shes yin la /
NK075(bu)003:6594: 'khor ni ci yang ma 'gags pa'i ye shes bzhir shar ba'o //
NK075(bu)003:6595: lnga pa lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK075(bu)003:6596: bsgom pa'i bya ba lhag pa ste /
NK075(bu)003:6597: tshogs lam sbyor lam bzhi rim gyis bsgom pa'i rang
NK075(bu)003:6598: rang gi mnyam bzhag chos nyid blo 'das de dkyil
NK075(bu)003:6599: yin la / rang rang gi skabs su tshogs drug gi gsal stong dang /
NK075(bu)003:6600: 'gyu stong ye shes sgyu ma dang /
NK075(bu)003:6601: lha dang lha mo'i sku mdog zhal phyag gi 'char snang rnams 'khor yin no //
NK075(bu)003:6602: yang bskyed rim gyi lha bsgom pa kho na la bzhed pa yang yod /
NK075(bu)003:6603: drug pa byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor la yang /
NK075(bu)003:6604: phyi byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor rtsa'i 'dus mdo dkyil yin la /
NK075(bu)003:6606: nang byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor 'dus mdo'i thig le dkyil yin la /
NK075(bu)003:6608: gsang ba byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor bde ba'i
NK075(bu)003:6609: ye shes lhan cig skyes pa de dkyil yin la
NK075(bu)003:6610: / dga' ba bcu drug dang ye shes lnga ni 'khor yin te /
NK075(bu)003:6612: zab phyir byang sems dkyil 'khor ni //
NK075(bu)003:6613: rten dang rten can tha snyad gnyis //
NK075(bu)003:6614: dbye na phyi nang mthar thug 'gyur //
NK075(bu)003:6616: bdun pa tshom bu tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK075(bu)003:6617: zhi khro gnyis ka'i tshom bu gcig gsum lnga pa'i dkyil ni rigs gcig dang /
NK075(bu)003:6620: 'khor ni rigs bzhi lha dang lha mo'o //
NK075(bu)003:6622: chogs ni 'byor pa rnam pa gsum //
NK075(bu)003:6623: tshom bu gcig gsum lnga pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:6627: dkyil 'khor bdun gyi dang po rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor la yang /
NK075(bu)003:6629: de nyid mthar phyin pa 'bras bu'i dkyil 'khor gnyis /
NK075(bu)003:6630: de la gdul bya lugs 'byung dang lugs zlog gi
NK075(bu)003:6631: snang ba'i khyad par gyis phye bas zhi ba dang
NK075(bu)003:6632: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gnyis su byung /
NK075(bu)003:6633: de gnyis la yang gdul bya rang rang gi mos pas phye ste /
NK075(bu)003:6638: la la phrin las la mos pa'i stobs kyis 'khor
NK075(bu)003:6639: gyi lha la khyad med kyang rigs lnga la gtsoo
NK075(bu)003:6640: bo gang byed des phye bas /
