NK075(bu)003:6641: zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor gnyis po re re la yang
NK075(bu)003:6642: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga lnga yod
NK075(bu)003:6643: do // gsum pa rnam grangs dang /
NK075(bu)003:6645: rtsa ba rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor de yang byed
NK075(bu)003:6646: las gnas skabs kyi sgo nas rnam grangs rnam par
NK075(bu)003:6651: gzhi'i dkyil 'khor dang sbyar nas rnam grangs dbye ba'am /
NK075(bu)003:6652: yang na 'bras bu sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin
NK075(bu)003:6653: las kyi gtso bos phye bas rnam grangs dang rjes
NK075(bu)003:6654: su mthun par sbyar nas dbye na /
NK075(bu)003:6655: mchod pa la sogs bzhi po sku gsung thugs yon
NK075(bu)003:6656: tan phrin las lnga po kun gyi rjes su 'jug
NK075(bu)003:6660: bsgrub pa la lnga ste nyi shu de zhi khro
NK075(bu)003:6661: gnyis kyis phye bas rnam grangs bcu tshan bzhi ste
NK075(bu)003:6662: bzhi bcu dang / rang bzhin gyi sgo nas dbye na /
NK075(bu)003:6663: gzhi la sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lhun grub tu gnas pa lnga /
NK075(bu)003:6664: de nyid mthar phyin pas zhi khro gnyis po re re la lnga lnga ste bco lnga /
NK075(bu)003:6665: de bzhin du mchod pa la lnga /
NK075(bu)003:6668: bsgrub pa la lnga ste kun bsdoms na suma cu rtsa lngar gyur pa yin no //
NK075(bu)003:6669: rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor gyi rnam grangs de yi
NK075(bu)003:6670: rjes su dkyil 'khor drug po'i rnam grangs kyang de
NK075(bu)003:6671: ltar du sbyar bar shes par bya' //
NK075(bu)003:6672: de yang rnam grangs bzhi bcu rtsa lnga po de dag /
NK075(bu)003:6673: gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor gyi gzugs brnyan ltar gsal
NK075(bu)003:6674: la sgrib g.yogs med pa'i ngang du snang ba yin
NK075(bu)003:6675: la / gnyis po'i don de dag /
NK075(bu)003:6676: lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor gyi mtshon byed kyi ngang du tshang la /
NK075(bu)003:6677: rnam grangs gnyis po'i don de nyid /
NK075(bu)003:6678: ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor gyis cig char du rtogs shing sgom pa'i ngang du rdzogs la /
NK075(bu)003:6680: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor gyis rim gyis nyams su len pa'i skabs su tshang la /
NK075(bu)003:6682: tshom bu tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor gyis bsgrub cing nyams su len pa yin la /
NK075(bu)003:6683: yang grangs gnyis po de dag /
NK075(bu)003:6684: byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor gyis thabs lam ltar nyams su len pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:6685: bzhi pa dgos ched dang dus thun mong du bstan pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:6690: bsgrub pa dang bzhi po'i dus su dkyil 'khor bsgoms
NK075(bu)003:6691: pas bdag gzhan gyi don bsgrub pa la ma bsgoms
NK075(bu)003:6692: na mi 'grub / bsgoms nas 'grub pa'i phyir /
NK075(bu)003:6693: gtan tshigs des na ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor spyan drang ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:6694: rten mi dang 'brel na dbang bskur ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:6695: lha dang 'brel na rab tu gnas pa'i dus dang /
NK075(bu)003:6696: mtshan bcas mtshan med kyi ting nge 'dzin bsgomsa pa la dkyil 'khor dgos pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:6697: bsnyen bsgrub rnam pa bzhi dang /
NK075(bu)003:6698: 'phrin las rnam bzhi'i sgo nas bdag gzhan gyi don rdzogs par byed pa'i dus su dgos pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:6700: mchog thun mong gi 'bras bu 'grub pa'i thabs la dkyil 'khor dgos pa de'i phyir na /
NK075(bu)003:6701: gong gi dkyil 'khor bdun po'i don rnams blos shin
NK075(bu)003:6702: tu nan tan gyi sgo nas nyams su blang bar
NK075(bu)003:6703: bya'o // lnga pa 'grub pa'i thabs dang /
NK075(bu)003:6705: 'dir lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi sa yi cho ga bya ba'i rim pa nas bzung ste /
NK075(bu)003:6707: sa gzhi mnyam dang tshad thig dang //
NK075(bu)003:6708: tshon dang bri ba'i rnam pa dang //
NK075(bu)003:6709: rab gnas sbyin sreg 'jug pa dang //
NK075(bu)003:6710: yon tan rnam bcu rgyas shes bya //
NK075(bu)003:6721: yon tan dang rnam pa bcu'i sgo nas nyams su blang bar bya'o //
NK075(bu)003:6722: de yang lhag pa gzugs brnyan de yi cho ga byed thabs ci lta ba dag na /
NK075(bu)003:6723: rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor la sogs pa dkyil bdun
NK075(bu)003:6724: po lhag ma dag la yang lhag pa gzugs brnyan
NK075(bu)003:6725: gang la bya thabs bcu po yoda pa de /
NK075(bu)003:6726: dkyil 'khor lhag ma kun la'ang bcu po don gyis yod de tshul ci ltar du dbye na /
NK075(bu)003:6728: shes rab ma dmigs pa'i byed las kyi cha nas phye bas /
NK075(bu)003:6729: des na dkyil 'khor lhag ma rnams kyi bya thabs de mngon du 'grub par 'gyur te /
NK075(bu)003:6731: rang bzhin gzhi'i dus su gong gi bya thabs bcu po'i don gnas pa yin la /
NK075(bu)003:6732: 'bras bu'i dus su don de mthar phyin pa yin la /
NK075(bu)003:6733: ting nge 'dzin gyis de cig char du bsgom la /
NK075(bu)003:6734: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyis de rim gyis bsgom la /
NK075(bu)003:6735: gzugs brnyan gyis de rtog tshogs ye shes su gnas pa'i ngos nas tshang la /
NK075(bu)003:6736: tshom bu tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor gyis don de nyid bsgrub cing nyams su len pa yin la /
NK075(bu)003:6737: byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor la bcu las /
NK075(bu)003:6738: dang po sa gzhi mnyam pa ni /
NK075(bu)003:6739: rig ma mtshan nyid dang ldan pa ste /
NK075(bu)003:6741: phyag rgya chen po nam mkha'i dbyings //
NK075(bu)003:6744: yum gyi mkha' sor bzhi ste /
NK075(bu)003:6746: sor bzhi'i tshad du rang bzhin gnas //
NK075(bu)003:6748: gsum pa thig ni bde ba'i ye shes mi 'gyur ba ste /
NK075(bu)003:6750: bde ba'i ye shes thugs dkyil 'khor //
NK075(bu)003:6753: yum gyi pad+ma'i kha dog dmar po //
NK075(bu)003:6755: gru gsum gru bzhi zlum po zla gam gyi tshul du yod de /
NK075(bu)003:6757: kha dog dbyibs dang ldan pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:6759: drug pa rnam pa dgod pa ni /
NK075(bu)003:6760: rdo rje dang sna rtse la dgod pa ste /
NK075(bu)003:6762: rdo rje mdzub mo'i rtse dag tu //
NK075(bu)003:6763: til 'bru nam mkha'i gzhal yas su //
NK075(bu)003:6764: ri rab tsam gyi phyag rgya dgod //
NK075(bu)003:6767: 'dod pa'i bstan bcos kyis bde ba rgyas par byed pa ste /
NK075(bu)003:6769: thabs kyi cho ga rab gnas ni //
NK075(bu)003:6778: gsang ba'i sbyin sreg lugs su 'bul //
NK075(bu)003:6783: 'jug pa pos kyang gsol ba gdab //
NK075(bu)003:6785: bcu pa yon tan ni sngon 'og min du mthar
NK075(bu)003:6786: lam pa zhugs pa dang skal ba mnyam pa yin
NK075(bu)003:6788: bde ba chen po'i dkyil 'khor ni //
NK075(bu)003:6789: stangs dpyal gnyis sam yang na lnga //
NK075(bu)003:6790: byas te dang ldan rab zhugs na //
NK075(bu)003:6795: dkyil 'khor bdun gyi skabs su gtso bo snying po gang dang gang ldan pa dkyil 'khor yin la /
NK075(bu)003:6796: de yi 'khor gang yin dang ldan pas na dkyil
NK075(bu)003:6797: 'khor zhes bya ba'i nges pa'i tshig gam sgra don
NK075(bu)003:6798: yin te / rgyas pa'i le'u don gsum pa'i lung
NK075(bu)003:6799: las gragsa pa ltar yin pas the tshom med de
NK075(bu)003:6800: yin te / / de yang rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK075(bu)003:6802: ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor dang gsum gyi nges tshig ni /
NK075(bu)003:6804: rang rig mtha' dbus med pa'i dkyil //
NK075(bu)003:6807: rang bzhin mthar phyin gyi nges tshig ni /
NK075(bu)003:6808: 'das pa rtag tu dkyil yin te //
NK075(bu)003:6813: tshom bu tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK075(bu)003:6816: rdo rje sems dpa' dkyil yin te //
NK075(bu)003:6817: rigs bzhi lha dang lha mos 'khor //
NK075(bu)003:6819: byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor gyi nges tshig ni /
NK075(bu)003:6821: snying po thams cad dus su dkyil //
NK075(bu)003:6822: gang yang yan lag 'khor du gsungs //
NK075(bu)003:6823: bco brgyad khams su snying po nyid //
NK075(bu)003:6824: de dag 'khor te bde ba'i khams //
NK075(bu)003:6825: byang sems bde ba'i ye shes te //
NK075(bu)003:6826: rten can ci bzhin rten de bzhin //
NK075(bu)003:6828: de ltar gtso 'khor du tha dad pa'i dus na
NK075(bu)003:6829: chos nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang du ma g.yos
NK075(bu)003:6830: pas du ma'i mtha' dang bral la /
NK075(bu)003:6831: ma g.yos bzhin du gtso 'khor gyi tshul du gsal
NK075(bu)003:6832: bar snang bas phyogs gcig gi mtha' dang bral te
NK075(bu)003:6833: dbyings phyogs gcig gi 'dzin pas bcings pa dang bral
NK075(bu)003:6834: ba'o // bdun pa yon tan dang /
NK075(bu)003:6836: de ltar dkyil 'khor gyi don nyams su blangs pas
NK075(bu)003:6837: ye shes 'phel sgrib pa 'grib gnas skabs dang mthar
NK075(bu)003:6839: las gang bsam mi 'grub pa'i skyon yod pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:6840: drug pa mchod pa la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:6844: yan lag drug pa mnyes par byed pa mchod pa'i sdom tshig ni 'di lta ste /
NK075(bu)003:6846: mchod pa'i ngo bo ngos bzungs ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:6847: mchod pa la rnam grangs du yod bstan pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:6848: skabs gar mkho ba'i dus dang /
NK075(bu)003:6850: 'bul ba'i yon tan la sogsa pa'i spyi don drug
NK075(bu)003:6851: po'i 'di'i nang du 'og rgyas bshad de ci lta
NK075(bu)003:6852: ba bzhin du shes par bya'o //
NK075(bu)003:6853: gnyis pa bshad pa de la drug ste /
NK075(bu)003:6857: mchod pa phul bas bdag gzhan gnyis kyi sgrib pa
NK075(bu)003:6858: dag tshogs gnyis rdzogsa lha tshogs mnyes dam tshig nyams
NK075(bu)003:6860: tshe 'di dang phyi mar mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub thob pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:6861: gzhan yang mchod pa phul ba'i yon tan bcom ldan
NK075(bu)003:6862: 'das kyis bka' mdo rgyud rnams las gsungs pa dang
NK075(bu)003:6863: / dam tshig nyams pa'i chad skyon mi 'byung bar
NK075(bu)003:6864: bya ba'i phyira mchod pa la brtson par 'gyur ro
NK075(bu)003:6867: mchod pa phul bya'i yul de la phul byed kyi
NK075(bu)003:6868: mkhan po des phul bar bya ba'i rgyu de phul
NK075(bu)003:6869: bar byed pa dang gsum 'dus pa'i dus na /
NK075(bu)003:6870: mchod yul gyi zhing de dgyes shing thugs tshim par
NK075(bu)003:6871: 'gyur ba ni mchod pa'i dngos po'am ngo bo nyid
NK075(bu)003:6872: yin no // gsum pa rnam grangs dang /
NK075(bu)003:6874: dper na 'jiga rten na 'bangs kyis rgyal po la
NK075(bu)003:6875: gus pa'i sgo nas zhabs thog gis mnyes par bya
NK075(bu)003:6876: ba'i spyod pa de dang cha mthun yin te /
NK075(bu)003:6877: sangs rgyas la mnyes bya mnyes byed med kyang /
NK075(bu)003:6878: gdul bya lam la mos pa'i gang zag de drang bar bya ba'i phyir /
NK075(bu)003:6879: zhi khro'i lha gang yin pa la gus pa phyag gi mchod pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:6880: phyag rgya gar tshogs kyi mchod pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:6884: tshig su ra to ste lha mo bcu drug gi mchod pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:6889: lha mo bzhi bsnol la sogs 'dod yon rnams dang /
NK075(bu)003:6890: nang mchod sman raka gtor gsum dang /
NK075(bu)003:6893: zhe sdang sgrol ba'i mchod pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:6894: 'dod chags sbyor ba'i mchod pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:6895: gti mug dam rdzas kyi mchod pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:6896: yang na mchod pa thams cad phyi nang gsang gsum du 'dus te /
NK075(bu)003:6897: phyi 'dod yon rdzas kyi mchod pa ni dngos su bshams pa /
NK075(bu)003:6898: nang dgongs pa ting nge 'dzin gyis mchod pa ni bsgom pa /
NK075(bu)003:6899: gsang ba dam rdzas rang gnas kyi mchod pa ste /
NK075(bu)003:6900: de rnams 'bul ba'i srog lha sgom dang ldan dgos pa yin te /
NK075(bu)003:6901: de la mchod pa'i dngos po ci ltar snang dus
NK075(bu)003:6902: ngo bo sems kyi chos nyid spros bral la mi
NK075(bu)003:6903: g.yo ba ni don dam pa'i bden pa'i bden pa
NK075(bu)003:6904: ma g.yos bzhin du spyod pa'i dngos po rnams la
NK075(bu)003:6905: 'dres par gsal ba ni kun rdzob bden pa de'i
NK075(bu)003:6906: dus su chu dang chu'i rlabs bzhin du gnyis su
NK075(bu)003:6907: med pa ni dbyer med bden pa /
NK075(bu)003:6908: de ltar bden pa gsum dbyer med kyi tshul du bsgom mo //
NK075(bu)003:6909: ting nge 'dzin gyi rtsi yis ma zin na mchod pa rang kha mar 'gyur bas /
NK075(bu)003:6910: des na ting nge 'dzin gyis zin pa gal che'o //
NK075(bu)003:6911: bzhi pa skabs gang du dgos pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:6913: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa gsum la spros pa'i
NK075(bu)003:6914: rnam grangs rnams gong du bshad pa de dag rang
NK075(bu)003:6915: bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor la sogs pa'i dkyil 'khor bdun
NK075(bu)003:6917: mchod pa 'bul dgos pa'i phyir dang /
NK075(bu)003:6918: gzhan yang dgos ched kyi rjes su zhugs pa'i sdig pa bshags pa'i dus dang /
NK075(bu)003:6920: lha mnyes par byed pa'i dus dang /
NK075(bu)003:6921: dam tshig nyams chag skong ba'i dus dang /
NK075(bu)003:6922: khyad par phrin las rnam bzhi la longs spyod pa'i dus dang /
NK075(bu)003:6923: bsgrub pa byed pa'i dus dang /
NK075(bu)003:6924: dbang bskur ba'i tshe na mchod pa dgos pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:6927: skabs gang du mkho ba'i dus kyi rjes su zhugs pa ni yon tan dag yin te /
NK075(bu)003:6928: de la spyi dang khyad par gyi dus kyi sgo nas dmigs ngos bzung na ni /
NK075(bu)003:6929: mchod pa phul bas sgrib pa dag /
NK075(bu)003:6932: dam tshig nyams chag bskangs nas mthar thug sangs rgyas thob pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:6933: bye brag tu phrin las kyis gnas skabs dang mthar thug gi 'bras bu gzung 'dzin zhi /
NK075(bu)003:6937: sgrub pa'i 'bras bu la gnas skabs thun mong dang /
NK075(bu)003:6938: mthar thug gi 'bras bu sangs rgyas /
NK075(bu)003:6939: dbang gi 'bras bu gnas skabs su mtho ris dang thar pa thob la /
NK075(bu)003:6940: mthar thug rigs thams cad kyi bdag por 'gyur ro //
NK075(bu)003:6941: de ltar mchod pas mnyes pas don gyi 'bras bu la reg pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:6942: de yang tshur bsdu na gong gi yon tan rnams
NK075(bu)003:6943: bdag dang gzhan don gyi yon tan gnyis su 'dus
NK075(bu)003:6947: yon tan de las bzlog tu 'gro ste /
NK075(bu)003:6948: dam tshig chag nyams mi skong ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:6949: ye shes kyi lha dang dam can srung ma rnams g.yel ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:6950: dam tshig nyams pa'i chad pa 'byung ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:6953: dbang gi dus su mchod pa ma phul na /
NK075(bu)003:6954: phrin las la sogs gang byed pa la mthu byin rlabsa dang bral bar 'gyur te med pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:6955: bdun pa dbang la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:6959: yan lag bdun ma thob pa thob para byed pa'i dbang gi sdom tshig ni 'di lta ste /
NK075(bu)003:6960: dbang bskur ba dang thob pa'i dgos ched dang /
NK075(bu)003:6962: dbang rang gi ngo bo dang /
NK075(bu)003:6967: dbang bskur ba'i snod kyi rim pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:6968: dbang thob pa'i yon tan dang /
NK075(bu)003:6969: ma thob pa'i skyon dang bcu'i sgo nas dkyil 'khor las rim dang /
NK075(bu)003:6970: dbang las rim gnyis dang sbyor na /
NK075(bu)003:6971: dbang de rdzogs pa yin no //
NK075(bu)003:6972: gnyis pa bshad pa de la bcu ste /
NK075(bu)003:6976: bdag don gzhan don gnyis don chos don du 'gyur ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:6977: bzhi las khyad par du bdag don du'ang /
NK075(bu)003:6978: lam la zhugs pa'i sngon du dbang thob dgos pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:6979: gzhan don du slob bu lam du 'jug nus par byed pa la dbang bskur dgos pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:6980: dbang thob pas tshogs bsgrub na thun mong dang mchog gi dngos grub 'grub pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:6982: rgyal bu rgyal sar bton pa ltar //
NK075(bu)003:6983: rim pa'ang dbang gi khyad par te //
NK075(bu)003:6984: sa lam rtsal gyis bgrod pa yis //
NK075(bu)003:6985: dbang rnams thob pa rab tu gces //
NK075(bu)003:6989: lung rtsa rgyud kyi le'u bcu dang /
NK075(bu)003:6990: bshad rgyud bla ma la sogs pa dang man ngag
NK075(bu)003:6991: las rim la sogs pa rnams kyi nang nas byung
NK075(bu)003:6992: ba'i mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu'ang lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu
NK075(bu)003:6996: de ma thag pa'i rkyen dang bzhi'i sgo nas phyi phan pa'i dbang bcu /
NK075(bu)003:6998: gsang ba zab mo'i dbang gsum gyi yan lag rgyas par bsnyad de bshad par bya gsungs pas /
NK075(bu)003:7000: rgyu gnyis rang bzhin mtshungs pa dang //
NK075(bu)003:7001: ngo bo bzhin du grangs 'jug pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:7004: lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu dang gnyis so //
NK075(bu)003:7005: dang po mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu ni /
NK075(bu)003:7006: rnam par shes pa tshogs brgyad ye shes lnga'i rang
NK075(bu)003:7007: bzhin du ye nas gnas pa ni dbu rgyan gyi
NK075(bu)003:7008: dbang gi mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu'o //
NK075(bu)003:7009: rtsa ro rkyang gnyis g.yas g.yon du 'phyang ba cod pan gyi dang /
NK075(bu)003:7010: rtsa dbu ma ste a wa d+hu ti'i nang du
NK075(bu)003:7011: thig le sum cu so gnyis yod pa phreng ba'i
NK075(bu)003:7012: dang / lus rtsa'i d+r+wa bas khyab pa go cha'i dang /
NK075(bu)003:7013: pho mo'i gsang ba'i dbang po rgyal mtshan gyi dang /
NK075(bu)003:7014: rtog tshogs bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis lha'i rang bzhin du gnas pa phyag rgya'i dang /
NK075(bu)003:7015: klad pa bde chen gyi 'khor lo na rtsa 'dab
NK075(bu)003:7016: sum cu rtsa gnyis gdug phub pa'i tshul du yod
NK075(bu)003:7018: rtsa gnas thig les gang bar gnas pa bum pa'i dang /
NK075(bu)003:7019: lce la bza' btung gi ro chos nyid du longs spyod nus pa bza' btung gi dang /
NK075(bu)003:7020: khams lnga'i bcud dam rdzas lnga rang la gnas pas
NK075(bu)003:7021: ni snying po lnga'i dbang gi mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu
NK075(bu)003:7022: yin no // de yang thal ba'i rgyud las /
NK075(bu)003:7023: khams bcud bde ba'i lam gnyis dang //
NK075(bu)003:7024: dbu ma bcud 'dud tshad ldan pa //
NK075(bu)003:7025: d+r+wa ba'i rtsa dang dbang po dang //
NK075(bu)003:7026: phung sogs ye shes bde 'khor lo //
NK075(bu)003:7027: h'u gi bde ba'i ye shes bcas //
NK075(bu)003:7028: tshogs brgyad rang bzhin ye shes lnga //
NK075(bu)003:7029: sngags rdzas dgongs pas gang bslang pa //
NK075(bu)003:7030: kun nas ldang bas skyob pa yis //
NK075(bu)003:7031: sdug bsngal las grol rigs su nges //
NK075(bu)003:7033: gnyis pa lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu ni /
NK075(bu)003:7034: dbang rdzas rab gnas dang ldan pa yin te /
NK075(bu)003:7036: dbu rgyan rin chen 'byung ldan gyi rab gnas bya'o //
NK075(bu)003:7038: cod pan la rdo rje sems dpa' dang /
NK075(bu)003:7039: snang ba mtha' yas kyi rab gnas bya /
NK075(bu)003:7040: phreng ba la'ang rin chen 'byung ldan gyis /
NK075(bu)003:7041: go cha la don yod grub pas /
NK075(bu)003:7043: phyag rgya la lha rang rang gis /
NK075(bu)003:7045: bum pa rigs lnga kar gyis /
NK075(bu)003:7046: bza' btung la rnam pa snang mdzad kyis /
NK075(bu)003:7047: snying po lnga la rang rang gi rigs kyis rab tu gnas pa can byas pa rnams ni /
NK075(bu)003:7048: phyi phan pa'ii dbang bcu'i lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu'o //
NK075(bu)003:7049: gnyis pa lhan cig byed pa'i rkyen la'ang /
NK075(bu)003:7050: rkyen bzhi snod kyis mtshan nyid gnyis /
NK075(bu)003:7051: zhes pa rkyen la'ang bzhi las /
NK075(bu)003:7052: phyi phan pa'i dbang bcu bskur du rung ba'i slob bu'i rgyu'i rkyen /
NK075(bu)003:7053: dbang bskur nus pa'i slob dpon bdag po'i rkyen /
NK075(bu)003:7054: dbang rdzas rab gnas dang ldan pa dmigs pa'i rkyen /
NK075(bu)003:7055: dbang snga mas go phyes nas phyi ma 'byung ba de ma thag pa'i rkyen no //
NK075(bu)003:7056: nus pa'i dbang lnga'i mtshungs rgyu ni /
NK075(bu)003:7057: slob bu'i rna ba'i 'dom rtsa gnyis na /
NK075(bu)003:7058: sgra mnyan pa'i reg shes kyi thig le gnas pa mnyan dbang gi mtshungs rgyu /
NK075(bu)003:7059: de bzhin du snying gi reg shes kyi thig le sgom dbang gi /
NK075(bu)003:7060: lag pa'i rtsa na skyod byed kyi thig le phrin las kyi /
NK075(bu)003:7061: lce rtsa na smra byed kyi thig le 'chad dbang gi /
NK075(bu)003:7062: yan lag lnga'i thig le lnga ni /
NK075(bu)003:7063: rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams kyi dbang gi mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu'o //
NK075(bu)003:7064: lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu ni /
NK075(bu)003:7065: dam rdzas rab gnas dang ldan pa ste /
NK075(bu)003:7066: bka' po ti glegs bam can rin 'byung rab gnas can mnyan dbang /
NK075(bu)003:7067: phreng ba yi dam gang yin gyi rab gnas can sgom dbang dang /
NK075(bu)003:7068: rgya gram don grub kyi rab gnas can phrin las /
NK075(bu)003:7069: dung dang phyag shing 'khor lo gsum snang mtha'i rab gnas can 'chad dbang /
NK075(bu)003:7070: rdo rje dril bu kun bzang yab yum gyi rab
NK075(bu)003:7071: gnas can ni rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams
NK075(bu)003:7072: kyi dbang gi lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu'o //
NK075(bu)003:7074: nus dbang lnga bskur du rung ba'i slob bu rgyu'i rkyen /
NK075(bu)003:7075: bskur nus pa'i slob dpon bdag po'i skyen /
NK075(bu)003:7076: dbang rdzas rab gnas dang ldan pa dmigs pa dmigs pa'i rkyen /
NK075(bu)003:7077: dbang snga mas go phyes nas phyi ma 'byung ba de ma thag pa'i rkyen no //
NK075(bu)003:7078: gsum pa zab pa'i dbang gsum gyi rgyu la gnyis las /
NK075(bu)003:7079: dang po mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu ni /
NK075(bu)003:7080: don dam bde stong gi ye shes rang chas su gnas pa gsang dbang gi mtshungs ldan /
NK075(bu)003:7081: kun rdzob bde stong gi ye shes rang chas su
NK075(bu)003:7082: gnas pa shes rab ye shes kyi dbang gi mtshungs
NK075(bu)003:7083: ldan / bden pa dbyer med rang chas su gnas
NK075(bu)003:7084: pa dbyer med bde chen gyi dbang gi mtshungs ldan
NK075(bu)003:7085: ldan / gyi rgyu'o // gnyis pa lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu ni /
NK075(bu)003:7086: phyag rgya ma lo nyi shu ma mtshan dang ldan pa gsang dbang gi /
NK075(bu)003:7087: bcu drug ma zla ba byang sems can shes rab ye shes kyi /
NK075(bu)003:7088: bcu gnyis ma nyi ma byang sems can dbyer med
NK075(bu)003:7089: bde ba chen po'i dbang gi lhan cig byed pa'i
NK075(bu)003:7090: rgyu yin no // gnyis pa rkyen bzhi ni /
NK075(bu)003:7091: zab dbang gsum bskur du rung ba'i slob ma rgyu'i rkyen /
NK075(bu)003:7092: bskur nus pa'i bla ma bdag po'i rkyen /
NK075(bu)003:7093: phyag rgya mo mtshan dang ldan pa dmigs pa'i /
NK075(bu)003:7094: dbang snga mas go phyes nas phyi ma 'byung ba ni de ma thag pa'i rkyen no //
NK075(bu)003:7097: rgyu rkyen drug gi sgo nas rang la gnas pa'i
NK075(bu)003:7098: dbang don de dngos su thob par bya ba la
NK075(bu)003:7099: grangs bco brgyad yod pa de /
NK075(bu)003:7100: dbang gi ngo bo de nyid yin ces lung nas rnam par bshad do //
NK075(bu)003:7103: dang po zhi ba'i dbang la phyi phan dbang nang nus dbang /
NK075(bu)003:7104: gsang ba zab mo'i dbang gsum dang rtsa ba rnama lnga las yan lag bco brgyad do //
NK075(bu)003:7107: zab mo'i dbang gsum dang bco brgyad do //
NK075(bu)003:7108: gnyis pa bsgyur ba khrag 'thung gi dbang la phan dbang /
NK075(bu)003:7112: dam rdzas te rtsa ba lnga la gyes pa'i yan lag sum cu rtsa drug ste /
NK075(bu)003:7113: de yang khrag 'thung rtsa rgyud las /
NK075(bu)003:7114: phyi dbang zhes par grags pa ni //
NK075(bu)003:7115: phan pa'i dbang bcu nus dbang lnga //
NK075(bu)003:7116: rgyan cha rol pa'i dbang brgyad dang //
NK075(bu)003:7117: bsgrub pa brgyad dang dam rdzas lnga //
NK075(bu)003:7118: ming gi dbang dang sum cu bdun //
NK075(bu)003:7119: ming dbang kun gyi mgo ru phyung //
NK075(bu)003:7121: ming dbang mi brtsi nas sum cu rtsa drug tu dabye'o //
NK075(bu)003:7122: yang na bla ma gong ma'i bzhed dgongs ltar na /
NK075(bu)003:7126: gsang dbang la gnyis dang sum cu rtsa drug ste /
NK075(bu)003:7127: rngam pa gleg phreng gi le'u bcu bdun las /
NK075(bu)003:7128: rnam grangs go rim mtshan nyid ni //
NK075(bu)003:7129: dang po phyi yi dbang bcu bskur //
NK075(bu)003:7130: de nas nang dbang bcu gcig bskur //
NK075(bu)003:7131: de nas bsgrub pa'i bcu gsum dang //
NK075(bu)003:7132: tha ma gsang ba'i rnam pa gnyis //
NK075(bu)003:7133: bcu phrag gsum dang drug dag gis //
NK075(bu)003:7134: dbang mchog dam pa bskur bar bya //
NK075(bu)003:7135: dang po bka' rtags phyag rgya'i dbang //
NK075(bu)003:7136: gnyis pa rtags kyi mtshan ma'i dbang //
NK075(bu)003:7137: gsum pa shes rab gzungs kyi dbang //
NK075(bu)003:7138: bzhi pa bkra shis bum pa'i dbang //
NK075(bu)003:7139: lnga pa bkra shis rdzas kyi dbang //
NK075(bu)003:7140: drug pa rin chen sna bdun dbang //
NK075(bu)003:7141: bdun pa gdan gyi dam pa'i dbang //
NK075(bu)003:7142: brgyad pa mdzes pa rgyan gyi dbang //
NK075(bu)003:7143: dgu pa gsang ba'i ming gi dbang //
NK075(bu)003:7144: bcu pa rgyal rtags 'khor lo ste //
NK075(bu)003:7145: phyi dbang bcu po rdzogs pa dang //
NK075(bu)003:7146: rdo rje gdan du gzhugs bya ba //
NK075(bu)003:7147: dang po gsang ba nyan cing slob pa'i dbang //
NK075(bu)003:7148: gnyis pa glegs bam zab mo gtad par bya //
NK075(bu)003:7149: gsum pa rnam bzhi las kyi rdzas kyang sbyin //
NK075(bu)003:7150: bzhi pa rgyal mtshan dam pa'i mchod gsum sbyin //
NK075(bu)003:7151: lnga pa slob dpon theg chen dgu yi rtags //
NK075(bu)003:7152: drug pa pad+ma nyi zla sems can gdan //
NK075(bu)003:7153: bdun pa rgyal po gsang ba rin chen bdun //
NK075(bu)003:7154: brgyad pa gzugs brnyan spyi bor bzhag /
NK075(bu)003:7155: dgu pa gzugs sku ye shes sbyin //
NK075(bu)003:7156: bcu pa bkra shis nang rdzas dang //
NK075(bu)003:7157: de sel lag tu rdo rje sbyin //
NK075(bu)003:7158: bcu dang bcu gcig nang sbyin nas //
NK075(bu)003:7159: sgrub pa'i dbang mchog sbyin par bya //
NK075(bu)003:7160: dang po sems kyi gtan tshigs sbyin //
NK075(bu)003:7161: gnyis pa snying rje dbang bskur sbyin //
NK075(bu)003:7162: gsum pa yi ge 'khor lo sbyin //
NK075(bu)003:7163: bzhi pa thong gshol 'bar ba sbyin //
NK075(bu)003:7164: b+han d+ha gang ba sbyin dang lnga //
NK075(bu)003:7165: drug pa tshon cha sna tshogs te //
NK075(bu)003:7166: bdun pa skyon med pad+ma ste //
NK075(bu)003:7167: brgyad pa sti ra dbyug pa sbyin //
NK075(bu)003:7168: dgu pa sbrul nag chun po sbyin //
NK075(bu)003:7169: bcu pa dri med lha mo sbyin //
NK075(bu)003:7170: gcig pa 'dod pa'i longs spyod sbyin //
NK075(bu)003:7171: gnyis pa sgrub rdzas thams cad sbyin //
NK075(bu)003:7172: gsum pa rdo rje gsang ming sbyin //
NK075(bu)003:7173: bcu dang gsum po rdzogs pa dang //
NK075(bu)003:7174: gsang ba dam pa sbyin pa yang //
NK075(bu)003:7175: dkar dmar 'dres pa'i byang chub sems //
NK075(bu)003:7176: bum pa mchog de lce la bzhag /
NK075(bu)003:7177: snying po don dam byang chub sems //
NK075(bu)003:7178: de yi blo la bzhag par bya //
NK075(bu)003:7182: de yang dang po dkyil 'khor rdo rje las kyi rim pa'i rjes su zhugsa pa ste /
NK075(bu)003:7183: sa gzhi mnyam dang tshang thig dang //
NK075(bu)003:7184: tshon dang bri ba'i rnam pa dang //
NK075(bu)003:7185: rab gnas sbyin sreg 'jug pa dang //
NK075(bu)003:7186: yon tan rnam bcu rgyas shes bya //
NK075(bu)003:7187: zhes gsungs pa'i don gzhung bzhin nyams su blangs la /
NK075(bu)003:7188: de nas dad brtson brtul zhugs kyi snod dang /
NK075(bu)003:7189: phan nus zab gsum gyi dbang rim pa ltar sbyar nas dbang bskur ba ste /
NK075(bu)003:7191: dad brtson brtul zhugs rab rtogs na //
NK075(bu)003:7192: phan pa'i dbang sbyin nus pa'i dbang //
NK075(bu)003:7193: rim pa bzhin du sbyin par bya //
NK075(bu)003:7194: snying rjes chud ma zos par bzungs //
NK075(bu)003:7196: de'i bskur thabs ni dbang rdo rje las rim gyi gzhung ltar /
NK075(bu)003:7197: rgyu rkyen ngo bo 'bras bu dang //
NK075(bu)003:7198: rim las skyon yon brgyad ces bya //
NK075(bu)003:7200: dbang rdzogs par bskur bar bya'o //
NK075(bu)003:7201: drug pa thob pa'i tshad dang /
NK075(bu)003:7203: dper na lcags bzang zhing rnon po la til mar
NK075(bu)003:7204: bskus nas ngar rim par blud na shin tu rno
NK075(bu)003:7205: ba bzhin du shes bya'i chos kyi nus mthu gzhan
NK075(bu)003:7206: la de ltar du mi smin la /
NK075(bu)003:7207: dbang ni rgyu rkyen snod bcud gnyis 'dzom na dbang
NK075(bu)003:7208: bskur ma thag tu nges par nus mthu dang ldan
NK075(bu)003:7209: pa ni thob pa'i tshad du bzhag pa yin te
NK075(bu)003:7211: rno la ngar btab nus pa bzhin //
NK075(bu)003:7212: nus pa skye ba thob pa'i tshad //
NK075(bu)003:7216: sngags kyi lam gyi rgyud du 'jug pa la dbang
NK075(bu)003:7217: dgos te de yang shes rab grol lam la rgyud
NK075(bu)003:7218: smin par byed pa la sngon du dbang 'gro ba
NK075(bu)003:7219: yin la / thabs lam la'ang dbang thob nas de nyid kyi don la rim par bslab dgos la /
NK075(bu)003:7220: gzhan yang thabs grol gnyis ka'i lam dang sa yi rim pas mtho dman gyi phye bas /
NK075(bu)003:7223: 'bras dus kyi dbang dang gsum ste /
NK075(bu)003:7224: de re re la yang slob ma las dang po ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:7225: sngags kyi drod rnyed pa dang phyir mi ldog pa'i
NK075(bu)003:7226: gang zag gsum gyi rig ma la'ang las kyi phyag
NK075(bu)003:7227: rgya mo dang / rig pa'i phyag rgya mo dang
NK075(bu)003:7228: ye shes kyi phyag rgya mo dang gsum las rim
NK075(bu)003:7229: par rol pas dbang gsum thob dgos te /
NK075(bu)003:7230: de yang gsang snying le'u dgu pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:7231: bcu pa las ston pa'i rgyu dus kyi dbang ni /
NK075(bu)003:7232: slob dpon drod thob pa des /
NK075(bu)003:7233: lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor la brten nas /
NK075(bu)003:7234: slob ma las dang pa de la /
NK075(bu)003:7235: rig ma las kyi phyag rgya mo mtshan nyid dang ldan pa la /
NK075(bu)003:7237: bde stong gi nges shes skye ba man chad kyi
NK075(bu)003:7238: gsang sngags bla med la 'jug nus pa'i chos sgo
NK075(bu)003:7240: le'u bco lnga pa'i nang du ston pa'i lam dus kyi dbang ni /
NK075(bu)003:7241: slob dpon sgom lam pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:7243: ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyiil 'khor la brten nas /
NK075(bu)003:7244: slob ma sbyor lam pa drod tshad rnyed pa'i gang zag de la /
NK075(bu)003:7245: rig pa'i phyag rgya mo ste /
NK075(bu)003:7246: ting nge 'dzin gyi phyag rgya mo la rol cing sbyor bas /
NK075(bu)003:7247: rjes shes mngon 'dzin gyi dri ma dag nas /
NK075(bu)003:7248: zag med mthong lam gyi dgongs pa mngon du gyur pa'i dbang thob pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:7249: le'u gnyis pa'i nang du ston pa'i 'bras dus kyi dbang ni /
NK075(bu)003:7251: dad pa can dang brtson 'grus can gnyis la gsum dang /
NK075(bu)003:7252: brtul zhugs can la'ang gsum ste /
NK075(bu)003:7253: de rnams gdul bya gang la yod pa de dag
NK075(bu)003:7254: phyi nang gsang ba'i dbang de yi snod du gyur
NK075(bu)003:7255: pa yin te / de yang dad pa can la phyi phan pa'i dbang bcu bskur la /
NK075(bu)003:7256: brtson 'grus can la nang nus pa'i dbang lnga bskur te /
NK075(bu)003:7258: bdag don du brtson 'grus nus na nyan dbang dang /
NK075(bu)003:7260: gzhan don du brtson 'grus nus na /
NK075(bu)003:7262: rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams kyi dbang dang gsum bskur te zhes spar khab las gsungs so //
NK075(bu)003:7263: brtul zhugs can la gsang ba zab dbang ste /
NK075(bu)003:7265: bdud rtsi lnga la sogs pa yab yum gyi byang
NK075(bu)003:7266: sems la spyod nus na spyod pa'i brtul zhugs lags
NK075(bu)003:7268: yum la sbyor ba'i dus su bde stong de nyid
NK075(bu)003:7269: rig pas nyams su myong nus na rig pa'i brtul
NK075(bu)003:7270: zhugs te / de la shes rab ye shes /
NK075(bu)003:7271: bde stong gi ye shes tha dad med par dbyer
NK075(bu)003:7272: med mnyam pa nyid du rtogs na mnyam pa'i brtul
NK075(bu)003:7273: zhugs te / de la bde ba chen po'i dbang bskur ba'o //
NK075(bu)003:7276: dbang bskur thob pa la tshe 'di dang phyi ma'i phana yon gyi rnam grangs ni /
NK075(bu)003:7278: gsungsa pa ci bzhin yin te /
NK075(bu)003:7279: dus 'di phyin chad rgyal ba'i sras //
NK075(bu)003:7280: ngan song thams cad med pa dang //
NK075(bu)003:7281: tshe ring bde ba phun sum tshogs //
NK075(bu)003:7282: mtho ris thar pa'i bdag por 'gyur //
NK075(bu)003:7285: gang yang phan pa'i dbang bskur bas //
NK075(bu)003:7286: dus 'di phyin chad rgyal ba'i sras //
NK075(bu)003:7287: phyir mi ldog phyir yon tan de //
NK075(bu)003:7288: lha mi yon tan yan chad nas //
NK075(bu)003:7289: rdo rje 'dzin pa skabs kyis thob //
NK075(bu)003:7293: yon tan de las bzlog pa ste dbang ma thob
NK075(bu)003:7294: par rang byan gyis brtag dpyad byas kyang rang gi
NK075(bu)003:7295: chos nyid mi rtogs pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:7296: gzhan la yang phan nus zab gsum gyi dbang ma thob par nyan pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:7300: bsgrub pa la sogs pa rdo rje slob dpon gyi las byas kyang 'bras bu med cing /
NK075(bu)003:7302: slob dpon mnyes par ma byas shing //
NK075(bu)003:7303: dbang rnams thob par ma byas par //
NK075(bu)003:7304: nyan pa la sogs brtsam pa rnams //
NK075(bu)003:7306: zhes gsungs pas dam tshig de nyams pa'i dbang gis
NK075(bu)003:7307: ngan song gsum du ltung zhing sdug bsngal gyi 'jigs
NK075(bu)003:7309: dper na so ma btang ba'i rdza ma'i nang du
NK075(bu)003:7310: chu blugs nas spyod tsam na zhig pa ltar 'gyur
NK075(bu)003:7311: ba ni / gsang ba'i snying po rtsa rgyud dang bshad rgyud kun la ltos dang der gsal lo //
NK075(bu)003:7313: slob dpon mnyes par ma byas shing //
NK075(bu)003:7314: dbang rnams thob par ma byas par //
NK075(bu)003:7317: brgyad pa bsgrub pa la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:7321: yan lag brgyad pa rnal 'byor pas lam don du
NK075(bu)003:7322: gnyer ba 'bras bu thob par bya ba yi thabs
NK075(bu)003:7324: de yang thun mong mchog gis phye bas bsgrub pa la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:7328: sogs kyis sgras de dag gi sgrub thabs mi 'dra
NK075(bu)003:7329: ba mang du yod pa rnams kyi sdom pa'i tshig
NK075(bu)003:7332: bsgrub pa rang gi ngo bo ngos bzung ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:7337: bsgrub pa'i yon tan dang rnam grangs bdun gyi sgo nas 'og rgyas bshad de shes par bya'o //
NK075(bu)003:7338: gnyis pa bshad pa de la bdun te /
NK075(bu)003:7342: thun mong gi bsgrub pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:7343: mchog gi bsgrub pa'i dngos grub kyi bye brag mi 'dra ba rnams 'thob par byed pa la /
NK075(bu)003:7344: bdag gzhan gyi don du mchog dang thun mong gi
NK075(bu)003:7345: dngos grub thob pa la sgrub pa dgos pa dang
NK075(bu)003:7346: / don gnyis lhun gyis grub nas sangs rgyas thob pa'i thabs dang /
NK075(bu)003:7347: chos don du 'gyur ba'i phyir sgrub pa dgos la /
NK075(bu)003:7348: de bas na don 'gyur bzhi yod pa'i phyir sgrub pa la brtson par bya'o //
NK075(bu)003:7351: rnal 'byor pa gang gis mchog thun mong gi 'bras
NK075(bu)003:7352: bu gang thob par 'dod pas don de bsgrub pa
NK075(bu)003:7353: dang ldan nas / lam gyi yan lag cha rkyen
NK075(bu)003:7354: bcu dang ldan pa'i rgyud don rnams gnyer bde ba
NK075(bu)003:7358: 'di la sa nang tshigs su bcad na gnyis las /
NK075(bu)003:7359: dang thun mong gi rnam grangs las /
NK075(bu)003:7360: mngon shes lnga bsgrub thabs dang /
NK075(bu)003:7363: rgyas pa'i re lnga pa nas byis pa gtsang ma la pra phabs thabs la sogs pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:7364: re bzhi pa nas tshe bsgrub thabs dang /
NK075(bu)003:7366: rgyas pa'i so brgyad pa las /
NK075(bu)003:7367: yi ge a la shes pa gtad nas lus mi snang bar bsgrub pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:7368: kun bzang yab yum gyi gsang bar zhi ba bzhi
NK075(bu)003:7369: bcu rtsa gnyis dkyil 'khor re re bsgom la sbyor
NK075(bu)003:7370: ba byas nas 'od du zhu nas kun tu bzang
NK075(bu)003:7371: mo la bstim pa la sogs pa'i sgo nas te
NK075(bu)003:7372: / mi gnas nam mkha'i mtha' klas pa //
NK075(bu)003:7373: goms par 'dod pa thob pa dang //
NK075(bu)003:7374: chu la sa bzhin 'gro ba dang //
NK075(bu)003:7375: rtsa ba rlung gis bteg nas kyang //
NK075(bu)003:7376: phyogs bcu kun tu phyin par byed //
NK075(bu)003:7378: gzhan yang rdo rje bkod pa kun 'dus kyi rgyud nas /
NK075(bu)003:7384: sol ba la ljon shing du bsgrub pa la sogs pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:7386: chang 'bebs rgyud gzhan du'ang mang du gsungs so //
NK075(bu)003:7387: gzhan yang rgyas pa'i le'u bdun cu pa nas ro
NK075(bu)003:7388: lang bsgrub pa'i sgo nas lha srin gyis bka' nyan
NK075(bu)003:7389: / ma h+aa de ba la sogs dbang du 'dus /
NK075(bu)003:7390: ro gser du 'gyur nas longs spyod kyi rten du 'gyur /
NK075(bu)003:7391: ro'i lce bcad nas gar bsam du phyin nas rkang mgyogs dang /
NK075(bu)003:7396: bdud rtsi 'khyil pa dang bzhi'i sgo nas ro lang bsgrubs pas /
NK075(bu)003:7397: ro lang pa'i lce bcad pas mtshon cha dang /
NK075(bu)003:7400: rkang mgyogs la sogs kyi rdzu 'phrul bsgrub thabs rnams dang /
NK075(bu)003:7401: pags pa la lhwam byas na chur mi bying ba la sogs pa rdzu 'phrul thob thabs rnams so //
NK075(bu)003:7403: rgyas pa'i le'u nga lnga pa nas drug cu rtsa
NK075(bu)003:7404: gcig gi bar du zhi rgyas dbang drag lhun grub
NK075(bu)003:7405: dang lnga / me'i sgo nas las bzhi bsgrub thabs dang /
NK075(bu)003:7406: le'u nyi shu pa las mchod rten gyi sgo nas las bzhi bsgrub thabs dang /
NK075(bu)003:7408: zhi ba la mi mthun kun sel /
NK075(bu)003:7410: dbang la gsang ba gnad kyi lcags kyu /
NK075(bu)003:7411: drag po la dgra bgegs bdud 'joms /
NK075(bu)003:7412: gzhan yang rgyas pa'i nang tshan la /
NK075(bu)003:7413: sri bu dang lo thog gso thabs rgyud gzhan du gsal la /
NK075(bu)003:7414: klu'i gegs sel mdze gso thabs le'u zhe drug pa las ston la /
NK075(bu)003:7415: gzhan yang dbang gi nang mtshan la /
NK075(bu)003:7416: rgyas pa'i le'u zhe gnyis pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:7418: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i gzungs ma rigs lnga'i yum dgug pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:7419: sems ma dgug pa yang ston la /
NK075(bu)003:7420: 'jig rten pa'i gzungs ma dgug pa ni /
NK075(bu)003:7421: rgyal po sa 'dzin gyi chung ma dang /
NK075(bu)003:7422: blon po sa 'dzin gyi chung ma dang /
NK075(bu)003:7423: lha chen po gzhan gyi chung ma bkug lugs le'u zhe lnga pa las ston la /
NK075(bu)003:7427: rigs ngan ma'i bu mo 'gugs pa yang ston no //
NK075(bu)003:7428: yul khams dbang du bya ba'i thabs le'u so brgyad pa las ston la /
NK075(bu)003:7429: gzhan yang ma h+aa de ba dbang du byas nas bsgrubs pas gang bsam bsgrub bcol ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:7430: rgyal po chen po sde bzhi bsgrubs nas dbang du
NK075(bu)003:7431: byas pas las gang bsam bsgrub bcol ba'i thabs le'u
NK075(bu)003:7432: re gsum pa las ston la /
NK075(bu)003:7433: drag po la nang tshan du /
NK075(bu)003:7434: dgra bgegs gling khams gzhan du 'phang ba'i thabs le'u so brgyad pa las ston la /
NK075(bu)003:7438: dgra bgegs dang nyi zla bsad pa la sogs pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:7439: gzhan gyi yul khams 'pham par byed pa la sogs pa rnams so //
NK075(bu)003:7440: sku de bzhin gshegs rigs kyis rgyal po'i lus la 'jug nas rang rgyal po red thabs dang /
NK075(bu)003:7441: gsung pad+ma rigs kyis zhang blon dbang chen gyi lus la 'jug nas dbang du bya thabs dang /
NK075(bu)003:7442: thugs rdo rje rigs kyis lcags spyang ki lus la 'jug pas rkang mgyogs bsgrub thabs dang /
NK075(bu)003:7443: yon tan rat+na rigs kyis blon po nor mang gi
NK075(bu)003:7444: lus la 'jug pas rang blon po nor mang red
NK075(bu)003:7445: thabs dang / phrin las kyis lha min gyi dmag
NK075(bu)003:7446: mi'i lus la 'jug nas dmag mang bsgrub thabs rnams
NK075(bu)003:7447: thabs dang / so // yang na sku rdzu 'phrul gyi bsgrub pa /
NK075(bu)003:7452: de ltar sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las kyi
NK075(bu)003:7453: sgo nas thun monga dag gi sgrub thabsa mi mthun
NK075(bu)003:7454: par grags pa de rnams ni thun mong gi bsgrub
NK075(bu)003:7455: pa'i rnam grangs yin pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:7456: gnyis pa zaga med kyi 'bras bu thob thabs mchog gi bsgrub pa la /
NK075(bu)003:7467: phrin las phur pa la sogs pa'i bsgrub thabs ni /
NK075(bu)003:7468: rgyud gzhung spyi'i chings yin la /
NK075(bu)003:7469: khyad par du sgyu 'phrul rang gzhung la zhi khro
NK075(bu)003:7470: gnyis kyi sgo nas chom bu gcig gsum lnga pa
NK075(bu)003:7471: / dkyil 'khor rgyas 'bring bsdus gsum gyi thog nas bsgrub thabs rnams so //
NK075(bu)003:7474: gong gi rnam grangs kyi bsgrub thabs skabs su bshad
NK075(bu)003:7475: pa'i thun mong dang mchog gi bsgrub pa'i thabas su
NK075(bu)003:7476: gragsa pa kun tshul ci ltar du bsgrub na /
NK075(bu)003:7480: yo byad de phun sum tshogs pa bzhi dang ldan nas gzhi bzung ba la'ang /
NK075(bu)003:7481: dang po gnas brtsal ba la sa brtags shing byin
NK075(bu)003:7482: gyis brlabs pa yan chad kyi cho ga rgyas par
NK075(bu)003:7483: byed la / gnas der sgrub khang brtsigs pa la byug bsrung bya /
NK075(bu)003:7484: chu gtor la sogs pa tshogs kyi dpung bskyed la sgrib sbyang bya /
NK075(bu)003:7487: bsgrub pa dang bsgrub pa chen po'i gzhung bsrangs la /
NK075(bu)003:7490: mtshan ma'i bsnyen pa so sora phye ba ste /
NK075(bu)003:7491: de rnams rgyud rgyas pa las gsungs pa bzhin du bsgrub dgos te /
NK075(bu)003:7492: de yang grangs bsnyen ni rgyud rang rang gi nang du bshad pa'i sngags kyi grangs them pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:7493: dus bsnyen ni zla drug bcu gnyis bcu bzhi bcu bcu drug go //
NK075(bu)003:7494: phyag rgya spros pa mthar phyin pa'i dus so //
NK075(bu)003:7496: rtags ma byung gi bar du'o //
NK075(bu)003:7499: rnal 'byor pa gang zhig gis lta ba bden gsum
NK075(bu)003:7500: dbyer med mngon sum du rtogs nas ting nge 'dzin
NK075(bu)003:7502: sngags kyi yan lag dang phyag rgya bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis sam /
NK075(bu)003:7503: lnga bcu rtsa brgyad la sogs pa lus dkyil du
NK075(bu)003:7504: bkod nas bsgom pa la brtan pa thob pa dang
NK075(bu)003:7505: / spros pa la sogs spyod pa'i bye brag rnams
NK075(bu)003:7506: mi lcog pa meda par gang yoda pa de dag
NK075(bu)003:7507: / dang / de ltar bsgrub pa'i cha rkyen bcu
NK075(bu)003:7508: po tshang bar byas tshe la dbang bsgyur ba'i rig
NK075(bu)003:7509: 'dzin ma thob pa'i sngon du tshogs bsgrub pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:7510: 'o na thun mong gi bsgrub pa 'dir ma smos sam zhe na ma yin te /
NK075(bu)003:7511: thun mong bsgrub pa'i dus kyang phyag rgya spros pa mthar phyin dgos te /
NK075(bu)003:7513: gso dang gsad dang pham dang rgyal //
NK075(bu)003:7518: ma bsgrubs na lha yal bas sgrib pa mi 'byong /
NK075(bu)003:7520: de yang thun mong dang mchog gi sku gsung thugs
NK075(bu)003:7521: yon tan phrin las lnga lnga ste bcu po mi
NK075(bu)003:7522: thob pa'o // bye brag tu bsgrub thabs mi 'dra
NK075(bu)003:7523: ba rnams rang rang ma bsgrub na mi 'grub pas
NK075(bu)003:7524: na rgyas pa de'i don khong du chud nas bsgrub
NK075(bu)003:7528: bsgrubs na skyon de las zlog pa yin te /
NK075(bu)003:7529: tshe 'di dang phyi mar thun mong gi 'bras bu sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga dang /
NK075(bu)003:7530: mchog gi 'bras bu sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin
NK075(bu)003:7531: las lnga thob pas bdag gzhan gyi don gnyis rdzogs
NK075(bu)003:7532: pa yin no // dgu pa sngags dang phyag rgya la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:7536: yan lag dgu pa sngags dang bcu pa phyag rgya'i sdom tshig ni 'di lta ste /
NK075(bu)003:7537: sngags dang phyag rgya'i dgos ched dang /
NK075(bu)003:7538: ngo bo ngos bzung ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:7539: rnam grangs la du yod pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:7540: bzlas pa dang bsgom pa'i thabs dang /
NK075(bu)003:7541: sngags dang phyag rgya'i nges tshig dang /
NK075(bu)003:7542: skabs gang du dgos pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:7543: sngags gsum bzla zhing phyag rgya bsgom pa'i yon tan dang /
NK075(bu)003:7544: bzlas bsgom ma byas pa'i skyon dang /
NK075(bu)003:7545: de dag rnal 'byor pa gang gi spyod yul yin
NK075(bu)003:7546: pa dang dgu'i sgo nas sngags dang phyag rgya'i don
NK075(bu)003:7548: gnyis pa bshad pa de la dgu ste /
NK075(bu)003:7552: gnas skabs su sgrib pa sbyang zhing ye shes kyi
NK075(bu)003:7553: lha nye bar bsnyen pa la sngags dgos pa dang
NK075(bu)003:7554: / mthar thug thob par bya ba'i 'bras bu rigs lnga'am /
NK075(bu)003:7555: sku lnga po rdzogs par bya ba'i phyir phyag rgya dgos pa de bas na /
NK075(bu)003:7556: bdag gzhan gnyis ka'i don grub pa'i ched du sngags
NK075(bu)003:7557: phyag rgya shin tu gces pas nyams su blang bar
NK075(bu)003:7558: bya'o // gnyis pa ngo bo dang /
NK075(bu)003:7560: lus kyi yi ge k+aa li dang /
NK075(bu)003:7561: yan lag gi yi ge +aa li gnyis lhan cig tu 'dus pa las ming /
NK075(bu)003:7562: ming de las grub pa bzhis brgyan pa'i nus mthu
NK075(bu)003:7563: chen po can du red pa gang yin pa de
NK075(bu)003:7564: ni sngags kyi ngo bo yin pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:7565: de yang chos rje'i bzhed la /
NK075(bu)003:7566: rang bzhin chos nyid kyi grub pa don las mi 'da' ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:7567: chos can rang gi mtshan nyid kyi grub pa ni
NK075(bu)003:7568: mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub thams cad snang
NK075(bu)003:7569: ba dang / byin rlabs lha'i grub pa ni sngags kyi nus pa mthu can du red pa /
NK075(bu)003:7570: mthus grub pa ni sngags kyi nus pa mthu can
NK075(bu)003:7571: du lta ba'i thun mong dang mchog gi dngos grub
NK075(bu)003:7573: dgongs 'dus kyi gsung mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo bkod pa'i le'u so bzhi pa'i skabs dang /
NK075(bu)003:7574: gsang snying le'u bzhi pa'i skabs la brtags na /
NK075(bu)003:7575: spyir shes bya 'khor 'das kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad /
NK075(bu)003:7578: des mtshon nas sngags tshig shad gcig la'ang /
NK075(bu)003:7579: grub pa bzhis brgyan pa yin te /
NK075(bu)003:7580: zhi ba'i snying po la yin na h'u gis ye shes lnga /
NK075(bu)003:7581: badz+ra rdo rje ste snang stong dbyer med skye 'jig dang bral ba /
NK075(bu)003:7582: d+h+rika 'dzin pa ste de'i don la mi 'da' ba
NK075(bu)003:7583: yin pas rang bzhin chos nyid 'grub pas brgyad la
NK075(bu)003:7584: / badz+ra d+h+ri ka ni dngos su rdo rje 'dzin
NK075(bu)003:7585: pa mtshon pas chos can gyi grub pas brgyan la
NK075(bu)003:7586: / / h'u badz+ra d+h+rika brjod pa'i byin rlabs des
NK075(bu)003:7587: lha'i sku wal gyis gsal bas byin rlabs lha'i grub
NK075(bu)003:7588: / / pas brgyan la / h'u badz+ra d+h+r+aika de
NK075(bu)003:7589: bzlas pas bdag gzhan thams cad la gnas skabs thun
NK075(bu)003:7590: mong la bar chad zhi la /
NK075(bu)003:7591: mthar thug mchog gi dngos grub sangs rgyas thob pa'i nus mthu yod pas mthu'i grub pas brgyan pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:7594: thugs dam tshig gi phyag rgya /
NK075(bu)003:7595: 'phro 'du 'phrin las kyi phyag rgya dang bzhi rdzogs
NK075(bu)003:7596: pa de nyid la mi 'da' ba'i don de gang
NK075(bu)003:7597: la snang ba de ni phyag rgya'i ngo bo yin
NK075(bu)003:7598: no // gsum pa rnam grangs la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:7600: dang po sngags kyi rnam grangs dang /
NK075(bu)003:7603: rigs yab kyis 'dzin pas yab sngags yin la /
NK075(bu)003:7604: gsang sngags ni theg 'og la gsang ba'i bde stong yum gyis 'dzin pas yum sngags yin la /
NK075(bu)003:7606: yab yum gnyis sbrel ba'i sngags yin pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:7607: de ni chos rje rin po che'i bzhed pa yin la /
NK075(bu)003:7608: yang na gsang ba grub pa'i rgyud las /
NK075(bu)003:7609: sngags rnams kun gyi dbye ba ni //
NK075(bu)003:7610: rig sngags thabs kyi ngo bo ste //
NK075(bu)003:7611: gzungs sngags shes rab rang bzhin te //
NK075(bu)003:7612: gsang sngags gnyis med ye shes yin //
NK075(bu)003:7614: dbang yon tan rim pa las /
NK075(bu)003:7615: stong pa dang ni snying rje nyid //
NK075(bu)003:7616: gnyis su med dang gnyis tshul gyis //
NK075(bu)003:7617: gsang sngags zhes ni de la bshad //
NK075(bu)003:7620: yum gyis bde ba gzungs bas gzungs sngags /
NK075(bu)003:7621: yab yum gnyis med kyi dgongs pa zab pas gsang sngags zhes bshad do //
NK075(bu)003:7622: yang rgyal po dzah'i dgongs 'dus 'grel par /
NK075(bu)003:7623: gsang sngags zhes bya ba ni /
NK075(bu)003:7624: lha mo rnams shes rab kyi rang bzhin te zab pas rtogs par daka'o //
NK075(bu)003:7625: rigs sngags zhes bya ba ni /
NK075(bu)003:7626: rig pa'i rgyal po lha pho'i rang bzhin thabs des rig pa'i phyir ro //
NK075(bu)003:7627: gzungs sngags zhes bya ba ni /
NK075(bu)003:7628: thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med pa'i kha sbyor gzungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK075(bu)003:7630: rgyu ma nor rtsa ba'i sngags dang /
NK075(bu)003:7631: bskyed pa rkyen gyi sngags dang /
NK075(bu)003:7632: bskul ba las kyi sngags te /
NK075(bu)003:7633: de la zhi ba ltar na /
NK075(bu)003:7635: badz+ra d+h+r+aika ni bskyed pa rkyen gyi sngags /
NK075(bu)003:7636: rtsa sngags dang bskyed sngags dril ba ni bzlas pa las kyi sngags su shes so //
NK075(bu)003:7639: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka sku bskyed sngags /
NK075(bu)003:7640: ma h+aa tsan+da sarba dush+tana ta ka ha na da
NK075(bu)003:7641: ha pa tsa h'u h'u h'u phata ni bzlas pa
NK075(bu)003:7643: zhes spar khab las bshad do //
NK075(bu)003:7644: gzhal yas khang bskyed sngags kyang bskyed pa rkyen gyi sngags yin no //
NK075(bu)003:7646: che ba'i yon tan gyi sgo nas bstod pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:7648: thugs dam gnad nas bskul ba'i sngags so //
NK075(bu)003:7652: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor snyan gsan dbab pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:7657: rigs pa'i me tog dor ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:7658: dngos grub bskul ba'i sngags rnams so //
NK075(bu)003:7668: las thams cad pa'i sngags mgo can /
NK075(bu)003:7672: 'gro lding la sogs pa rnams ni sngags kyi rnam grangs so //
NK075(bu)003:7673: gnyis pa phyag rgya'i rnam grangs la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:7679: thugs dam tshig gi phyag rgya /
NK075(bu)003:7680: 'phro 'du 'phrin las kyi phyag rgya dang bzhi yod pa las /
NK075(bu)003:7681: gnyis pa bshad pa de la bzhi ste /
NK075(bu)003:7683: dang po phyag rgya chen po'i rnam grangs dang /
NK075(bu)003:7685: sku phyag rgya chen po la'ang bzhi ste /
NK075(bu)003:7686: rang bzhin gyi phyag rgya chen po ni phung khams
NK075(bu)003:7687: skye mched thams cad rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor du gnas
NK075(bu)003:7688: pa yin te / rgyas pa'i le'u don drug pa las /
NK075(bu)003:7689: rang bzhin phyag rgya chen po ni //
NK075(bu)003:7690: phyi nang snod bcud thams cad kun //
NK075(bu)003:7691: thabs dang shes rab ngang du gnas //
NK075(bu)003:7692: rigs lnga bde gshegs yab yum dang //
NK075(bu)003:7693: ma bcos ye nas de ltar gnas //
NK075(bu)003:7696: rang bzhin gzugs kyi sku ni 'og min bzhugs pa nyid dang /
NK075(bu)003:7698: yon tan rdzogs pa'i gzhir gyur pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:7700: ting nge 'dzin gyi phyag rgya chen po ni /
NK075(bu)003:7701: rang gnas de nyid lta bas rtogs nas ting nge
NK075(bu)003:7702: 'dzin gyi lha'i sku phyag rgya chen po dbu'i gtsug
NK075(bu)003:7703: tor nas 'og gdan khri'i bar gsal bar bsgom pa
NK075(bu)003:7705: lhag pa'i phyag rgya chen po 'di //
NK075(bu)003:7706: nang gi rtags ni phyi ru ste //
NK075(bu)003:7707: mdor bsdus phyag rgya drug pa dang //
NK075(bu)003:7708: gzhan yang phyag rgya sna tshogs te //
NK075(bu)003:7710: lha bsgom pa de nyid dngos su gzugs brnyan gyis
NK075(bu)003:7711: mtshon pa ni mtshan pa'i phyag rgya chen po ste
NK075(bu)003:7712: / ras dang shog gu sa thang dang gyang la ris su bri ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:7713: rwa'am rus pa shing dang rdo la 'bur du btod pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:7714: gser dngul zang sogs la lugs su blugs pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:7715: 'jim pa la 'der so byas pa rnams so //
NK075(bu)003:7716: ting nge 'dzin mthar phyin pa'i rtags la dang mtshan ma'i phyag rgya chen po ste /
NK075(bu)003:7717: sku gdung dang ring bsrel la sogs pa rnams so //
NK075(bu)003:7718: gnyis pa dam tshig gi phyag rgya dang /
NK075(bu)003:7720: bde ba 'dzin pa la mi 'da' bas yum dam
NK075(bu)003:7721: tshig gi phyag rgya dang dgongs pa chos nyid la
NK075(bu)003:7722: mi 'da' ba'i rtags su rigs rang rang gi phyag
NK075(bu)003:7723: mtshan 'dzin pa dam tshig gi phyag rgya dang /
NK075(bu)003:7724: gung mo la sogs pa'i rtse mo la rdo rje
NK075(bu)003:7725: la sogs pa rang rang gi phyag mtshan bsam pa
NK075(bu)003:7726: ni bsdam pa dam tshig gi phyag rgya dang /
NK075(bu)003:7727: 'bru bzhi sbas nas gung mo la sogs rim pa
NK075(bu)003:7728: ltar gyen du bsgreng ba thugs kar bkan thabs su
NK075(bu)003:7729: bca' ba ni bca' ba dam tshig gi phyag rgya
NK075(bu)003:7730: dang bzhi'o // gsum pa las kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK075(bu)003:7732: yum la 'khyud par bsam pa ni bsam pa las kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK075(bu)003:7733: yum la 'khril ba'i tshul gyis barla g.yon pa chos
NK075(bu)003:7734: kyi rigs la brten pa'i phyag rgya dngos su bca'
NK075(bu)003:7735: ba ni bca' ba las kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK075(bu)003:7736: 'o na de gnyis las rgya ci ltar zhe na /
NK075(bu)003:7738: des thabs dang shes rab 'khril bar sbyor bar byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK075(bu)003:7741: phyed phyung tshul gyis gar bskyod pa //
NK075(bu)003:7742: ltung ba med phyir brten par bshad //
NK075(bu)003:7744: yab yum 'khril ba'i las byas pas //
NK075(bu)003:7745: byang sems kyi 'phro 'dus 'byung bar bskyed nas bde stong bskyed do //
NK075(bu)003:7746: rang bzhin ma bcos pa'i ngo bo phrin las thams
NK075(bu)003:7747: cad lhun grub tu rdzogs pa ni rang bzhin las
NK075(bu)003:7748: kyi phyag rgya yin pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:7749: chos rjes rang bzhin las kyi phyag rgya ni /
NK075(bu)003:7750: 'og min na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi phrin las mdzad pa la gsungs te /
NK075(bu)003:7751: de yang rgyas pa'i le'u so drug pa las /
NK075(bu)003:7752: bya ba med pa'i tshul gyis su //
NK075(bu)003:7753: las rnams ma lus rdzogs par byed //
NK075(bu)003:7755: mdzad pa bcu gnyis la sogs pa'i sgo nas sems
NK075(bu)003:7756: can gyi don byed pa ni ting nge 'dzin 'phro
NK075(bu)003:7757: 'du las kyi phyag rgya yin pa dang bzhi'o //
NK075(bu)003:7758: bzhi pa chos kyi phyag rgya'i rnam grangs so //
NK075(bu)003:7760: bde stong gi ye shes myong ba ni bde ba chos kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK075(bu)003:7761: dbyer med ma bcos pa'i don dam nyams myong ba ni rang bzhin chos kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK075(bu)003:7762: sngags brjod pa ni bzlas pa chos kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK075(bu)003:7763: phyag rgya'i rtse mo dang thugs kar yig 'bru bsgom
NK075(bu)003:7764: pa ni bsam pa chos kyi phyag rgya dang bzhi'o
NK075(bu)003:7765: // phyag rgya bzhi po de dag re la bzhi bzhir byung ba ni thabs lam dang grol lam /
NK075(bu)003:7766: grol lam la'ang bskyed rdzogs rnams kyis phye bas grangs mang po 'byung ba yin te /
NK075(bu)003:7767: de yang sku phyag rgya chen po la thabs grol mthun la /
NK075(bu)003:7768: thugs dam tshig la yum ni thabs lam yin la /
NK075(bu)003:7769: gsum po ni grol lam mo //
NK075(bu)003:7771: bsam bca' gnyis thabs lam gtso che la /
NK075(bu)003:7772: rang bzhin ni grol lam rdzogs rim yin la /
NK075(bu)003:7775: bde ba ni thabs lam yin la /
NK075(bu)003:7777: bzlas bsam gnyis ni bskyed rim mo //
NK075(bu)003:7782: sngags bzlas pa'i sgra skyon dang /
NK075(bu)003:7783: bar chad skyon bcu spang ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:7784: sngags la bsam dpyod kyis bar du gcod pa'i skyon bcu spang ba'o //
NK075(bu)003:7786: dang po sgra skyon lnga ni /
NK075(bu)003:7790: de dag spang ba shin tu gal che ste /
NK075(bu)003:7791: de yang sgra che na 'byung po dang /
NK075(bu)003:7792: snod med kyis thos nas bar chad 'byung /
NK075(bu)003:7798: sgra med na tshig nyams pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:7800: sgra che ba ma yin chung bar min //
NK075(bu)003:7801: mgyogs par ma yin bul bar min //
NK075(bu)003:7802: drag pa ma yin zhan ma yin //
NK075(bu)003:7803: yig 'bru'i yan lag nyams ma yin //
NK075(bu)003:7804: yeng ba nga rgyal dang ldan min //
NK075(bu)003:7805: rgyu ba'i sems dpa' spang bar bya //
NK075(bu)003:7808: sgra med bar chad mthu med 'gyur //
NK075(bu)003:7810: de la sngags kyi nus pa med //
NK075(bu)003:7811: bul na bzlas pa'i grangs med pas //
NK075(bu)003:7814: gnyis pa bar chad kyi skyon lnga ni /
NK075(bu)003:7818: gnyid dang bzhi pos bar chod na byin brlabs yal /
NK075(bu)003:7819: sems yengs na ting nge 'dzin gyi srog med pas don gyi nus mthu med de /
NK075(bu)003:7820: tshig tsam gyis nus pa bas mi 'byung ste /
NK075(bu)003:7821: glo dang sbrid dang gtam dang ni /
NK075(bu)003:7822: gnyid la sogs pas bar chad na //
NK075(bu)003:7823: des ni yi dwags bdud la sogs //
NK075(bu)003:7824: spros nas bar chad sbyor ba bya //
NK075(bu)003:7825: sems g.yeng nus mthu mi 'byung ngo //
NK075(bu)003:7827: gnyis pa bsam dpyod kyi skyon bcu ni /
NK075(bu)003:7828: nyon mongs pa'i dug lnga bsam pa'i skyon dang /
NK075(bu)003:7829: brtson 'grus chung ba bsam pa'i skyon dang drug /
NK075(bu)003:7830: 'dod chags che ba re dogs skyon dang bdun /
NK075(bu)003:7831: ting nge 'dzin dang bral ba g.yeng ba'i skyon dang brgyad /
NK075(bu)003:7832: yid ches med pa the tshom gyi skyon dang dgu /
NK075(bu)003:7833: don dang mi ldan pa rang rgyud pa'i skyon dang bcu'o //
NK075(bu)003:7834: de yang nag po drug cu pa las /
NK075(bu)003:7835: sngags kyi bsnyen pa byed dus su //
NK075(bu)003:7836: me dang 'dra ba'i zhe sdang gis //
NK075(bu)003:7837: sngags kyi 'bras bu sreg par byed //
NK075(bu)003:7838: kun nas 'khrig pa'i chags pa yis //
NK075(bu)003:7839: yon tan rgyud rnams chings bar byed //
NK075(bu)003:7840: mun pa lta bu'i gti mug gis //
NK075(bu)003:7841: dngos grub nye ba rnyed mi 'gyur //
NK075(bu)003:7842: glang bu lta bu'i nga rgyal gyis //
NK075(bu)003:7843: dngos grub chu 'dra rtse nas bsnyil //
NK075(bu)003:7844: sngags kyi yon tan sprin 'dra la //
NK075(bu)003:7845: phrag dog rlung gis 'thor bar byed //
NK075(bu)003:7846: dngos grub chu bo rgyun bsdus la //
NK075(bu)003:7847: brtson 'grus rdo rje brag med na //
NK075(bu)003:7848: le lo'i rba rlabs chen po 'khrugs //
NK075(bu)003:7850: sngags kyi dngos grub 'dod pas spongs //
NK075(bu)003:7851: bzlas med me yi rgyun 'dra la //
NK075(bu)003:7852: sdig pa chu dang 'dra ba gsod //
NK075(bu)003:7854: bcu po de dag le lo mi byed nas dor ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:7855: lha bsgom pa la skyon brgyad de che chung gi tshad 'gyur ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:7862: gtsug tor nas rim par nub nas mi gsal ba'i
NK075(bu)003:7863: skyon rnams spang ba ste bcos nas lha bsgom pa
NK075(bu)003:7864: la shin tu brtson par sbyar ba ste /
NK075(bu)003:7866: gang tshad dmigs la tshad dang tshul //
NK075(bu)003:7867: grangs dang cha lugs mdog dbyibs dang //
NK075(bu)003:7868: kha dog 'ba' zhig rim par nus //
NK075(bu)003:7871: drug la ri ltar che gdos bya //
NK075(bu)003:7872: bdun pa dbyibs dang bsre bar bya //
NK075(bu)003:7873: brgyad pa spyi min bye brag gnas //
NK075(bu)003:7877: thun mong dang mchog la sogs gang bsgrub pa la
NK075(bu)003:7878: bzlas pa byas pas nus mthu byin rlabs dang ldan
NK075(bu)003:7879: zhing skyob pa'i phyir sngags zhes bya'o //
NK075(bu)003:7880: bskyed rdzogs kyi don la mi 'da' bas na phyag rgya /
NK075(bu)003:7881: gtan tshigs de'i phyir na sngags phyag rgya zhes ming gi sgra don nam nges tshig tu 'jug ga //
NK075(bu)003:7882: drug pa skabs gang du dgos pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:7884: dkyil 'khor dgos pa'i dus lnga'i skabs la sngags phyag rgya dgos pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:7886: zhi khro'i lha mchod pa la dkyil 'khor dgos pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:7887: dbang bskur ba la dkyil 'khor dang /
NK075(bu)003:7888: mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub thob thabs la dkyil 'khor dang /
NK075(bu)003:7889: zhi rgyas dbang drag gang byed la dkyil 'khor dgos pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:7890: sku gsung thugs kyi rab gnas la bsod nams rten gyi dkyil 'khor dgos pa dang lnga'o //
NK075(bu)003:7891: gzhan yang bsnyen bsgrub rnam pa bzhi'i don nyams su
NK075(bu)003:7892: len pa'i tsha na sngags dang phyag rgya dgos pa'o
NK075(bu)003:7896: phyag rgya bzhi bsgoms pa la rab tu brtan pa thob nas /
NK075(bu)003:7897: mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub ya mtshan chen
NK075(bu)003:7898: por snang ba de dngos su 'grub par 'gyur nas
NK075(bu)003:7899: / yid la gang bsam pa'i 'bras bu thamsa cad 'grub pa yin no //
NK075(bu)003:7901: sngags dang phyag rgya rab brtan na //
NK075(bu)003:7902: dngos grub ya mtshan chen por 'gyur //
NK075(bu)003:7906: dpe na ral gri'i yu ba nas ma bzung nas
NK075(bu)003:7907: so la bzung na tshur rang gi lag pa nyes
NK075(bu)003:7908: pa ltar / sngags bzla ba dang phyag rgya bsgom
NK075(bu)003:7909: pa la dad pa dang brtson 'grus kyis nan tan
NK075(bu)003:7910: med cing gzhung bzhin ma spyod pa'i gsang sngags pa
NK075(bu)003:7911: pa ltar / 'ga' zhig gis / dam tshig nyams
NK075(bu)003:7912: pas tshe 'dir phung bzhin phyi mar mtho ris dang
NK075(bu)003:7913: thar pa'i 'bras bu rnams med par 'gyur ro //
NK075(bu)003:7915: dad med nyams na phung bar 'gyur //
NK075(bu)003:7917: dgu pa gang gi spyod yul yin pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:7921: gzungs sngags dang gsum po gang la mosa pa'i rim
NK075(bu)003:7922: pa rnams nyams len gang byed de'i spyod yul yin
NK075(bu)003:7923: pa dang / phyag rgya bzhi gang la spyod pa'i
NK075(bu)003:7924: gang zag phyag rgya gcig pa dang spros pa yan
NK075(bu)003:7926: gsum pa tha ma tshogs sgrub la drod tshad rtags dang ldan nas 'bras mthong lam la sbyor ba'o //
NK075(bu)003:7928: dang po shes par bya ba'i yul lnga dang /
NK075(bu)003:7929: bar du thun mong dang mchog gi lam gnyis po gong du song nas /
NK075(bu)003:7930: 'dir tha ma rtogs pa'i rig pa la dbyer med
NK075(bu)003:7931: kyis drod thob pa'i tshad dang ldan pa des 'bras
NK075(bu)003:7932: bu mthong lam la nye bar sbyor bar byed pa'i
NK075(bu)003:7933: bar chad med par tshogs sgrub pa de ni 'di
NK075(bu)003:7934: lta ste / rnal 'byor pa rang gi nyams su
NK075(bu)003:7935: len pa'i yi dam gyi lha de bsgrub pa dang
NK075(bu)003:7936: lta ste / / de yang sngon du tshogs lam gyi ting nge 'dzina mthar phyin pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:7937: dam tshig sdom pa la sel med pa dang ldan
NK075(bu)003:7938: nas zag bcas de nyid zag med kyi lam la
NK075(bu)003:7939: sbyor ba'i thabs la tshogs bsgrub dgos te /
NK075(bu)003:7940: de yang zhi khro gnyis kyi tshom bu gcig gsum
NK075(bu)003:7941: lnga pa'i rnam grangs rnams gzhung nas bshad pa bzhin
NK075(bu)003:7943: dang po tshogs lam gyi thabs lam dang shes rab
NK075(bu)003:7944: grol lam gyi ting nge 'dzin gyi rnam grangs rnams
NK075(bu)003:7945: la / rgyal ba'i bka' lung tshad ma dang bla
NK075(bu)003:7946: ma dam pa'i man ngag tshad ma gnyis las gragsa
NK075(bu)003:7948: rig pa tshad mas legs par sbyangs nas thabs grol
NK075(bu)003:7949: zung 'jug gi ting nge 'dzin la brtan pa thob
NK075(bu)003:7950: nas sgrub pa byas nas zag bcas de nyid zag
NK075(bu)003:7951: pa med pa'i sa la sbyor ba yin no //
NK075(bu)003:7952: spyi don gsum pa tha ma lam gyis 'thob par
NK075(bu)003:7953: byed pas lam shes pa'i rgyu 'bru re nas bstan
NK075(bu)003:7957: 'bring la rnam par dbye ba gnyis gong du song nas /
NK075(bu)003:7958: 'dir blo tha ma la 'bru re nas gnyer zhing bshad pas /
NK075(bu)003:7959: lam gyi snga ma lta ba rtogs pa'i rgyu byas nas /
NK075(bu)003:7960: des lam mthar phyin cing 'bras bu thob pa de'i sdom tshig ni 'di lta ste /
NK075(bu)003:7961: 'bru gnyer la brten nas lta ba rtogs /
NK075(bu)003:7962: de nyid nyams su blangs pa la lam lnga rim
NK075(bu)003:7963: par bgrod nas mthar phyin pa la 'bras bu bde
NK075(bu)003:7964: bar gshegs pa rgyal ba de nyid dngos su thob
NK075(bu)003:7965: pa yin no // 'bras bu thob pa'i yon tan
NK075(bu)003:7966: de yod pa'i phyir na blo tha mas rgyud don
NK075(bu)003:7967: gtan la 'bebs par byed pa la bshad thabs 'dren
NK075(bu)003:7968: pa'i tshig bcu yi sgo nas 'bru re dang don
NK075(bu)003:7970: khyad par du rus sbal gnur shugsa kyi sgo nas 'bru gnyer nyams su blang bar bya ste /
NK075(bu)003:7972: rus sbal gnur 'gros lta bu'i blos //
NK075(bu)003:7973: yi ge'i 'bru rnams chum par bshad //
NK075(bu)003:7974: ces gsungs pas tshig 'bru re nas gnyer bas de
NK075(bu)003:7975: bsam byung gis gzhal ba'i yul du byas nas rgyud
NK075(bu)003:7976: kyi don mngon sum du rnyed cing rtogs pa'i don
NK075(bu)003:7977: de la rgyud dbu zhabs kyi don lhag ma ma
NK075(bu)003:7981: thugs kyi thigs pa las zhes pa 'bru mthun no //
NK075(bu)003:7982: rang bzhin dang sbyangs pa'i snod du rung ba gcig
NK075(bu)003:7983: la gdul bya rgyud daga pa'i blo dang 'tshams par
NK075(bu)003:7984: snang ba de'i gzhung don gcod cing mtshams 'dzin pas
NK075(bu)003:7986: yas bgrang gsuma pa'i don du gada'o //
NK075(bu)003:7988: // bzhi pa 'bras bu bde bar gshegs pa'i snang ba la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:7992: gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa gtan la dbab par
NK075(bu)003:7993: byed pa'i yan lag la shes bya rang bzhin gyi
NK075(bu)003:7994: snang ba dang / de ma rtogs pa la 'gro drug 'khrul pa'i snang ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:7995: de'i gnyen po lta sgom spyod sogs gdul bya lam
NK075(bu)003:7996: gyi snang ba dang gsum po gong du song la
NK075(bu)003:7997: / 'dir bzhi pa 'bras bu mthar phyin pa bde
NK075(bu)003:7998: bar gshegs pa'i snang ba'i sdom tshig ni 'di lta
NK075(bu)003:7999: / ste / de yang lam pas rtogs shing nyams
NK075(bu)003:8000: su blangs nas 'bras bu snang ba'i bar la mtshan
NK075(bu)003:8001: / ste / nyid gsum ste / rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba rtogs pa /
NK075(bu)003:8002: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid spyod sgom gyis nyams su blang ba /
NK075(bu)003:8003: 'bras bu mngon du gyur pa'i mtshan nyid lam gyi
NK075(bu)003:8004: spang gnyen gyi bya ba zad pa'i yar gyi tha
NK075(bu)003:8006: de nyid las kyi don phyi ci ma log par gsal bar lung bstana pa la /
NK075(bu)003:8007: gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu rig pa 'dzin pa dang
NK075(bu)003:8008: mthar thug gi 'bras bu rdzogs pa'i sangas rgyas thob
NK075(bu)003:8010: gnyis pa bshad pa de la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:8017: 'bras bu la gnyis su phye ba'i snga ma rig 'dzin la'ang bzhi ste /
NK075(bu)003:8018: zag bcas nas zag med du sbyor ba'i thob tshul dang /
NK075(bu)003:8020: rig 'dzin zhes bya ba'i nges tshig dang /
NK075(bu)003:8021: gnas su zhugs tshul dang bzhi'i sgo nas rnam par bshad pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:8022: gnyis pa bshad pa de la bzhi ste /
NK075(bu)003:8026: nyan thos kyi theg pa la lhag ma'i lus dang bcas pa yod pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:8027: med pa'i mya ngan las 'da' ba'i 'bras bu thob tshul gyi dpe gnyis bzhin du /
NK075(bu)003:8028: 'dir lhag bcas tshe dbang thob tshul dang lhag med
NK075(bu)003:8029: rnam smin rig 'dzin thob tshul gnyis kyi rab kyis
NK075(bu)003:8031: tha mas bar ma do la tshe rnam gnyis thob nas phyag chen la rnam par sbyor te /
NK075(bu)003:8032: de nas lhun grub la rnam pa sbyor bar bya'o //
NK075(bu)003:8035: rnam par smin pa'i rig 'dzin ni dpe bya khyung
NK075(bu)003:8036: gi phru gu'i sgong rgya de bcag ma thag ma
NK075(bu)003:8037: dang rtsal mnyam / gcan gzan seng phrug gi mngal
NK075(bu)003:8038: rgya la ma'i mche zur gyis bkral ma thag ma
NK075(bu)003:8039: dang rtsal mnyam pa'i tshul du rnal 'byor pa lus
NK075(bu)003:8040: rgya dang bral ma thag tu phyag chen gyi skur
NK075(bu)003:8041: dang rtsal mnyam / gyur te / rin chen 'phrul skabs su /
NK075(bu)003:8042: sgo nga nang du 'dug pa'i khyung //
NK075(bu)003:8043: de bzhin seng ge mngal gyi rgya //
NK075(bu)003:8044: rgya mig dang ni rgyas pa bzhin //
NK075(bu)003:8045: rnal 'byor pa ni lus rgyas btum //
NK075(bu)003:8046: yon tan 'char ba ga la nus //
NK075(bu)003:8047: phung po bor bas dbyings su grol //
NK075(bu)003:8050: yid kyis lha yi gzugs brten cing //
NK075(bu)003:8051: phyag rgya sku nyid gsal gyur pa //
NK075(bu)003:8052: lhag ma bzhag pa'i bar ma la //
NK075(bu)003:8053: de med phyag rgya chen por smin //
NK075(bu)003:8054: las kyi lus sbubs rnal 'byor ces so //
NK075(bu)003:8055: lus khams skye gnas kyi zag pa gsum dang bral ba'i mthong lam pa ni /
NK075(bu)003:8056: don la lus snang sems gsum dbyer med du rig
NK075(bu)003:8057: pa rang snang gi sku ye shes su dbang bsgyur
NK075(bu)003:8058: zhing / rtags la tshe la dbang bsgyur ba ste /
NK075(bu)003:8059: bral 'bras la phung po lnga la 'jig pa med
NK075(bu)003:8060: par 'ja' lus su lam gong ma dang sangs rgyas
NK075(bu)003:8061: kyi sa la khyer ba yin te /
NK075(bu)003:8063: lus khams skye gnas zag pa zad //
NK075(bu)003:8064: rdo rje'i lus gyur tshe yi rigs //
NK075(bu)003:8065: mthong ba'i chos la mya ngan 'das //
NK075(bu)003:8066: lus ma bor bar sangs rgyas pa //
NK075(bu)003:8069: sgom lam phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin ni rnal
NK075(bu)003:8070: 'byor pa bdag gi lus 'di nyid sngar phyag rgya
NK075(bu)003:8071: gcig pa'i skabs su yi dam gyi lha rigs lnga
NK075(bu)003:8072: gang bsgom gyi skur rtsa lus su snang zhing grangs
NK075(bu)003:8073: can gyi 'khor lor dgongs pa mi g.yo bar bzhugs
NK075(bu)003:8075: rang lus gdod nas phyag rgya cher //
NK075(bu)003:8076: bsgom pa mngon du gyur pa'i sku //
NK075(bu)003:8077: mtshan dpe bzhi mngon drug rdzogs pa //
NK075(bu)003:8078: phyag rgya chen po'i rigs su grags //
NK075(bu)003:8079: ye shes sku yi cha lugs can //
NK075(bu)003:8080: 'byung ba rdo rje'i lus la grol //
NK075(bu)003:8081: grangs can 'khor lo mngon du snang //
NK075(bu)003:8082: zag pa med pa bsgom pa'i lam //
NK075(bu)003:8083: mi g.yo rnal 'byor nyid du brjod //
NK075(bu)003:8086: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga /
NK075(bu)003:8087: de re re la'ang lnga lnga ste sku rig rgyan
NK075(bu)003:8088: gyi 'khor lo nyi shu rtsa lngar lhun grub tu
NK075(bu)003:8090: 'o na sangs rgyas dang khyad par med dam zhe na /
NK075(bu)003:8091: mnyam bzhag la sangs rgyas dang khyad med kyang /
NK075(bu)003:8092: lhun grub rig 'dzin de la rjes thob la bag
NK075(bu)003:8093: nyal de yi dri ma yod pas da rung mnyam
NK075(bu)003:8094: bzhag dang gnyen po'i rtsol ba ca na yin te
NK075(bu)003:8096: bsam yas lhun gyi grub pa'i phyir //
NK075(bu)003:8097: thams cad mkhyen pa'i spyan mchog 'chang //
NK075(bu)003:8098: yi ge 'khor lo mngon gzigs pa //
NK075(bu)003:8099: mi g.yo ba la mi rtog pa //
NK075(bu)003:8100: da dung mngon par mi rgya ste //
NK075(bu)003:8101: dus mtha'i skad cig nyid kyis gshegs //
NK075(bu)003:8105: me la gnas pa'i sems can gyi rigs la drang srong me'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK075(bu)003:8106: ri dwags me byi dkar po gnyis kyi gnas kyang me la /
NK075(bu)003:8107: zas gos la sogs pa'i longs spyod rnams kyang me la longs spyod pas /
NK075(bu)003:8108: me dang bral na 'chi bas me las mi 'da' ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:8109: chu la gnas pa'i sems can rnams kyi gnas kyang chu la /
NK075(bu)003:8110: zas gos la sogs longs spyod kyang chu la byed /
NK075(bu)003:8111: chu dang bral na 'chi bas chu las mi 'da' ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:8112: rlung la gnas pa'i sems can dag gi rigs bya
NK075(bu)003:8113: mkha' lding nam mkha' tshang 'jug bya ba des gnas
NK075(bu)003:8115: zas la sogs pa'i yo byad kyang rlung la byed pa /
NK075(bu)003:8116: rlung dang bral na 'chi bas rlung las mi 'da' ba bzhin du'am /
NK075(bu)003:8117: yang na me'i mtshan nyid tsha ba la /
NK075(bu)003:8118: chu'i mtshan nyid gsher ba la /
NK075(bu)003:8119: rlung gi mtshan nyid yang zhing g.yo ba las mi 'da' ba bzhin du /
NK075(bu)003:8120: rnal 'byor pa gang dag 'di rnams sangs rgyas kyi
NK075(bu)003:8121: rigs kyis zin nas slar mi gtong bas na rig
NK075(bu)003:8123: de yang dang po lta ba rtogs pa las byung ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:8124: bar du dpyad sgom gyi bya ba byed pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:8125: tha mar zag med kyi chos nyid la mthong lam
NK075(bu)003:8126: yan chad nas 'da' nyams med pas na sangs rgyas
NK075(bu)003:8127: kyi rgyud 'dzin pa dang gsum gyis rig 'dzin zhes
NK075(bu)003:8128: bya ba'i nges tshig de 'grub pa yin te /
NK075(bu)003:8130: mkhas rtogs goms spyod rig pa 'dzin //
NK075(bu)003:8131: lha la sogs pa rdo rje 'dzin //
NK075(bu)003:8132: mi gtong gzungs las ming thob pa //
NK075(bu)003:8135: dang po gnas sa gang yin par //
NK075(bu)003:8136: tha ma de yi gnas su 'gro //
NK075(bu)003:8137: da lta de yi don la gnas //
NK075(bu)003:8138: bar du ye shes rgyud rtsal sbyangs //
NK075(bu)003:8142: rig 'dzina de yi bzhugs gnas la nges pa phyogs gcig tu grub pa med de /
NK075(bu)003:8144: phyi snang snod bcud kyi chos thams cad semsa nyid
NK075(bu)003:8145: rig pa rang snang du shar bas na gnas gang
NK075(bu)003:8148: snang ba rig pa 'dzin pa'i gnas //
NK075(bu)003:8149: rig snang gnas la nges pa med //
NK075(bu)003:8150: skye ba cha byad don gyis 'gyur //
NK075(bu)003:8152: gnyis pa sangs rgyas la gnyis /
NK075(bu)003:8156: lam lnga'i spang gnyen gyi bya ba ma lus pa
NK075(bu)003:8157: kun byas pa'i 'bras bu sangs rgyas grub pa dag
NK075(bu)003:8159: 'bras bu sangs rgyas thobsa tshul dang /
NK075(bu)003:8161: 'bras bu sa'i rnam grangsa dang gdul bya'i spyod yul la ye shes kyi gzigs tshul dang /
NK075(bu)003:8162: brtse ba'i thugsa rje sprul pa 'char tshur dang /
NK075(bu)003:8163: gzhan don mdzad pa'i tshul dang /
NK075(bu)003:8164: dgongs pa'i ye shesa la bzhugs pa'i tshul dang bdun
NK075(bu)003:8165: gyi sdom tshig gi nang du rgyas bshad de shes
NK075(bu)003:8166: par bya'o // gnyis pa bshad pa de la bdun te /
NK075(bu)003:8170: gdul bya la gzigs tshul dang /
NK075(bu)003:8171: thugs rje sprul pa snang tshul dang /
NK075(bu)003:8172: mdzad pa bya byed kyi rtsol ba med par don mdzad tshul dang /
NK075(bu)003:8173: dgongs pa'i gnas tshul gcig dang du ma las grol ba smra bsam las 'das par bstan pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:8174: dang po thob tshul la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:8176: dang po bdag don du rang snang thob pa'i tshul dang /
NK075(bu)003:8178: bdag don gi dbang du 'bras bu thob tshul ni rgyas pa las 'di skada du gsung ste /
NK075(bu)003:8179: dper na dpag bsam gyi ljon shing la lo ma dang 'bras bu'i dgos 'dod gsal ba'i dpe dang /
NK075(bu)003:8180: yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che la gsol
NK075(bu)003:8181: ba gang btab kyis snang ngor dgos 'dod sna tshogs
NK075(bu)003:8182: 'byung ba'i dus su rtog pa med pa ltar /
NK075(bu)003:8183: dpe gnyis po de dag la snang tshul du dngos po rdzas grub ltar snang yang /
NK075(bu)003:8184: don la de dag rang rgyud kyi rdzas su grub pa rdul tsam yang yod pa ma yin te /
NK075(bu)003:8185: 'o na gang las byung zhe na /
NK075(bu)003:8186: gdul bya so so rang rang gi sems kyis bsod
NK075(bu)003:8187: nams dpag tu med pa bsags pa'i mthus brtan pa'i
NK075(bu)003:8188: stobs las dgos 'dod gang bsam 'grub pa yin pa
NK075(bu)003:8189: bzhin du gzhi sems nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang
NK075(bu)003:8190: la sangs rgyas kyi yon tan cir yang snang bas
NK075(bu)003:8191: na ngo matshara zhing sems kyi cho 'phrul sku gsung
NK075(bu)003:8192: thugs yon tan phrin las lnga'am /
NK075(bu)003:8193: nyi shu rtsa lnga la sogs pa mtha' yas pas
NK075(bu)003:8194: rang byung gi ye shes rang la byung ba ni
NK075(bu)003:8196: gzhan nas bkug pa'am yoda pa gcig 'dir 'ong ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:8197: rgyu rkyen gang gi sgo nas thob pa ma yin /
NK075(bu)003:8198: te yi sgras tshul ci ltar du byung na /
NK075(bu)003:8199: phung po lnga la sogs pa'i rtog tshogs lha'i sku
NK075(bu)003:8200: gsung thugs kyi phyag rgyar gsal ba'i thabs snang la
NK075(bu)003:8202: shes rab rang bzhin med pa ste /
NK075(bu)003:8203: de ltar thabs shes rab gnyis su med pa de
NK075(bu)003:8204: nyid rang rig par rgyun du brten par sgom pa
NK075(bu)003:8206: dpe gnyis po de lta bu don rgyu 'bras gnyis
NK075(bu)003:8207: su med par snang ba yi ngang du sangs rgyas
NK075(bu)003:8208: kyi che yon thams cad 'bad med lhun grub tu
NK075(bu)003:8210: gnyis pa gzhan don du lam gyi mdzad pa rdzogs nas thob tshul lo //
NK075(bu)003:8212: gdul bya gzhan gyi don du gzugs sku'i sangs rgyas thob lugs ni /
NK075(bu)003:8215: yang lam lnga'i bya ba ma lus pa kun byas nas mthar thug gi 'bras bu ni /
NK075(bu)003:8216: skye 'jig med pa rdo rje'i sku drug pa thob
NK075(bu)003:8217: nas sprul sku sna tshogs kyis 'gro ba'i don mdzad
NK075(bu)003:8218: ces rgyud las de ltar gsunga pa'i don ni /
NK075(bu)003:8219: srid pa tha ma pa lhun grub rig 'dzin dang /
NK075(bu)003:8220: bcu gcig kun tu 'od kyi sangs rgyas de la /
NK075(bu)003:8221: sku lnga lhun grub kyi sangs spyi gzugs can des dbang bskur bas dbang don rdzogs pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:8222: ston pa rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sku dang dbyer med
NK075(bu)003:8223: du sangs rgyas ma thag tu gsang sngags rtogs nus
NK075(bu)003:8224: kyi snang ngo la longs sku dang /
NK075(bu)003:8225: mi nus pa rnams kyi snang ngo la sku rdo rje /
NK075(bu)003:8227: thugs rdo rje gsum dbyer med pa las /
NK075(bu)003:8228: sprul pa thub pa drug gi dbang po ste gtso
NK075(bu)003:8229: bor snang nas gang la gang 'dul ba yi sgo
NK075(bu)003:8230: nas sems can gyi don mdzad de /
NK075(bu)003:8231: khyad par du mi'i thub pas lam gyi mdzad pa rdzogs nas sangs rgyas pa'i tshul gyis /
NK075(bu)003:8232: sems can gyi nyon mongs pa brgyad khri bzhi stong
NK075(bu)003:8233: gi gnyen por chos kyi sgo mo brgyad khri bzhi
NK075(bu)003:8234: stong gsungs na don mdzad pa de'i rgyas bshad ni
NK075(bu)003:8235: gsang ba'i snying po le'u gsum pa'i bstan pa 'byung
NK075(bu)003:8236: ba spyi'i gleng gzhi'i skabs las shes par bya'o //
NK075(bu)003:8239: 'khor 'das gnyis su med pa'i sems nyid rig pa'i
NK075(bu)003:8240: ye shes su mngon sum du rtogs shing grub mtha'
NK075(bu)003:8241: ma lus pa rdzogs par byas nas /
NK075(bu)003:8242: bdena gnyis dbyer med cing skye 'jig dang bral bas rdo rje'i sku thob ste /
NK075(bu)003:8243: dper na chu yi nang gi zla ba'i gzugs brnyan
NK075(bu)003:8244: snang dus chu las ma g.yos nas dbyer med du
NK075(bu)003:8246: don la shes bya 'khor 'das kyi chos kun ma
NK075(bu)003:8247: 'dres pa la yongs su rdzogs shing thams cad du
NK075(bu)003:8248: rig pa rang snang ba la gzhan gyi lhad med
NK075(bu)003:8249: pas na rang bzhin 'khor 'das kyi chos kun dang
NK075(bu)003:8250: tha mi dad cing dbyer med pa ste /
NK075(bu)003:8252: bden pa gnyis med dbang bsgyur ba //
NK075(bu)003:8253: bdag dang gzhan gyi gnyis med de //
NK075(bu)003:8254: so so med phyir der son pa //
NK075(bu)003:8255: mtha' rnams kun bral kun ldan par //
NK075(bu)003:8256: rang snang zhen bral mngon byas pa //
NK075(bu)003:8261: rten byed pa'i cha nas sku lnga dang /
NK075(bu)003:8262: brda' sprod pas gsung lnga dang /
NK075(bu)003:8263: dgongs pa zab pas thugs lnga dang /
NK075(bu)003:8264: dgos 'dod 'byung bas yon tan lnga dang /
NK075(bu)003:8265: bya ba byed pa'i cha nas phrin las lnga dang /
NK075(bu)003:8266: de ltar nyer lnga ma 'gags pa ni chos sku'i
NK075(bu)003:8267: rgyan gyi mchog yin cing de nyid rgyun chad med
NK075(bu)003:8269: de nyid gsar du thob pa ni ma yin te
NK075(bu)003:8270: ye gdod ma nas rang bzhin gyis gnas pa'i don
NK075(bu)003:8273: 'khor 'das kyi chos kun snang la rang bzhin med
NK075(bu)003:8274: pa dbyer med mngon du gyur pa ni chos sku
NK075(bu)003:8276: 'jig rten brtan g.yo la sogs pa //
NK075(bu)003:8277: snang ba nyid na ngo bo med //
NK075(bu)003:8278: de nyid chos sku chen po yin //
NK075(bu)003:8282: dus gsum chos kun gcig pa yi //
NK075(bu)003:8283: rgyal ba nyid phyir sna tshogs chos //
NK075(bu)003:8284: snang la rang bzhin med pa'i phyir //
NK075(bu)003:8285: de nyid d+harma k+aa yar gnas //
NK075(bu)003:8287: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad ma 'gags ma dmigs
NK075(bu)003:8288: bdag nyid chen por longs spyod pa ni drug pa
NK075(bu)003:8289: spyi'i gzugs can longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku'o //
NK075(bu)003:8291: de nyid gdul bya lugs bzlog sna tshogs la /
NK075(bu)003:8292: zhi khro'i sku sna tshogs su rang snang ba'o //
NK075(bu)003:8293: rdo rje'i sku ni de ltar sku gsum chu dang gzugs brnyan ltar dbyer med pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:8294: mngon byang gi sku ni sku bzhi po de nyid
NK075(bu)003:8295: rig pa rang snang gi ye shes lnga las ma
NK075(bu)003:8296: g.yos pa'o // de yang gsang snying las /
NK075(bu)003:8297: phyogs bcu dus bzhi rdzogs pa yi //
NK075(bu)003:8298: ye shes dkyil 'khor thig le che //
NK075(bu)003:8299: bsod nams dkyil 'khor sku yi tshogs //
NK075(bu)003:8300: snang stong thig le kun tu rdzogs ho /
NK075(bu)003:8303: chos sku dbyer med don gyi gsung rgyal ba dgongs brgyud du brda' 'phrod pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:8305: sku mthong ba tsam gyis me long gzugs brnyan ltar skyon yon brda mjal ba'o //
NK075(bu)003:8306: sprul sku tshig gi gsung ni tshangs pa'i gsung ltar
NK075(bu)003:8307: gsung gcig gdul bya sna tshogs rang rang gi blo
NK075(bu)003:8309: rdo rje'i sku'i gsung ni chos thams cad dbyer med du brda 'phrod pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:8310: mngon byang rig pa byin rlabs kyi gsung ni ye shes lnga rang du brda mjal ba'o //
NK075(bu)003:8312: rdo rje bsod nams thig le che //
NK075(bu)003:8313: rdo rje ye shes dkyil 'khor ldan //
NK075(bu)003:8314: rdo rje sgra chen mtha' yas pa //
NK075(bu)003:8315: rdo rje rgyal po thig le che ho //
NK075(bu)003:8317: thugs lnga ni ye shes lnga ste /
NK075(bu)003:8318: rnam kun mchog ldan gyi stong pa nyid ni chos dbyings ye shes te chos sku'i thugs /
NK075(bu)003:8319: gsal la 'dzin pa med pa ni me long ye shes te mngon byang gi sku'i thugs /
NK075(bu)003:8320: gsal stong dbyed med ni mnyam nyid ye shes te longs sku'i thugs /
NK075(bu)003:8321: shes bya ma 'dres par gsal ba ni so ra rtogs ye shes te rdo rje'i sku'i thugs /
NK075(bu)003:8322: don gnyis rang snang du lhun gyis grub pa ni bya grub ye shes te sprul sku'i thugs so //
NK075(bu)003:8324: sku gsung thugs kyi rdzogs pa che //
NK075(bu)003:8325: yon tan phrin las kun tu rdzogs //
NK075(bu)003:8326: ye nas lhun rdzogs kun tu bzang //
NK075(bu)003:8327: 'dus pa'i tshogs chen theg le che ho //
NK075(bu)003:8330: spyir gzung yul gnas su dag cing rig pa rang
NK075(bu)003:8331: snang bas sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams su shar ba
NK075(bu)003:8332: ni zhing khams yon tan can dang /
NK075(bu)003:8333: snang ba gnas su dag nas 'bras bu'i chos thams
NK075(bu)003:8334: cad lhun grub tu rdzogs par rang snang ba ni
NK075(bu)003:8336: 'dod yon lnga la sogs pa ma spang bar rang
NK075(bu)003:8337: rig pa'i ye shes su lhun gyis rdzogs pa'i phyir
NK075(bu)003:8338: rgyan cha dang / ye shes lnga yi dkyil 'khor du gsal zhing /
NK075(bu)003:8340: 'bras bu'i stobs dang mi 'jigs pa la sogs pa
NK075(bu)003:8341: lhun gyis grub pa'i rtags su seng ge la sogs
NK075(bu)003:8342: par snang ba ni gdan khri yon tan can no
NK075(bu)003:8344: mi dmigs sgyu 'phrul mnyam pa'i dbyings //
NK075(bu)003:8345: mtha' yas kun tu sna tshogs 'phro //
NK075(bu)003:8346: mtha' yas kun nas lhun gyis thim //
NK075(bu)003:8347: sna tshogs sku gsung thugs chen po ho //
NK075(bu)003:8350: zhi rgyas dbang drag lhun gyis grub pa'i phrin las
NK075(bu)003:8351: dang lnga'i sgo nas gdul bya'i blo dang 'tshams par
NK075(bu)003:8354: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten rdul snyed du //
NK075(bu)003:8355: rgyal ba'i don rnams rdul phran snyed //
NK075(bu)003:8356: sprul pa rdul phran bsam yas kyis //
NK075(bu)003:8357: skad cig yud la lhun gyis grub ho //
NK075(bu)003:8359: bzhi pa gdul bya gzigs tshul dang /
NK075(bu)003:8361: shes bya thams cad mkhyen pa'i sangs rgyas kyi yul
NK075(bu)003:8362: gdul bya sems can thams cad la gzigs tshul ni
