NK075(bu)003:8364: gnyis med kyi ye shes rang ngo ma shes pa lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:8365: der yang ma zad log par rtog pa gzung 'dzin
NK075(bu)003:8366: kun brtagsa kyi ma rig pa dang gnyis rnam par
NK075(bu)003:8367: dag cing / mngon sum du rtogs pa'i yee shes
NK075(bu)003:8368: ni rtogs bya dbyings mnyam pa nyid las mi gzhan
NK075(bu)003:8369: cing dbyer med kyi don rtogs pa'i phyir na /
NK075(bu)003:8370: thugs spros pa thams cad dang bral ba des shes bya thams cad la khyab pas rje ste /
NK075(bu)003:8371: de'i phyir skye byed kyi sangs rgyas dang /
NK075(bu)003:8372: skye bya'i yul sems can dang /
NK075(bu)003:8373: skye bdo ba'i thugs rje gsum gnyis med rang snang du shar bas chen po /
NK075(bu)003:8374: de nyid ngo bo bdag nyid gcig par 'brel pas na /
NK075(bu)003:8375: 'gro ba rigs drug gi dus snga phyi dang /
NK075(bu)003:8376: gnas la mthon dman la sogs pa shes bya ma lus pa kun snang nas mkhyen pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:8377: de ltar ma 'dres yongs rdzogs su mkhyen pa'i dus nyid na yang /
NK075(bu)003:8378: rgyas pa'i lung las 'di skad gsungs te /
NK075(bu)003:8379: yul yul can gyi rnam par rtog pa mi mnga' ba ste dbyings mnyam pa nyid las ma g.yos /
NK075(bu)003:8380: ma g.yos bzhin du de yi ye shes kyis mi
NK075(bu)003:8381: mkhyen pa dang mi gzigs pa dang gang yang med
NK075(bu)003:8382: de / tshul ci ltar du mkhyen zhe na /
NK075(bu)003:8383: yang kun byed kyi lung las gsungs pa ni dper
NK075(bu)003:8384: na me long la gzugs brnyan 'char dus me long
NK075(bu)003:8385: las ma g.yos pa lta bu'i tshul bzhin du /
NK075(bu)003:8386: don dbyings las ma g.yos bzhin du ye shes kyi
NK075(bu)003:8387: shes bya sna tshogsa so so'i kha dog mi 'dra
NK075(bu)003:8388: ba sna tshogs dbyibs mi 'dra ba sna tshogs ma
NK075(bu)003:8389: 'dres yongs rdzogs su shar nas snang ba ste /
NK075(bu)003:8391: ma bcos ngang la gnyis med kyang //
NK075(bu)003:8392: shes rab 'od gsal chen po yi //
NK075(bu)003:8393: mkha' la gza' skar bkram pa'am //
NK075(bu)003:8394: me tog mdzes pa'i phung po ltar //
NK075(bu)003:8395: so sor gsal la gcig tu 'dus //
NK075(bu)003:8396: ma 'dres yongs su rdzogs par ni //
NK075(bu)003:8397: phyogs med dang gsal ye shes su //
NK075(bu)003:8398: dus mtha'i tshad las 'das par mkhyen //
NK075(bu)003:8400: lnga pa thugs rje'i sprul pa snang tshul dang /
NK075(bu)003:8402: 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i bde bar gshegs pa thams
NK075(bu)003:8403: cad kyi dgongs pa'i rang bzhin de la 'khor ba'i
NK075(bu)003:8404: chos thams cad dang dbyer med du rang snang ba'i
NK075(bu)003:8405: phyir na / sprul pa sna tshogs kyis 'gro ba'i don byed pa'i dus su /
NK075(bu)003:8407: tsan+d+ra ste zla ba'i gzugs brnyan 'gro 'ong dang thogs chags med par chu la 'char ba bzhin du /
NK075(bu)003:8408: dgongs pa chos sku las ma g.yos bzhin du gzugs
NK075(bu)003:8409: sku sna tshogs su snang nas 'gro ba'i don byed
NK075(bu)003:8410: pa de yang gzhan don du gdul bya'i don byed
NK075(bu)003:8412: don byed rdzogs nas rang gnas su 'ong ba'i byed
NK075(bu)003:8413: bya byed byed kyi rtsol rtog gi rnam pa ga
NK075(bu)003:8415: gal te rtsol rtog gi sgo nas 'gro 'ong de
NK075(bu)003:8416: yod na ni gzung 'dzin can du 'gyur bas sems
NK075(bu)003:8418: drug pa mdzad pa bya byed kyi rtsol ba med par don mdzad tshul dang /
NK075(bu)003:8420: dper na sgyu ma'i 'khrul 'khor mkhan gyi rta glang snang yang bden dngos kyis stong pa bzhin du /
NK075(bu)003:8421: don ye shes sgyu ma'i dkyil 'khor gzugs sku gnyis
NK075(bu)003:8422: su snang nas 'gro ba sems can rnams grol bar
NK075(bu)003:8424: don bya ba'i yul dang byed pa'i mkhan po dang
NK075(bu)003:8425: don bya ba'i dngos po gsum du 'dzin pa meda
NK075(bu)003:8426: par rang rig pa'i sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil
NK075(bu)003:8427: 'khor gyi ngang nas sems can gyi don spyod de
NK075(bu)003:8428: mdzad pa'o // bdun pa dgongs pa rgyud kyi gnas
NK075(bu)003:8429: tshul gcig dang du ma las grol ba smra bsam
NK075(bu)003:8434: ma 'ongs pa dang gsum du lam pa rnams rim pa ltar sangs rgyas pa'i rgyal ba rnams ni /
NK075(bu)003:8435: kha cig gis chos sku stong pa'i ngo bo la thams cad tha dad med par 'dod pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:8436: kha cig gis gzugs sku'i sangs rgyas tsam du 'dra yang /
NK075(bu)003:8437: sbyangs pa'i ye shes mi 'dra bas mi gcig par 'dod pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:8438: de dag gi log rtog gi bye brag tha dad dag pa de yang 'di lta ste /
NK075(bu)003:8439: sems tsam dang sngags phyi rgyud kyis sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dgongs pa'i ngo bo gcig kyang /
NK075(bu)003:8440: sngon las gyis sbyangs pa mi 'dra ba'i stobs kyis
NK075(bu)003:8441: 'bras bu'i dus su sbyangs pa'i ye shes dang gzugs
NK075(bu)003:8443: shing gi me dpung ltar du 'dod pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:8444: dbu mas sangs rgyas thams cad dbyings stong pa'i cha nas tha dad med de /
NK075(bu)003:8445: chu la chu thim pa ltar 'dod pa de dag
NK075(bu)003:8446: ni theg 'og drang don gyi sangs rgyas yin la
NK075(bu)003:8447: / theg mchog nges don gyi sangs rgyas ni ye
NK075(bu)003:8448: gdod ma nyid nas ka dag lhun grub dbyer med
NK075(bu)003:8449: kyi don mngon du gyur pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi
NK075(bu)003:8450: spyi'i gzugs can ni dbyings dang ye shes sam /
NK075(bu)003:8451: chos sku dang gzugs sku phyogs rer bzung ba'i mtha' thams cad las grol ba'i phyir /
NK075(bu)003:8452: des na dbyings chos sku'i cha nas sangs rgyas thams
NK075(bu)003:8453: cad gcig pa dang ye shes gzugs sku'i cha nas
NK075(bu)003:8454: sangs rgyas thams cad mi gcig ces ngag tu brjod
NK075(bu)003:8455: pa dang yid kyis bsam pa'i mtha' thams cad las
NK075(bu)003:8456: 'das te chos kun ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs
NK075(bu)003:8457: par bzhugs pa'o // de ltar phyogs re'i gzung 'dzin
NK075(bu)003:8458: thams cad dang bral ba'i dbyer med kyi ye shes
NK075(bu)003:8459: ni 'bras bu mthar phyin gyi de bzhin gshegs pa
NK075(bu)003:8460: sangs rgyas kun gyis spyi gzugs can gyi bzhugs gnas
NK075(bu)003:8461: yin ces rgyud rgyas pa las gsungs pas na lung
NK075(bu)003:8462: de nyid 'dir drang zhing bgrod par gyis dang go
NK075(bu)003:8463: ba dang the tshom med par yang sla'o //
NK075(bu)003:8464: mdor bsdus na sku lnga lhun grub kyi sangs rgyas
NK075(bu)003:8465: ni dper na rgya mtsho'i chu dang brlabs la dbye
NK075(bu)003:8467: gzugs sku sna tshogs pa gdul bya la snang dus
NK075(bu)003:8468: dgongs pa mthar 'bras chos sku las ma g.yos pa
NK075(bu)003:8469: yin no // de ltar sangs rgyas thams cad dgongs
NK075(bu)003:8470: pa rgyud kyi bzhugs tshul las dgag bsgrub kyi gtan
NK075(bu)003:8475: dbu ma pas sangs rgyas thams cad stong par gcig par 'dod pa dgag pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:8476: sems tsam dang sngags phyi rgyud pas ma 'dres par 'dod pa dgag pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:8481: dbu mas dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas thams cad kyi
NK075(bu)003:8482: dgongs pa stong pa nyid du rgyud gcig par 'dod
NK075(bu)003:8483: pa ste / dpe na chu la chu thim pa'am /
NK075(bu)003:8484: mar la mar bzhag pa bzhin du 'dod de /
NK075(bu)003:8486: bdag cag ci ltar sangs rgyas pa //
NK075(bu)003:8487: de ltar kho nar sangs rgyas pas //
NK075(bu)003:8488: dper na mar dang mar nyid kyi //
NK075(bu)003:8489: snying khu mtshungs par 'gyur ba bzhin //
NK075(bu)003:8492: 'di ni spros dang bral ba rnams la snang bar 'gyur //
NK075(bu)003:8494: gnyis pa de dgag pa la bzhi ste /
NK075(bu)003:8495: rgyu rkyen gyis bsgrub pa'i 'bras bu med par 'gyur ba'i skyon dang /
NK075(bu)003:8496: 'bras bu sangs rgyas chad par 'gyur ba'i skyon dang /
NK075(bu)003:8497: mdo sngags kyi 'bras bu khyad med du 'gyur ba'i skyon dang /
NK075(bu)003:8499: theg pa 'og ma'i 'bras bu rnams la mtho dman med par 'gyur ba'i skyon no //
NK075(bu)003:8501: lam gyi dus su lha bsgom pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:8502: gzugs sogs lam du khyer ba don med du 'gyur ba'i skyon dang /
NK075(bu)003:8503: rgyud rtog tshogs zhe gnyis gnas su gyur pa las
NK075(bu)003:8504: 'bras bu sangs rgyas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis la sogs
NK075(bu)003:8505: pa mi thob par 'gyur ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:8506: rgyu rnam shes tshogs brgyad gnas su gyur pas 'bras bu ye shes lnga mi thob par 'gyur te /
NK075(bu)003:8507: mthar thug stong pa phyogs gcig las med pa'i phyir ro //
NK075(bu)003:8509: de thob rgyud rnams ci lta ba //
NK075(bu)003:8510: so so rnam pa tha dad pas //
NK075(bu)003:8511: sgrub pas de bzhin gshegs pa'i tshe //
NK075(bu)003:8512: rgyud dag lhun grub rgyal ba rnams //
NK075(bu)003:8516: de phyir sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK075(bu)003:8517: ye shes rgyu ni ma 'dres te //
NK075(bu)003:8519: gcig la mthun snang sgra mi 'jug /
NK075(bu)003:8522: 'on te thams cad gcig ce na //
NK075(bu)003:8523: gnas gyur rdzun zhing stong mthar 'gyur //
NK075(bu)003:8526: tshogs brgyad ye shes lngar rtogs pa //
NK075(bu)003:8530: ye shes lnga yang rang byung gi //
NK075(bu)003:8531: cha lngas btags kyi gzhan na med //
NK075(bu)003:8532: de phyir gcig mthar ltung ba med //
NK075(bu)003:8535: rgyal ba thams cad kyi dgongs pa stong pa phyogs gcig pa yin par thal /
NK075(bu)003:8538: gnyis med sems su mngon byas pa //
NK075(bu)003:8539: bden gnyis dbyer med rdo rje'i sku //
NK075(bu)003:8540: chu yi zla ba lta bu la //
NK075(bu)003:8541: rang bzhin kun dang tha mi dad //
NK075(bu)003:8543: gzhan yang ci yang med pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:8546: mu stegs rgyang 'phen pa dang khyad par med par 'gyur te /
NK075(bu)003:8547: snang ba spangs pa'i phyir ro //
NK075(bu)003:8549: gal te snga phyi gcig 'gro na //
NK075(bu)003:8550: stong pa'i mur thim rigs pas 'gal //
NK075(bu)003:8551: snang ba spangs pa'i skyon du 'gyur //
NK075(bu)003:8552: mtha' la thug par the tshom med //
NK075(bu)003:8556: dbu sems sngags phyi nang gi sangs rgyas la dgongs pa khyad med du thal /
NK075(bu)003:8561: so so'i grub mtha'i khyad par yang //
NK075(bu)003:8563: so sor bsgrub phyir gcig pa 'gal //
NK075(bu)003:8564: gal te rgyal ba'ang rang rgyud 'gyur //
NK075(bu)003:8567: grangs rdzogs ngo bo byin rlabs las //
NK075(bu)003:8568: snang dang don byed che chung gis //
NK075(bu)003:8569: dpags pas ngo bo nyid kyis gsal //
NK075(bu)003:8570: de tshul sa bzhi rgyal ba dag /
NK075(bu)003:8571: rgyud gcig 'dres dang grol smra ba //
NK075(bu)003:8572: 'dir drang tsam yin bshad yin phyir //
NK075(bu)003:8573: rgyud kyi khyad par bsam las 'das //
NK075(bu)003:8576: 'og ma'i 'bras bu nas gong ma'i 'bras bur 'jug pa med par thal /
NK075(bu)003:8577: sangs rgyas rnams dgongs rgyud gcig pa'i phyir /
NK075(bu)003:8581: thabs chen theg pa'i bsti gnas yin //
NK075(bu)003:8584: lam gyi rtsol bas ngal ba rnams //
NK075(bu)003:8585: brod pa bskyed pa'i phyir kun tu'o //
NK075(bu)003:8586: rdor 'dzin stug po bkod par bstan //
NK075(bu)003:8588: rang sa thob las ngo bo nyid //
NK075(bu)003:8589: gcig par smra ba mun spral pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:8591: gzhan yang mdo dgongs 'dus kyi nang du khye'u lnga 'bras bu la 'jug pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:8592: gsang snying le'u drug pa las spar khab mkhan pos 'bras 'jug ltar bshad pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:8593: lam chung la sogs pa rnams kyi nang du bshad pas spangs daka'o //
NK075(bu)003:8594: gnyis pa dgongs rgyud tha dad du 'dod pa dgag pa la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)003:8595: gzhan gyi 'dod pa dgod pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:8598: 'bras bu dus gsum gyi rgyal ba rnams sangs rgyas tsam du mtshungs kyang /
NK075(bu)003:8599: lam gyi sbyangs pa'i rtsal tha dad pa'i dbang gis /
NK075(bu)003:8600: 'bras bu dgongs pa'i rgyud rang mtshan ma 'dres te /
NK075(bu)003:8601: dper na shing du ma'i me bzhin no //
NK075(bu)003:8602: gnyis pa de dgag pa la kun khyab gsum las /
NK075(bu)003:8603: dang po lung tshad ma ni /
NK075(bu)003:8605: nam mkha' kun khyab rgyal ba dang //
NK075(bu)003:8606: nyag gcig snang ba'i rgyal ba gnyis //
NK075(bu)003:8607: gdul bya'i dbang gi khyad par las //
NK075(bu)003:8608: sku dang gsung thugs gcig las med //
NK075(bu)003:8611: sangs rgyas rnams kyi dgongs rgyud ci lta bu //
NK075(bu)003:8612: rang gi mtshan nyid ma bcos de bzhin nyid //
NK075(bu)003:8614: gnyis pa man ngag tshad ma ni /
NK075(bu)003:8616: 'on te de ltar mi gcig na'ang //
NK075(bu)003:8617: rang rig rang byung mngon byas la //
NK075(bu)003:8618: snga phyi'i sangs rgyas bla dwags btags //
NK075(bu)003:8619: rang byung rang la shar bar zad //
NK075(bu)003:8620: rang byung rigs dang rgyud med par //
NK075(bu)003:8621: so so tha dad gang gi rung //
NK075(bu)003:8624: spyan drang byon dang mi byon 'byung //
NK075(bu)003:8625: sangs rgyas sangs rgyas zhes brjod pa //
NK075(bu)003:8626: dngos po rnams kyi de nyid ni //
NK075(bu)003:8627: de la gnyis pa yod par 'gyur //
NK075(bu)003:8628: de phyir gzhi yi don dang 'gal //
NK075(bu)003:8629: mi gcig gtan tshigs rgyas par 'gyur //
NK075(bu)003:8632: rgyal ba kun dang dus gsum chos //
NK075(bu)003:8633: bdag phyir kun gyi spyi gzugs can //
NK075(bu)003:8634: chos gnyis yod pa gang gi rung //
NK075(bu)003:8635: yod na bdag nyid chen po rdzun //
NK075(bu)003:8638: gcig shos bden par ma yin pas //
NK075(bu)003:8639: so sor tha dad cha rigs med //
NK075(bu)003:8641: ngo bo gcig la rgyud 'dres min //
NK075(bu)003:8642: shing gi me dpung ltar brjod pa //
NK075(bu)003:8643: drang pa tsam ste de nyid min //
NK075(bu)003:8645: gsum pa rig pa tshad ma la dgag pa la lnga ste /
NK075(bu)003:8646: gzhi la bzang ngan tha dad can du yod par thal ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:8647: 'bras bu rang byung ye shes su mi gcig par 'gyur ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:8648: don res mos su byed par 'gyur ba dang /
NK075(bu)003:8649: lha spyan drang ba la byon mi byon yod par 'gyur ro //
NK075(bu)003:8651: sangs rgyas zhes bya ba gzhi gnas lugs kyi don
NK075(bu)003:8652: mngon sum byas pa la dgongs pa gcig yin nam
NK075(bu)003:8653: ma yin / yin na dgongs rgyud tha dad du 'dod pa dang 'gal /
NK075(bu)003:8654: min na dgongs pa gang yin /
NK075(bu)003:8655: yin kyang dgongs rgyud tha dad na /
NK075(bu)003:8656: gzhi bzang ngan can du thal te /
NK075(bu)003:8657: gzhi mngon du byas pa'i sangs rgyas rnams dgongs rgyud tha dad pa'i phyir ro //
NK075(bu)003:8659: sangs rgyas sangs rgyas zhes brjod pa //
NK075(bu)003:8660: dngos po rnams kyi de kho na //
NK075(bu)003:8661: de la gnyis pa yod par 'gyur //
NK075(bu)003:8662: de phyir gzhi yi don dang 'gal //
NK075(bu)003:8665: 'bras bu sku ye shes kyi dus su rang byung
NK075(bu)003:8666: ngam ci lta ba mkhyen pa mi gcig par thal
NK075(bu)003:8669: rang byung ye shes nyag gcig la //
NK075(bu)003:8670: gdul bya'i mos dang bsam dbang gis //
NK075(bu)003:8671: khyad par bye brag lnga sogs snang //
NK075(bu)003:8672: rigs rgyud don la gcig tu gnas //
NK075(bu)003:8675: 'on te de ltar mi gcig na //
NK075(bu)003:8676: rang rig rang byung mngon byas la //
NK075(bu)003:8677: snga phyi'i sangs rgyas bla dwags tsam //
NK075(bu)003:8678: rang byung rang la shar bar zad //
NK075(bu)003:8679: rang byung rigs dang rgyud med par //
NK075(bu)003:8680: so sor ma 'dres gang gis rung //
NK075(bu)003:8683: shing gi me dpung ltar brjod pa //
NK075(bu)003:8684: drang ba tsam ste nyi de min //
NK075(bu)003:8687: dgongs pa tha dad na sprul pa yang tha dad pas /
NK075(bu)003:8688: sprul sku byang chub sems dpa' la snang ba de
NK075(bu)003:8689: gdul bya thams cad la mthun par snang bar thal
NK075(bu)003:8690: te / sprul pa gcig la du mar snang ba med de /
NK075(bu)003:8693: nyi zer nyi ma'am shing me bzhin //
NK075(bu)003:8694: ngo bo gcig la ye shes rgyud //
NK075(bu)003:8695: so so yin na sprul pa yang //
NK075(bu)003:8696: gdul bya gcig la mthun snang ba'ang //
NK075(bu)003:8697: sems dpa' che dang khyad med 'gyur //
NK075(bu)003:8700: rgyal bas sems can gyi don byed pa'i tshe /
NK075(bu)003:8701: bgo basha'i tshul gyi res mos su byed par thal te /
NK075(bu)003:8702: don byed mkhan tha dad pa'i phyir ro //
NK075(bu)003:8703: 'dod na phyogs med lhun grub tu bshad pa dang 'gal te /
NK075(bu)003:8705: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten rdul snyed du //
NK075(bu)003:8706: rgyal ba'i don rnams rdul phran snyed //
NK075(bu)003:8707: sprul pa rdul phran bsam yas kyis //
NK075(bu)003:8708: skad cig yud la lhun gyis grub ho //
NK075(bu)003:8711: rgyud tha dad na skal ldan rnams kyis zhi ba'i lha spyan drangs pa'i tshe /
NK075(bu)003:8713: khro bo'i lha mi byon par thal ba la sogs pa'i skyon du ma yod de /
NK075(bu)003:8714: dper na mgron po bos ma bos bzhin no //
NK075(bu)003:8716: spyan drangs byon dang mi byon 'byung //
NK075(bu)003:8717: gzhi don lung rigs kun dang 'gal //
NK075(bu)003:8718: thugs rje che ba'i rigs chad 'gyur //
NK075(bu)003:8721: shes bya'i gshis la don dam dang kun rdzob dbyer med pas /
NK075(bu)003:8722: de nyid mngon du byas pa mthar phyin pas sangs
NK075(bu)003:8723: rgyas kun gyi spyi'i gzugs can thob pa ni mthar
NK075(bu)003:8724: thug gi 'bras bu sangs rgyas zhes bya bar ming
NK075(bu)003:8725: 'dogs te / de yang dgongs pa gcig dang du mi'i mtha' las grol ba'i tshul du bzhugs te /
NK075(bu)003:8726: dper na rdul gcig gi steng na rdul snyed kyi
NK075(bu)003:8727: sangs rgyas ma 'dres pa'i ngos nas bzhugs pas gcig
NK075(bu)003:8729: sangs rgyas thams cad dgongs pa mnyam pa nyid gcig la bzhugs pas du ma'i mtha' las grol ba'o //
NK075(bu)003:8731: gcig dang du ma bral ba yi //
NK075(bu)003:8732: mtha' dang dbus med de bzhin nyid //
NK075(bu)003:8735: mnyam pa gsum pa yin pa'i phyir //
NK075(bu)003:8737: tha snyad bral ba'i tshul du gnas //
NK075(bu)003:8744: mtsho nyid rlabs ltar thams cad kun //
NK075(bu)003:8745: gdod nas rang byung ye shes gcig /
NK075(bu)003:8747: mtha' brjod ma lus der snang phyir //
NK075(bu)003:8748: du ma nyid du gcig pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:8749: du mar rgya chad yod gyur na //
NK075(bu)003:8750: rang byung rang snang bden mi 'gyur //
NK075(bu)003:8754: mi rtag par yang zungs shig /
NK075(bu)003:8757: tha dad par yang zungs shig /
NK075(bu)003:8758: tha dad kyi ngo bo las grol bar zungs shig /
NK075(bu)003:8760: spar khab kyi nang du 'bras bu'i skabs thams cad du'ang de ltar du gsungs so //
NK075(bu)003:8761: de ltar rgyud gcig 'dod pa ni rten med kyi don byed pa yin la /
NK075(bu)003:8762: ma 'dres par 'dod pa ni rten can gyis don byed par 'dod pa yin cing /
NK075(bu)003:8763: rang lugs ni dbyer med ngo bo nyid kyis don byed par 'dod pa'i lugs so //
NK075(bu)003:8766: thugs kyi thig pa lasa 'bru mthun zug rngu med
NK075(bu)003:8767: cing nar son pas bde bar gshegas pa rtogs pa'i
NK075(bu)003:8768: rig pa la sku dang ye shes su rang snang
NK075(bu)003:8769: ba'i gzhung gi tshig don gyi mtshams gcod cing 'dzin
NK075(bu)003:8770: pas na le'u zhes bya ste yas bgrang bzhi ba'i
NK075(bu)003:8772: spyi don gsum pa zhabs kyi don no //
NK075(bu)003:8774: dper na nam mkha' la 'aja'a tshon shar ba bzhin
NK075(bu)003:8775: du thugs sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i rgyud don rnams ma
NK075(bu)003:8776: 'dres par bkra zhing gsal bar byed pa'i man ngag
NK075(bu)003:8777: thugs thigs 'di brtsams pas rgyud kyi don bshad pa
NK075(bu)003:8778: la / gzhung 'di bzhin du chos spyi dang rang
NK075(bu)003:8779: gi mtshan nyid mi shes par mkhas par rlom pa'i
NK075(bu)003:8780: nga rgyal snyoms shing khams gsum gyi nyon mongs kyi
NK075(bu)003:8781: dgra kun las rgyal ba 'di ni /
NK075(bu)003:8782: dper na gshis nas dapa'a bo'i ru mtshon gnam lcags
NK075(bu)003:8783: shag+ti ste ral gri phyar ba dang 'dra ba'i thugs
NK075(bu)003:8784: thigs 'di / rtsom pa pos rang bzo ma yin te /
NK075(bu)003:8785: thugs sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i rgyud kyi don bcud snang
NK075(bu)003:8786: ba bzhi po gcig thog na gcig 'ong bas 'khor
NK075(bu)003:8788: dper na bya ngang pa'i rgyal po'i mchu la skyur
NK075(bu)003:8789: rtsi yod pa des rgya mtsho'i nang na 'o ma
NK075(bu)003:8790: thig gcig yod na sdud pa ltar /
NK075(bu)003:8791: thugs kyi rgyud sde rgya mtsho dang 'dra ba'i nang
NK075(bu)003:8792: nas slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba'i nyer len gyi
NK075(bu)003:8793: shes rab skyur rtsi dang 'dra ba des /
NK075(bu)003:8794: 'o ma dang 'dra ba'i snang ba bzhi'i man ngag 'di nyid blangs pa'i dge ba des /
NK075(bu)003:8795: gsang don mi shes shing nyon mongs pa'i dra bar
NK075(bu)003:8796: chud pa'i gang zag rnams kyis rang bzhin gsang ba'i
NK075(bu)003:8797: snying po'i / don rtogs nas sangs rgyas par shog cig ces smon lam rgya chen po btab pa'o //
NK075(bu)003:8798: thugs kyi thigs pa'i sgyu 'phrul ni 'bru mthun /
NK075(bu)003:8799: spyi don gyi khog dbub pa dang /
NK075(bu)003:8800: gzhung don gyi sa gcod pa'i don no //
NK075(bu)003:8801: rdzogs so ni tshig don ma lus pa'i tha tshig gam /
NK075(bu)003:8802: gnas skabs re zhig rdzogs nas bshad du ma mchis pas don du gada'o //
NK075(bu)003:8804: // rgyal ba'i bstan pa dam chos bdud rtsi'i bcud //
NK075(bu)003:8805: bka' brgyud dri med gzhung mang rgya che dang //
NK075(bu)003:8806: mkhas pa'i 'grel dang t+aika bstan chos dang //
NK075(bu)003:8807: zab mo'i gdams ngag dgongs pa'i gter mdzod las //
NK075(bu)003:8808: legs dpyad shes rab rnam grol lde mig gis //
NK075(bu)003:8809: don gyi gnad gdams dgongs pa'i bcud blangs 'di //
NK075(bu)003:8810: rje yi gsung dang rang gi nyams myong gis //
NK075(bu)003:8811: lung dang man ngag mi 'gal rig par sbyar //
NK075(bu)003:8812: 'on kyang 'grel rtsam tshad ldan nus med kyang //
NK075(bu)003:8813: don gnyer gzhan gyis bskul phyir 'di brtsam pa //
NK075(bu)003:8814: 'khrul na bzod gsol ma 'khrul dge ba des //
NK075(bu)003:8815: 'gro rnams thams cad mkhyen pa'i sa thob shog /
NK075(bu)003:8816: gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i rgyud mchog sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba stong phrag brgya ba'i bcud bsdus pa /
NK075(bu)003:8817: rgya gar gyi mkhas grub chen po sangs rgyas gsang
NK075(bu)003:8818: bas mdzad pa'i thugs thigs kyi 'grel bshad 'di nyid
NK075(bu)003:8819: / bla ma brgyud pa mkhas btsun gong ma rnams kyi 'grel bshad gsung sgros tshad ma rnams dang /
NK075(bu)003:8820: khyad par du bdag la drin che ba'i mkhas grub
NK075(bu)003:8821: yab sras kyi zhal shes ngo sprod kyi man ngag
NK075(bu)003:8822: la brten nas / mkhas btsun rnams kyis yang yang bskul ba'i ngor /
NK075(bu)003:8823: shak+y+aa'i dge slong nam mkha' dpal gyis sa pho sprel gyi lo zla ba dgu pa'i yar tshes la /
